#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:51
msgid ""
"Before an inventory adjustment can be performed with the **Barcode** app, "
"the app has to be installed and configured. Navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`, and scroll "
"to the :guilabel:`Barcode` section. Select the checkbox next "
"to :guilabel:`Barcode Scanner`, and click :guilabel:`Save` to save any "
"changes. If necessary, click :guilabel:`Confirm` on the pop-up."
msgstr ""
"Før en lagerjustering kan udføres med **Stregkode**-appen, skal appen "
"installeres og konfigureres. Naviger til :menuselection:`Lager-app --> "
"Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, og rul ned til "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Stregkode`. Marker afkrydsningsfeltet ved siden "
"af :guilabel:`Stregkodescanner`, og klik på :guilabel:`Gem` for at gemme "
"eventuelle ændringer. Klik om nødvendigt på :guilabel:`Bekræft` i pop-up-"
"vinduet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:58
msgid ""
"Enabling the **Barcode** feature requires installing the **Barcode** "
"application. Installing a new application on a One-App-Free database "
"triggers a fifteen-day trial. At the end of the trial, if a paid "
"subscription has not been added to the database, it will no longer be "
"accessible."
msgstr ""
"Aktivering af **Stregkode**-funktionen kræver installation af **Stregkode**-"
"applikationen. Installation af en ny applikation på en One-App-Free-database "
"udløser en femten-dages prøveperiode. Når prøveperioden slutter, vil "
"databasen ikke længere være tilgængelig, hvis der ikke er tilføjet et betalt "
"abonnement til databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:62
msgid ""
"After saving, a new drop-down menu appears under the :guilabel:`Barcode "
"Scanner` option, labeled :guilabel:`Barcode Nomenclature`, where "
"either :guilabel:`Default Nomenclature` or :guilabel:`Default GS1 "
"Nomenclature` can be selected. Each nomenclature option determines how "
"scanners interpret barcodes in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Efter lagring vises en ny rullemenu under "
"valgmuligheden :guilabel:`Stregkodescanner`, "
"mærket :guilabel:`Stregkodenomenklatur`, hvor "
"enten :guilabel:`Standardnomenklatur` eller :guilabel:`Standard GS1-"
"nomenklatur` kan vælges. Hver nomenklaturoption bestemmer, hvordan scannere "
"fortolker stregkoder i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:67
msgid ""
"To count products using barcodes, ensure that barcodes for products and "
"storage locations are set up within Odoo first. Refer to this section for "
"detailed instructions: :ref:`Set Product Barcodes <inventory/barcode/set-"
"barcodes>`."
msgstr ""
"For at tælle produkter ved hjælp af stregkoder skal du sikre, at stregkoder "
"for produkter og lagerplaceringer er sat op i Odoo først. Se dette afsnit "
"for detaljerede instruktioner: :ref:`Indstil produktstregkoder <inventory/"
"barcode/set-barcodes>`."

