msgstr ""
"Åbn :menuselection:`Lager app --> Konfiguration --> Lokationer`. Vælg den "
"ønskede lokation. På lokationsformularen under "
"overskriften :guilabel:`Logistik` skal du vælge :guilabel:`First In First "
"Out (FIFO)` fra listen over fjernelsesstrategier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fifo.rst:None
