#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fifo.rst:143
msgid ""
"To view the detailed pickings, click the :guilabel:`Details` link, located "
"on the far-right of the white shirt's product line in "
