#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:3
msgid "At confirmation reservation"
msgstr "Reservation ved bekræftelse"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:9
msgid ""
"The *at confirmation* reservation method reserves products **only** when a "
"sales order (SO) is confirmed, **and** enough product stock is available."
msgstr ""
"Reservationsmetoden *ved bekræftelse* reserverer produkter **kun**, når en "
"salgsordre er bekræftet, **og** der er tilstrækkelig lagerbeholdning."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:13
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:14
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:16
msgid ":doc:`About reservation methods <../reservation_methods>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Om reservationsmetoder <../reservation_methods>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:18
msgid ""
"To set the reservation method to *at confirmation*, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Operations Types`. "
"Then, select the desired :guilabel:`Operation Type` to configure, or create "
"a new one by clicking :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"For at indstille reservationsmetoden til *ved bekræftelse* skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Lager --> Konfiguration --> Operationstyper`. Vælg "
"derefter den ønskede :guilabel:`Operationstype`, der skal konfigureres, "
"eller opret en ny ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:22
msgid ""
"In the *General* tab on the operation type form, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Reservation Method` field and select :guilabel:`At "
"Confirmation`."
msgstr ""
"I fanen *Generelt* på operationstypeformularen skal du finde "
"feltet :guilabel:`Reservationsmetode` og vælge :guilabel:`Ved bekræftelse`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:31
msgid ""
"To see the *at confirmation* reservation method in action, create a new |SO| "
"by navigating to the :menuselection:`Sales app`. On the *Quotations* page, "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"For at se reservationsmetoden *ved bekræftelse* i aktion skal du oprette en "
"ny |SO| ved at gå til :menuselection:`Salg`. På siden *Tilbud* skal du "
"klikke på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:34
msgid ""
"On the quotation, add a customer in the :guilabel:`Customer` field. Then, in "
"the *Order Lines* tab, click :guilabel:`Add a product` and select a product "
"to add to the quotation from the drop-down menu. Finally, in "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` column, adjust the desired quantity of the product "
"to sell."
msgstr ""
"På tilbuddet skal du tilføje en kunde i feltet :guilabel:`Kunde`. Klik "
"derefter i fanen *Ordrelinjer* på :guilabel:`Tilføj et produkt`, og vælg et "
"produkt, der skal tilføjes til tilbuddet, fra rullemenuen. Juster til sidst "
"i kolonnen :guilabel:`Antal` den ønskede mængde af produktet, der skal "
"sælges."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:39
msgid "Once ready, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to create the sales order."
msgstr ""
"Når du er klar, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Bekræft` for at oprette "
"salgsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:41
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`(area chart)` icon on the product "
"line to reveal the product's :guilabel:`Availability` tooltip, which shows "
"the :guilabel:`Reserved` quantity for this order."
msgstr ""
"Klik på ikonet :icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`(områdediagram)` på "
"produktlinjen for at vise produktets :guilabel:`Tilgængelighed`-værktøjstip, "
"som viser det :guilabel:`Reserverede` antal for denne ordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:None
msgid "Confirmed sales order with product availability tooltip selected."
msgstr "Bekræftet salgsordre med værktøjstip for produkttilgængelighed valgt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:49
msgid ""
"If there is **not** sufficient quantity of stock for the product included in "
"the |SO|, the :icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`(area chart)` icon is red "
"instead of green."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der **ikke** er tilstrækkelig lagerbeholdning af produktet inkluderet i "
"|SO|, er ikonet :icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`(områdediagram)` rødt i "
"stedet for grønt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:52
msgid ""
"Instead of showing the reserved number of units for the order, "
"the :guilabel:`Availability` tooltip reads :guilabel:`Reserved` and shows "
"the reserved number of units (e.g., `0 Units`)."
msgstr ""
"I stedet for at vise det reserverede antal enheder for ordren viser "
"værktøjstippet :guilabel:`Tilgængelighed` :guilabel:`Reserveret` og viser "
"det reserverede antal enheder (f.eks. `0 Enheder`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:55
msgid "Forecasted Report"
msgstr "Prognoseret Rapport"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:57
msgid ""
"To see all the factors that affect product reservation, click the :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`View Forecast` internal link arrow to view "
"the :guilabel:`Forecasted Report` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"For at se alle faktorer, der påvirker produktreservation, skal du klikke på "
"den interne linkpil :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Vis prognose` for at "
"se dashboardet :guilabel:`Prognoserapport`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:61
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Forecasted Report` displays forecast information for the "
"products included in the sales order, namely any live receipts of the "
"product and any active sales orders, which are listed in the :guilabel:`Used "
"By` column. See how each order is fulfilled in the :guilabel:`Replenishment` "
"column."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prognoserapport` viser prognoseoplysninger for produkterne "
"inkluderet i salgsordren, nemlig eventuelle aktive modtagelser af produktet "
"og eventuelle aktive salgsordrer, som er anført i kolonnen :guilabel:`Brugt "
"af`. Se, hvordan hver ordre opfyldes i kolonnen :guilabel:`Genopfyldning`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:66
msgid ""
"Additionally, the :guilabel:`Forecasted` quantity is calculated at the top "
"of the page by adding the :guilabel:`On Hand` and :guilabel:`Incoming` "
"quantity and subtracting the :guilabel:`Outgoing` quantity, as shown below:"
msgstr ""
"Desuden beregnes det :guilabel:`Prognosticerede` antal øverst på siden ved "
"at lægge :guilabel:`På lager` og :guilabel:`Indgående` antal sammen og "
"trække det :guilabel:`Udgående` antal fra, som vist nedenfor:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:None
msgid "Forecasted quantity equation from the Forecasted Report page."
msgstr "Forventet antal-ligning fra siden Forventet rapport."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:73
msgid ""
"If one order should be prioritized over another order, click "
"the :guilabel:`Unreserve` button on the corresponding order line in "
"the :guilabel:`Replenishment` column."
msgstr ""
"Hvis én ordre skal prioriteres over en anden ordre, skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Frigør reservation` på den tilsvarende ordrelinje i "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Genopfyldning`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:76
msgid ""
"To deliver the products, click the :icon:`fa-truck` :guilabel:`Delivery` "
"smart button at the top of the sales order form. To confirm that the "
"reservation worked properly, ensure that the :guilabel:`Product "
"Availability` field reads `Available` (in green text), and that the numbers "
"in the :guilabel:`Demand` and :guilabel:`Quantity` columns match (in this "
"case, both should read `10.00`)."
msgstr ""
"For at levere produkterne skal du klikke på den smarte knap :icon:`fa-"
"truck` :guilabel:`Levering` øverst på salgsordreformularen. For at bekræfte, "
"at reservationen fungerede korrekt, skal du sikre dig, at "
"feltet :guilabel:`Produkttilgængelighed` viser `Tilgængelig` (i grøn tekst), "
"og at tallene i kolonnerne :guilabel:`Efterspørgsel` og :guilabel:`Antal` "
"matcher (i dette tilfælde skal begge vise `10,00`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:None
msgid ""
"Delivery order for product included in sales order with at confirmation "
"reservation."
msgstr ""
"Leveringsordre for produkt inkluderet i salgsordre med reservation ved "
"bekræftelse."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:85
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:149
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:108
msgid "Once ready, click :guilabel:`Validate`."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Valider`, når du er klar."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:88
msgid ""
"Delivery orders can be starred, or favorited. Unlike :guilabel:`Before "
"scheduled date` reservations, adding a delivery order to favorites via "
"the :guilabel:`At Confirmation` reservation does not prioritize it. The "
"delivery order is only prioritized in the **Inventory** app's display of "
"delivery orders."
msgstr ""
"Leveringsordrer kan sternes eller markeres som favoritter. I modsætning til "
"reservationer :guilabel:`Før planlagt dato` prioriterer tilføjelse af en "
"leveringsordre til favoritter via reservationen :guilabel:`Ved bekræftelse` "
"den ikke. Leveringsordren prioriteres kun i **Lager**-appens visning af "
"leveringsordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:94
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:152
msgid ":doc:`Manual reservation <manually>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Manuel reservation <manually>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/at_confirmation.rst:95
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:139
msgid ":doc:`Before scheduled date reservation <before_scheduled_date>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Reservation før planlagt dato <before_scheduled_date>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:3
msgid "Before scheduled date reservation"
msgstr "Reservation før planlagt dato"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:9
msgid ""
"The *Before scheduled date* reservation method allows users to select a "
"specific number of days that act as the maximum number of days **before** a "
"scheduled delivery date, when products included in a sales order (SO) should "
"be reserved."
msgstr ""
"Reservationsmetoden *Før planlagt dato* giver brugerne mulighed for at vælge "
"et bestemt antal dage, der fungerer som det maksimale antal dage **før** en "
"planlagt leveringsdato, hvor produkter inkluderet i en salgsordre (SO) skal "
"reserveres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:19
msgid ""
"To set the reservation method to *Before scheduled date*, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Operations Types`. "
"Then, select the desired :guilabel:`Operation Type` to configure, or create "
"a new one by clicking :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"For at indstille reservationsmetoden til *Før planlagt dato* skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Konfiguration --> Operationstyper`. Vælg "
"derefter den ønskede :guilabel:`Operationstype`, der skal konfigureres, "
"eller opret en ny ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:23
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`General` tab, locate the :guilabel:`Reservation Method` "
"field, and select :guilabel:`Before scheduled date`."
msgstr ""
"Find feltet :guilabel:`Reservationsmetode` på fanen :guilabel:`Generelt`, og "
"vælg :guilabel:`Før planlagt dato`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:34
msgid ""
"Once selected, a new :guilabel:`Reserve before scheduled date` field appears "
"below. From this field, the number of :guilabel:`days before` "
"and :guilabel:`days before when starred` can be changed from the default `0`."
msgstr ""
"Når den er valgt, vises et nyt felt :guilabel:`Reserver før planlagt dato` "
"nedenfor. Fra dette felt kan antallet af :guilabel:`dage før` "
"og :guilabel:`dage før når markeret med stjerne` ændres fra standardværdien "
"`0`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:41
msgid ""
"Changing the :guilabel:`days before when starred` value changes the maximum "
"number of days before a scheduled date that products should be reserved if "
"the transfers are starred (favorited)."
msgstr ""
"Ændring af værdien :guilabel:`dage før når markeret med stjerne` ændrer det "
"maksimale antal dage før en planlagt dato, hvor produkter skal reserveres, "
"hvis overførslerne er markeret med stjerne (favoritter)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:45
msgid ""
"Here, the :guilabel:`days before` value is set to `2` days before, and "
"the :guilabel:`days before when starred` value is set to `3`."
msgstr ""
"Her er værdien :guilabel:`dage før` sat til `2` dage før, og "
"værdien :guilabel:`dage før når markeret med stjerne` er sat til `3`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:48
msgid ""
"This means products are reserved two days before the scheduled delivery date "
"for normal orders, and three days before the scheduled delivery date for "
"starred (favorited) transfers."
msgstr ""
"To znamená, že produkty jsou rezervovány dva dny před plánovaným datem "
"dodání u běžných objednávek a tři dny před plánovaným datem dodání u "
"objednávek označených hvězdičkou (oblíbených)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:None
msgid "Reserve before scheduled date field with set numerical values."
msgstr ""
"Pole Rezervovat před plánovaným datem s nastavenými číselnými hodnotami."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:55
msgid ""
"This is the configuration applied for the following workflow found below."
msgstr ""
"Toto je konfigurace použitá pro následující pracovní postup uvedený níže."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:58
msgid "Edit product form"
msgstr "Upravit formulář produktu"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:60
msgid ""
"Before the *Before scheduled date* reservation method can be used, ensure "
"that a *customer lead time* is added to products that plan to be sold with "
"this method."
msgstr ""
"Než lze použít rezervační metodu *Před plánovaným datem*, ujistěte se, že je "
"k produktům, které se plánují prodávat s touto metodou, přidána *dodací "
"lhůta pro zákazníka*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:63
msgid ""
"To do that, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Products --> "
"Products`, and select the desired product to configure."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li to provést, přejděte na :menuselection:`aplikace Lager --> "
"Produkty --> Produkty` a vyberte požadovaný produkt ke konfiguraci."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:66
msgid ""
"On the product form, click the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab, and under "
"the :guilabel:`Logistics` section, change the value in "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Lead Time` field."
msgstr ""
"Ve formuláři produktu klikněte na kartu :guilabel:`Lager` a v "
"sekci :guilabel:`Logistika` změňte hodnotu v poli :guilabel:`Dodací lhůta "
"pro zákazníka`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:69
msgid "For this example workflow, change it to `5` days."
msgstr "V tomto příkladu pracovního postupu ji změňte na `5` dní."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:71
msgid ""
"This sets the scheduled delivery date for this specific product to five days "
"after the creation date of the sales order."
msgstr ""
"Tím se nastaví plánované datum dodání pro tento konkrétní produkt na pět dní "
"po datu vytvoření salgsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:None
msgid "Product form with customer lead time set in Inventory tab."
msgstr ""
"Formulář produktu s dodací lhůtou pro zákazníka nastavenou na kartě Lager."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:81
msgid ""
"To see the *Before scheduled date* reservation method in action, create a "
"new |SO| by navigating to :menuselection:`Sales app --> New`."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li vidět rezervační metodu *Před plánovaným datem* v akci, vytvořte "
"novou |SO| přechodem na :menuselection:`aplikace Salg --> Nový`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:84
msgid ""
"Add a customer in the :guilabel:`Customer` field, then, in "
"the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a product`, and select "
"a product from the drop-down menu that has a configured *customer lead "
"time*, to add to the quotation form."
msgstr ""
"Přidejte zákazníka do pole :guilabel:`Zákazník`, poté na "
"kartě :guilabel:`Řádky objednávky` klikněte na :guilabel:`Přidat produkt` a "
"vyberte z rozbalovací nabídky produkt, který má nakonfigurovanou *dodací "
"lhůtu pro zákazníka*, a přidejte jej do formuláře nabídky."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:88
msgid ""
"Finally, in the :guilabel:`Quantity` column, adjust the desired quantity of "
"the product to sell."
msgstr ""
"Nakonec ve sloupci :guilabel:`Množství` upravte požadované množství produktu "
"k prodeji."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:90
msgid "For this sample workflow, set the :guilabel:`Quantity` to `10`."
msgstr ""
"V tomto ukázkovém pracovním postupu nastavte :guilabel:`Množství` na `10`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:92
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:46
msgid "Once ready, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the sales order."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Bekræft`, når du er klar til at bekræfte salgsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:94
msgid ""
"Click the green :guilabel:`📈 (area graph)` icon on the product line to "
"reveal the product's :guilabel:`Availability` tooltip. This tooltip reveals "
"the reserved number of units for this order. Because the reservation method "
"is set to *Before scheduled date*, the :guilabel:`Reserved` quantity reads "
"`0 Units`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknutím na zelenou ikonu :guilabel:`📈 (plošný graf)` na řádku produktu "
"zobrazíte tooltip produktu :guilabel:`Dostupnost`. Tento tooltip odhalí "
"rezervované množství jednotek pro tuto objednávku. Protože je rezervační "
"metoda nastavena na *Před plánovaným datem*, :guilabel:`Rezervované` "
"množství ukazuje `0 jednotek`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:99
msgid ""
"However, below that quantity reads `Available in stock`. This is because the "
"quantity is available, but the scheduled date, for this example workflow, is "
"five days from the order date."
msgstr ""
"Pod tímto množstvím je však uvedeno `Dostupné na skladě`. Je to proto, že "
"množství je dostupné, ale plánované datum je v tomto příkladu pět dní od "
"data objednávky."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:102
msgid ""
"Since reservation is not until two days before the scheduled delivery, it "
"will not reserve the products until then."
msgstr ""
"Protože rezervace proběhne až dva dny před plánovaným dodáním, produkty "
"nebudou rezervovány dříve."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:106
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:57
msgid ""
"If there is **not** sufficient quantity of stock for the product included in "
"the |SO|, the :guilabel:`📈 (area graph)` icon is red, instead of green."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der **ikke** er tilstrækkelig lagerbeholdning af det produkt, der er "
"inkluderet i |SO|, er ikonet :guilabel:`📈 (områdediagram)` rødt i stedet "
"for grønt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:109
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:60
msgid ""
"Instead of revealing the reserved number of units for the order, "
"the :guilabel:`Availability` tooltip reads :guilabel:`Reserved`, and reveals "
"the available number of units (e.g., `0 Units`)."
msgstr ""
"Místo odhalení rezervovaného množství jednotek pro objednávku "
"tooltip :guilabel:`Dostupnost` ukazuje :guilabel:`Rezervováno` a odhaluje "
"dostupné množství jednotek (např. `0 jednotek`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:112
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:63
msgid ""
"Additionally, unless there is a set replenishment or a live receipt, it also "
"reads :guilabel:`No future availability`, in red text."
msgstr ""
"Navíc, pokud není nastaveno doplnění nebo živý příjem, zobrazí se "
"také :guilabel:`Žádná budoucí dostupnost` červeným textem."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:119
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button to see the delivery order form."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na chytré tlačítko :guilabel:`Dodání` a zobrazí se formulář "
"leveringsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:121
msgid ""
"On the delivery order form, the status in the :guilabel:`Product "
"Availability` field is listed as `Available`, in yellow text, instead of "
"green. This is because there is sufficient stock on-hand for this order, but "
"no quantity has been reserved yet."
msgstr ""
"På leveringsordreformularen vises status i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Produkttilgængelighed` som `Available` i gul tekst i "
"stedet for grøn. Det skyldes, at der er tilstrækkelig lagerbeholdning til "
"denne ordre, men der er endnu ikke reserveret noget antal."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:125
msgid ""
"Note the :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` field, above the :guilabel:`Product "
"Availability` field, displays the date five days from the order creation "
"date. This indicates that the products are not reserved until three days "
"from today's date (two days before the scheduled delivery date)."
msgstr ""
"Bemærk, at feltet :guilabel:`Planlagt dato` over "
"feltet :guilabel:`Produkttilgængelighed` viser datoen fem dage fra "
"ordreoprettelsesdatoen. Dette indikerer, at produkterne ikke reserveres før "
"tre dage fra i dag (to dage før den planlagte leveringsdato)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:None
msgid "Delivery order form with product availability and reserved quantity."
msgstr "Leveringsordreformular med produkttilgængelighed og reserveret antal."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:133
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Operations` tab on the :guilabel:`Product` line, the "
"numbers in the :guilabel:`Demand` column and the :guilabel:`Quantity` column "
"do not match (in this case, the :guilabel:`Demand` column lists `10.00`, "
"while the :guilabel:`Quantity` column lists `0`)."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Operationer` på linjen :guilabel:`Produkt` matcher "
"tallene i kolonnen :guilabel:`Behov` og kolonnen :guilabel:`Antal` ikke (i "
"dette tilfælde viser kolonnen :guilabel:`Behov` `10.00`, mens "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Antal` viser `0`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:137
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Quantity` column lists `0` because the products aren't "
"reserved until two days *before* their delivery date. Odoo automatically "
"reserves the products once the scheduled date arrives, at which point "
"the :guilabel:`Demand` and :guilabel:`Quantity` columns will match."
msgstr ""
"Kolonnen :guilabel:`Antal` viser `0`, fordi produkterne ikke reserveres før "
"to dage *før* deres leveringsdato. Odoo reserverer automatisk produkterne, "
"når den planlagte dato indtræffer, hvorefter kolonnerne :guilabel:`Behov` "
"og :guilabel:`Antal` vil matche."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:142
msgid ""
"If the products in the |SO| should be reserved *sooner* than the scheduled "
"reservation date, the reservation can be manually overridden. To manually "
"reserve the products sooner than scheduled, click :guilabel:`Check "
"Availability` at the top of the form."
msgstr ""
"Hvis produkterne i |SO| skal reserveres *tidligere* end den planlagte "
"reservationsdato, kan reservationen manuelt tilsidesættes. For at reservere "
"produkterne manuelt tidligere end planlagt skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Tjek "
"tilgængelighed` øverst på formularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:146
msgid ""
"This turns the `Available` status in the :guilabel:`Product Availability` "
"field green, and changes the number in the :guilabel:`Quantity` column to "
"match the :guilabel:`Demand` column."
msgstr ""
"Dette ændrer statusen `Available` i feltet :guilabel:`Produkttilgængelighed` "
"til grøn og ændrer tallet i kolonnen :guilabel:`Antal`, så det matcher "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Behov`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/before_scheduled_date.rst:153
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:138
msgid ":doc:`At confirmation reservation <at_confirmation>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Reservation ved bekræftelse <at_confirmation>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:3
msgid "Manual reservation"
msgstr "Manuel reservation"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:9
msgid ""
"Unlike the *At Confirmation* reservation method, the *Manually* reservation "
"method does **not** reserve products automatically."
msgstr ""
"I modsætning til reservationsmetoden *Ved bekræftelse* reserverer "
"reservationsmetoden *Manuelt* **ikke** produkter automatisk."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:12
msgid ""
"Instead, once a sales order (SO) is confirmed, product availability **must** "
"be checked manually, and the required quantity **must** be reserved manually."
msgstr ""
"I stedet skal produkttilgængeligheden kontrolleres manuelt, når en "
"salgsordre (SO) er bekræftet, og det nødvendige antal **skal** reserveres "
"manuelt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:21
msgid ""
"To set the reservation method to *Manually*, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Operations Types`. "
"Then, select the desired :guilabel:`Operation Type` to be configured, or "
"create a new one by clicking :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"For at indstille reservationsmetoden til *Manuelt* skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Lager app --> Konfiguration --> Operationstyper`. Vælg "
"derefter den ønskede :guilabel:`Operationstype`, der skal konfigureres, "
"eller opret en ny ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:25
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`General` tab, locate the :guilabel:`Reservation Method` "
"field, and select :guilabel:`Manually`."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Generelt` skal du finde "
"feltet :guilabel:`Reservationsmetode` og vælge :guilabel:`Manuelt`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:39
msgid ""
"To see the *Manually* reservation method in action, create a new |SO| by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Sales app --> New`."
msgstr ""
"For at se reservationsmetoden *Manuelt* i aktion skal du oprette en ny |SO| "
"ved at navigere til :menuselection:`Salg app --> Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:42
msgid ""
"Add a customer in the :guilabel:`Customer` field. Then, in "
"the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a product`, and select "
"a product to add to the quotation from the drop-down menu. Finally, in "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` column, adjust the desired quantity of the product "
"to sell."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj en kunde i feltet :guilabel:`Kunde`. Klik derefter på "
"fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer` på :guilabel:`Tilføj et produkt`, og vælg et "
"produkt, der skal tilføjes til tilbuddet, fra rullemenuen. Juster til sidst "
"i kolonnen :guilabel:`Antal` den ønskede mængde af produktet, der skal "
"sælges."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:48
msgid ""
"Click the green :guilabel:`📈 (area graph)` icon on the product line to "
"reveal the product's :guilabel:`Availability` tooltip. This tooltip reveals "
"the reserved number of units for this order. Because the reservation method "
"is set to *Manually*, the :guilabel:`Reserved` quantity reads `0 Units`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på det grønne :guilabel:`📈 (områdegraf)`-ikon på produktlinjen for at "
"åbne produktets :guilabel:`Tilgængelighed`-værktøjstip. Dette værktøjstip "
"viser det reserverede antal enheder for denne ordre. Fordi "
"reservationsmetoden er indstillet til *Manuelt*, viser "
"det :guilabel:`Reserverede` antal `0 enheder`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:53
msgid ""
"However, below that quantity reads `Available in stock`. This is because the "
"quantity is available, but must be manually reserved."
msgstr ""
"Dog står der nedenfor dette antal `Tilgængeligt på lager`. Det skyldes, at "
"antallet er tilgængeligt, men skal reserveres manuelt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:70
msgid ""
"Once the |SO| is confirmed, navigate to the :menuselection:`Inventory app`, "
"and locate the :guilabel:`Delivery Orders` card on the :guilabel:`Inventory "
"Overview` page."
msgstr ""
"Når |SO| er bekræftet, skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Lager app` og "
"finde kortet :guilabel:`Leveringsordrer` på siden :guilabel:`Lageroversigt`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:73
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Delivery Orders` card displays the current status of live "
"orders, including those with a :guilabel:`Waiting` status. Orders with this "
"status indicate that the products in those orders have either not been "
"reserved yet, or are not in stock at all."
msgstr ""
"Kortet :guilabel:`Leveringsordrer` viser den aktuelle status for aktive "
"ordrer, herunder dem med statussen :guilabel:`Venter`. Ordrer med denne "
"status indikerer, at produkterne i disse ordrer enten ikke er reserveret "
"endnu eller slet ikke er på lager."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:None
msgid "Delivery orders task card with waiting status orders."
msgstr "Leveringsordre-opgavekort med ordrer med status venter."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:81
msgid ""
"To see the |SO| created previously, click the :guilabel:`(#) Waiting` button "
"on the card (in this case, `8 Waiting`)."
msgstr ""
"For at se den |SO|, der blev oprettet tidligere, skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`(#) Venter` på kortet (i dette tilfælde `8 venter`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:84
msgid ""
"Locate the delivery order (DO) tied to the |SO| that was previously created, "
"and click the line to view it."
msgstr ""
"Find leveringsordren (LO) knyttet til |SO|, der tidligere blev oprettet, og "
"klik på linjen for at se den."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:87
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Delivery Order` form, the status in the :guilabel:`Product "
"Availability` field is listed as `Available`, in yellow text, instead of "
"green. This is because there is sufficient stock on hand for this order, but "
"no quantity has been reserved yet."
msgstr ""
"På :guilabel:`Leveringsordre`-formularen er status i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Produkttilgængelighed` angivet som `Available` i gul tekst "
"i stedet for grøn. Dette skyldes, at der er tilstrækkelig lagerbeholdning "
"til denne ordre, men der er endnu ikke reserveret nogen mængde."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:91
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Operations` tab, on the :guilabel:`Product` line, the "
"numbers in the :guilabel:`Demand` column and the :guilabel:`Quantity` column "
"do *not* match."
msgstr ""
"Under fanen :guilabel:`Operationer` matcher tallene i "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Behov` og kolonnen :guilabel:`Mængde` på "
"linjen :guilabel:`Produkt` *ikke* hinanden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:94
msgid ""
"In this case, the :guilabel:`Demand` column lists `10.00`, while "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` column lists `0`."
msgstr ""
"I dette tilfælde viser kolonnen :guilabel:`Behov` `10.00`, mens "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Mængde` viser `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:101
msgid ""
"To manually reserve the specified quantity of the product for this order, "
"click the :guilabel:`Check Availability` button at the top of the form. "
"Doing so turns the `Available` status in the :guilabel:`Product "
"Availability` field green, and changes the number in "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` column to match the :guilabel:`Demand` column."
msgstr ""
"For manuelt at reservere den angivne mængde af produktet til denne ordre "
"skal du klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Tjek tilgængelighed` øverst i "
"formularen. Dette ændrer `Available`-status i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Produkttilgængelighed` til grøn og ændrer tallet i "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Mængde`, så det matcher kolonnen :guilabel:`Behov`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:106
msgid ""
"This is because there is sufficient quantity in stock to reserve for the "
"order."
msgstr ""
"Dette skyldes, at der er tilstrækkelig mængde på lager til at reservere til "
"ordren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:111
msgid ""
"Multiple orders with a *Waiting* status can be manually reserved at the same "
"time, and set to *Ready* status."
msgstr ""
"Flere ordrer med status *Venter* kan reserveres manuelt på samme tid og "
"sættes til status *Klar*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:114
msgid ""
"To do that, open the :menuselection:`Inventory` app, which reveals "
"the :guilabel:`Inventory Overview` page. The :guilabel:`Inventory Overview` "
"page is also accessible by navigating to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Overview`."
msgstr ""
"For at gøre det skal du åbne appen :menuselection:`Lager`, hvilket viser "
"siden :guilabel:`Lageroversigt`. Siden :guilabel:`Lageroversigt` er også "
"tilgængelig ved at navigere til :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Oversigt`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:118
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Inventory Overview` page, click the :guilabel:`(#) "
"Waiting` button on the :guilabel:`Delivery Orders` card."
msgstr ""
"Fra siden :guilabel:`Lageroversigt` skal du klikke på knappen :guilabel:`(#) "
"Venter` på kortet :guilabel:`Leveringsordrer`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:121
msgid ""
"Then, tick the checkboxes to the left of each desired order, or tick the "
"checkbox in the header row, to the far-left, to select all orders on the "
"page at once."
msgstr ""
"Sæt derefter flueben i afkrydsningsfelterne til venstre for hver ønsket "
"ordre, eller sæt flueben i afkrydsningsfeltet i headerrækken yderst til "
"venstre for at vælge alle ordrer på siden på én gang."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:124
msgid ""
"Then, click the :guilabel:`Check Availability` button at the top of the page."
msgstr ""
"Klik derefter på knappen :guilabel:`Tjek tilgængelighed` øverst på siden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:126
msgid ""
"If the products included in every selected order have enough stock on-hand, "
"this reserves the products, and moves the order into :guilabel:`Ready` "
"status. Upon receiving a :guilabel:`Ready` status, the order disappears from "
"the :guilabel:`Waiting` list."
msgstr ""
"Hvis produkterne inkluderet i hver valgt ordre har nok lagerbeholdning, "
"reserverer dette produkterne og flytter ordren til status :guilabel:`Klar`. "
"Ved modtagelse af status :guilabel:`Klar` forsvinder ordren fra "
"listen :guilabel:`Venter`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:130
msgid ""
"If there is *not* enough stock on-hand, the order retains its current "
"status, and remains on the list."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der *ikke* er nok lagerbeholdning, beholder ordren sin nuværende status "
"og forbliver på listen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods/manually.rst:0
msgid "List of orders in waiting status and check availability button."
msgstr "Liste over ordrer med status venter og knappen tjek tilgængelighed."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:5
msgid "Delivery methods"
msgstr "Leveringsmetoder"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:7
msgid ""
"In Odoo, *delivery methods* make it possible to calculate shipping costs "
"directly on sales orders and :doc:`e-commerce </applications/websites/"
"ecommerce/shipping>` carts, providing customers and sales teams with "
"accurate shipping fee information. This transparency helps close sales by "
"showing customers the exact cost for each shipping carrier or delivery "
"timeframe."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo gør *leveringsmetoder* det muligt at beregne forsendelsesomkostninger "
"direkte på salgsordrer og :doc:`webshop </applications/websites/ecommerce/"
"shipping>`-kurve, hvilket giver kunder og salgsteams nøjagtige oplysninger "
"om forsendelsesgebyrer. Denne gennemsigtighed hjælper med at lukke salg ved "
"at vise kunderne de præcise omkostninger for hver fragtoperatør eller "
"leveringstidsramme."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:12
msgid ""
"When activated in Odoo, the *Delivery Methods* setting adds the option of "
"calculating the cost of shipping on sales orders and e-commerce shopping "
"carts."
msgstr ""
"Når den aktiveres i Odoo, tilføjer indstillingen *Leveringsmetoder* "
"muligheden for at beregne forsendelsesomkostninger på salgsordrer og e-"
"handelsindkøbskurve."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:15
msgid ""
"When integrated with a :ref:`third-party carrier <inventory/shipping/"
"third_party>`, shipping prices are calculated based on the carrier's pricing "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Når den er integreret med en :ref:`tredjeparts fragtmand <inventory/shipping/"
"third_party>`, beregnes forsendelsespriserne baseret på fragtmandens "
"prisinformation."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:19
msgid ""
":ref:`Third-party shipping carrier setup <inventory/shipping/third_party>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Opsætning af tredjeparts fragtmand <inventory/shipping/third_party>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:20
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Delivery Prices <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/delivery-"
"prices-613?fullscreen=1>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo-vejledninger: Leveringspriser <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"delivery-prices-613?fullscreen=1>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:26
msgid ""
"To calculate shipping on sales orders and e-commerce, the **Delivery Costs** "
"module must be installed. To do so, navigate to the :menuselection:`Apps` "
"application from the main Odoo dashboard."
msgstr ""
"For at beregne forsendelsesomkostninger på salgsordrer og e-handel skal "
"modulet **Leveringsomkostninger** installeres. For at gøre det navigeres til "
"applikationen :menuselection:`Apps` fra Odoos hoveddashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:29
msgid ""
"Then, remove the :guilabel:`Apps` filter, and type in `Delivery Costs` in "
"the search bar. After finding the :guilabel:`Delivery Costs` module, "
"click :guilabel:`Install` to install it."
msgstr ""
"Fjern derefter filteret :guilabel:`Apps`, og indtast `Delivery Costs` i "
"søgefeltet. Når modulet :guilabel:`Delivery Costs` er fundet, skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Installer` for at installere det."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:None
msgid "Install the Delivery Costs module."
msgstr "Installer modulet Leveringsomkostninger."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:38
msgid "Add shipping"
msgstr "Tilføj levering"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:40
msgid ""
"Shipping methods are added to sales orders in the form of delivery products, "
"which appear as individual line items. First, navigate to the desired sales "
"order by going to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> Orders`."
msgstr ""
"Forsendelsesmetoder tilføjes til salgsordrer i form af leveringsprodukter, "
"som vises som individuelle linjeemner. Naviger først til den ønskede "
"salgsordre ved at gå til :menuselection:`Salg-app --> Ordrer --> Ordrer`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:44
msgid ""
"Open the desired sales order, then click the :guilabel:`Add shipping` "
"button. The :guilabel:`Add a shipping method` pop-up window opens. Then, "
"using the drop-down menu, select an available shipping method."
msgstr ""
"Åbn den ønskede salgsordre, og klik derefter på knappen :guilabel:`Tilføj "
"forsendelse`. Pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Tilføj en forsendelsesmetode` åbnes. "
"Vælg derefter en tilgængelig forsendelsesmetode ved hjælp af rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:48
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Total Order Weight` is pre-filled based on product weights "
"(that are defined in the :ref:`Inventory <inventory/product_management/"
"manufacture>` tab for each product form). Edit the field to specify the "
"exact weight, and then click :guilabel:`Add` to add the shipping method."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Samlet ordrevægt` er udfyldt på forhånd baseret på produktvægte "
"(som er defineret under fanen :ref:`Lager <inventory/product_management/"
"manufacture>` for hver produktformular). Rediger feltet for at angive den "
"nøjagtige vægt, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Tilføj` for at tilføje "
"forsendelsesmetoden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:53
msgid ""
"The amount defined in :guilabel:`Total Order Weight` overwrites the total "
"product weights defined on the product form."
msgstr ""
"Værdien defineret i :guilabel:`Samlet ordrevægt` overskriver de samlede "
"produktvægte defineret på produktformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:57
msgid ""
"Some connected shipping methods require obtaining rates from the carrier. In "
"this situation, click the :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Get rate` "
"button, and the shipping costs are automatically updated from the carrier. "
"These rates cannot be modified."
msgstr ""
"Nogle tilknyttede forsendelsesmetoder kræver, at der indhentes takster fra "
"fragtmanden. I denne situation skal du klikke på knappen :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Hent takst`, og forsendelsesomkostningerne opdateres "
"automatisk fra fragtmanden. Disse takster kan ikke ændres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:61
msgid ""
"The shipping cost is added as a line item in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab "
"as the :guilabel:`Delivery Product` detailed on the shipping method form."
msgstr ""
"Forsendelsesomkostningerne tilføjes som et linjeelement under "
"fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer` som det :guilabel:`Leveringsprodukt`, der er "
"angivet på forsendelsesmetodeformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:65
msgid ""
"A customer purchased a left-sided desk with storage and requested the item "
"be delivered by hand. This delivery method is defined as `Furniture Delivery "
"(Manual)` and has a cost of `$200`. The sales order contains two line items: "
"one for the desk, and another for the delivery method."
msgstr ""
"En kunde købte et venstresidigt skrivebord med opbevaring og bad om, at "
"varen blev leveret manuelt. Denne leveringsmetode er defineret som "
"`Furniture Delivery (Manual)` og har en pris på `$200`. Salgsordren "
"indeholder to linjeelementer: et for skrivebordet og et andet for "
"leveringsmetoden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:0
msgid "Show delivery order on the sales order line."
msgstr "Vis leveringsordre på salgsordrelinjen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:73
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:267
msgid "Delivery order"
msgstr "Leveringsordre"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:75
msgid ""
"The shipping method added to the sales order is linked to the shipping "
"carrier details on the delivery order. After confirming the order, "
"a :icon:`fa-truck` :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button appears at the top of "
"the page. Click the :icon:`fa-truck` :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button to "
"open the warehouse delivery form. To add or change the delivery method on "
"the delivery itself, open the :guilabel:`Additional Info` tab and modify "
"the :guilabel:`Carrier` field."
msgstr ""
"Den forsendelsesmetode, der tilføjes til salgsordren, er knyttet til "
"fragtmandens detaljer på leveringsordren. Efter bekræftelse af ordren vises "
"en smartknap :icon:`fa-truck` :guilabel:`Levering` øverst på siden. Klik på "
"smartknappen :icon:`fa-truck` :guilabel:`Levering` for at åbne "
"lagerleveringsformularen. For at tilføje eller ændre leveringsmetoden på "
"selve leveringen skal du åbne fanen :guilabel:`Yderligere info` og ændre "
"feltet :guilabel:`Fragtmand`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:None
msgid "Shipping carrier information on the delivery form."
msgstr "Fragtfirmaoplysninger på leveringsformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:85
msgid "Supported hardware"
msgstr "Understøttet hardware"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:None
msgid "The Zebra ZD411 works best to print labels from Odoo."
msgstr "Zebra ZD411 fungerer bedst til at udskrive etiketter fra Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:90
msgid ""
"For label printers, Odoo recommends the `Zebra ZD411 <https://www.zebra.com/"
"us/en/products/spec-sheets/printers/desktop/zd411-series.html>`__, as Odoo "
"supports the ZPL protocol for automatic printing from a point of sale."
msgstr ""
"Til etiketteprintere anbefaler Odoo `Zebra ZD411 <https://www.zebra.com/us/"
"en/products/spec-sheets/printers/desktop/zd411-series.html>`__, da Odoo "
"understøtter ZPL-protokollen til automatisk udskrivning fra et salgssted."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:94
msgid ""
"This printer has been tested on most label formats (PDF, PNG, ZPL) for all "
"carriers that Odoo supports."
msgstr ""
"Denne printer er blevet testet på de fleste etiketformater (PDF, PNG, ZPL) "
"for alle fragtfirmaer, som Odoo understøtter."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/bpost.rst:3
msgid "Bpost integration"
msgstr "Bpost-integration"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/bpost.rst:5
msgid ""
"Set up the *Bpost* shipping connector in Odoo to manage Bpost shipments to "
"clients directly within Odoo. To configure it, complete these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Opsæt *Bpost*-forsendelsesconnectoren i Odoo til at håndtere Bpost-"
"forsendelser til kunder direkte i Odoo. For at konfigurere den skal du "
"gennemføre disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/bpost.rst:8
msgid "Create a Bpost account."
msgstr "Opret en Bpost-konto."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/bpost.rst:9
msgid ""
"Get the :ref:`Account ID and passphrase <inventory/shipping_receiving/bpost-"
"account>`."
msgstr ""
"Hent :ref:`konto-id og adgangskode <inventory/shipping_receiving/bpost-"
"account>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/bpost.rst:10
msgid ""
":ref:`Set up the shipping method in Odoo <inventory/shipping_receiving/bpost-"
"method>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Opsæt forsendelsesmetoden i Odoo <inventory/shipping_receiving/bpost-"
"method>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/bpost.rst:12
msgid ""
"Upon completion, it is possible to calculate the cost of shipping, based on "
"package size and weight, have the charges applied directly to a Bpost "
"business account, and automatically print Bpost tracking labels through Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Efter gennemførelse er det muligt at beregne forsendelsesomkostninger "
"baseret på pakkestørrelse og vægt, få gebyrerne opkrævet direkte på en Bpost-"
"erhvervskonto og automatisk udskrive Bpost-sporingslabels via Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/bpost.rst:17
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials.rst:10
