#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:3
msgid "EasyPost integration"
msgstr "EasyPost-integration"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:5
msgid ""
"Set up the EasyPost delivery connector in Odoo to manage EasyPost shipments "
"to clients directly within Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Opsæt EasyPost-leverancekonnektoren i Odoo for at administrere EasyPost-"
"forsendelser til kunder direkte i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:8
msgid ""
"EasyPost is a service that allows users to connect with multiple carriers, "
"like UPS, USPS, FedEx, DHL, and more. Odoo can then connect to EasyPost to "
"purchase labels from those carriers."
msgstr ""
"EasyPost er en tjeneste, der giver brugere mulighed for at oprette "
"forbindelse til flere transportører som UPS, USPS, FedEx, DHL og flere. Odoo "
"kan derefter oprette forbindelse til EasyPost for at købe etiketter fra "
"disse transportører."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:11
msgid "To configure it, complete these steps:"
msgstr "For at konfigurere det skal du gennemføre disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:13
msgid ""
":ref:`Create an EasyPost account <inventory/shipping_receiving/easypost-"
"account>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Opret en EasyPost-konto <inventory/shipping_receiving/easypost-"
"account>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:14
msgid ""
":ref:`Integrate carrier accounts if the carrier is not enabled on the "
"EasyPost account <inventory/shipping_receiving/integrate-easypost-carrier>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Integrer transportørkontoen, hvis transportøren ikke er aktiveret på "
"EasyPost-kontoen <inventory/shipping_receiving/integrate-easypost-carrier>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:16
msgid ""
":ref:`Obtain Test and Production API keys <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"easypost-api-keys>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Hent test- og produktions-API-nøgler <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"easypost-api-keys>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:17
msgid ""
":ref:`Set up the delivery method in Odoo <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"easypost-method>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Opsæt leveringsmetoden i Odoo <inventory/shipping_receiving/easypost-"
"method>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:19
msgid ""
"Upon completion, it is possible to calculate shipping costs based on package "
"size and weight, have the charges applied directly to an EasyPost business "
"account, and automatically print EasyPost tracking labels in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Når det er fuldført, er det muligt at beregne forsendelsesomkostninger "
"baseret på pakkestørrelse og vægt, få gebyrerne anvendt direkte på en "
"EasyPost-virksomhedskonto og automatisk udskrive EasyPost-sporingslabels i "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:28
msgid ""
"To begin, go to the `EasyPost <https://www.easypost.com>`__ website to "
"create or log into the company's EasyPost business account."
msgstr ""
"For at begynde skal du gå til `EasyPost <https://www.easypost.com>`__ "
"hjemmesiden for at oprette eller logge ind på virksomhedens EasyPost-"
"virksomhedskonto."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:31
msgid ""
"Follow the website's steps to complete registration and sign up for shipping "
"services. Some shipping services (like USPS and DHL Express) are "
"automatically enabled."
msgstr ""
"Følg hjemmesidens trin for at fuldføre registreringen og tilmelde dig "
"forsendelsestjenester. Nogle forsendelsestjenester (som USPS og DHL Express) "
"er automatisk aktiveret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:37
msgid "Integrating other carrier accounts"
msgstr "Integration af andre transportørkonti"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:39
msgid ""
"To use a different carrier, it is possible to `enable Wallet Carrier "
"Accounts <https://support.easypost.com/hc/en-us/articles/21336276718605-"
"Enabling-Wallet-Carriers-Using-the-EasyPost-Dashboard>`__ to purchase labels "
"from EasyPost. Alternatively, if a user has their own carrier account, they "
"can `enable it on EasyPost <https://support.easypost.com/hc/en-us/articles/"
"25246240687373-Bring-Your-Own-Carrier-Account-to-EasyPost>`__. Then, after "
"these accounts are enabled, Odoo can integrate with the EasyPost account and "
"manage labels."
msgstr ""
"For at bruge en anden transportør er det muligt at `aktivere Wallet Carrier "
"Accounts <https://support.easypost.com/hc/en-us/articles/21336276718605-"
"Enabling-Wallet-Carriers-Using-the-EasyPost-Dashboard>`__ for at købe labels "
"fra EasyPost. Alternativt, hvis en bruger har sin egen transportørkonto, kan "
"de `aktivere den på EasyPost <https://support.easypost.com/hc/en-us/articles/"
"25246240687373-Bring-Your-Own-Carrier-Account-to-EasyPost>`__. Derefter, "
"efter disse konti er aktiveret, kan Odoo integrere med EasyPost-kontoen og "
"administrere labels."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:50
msgid "Obtain Test and Production API keys"
msgstr "Hent test- og produktions-API-nøgler"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:52
msgid ""
"After completing the setup, create Test and Production API keys. On the "
"EasyPost website, click the :guilabel:`Account Settings` link, then open "
"the :guilabel:`API Keys` page."
msgstr ""
"Efter fuldførelse af opsætningen skal du oprette test- og produktions-API-"
"nøgler. På EasyPost-hjemmesiden skal du klikke på "
"linket :guilabel:`Kontoindstillinger` og derefter åbne siden :guilabel:`API-"
"nøgler`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:55
msgid ""
"If these API keys have not yet been created, click :guilabel:`Add Additional "
"API Key`. Select either :guilabel:`Production` or :guilabel:`Test`. The API "
"key is automatically created. Follow the same process to create both keys."
msgstr ""
"Hvis disse API-nøgler endnu ikke er oprettet, skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Tilføj yderligere API-nøgle`. Vælg "
"enten :guilabel:`Produktion` eller :guilabel:`Test`. API-nøglen oprettes "
"automatisk. Følg samme proces for at oprette begge nøgler."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:None
msgid "Create API keys on the EasyPost API Keys page."
msgstr "Opret API-nøgler på EasyPost API-nøglesiden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:65
msgid "Delivery method configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguration af leveringsmetode"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:67
msgid ""
"With those necessary credentials, configure the EasyPost delivery method in "
"Odoo by going to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> "
"Delivery Methods`."
msgstr ""
"Med disse nødvendige legitimationsoplysninger skal du konfigurere EasyPost-"
"leveringsmetoden i Odoo ved at gå til :menuselection:`Lager-appen --> "
"Konfiguration --> Leveringsmetoder`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:70
msgid "On the *Delivery Methods* page, click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr "På siden *Leveringsmetoder* skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:72
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Provider` field, select :guilabel:`Easypost` from the drop-"
"down menu. Doing so reveals the *Easypost Configuration* tab at the bottom "
"of the form, where the EasyPost API keys should be entered."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Udbyder` skal du vælge :guilabel:`Easypost` fra "
"rullemenuen. Dette afslører fanen *Easypost-konfiguration* nederst i "
"formularen, hvor EasyPost API-nøglerne skal indtastes."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:76
msgid ""
"For details on configuring the other fields on the delivery method, such "
"as :guilabel:`Delivery Product`, refer to the :doc:`new_delivery_method` "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"For detaljer om konfiguration af de andre felter på leveringsmetoden, "
"såsom :guilabel:`Leveringsprodukt`, se :doc:`new_delivery_method` "
"dokumentationen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:80
msgid ""
"To generate EasyPost shipping labels through Odoo, ensure "
"the :guilabel:`Integration Level` option is set to :guilabel:`Get Rate and "
"Create Shipment`."
msgstr ""
"For at generere EasyPost-forsendelsesetiketter gennem Odoo skal du sikre, at "
"indstillingen :guilabel:`Integrationsniveau` er sat til :guilabel:`Hent pris "
"og opret forsendelse`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:83
msgid "In the *Easypost Configuration* tab, complete the following fields:"
msgstr "I fanen *Easypost-konfiguration* skal du udfylde følgende felter:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:85
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Test API Key`: the Test API key in the EasyPost Account Settings."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Test API-nøgle`: Test API-nøglen i EasyPost-kontoindstillingerne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Production API Key`: the Production API key in the EasyPost "
"Account Settings."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produktions-API-nøgle`: Produktions-API-nøglen i EasyPost-"
"kontoindstillingerne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:87
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Label Format`: "
"Choose :guilabel:`PNG`, :guilabel:`PDF`, :guilabel:`ZPL`, "
"or :guilabel:`EPL2` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Labelformat`: "
"Vælg :guilabel:`PNG`, :guilabel:`PDF`, :guilabel:`ZPL` "
"eller :guilabel:`EPL2` fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Generate Return Label`: Select to automatically generate a return "
"label when validating the delivery."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Generer returlabel`: Vælg for automatisk at generere en "
"returlabel ved validering af leveringen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:92
msgid ""
"Save the delivery method by clicking the :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(Save manually)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Gem leveringsmetoden ved at klikke på :icon:`fa-cloud-upload` :guilabel:`Gem "
"manuelt`-ikonet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:94
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Load your Easypost carrier accounts` link under the API "
"keys."
msgstr ""
"Klik på linket :guilabel:`Indlæs dine Easypost-transportørkonti` under API-"
"nøglerne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:None
msgid "Load the EasyPost carrier accounts into Odoo."
msgstr "Indlæs EasyPost-transportørkontiene i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:99
msgid ""
"The *Select a carrier* pop-up window opens. Select a shipping carrier from "
"the drop-down menu, then click :guilabel:`Select`."
msgstr ""
"Pop op-vinduet *Vælg en transportør* åbnes. Vælg en fragttransportør fra "
"rullemenuen, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Vælg`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:102
msgid ""
"After the carrier type has been selected, complete the :guilabel:`Default "
"Package Type` and :guilabel:`Default Service Level` fields."
msgstr ""
"Når transportørtypen er valgt, udfyld felterne :guilabel:`Standardpakketype` "
"og :guilabel:`Standardserviceniveau`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:None
msgid ""
"Select a package type and service level that should be used for the carrier."
msgstr ""
"Vælg en pakketype og et serviceniveau, der skal bruges til transportøren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:109
msgid "Turn on the Easypost integration"
msgstr "Slå Easypost-integrationen til"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:111
msgid ""
"After the EasyPost connection is set up, use the smart buttons at the top of "
"the form to publish, turn on production mode, or activate debug logging."
msgstr ""
"Når EasyPost-forbindelsen er oprettet, skal du bruge de smarte knapper "
"øverst på formularen til at publicere, slå produktionstilstand til eller "
"aktivere fejlfindingslogning."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:114
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unpublished/Published`: determines if this delivery method is "
"available on the user's **eCommerce** website."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Upubliceret/Publiceret`: afgør, om denne leveringsmetode er "
"tilgængelig på brugerens **Webshop**-hjemmeside."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:116
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Test Environment/Production Environment`: determines whether "
"label creation is for testing and cancelled immediately (Test) or generating "
"a real shipping label that is charged to the EasyPost account (Production)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Testmiljø/Produktionsmiljø`: afgør, om labeloprettelse er til "
"test og annulleres med det samme (Test), eller genererer en ægte "
"forsendelsesetiket, der debiteres EasyPost-kontoen (Produktion)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No Debug/Debug Requests`: determines whether API requests and "
"responses are logged in Odoo (turn on **developer mode** and go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> Logging`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ingen fejlfinding/Fejlfindingsanmodninger`: afgør, om API-"
"anmodninger og -svar logges i Odoo (slå **udviklertilstand** til og gå "
"til :menuselection:`Indstillinger-app --> Teknisk --> Logning`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:3
msgid "Envia.com integration"
msgstr "Envia.com-integration"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:5
msgid ""
"Envia.com is a shipping service that connects businesses with multiple "
"carriers in Odoo. Key features include:"
msgstr ""
"Envia.com er en forsendelsestjeneste, der forbinder virksomheder med flere "
"fragtmænd i Odoo. Nøglefunktioner omfatter:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:8
msgid ""
"**Multi-carrier & international shipping**: Compare rates across carriers "
"and select the best option for domestic or global shipments."
msgstr ""
"**Multi-fragtmand & international forsendelse**: Sammenlign priser på tværs "
"af fragtmænd og vælg den bedste mulighed for nationale eller globale "
"forsendelser."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:10
msgid ""
"**Automated label generation**: Generate shipping labels at order "
"confirmation."
msgstr ""
"**Automatiseret etiketgenerering**: Generer forsendelsesetiketter ved "
"ordrebekræftelse."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:11
msgid ""
"**Real-time rate calculation**: Fetch rates based on package details and "
"destination."
msgstr ""
"**Prisberegning i realtid**: Hent priser baseret på pakkedetaljer og "
"destination."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:14
msgid "Setup in Envia"
msgstr "Opsætning i Envia"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:16
msgid ""
"To integrate `Envia.com <https://www.envia.com>`_ with Odoo, first create an "
"account and activate the necessary shipping carriers. Then, obtain the API "
"credentials, which is used to connect Envia.com to the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"For at integrere `Envia.com <https://www.envia.com>`_ med Odoo skal du først "
"oprette en konto og aktivere de nødvendige fragtmænd. Hent derefter API-"
"legitimationsoplysningerne, som bruges til at forbinde Envia.com til Odoo-"
"databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:21
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:13
msgid "Create an account and activate carriers"
msgstr "Opret en konto og aktiver fragtmænd"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:23
msgid "Begin by going to `Envia.com <https://www.envia.com>`_."
msgstr "Begynd med at gå til `Envia.com <https://www.envia.com>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:25
msgid ""
"After signing in, in the left sidebar, click :menuselection:`Settings --> "
"Print Options and Carriers`. Next, select the country to set the currency "
"and display available shipping carriers."
msgstr ""
"Efter login skal du i venstre sidepanel klikke "
"på :menuselection:`Indstillinger --> Udskriftsindstillinger og fragtmænd`. "
"Vælg derefter landet for at indstille valutaen og vise tilgængelige "
"fragtmænd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:29
msgid ""
"When signing up, make sure to select the correct language **and** country in "
"the upper right-hand corner. This affects the currency of the account!"
msgstr ""
"Ved tilmelding skal du sørge for at vælge det korrekte sprog **og** land i "
"øverste højre hjørne. Dette påvirker kontoens valuta!"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:0
msgid "Registry process in website with Envia.com."
msgstr "Registreringsproces på hjemmeside med Envia.com."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:35
msgid ""
"After deciding on the desired carrier, click :guilabel:`Activate`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Services` to select the carrier's available shipping "
"options."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have besluttet dig for den ønskede fragtmand skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Aktiver` og derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Tjenester` for at "
"vælge fragtmandens tilgængelige forsendelsesmuligheder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:39
msgid ""
"Billing is always processed in the currency of the country that matches the "
"primary billing address. If the company operates in multiple countries, "
"consider creating separate accounts for each location."
msgstr ""
"Fakturering behandles altid i valutaen for det land, der matcher den primære "
"faktureringsadresse. Hvis virksomheden opererer i flere lande, kan du "
"overveje at oprette separate konti for hver lokation."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:44
msgid ""
"Envia will send an SMS or WhatsApp message to confirm the email address and "
"phone number."
msgstr ""
"Envia sender en SMS- eller WhatsApp-besked for at bekræfte e-mailadressen og "
"telefonnummeret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Select carrier services."
msgstr "Vælg fragtmandstjenester."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:50
msgid "Generate Envia.com credentials"
msgstr "Generer legitimationsoplysninger til Envia.com"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:52
msgid ""
"Go to `Envia.com <https://www.envia.com>`_, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Developers --> API Keys`, on the left menu, then "
"click :guilabel:`add` to generate a new key."
msgstr ""
"Gå til `Envia.com <https://www.envia.com>`_, naviger "
"til :menuselection:`Developers --> API Keys` i menuen til venstre, og klik "
"derefter på :guilabel:`tilføj` for at generere en ny nøgle."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:55
msgid ""
"This key is required to authenticate Odoo's connection with Envia.com. "
"Retrieve it at any time by returning to the :guilabel:`API Keys` section."
msgstr ""
"Denne nøgle er påkrævet for at autentificere Odoos forbindelse med "
"Envia.com. Den kan hentes til enhver tid ved at vende tilbage til "
"sektionen :guilabel:`API Keys`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:None
msgid "API Keys in Envia.com."
msgstr "API-nøgler i Envia.com."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:62
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:88
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:90
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:165
msgid "Setup in Odoo"
msgstr "Opsætning i Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:64
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`Envia Shipping` "
"(`delivery_envia`) module, and proceed to the following sections to "
"configure the integration in Odoo."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Installer <general/install>` modulet :guilabel:`Forsendelse med Envia` "
"(`delivery_envia`), og fortsæt til følgende sektioner for at konfigurere "
"integrationen i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:68
msgid "Envia.com shipping connector configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguration af forsendelsesconnector til Envia.com"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:70
msgid ""
"After activating the Envia.com connector, create a delivery method by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Delivery Methods` and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Efter aktivering af Envia.com-connectoren skal du oprette en leveringsmetode "
"ved at gå til :menuselection:`Lager --> Konfiguration --> Leveringsmetoder` "
"og klikke på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:73
msgid "Fill out the following form fields:"
msgstr "Udfyld følgende formularfelter:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:75
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shipping Method`: Name of the shipping method, e.g. `Envia.com`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forsendelsesmetode`: Navn på forsendelsesmetoden, f.eks. "
"`Envia.com`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:76
msgid ":guilabel:`Provider`: Select :guilabel:`Envia` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Udbyder`: Vælg :guilabel:`Envia` fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:77
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Product`: The product listed on the sales order as the "
"delivery charge. A specific delivery product for Envia.com must be created."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Leveringsprodukt`: Det produkt, der er anført på salgsordren som "
"leveringsgebyr. Der skal oprettes et specifikt leveringsprodukt til "
"Envia.com."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:79
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Envia Configuration` tab, enter the :guilabel:`Envia "
"Production Access Token`."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Envia-konfiguration` skal du indtaste :guilabel:`Envia-"
"produktionsadgangstoken`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:80
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Envia Configuration` tab, enter the :guilabel:`Envia "
"Sandbox Access Token`."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Envia-konfiguration` skal du indtaste :guilabel:`Envia-"
"sandkasseadgangstoken`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:81
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Insurance percentage`: If insurance is needed, place a percentage "
"of the value to insure. If not, leave it as 0. Keep in mind that the "
"insurance price is calculated only after the label has been generated, "
"including for LTL shipments."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forsikringsprocent`: Hvis forsikring er nødvendig, angiv en "
"procentdel af værdien, der skal forsikres. Hvis ikke, lad den stå som 0. "
"Husk, at forsikringsprisen først beregnes, efter at etiketten er genereret, "
"også for LTL-forsendelser."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:86
msgid ""
"It is mandatory to fill both the production and sandbox tokens, but it could "
"be left as a random character as it is not validated at this point."
msgstr ""
"Det er obligatorisk at udfylde både produktions- og sandbox-tokens, men det "
"kan efterlades som et tilfældigt tegn, da det ikke valideres på dette "
"tidspunkt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:89
msgid "Additional considerations for the :guilabel:`Envia Default Package`:"
msgstr "Yderligere overvejelser for :guilabel:`Envia Default Package`:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:91
msgid ""
"The package is specified in :guilabel:`mm` and :guilabel:`kg`. The weight "
"refers to the container itself, not its contents. Leave the weight as `0` if "
"no weight is reported, and set the max weight to `0` if there is no "
"specified limit."
msgstr ""
"Pakken er specificeret i :guilabel:`mm` og :guilabel:`kg`. Vægten refererer "
"til selve beholderen, ikke dens indhold. Lad vægten stå som `0`, hvis der "
"ikke er angivet nogen vægt, og sæt maksimalvægten til `0`, hvis der ikke er "
"nogen specificeret grænse."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Envia Package Type`: Set to :guilabel:`Box` by default. Ensure "
"the correct type is selected, as it affects the available carriers and "
"options displayed, which vary depending on this selection."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Envia Package Type`: Indstillet til :guilabel:`Box` som standard. "
"Sørg for, at den korrekte type er valgt, da det påvirker de tilgængelige "
"fragtfirmaer og viste muligheder, som varierer afhængigt af dette valg."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:98
msgid ""
"Once previous fields are properly set, navigate to the :guilabel:`Envia "
"Configuration` tab, and in the :guilabel:`Envia.com Service Name` field, "
"click the :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(refresh)` icon to sync the "
"carriers. In the pop-up window that appears, select a carrier and a service "
"level from the list."
msgstr ""
"Når de forrige felter er korrekt indstillet, naviger til "
"fanen :guilabel:`Envia Configuration`, og i feltet :guilabel:`Envia.com "
"Service Name` skal du klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-"
"refresh` :guilabel:`(opdater)` for at synkronisere fragtfirmaerne. I pop op-"
"vinduet, der vises, vælg et fragtfirma og et serviceniveau fra listen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Envia.com carrier and services popup."
msgstr "Pop op med Envia.com fragtfirma og tjenester."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:107
msgid ""
"Envia keeps the main currency of the account fixed. In order to provide more "
"precise conversions for the costs of shipping, specify the currency that is "
"set for the account on Envia. If necessary, Odoo offers the option to change "
"the country. By default it uses the country associated with the company."
msgstr ""
"Envia holder hovedvalutaen for kontoen fast. For at give mere præcise "
"omregninger for fragtomkostninger, angiv den valuta, der er indstillet for "
"kontoen på Envia. Om nødvendigt tilbyder Odoo muligheden for at ændre "
"landet. Som standard bruges det land, der er tilknyttet virksomheden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:113
msgid ""
"If more than one shipping option is needed, create more shipping methods in "
"Odoo and modify any parameter like the package, carrier, or service."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der er brug for mere end én forsendelsesmulighed, opret flere "
"forsendelsesmetoder i Odoo og modificer enhver parameter som pakke, "
"fragtfirma eller service."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:119
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:211
msgid "Shipping information"
msgstr "Forsendelsesoplysninger"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:121
msgid ""
"To use Envia.com to generate shipping labels, the following information "
"**must** be filled out accurately and completely in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"For at bruge Envia.com til at generere forsendelsesetiketter **skal** "
"følgende oplysninger udfyldes nøjagtigt og fuldstændigt i Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:124
msgid ""
"**Customer information**: When creating a quotation, ensure the "
"selected :guilabel:`Customer` has a valid phone number, email address, and "
"shipping address."
msgstr ""
"**Kundeoplysninger**: Når du opretter et tilbud, skal du sikre, at den "
"valgte :guilabel:`Kunde` har et gyldigt telefonnummer, en e-mailadresse og "
"en forsendelsesadresse."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:127
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:219
msgid ""
"To verify, select the :guilabel:`Customer` field to open their contact page. "
"Here, add their shipping address in the :guilabel:`Contact` field, along "
"with their :guilabel:`Mobile` number and :guilabel:`Email` address."
msgstr ""
"For at verificere skal du vælge feltet :guilabel:`Kunde` for at åbne deres "
"kontaktside. Her tilføjes deres forsendelsesadresse i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Kontakt` sammen med deres :guilabel:`Mobilnummer` "
"og :guilabel:`E-mailadresse`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:130
msgid ""
"**Product weight**: Ensure all products in a delivery order have a "
"specified :guilabel:`Weight` in the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab of their "
"product form. Refer to the :ref:`Product weight section <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-weight>` of this article for detailed "
"instructions."
msgstr ""
"**Produktvægt**: Sørg for, at alle produkter i en leveringsordre har en "
"specificeret :guilabel:`Vægt` i fanen :guilabel:`Lager` på deres "
"produktformular. Se :ref:`Produktvægtafsnittet <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"configure-weight>` i denne artikel for detaljerede instruktioner."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping.rst:133
msgid ""
"**Warehouse address**: By default all packages are sent from the specified "
"address in the warehouse, make sure to set the address for correct label "
"generation."
msgstr ""
"**Lageradresse**: Som standard sendes alle pakker fra den angivne adresse i "
"lageret, så sørg for at indstille adressen for korrekt etiketgenerering."

