"Configuration --> Operation Types`, and select the desired operation type. "
"Then, go to the :guilabel:`Hardware` tab, and tick the :guilabel:`Package "
"Contents` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"For at udskrive denne formular automatisk skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Konfiguration --> Operationstyper` og "
"vælge den ønskede operationstype. Gå derefter til fanen :guilabel:`Hardware` "
"og markér afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Pakkeindhold`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:292
msgid ""
"If the option is not available, enable the :doc:`Packages <../../"
"product_management/configure/package>` feature, by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`, ticking "
"the :guilabel:`Packages` checkbox, and clicking :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis indstillingen ikke er tilgængelig, skal du aktivere "
"funktionen :doc:`Pakker <../../product_management/configure/package>` ved at "
"gå til :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, "
"markere afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Pakker` og klikke på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:297
msgid ""
"After enabling the feature in the :guilabel:`Hardware` tab, validating the "
"operation prints a PDF of the package contents."
msgstr ""
"Efter aktivering af funktionen i fanen :guilabel:`Hardware` udskriver "
"validering af operationen en PDF med pakkeindholdet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:0
msgid ""
"Package contents form showing the package contents, barcode, and pack date."
msgstr ""
"Formular for pakkeindhold, der viser pakkeindholdet, stregkode og pakkedato."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:306
msgid "Package contents showing the package contents, barcode, and pack date."
msgstr "Pakkeindhold, der viser pakkeindholdet, stregkode og pakkedato."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:311
msgid "Package label"
msgstr "Pakkelabel"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:313
msgid ""
"A *package label* that shows the package's barcode and pack date can be "
"configured to print upon clicking the *Put in Pack* button."
msgstr ""
"En *pakkelabel*, der viser pakkens stregkode og pakkedato, kan konfigureres "
"til at blive udskrevet ved klik på knappen *Læg i pakke*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:317
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Put in Pack` button is available **only** when "
"the :doc:`Packages <../../product_management/configure/package>` feature is "
"enabled in :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Knappen :guilabel:`Læg i pakke` er **kun** tilgængelig, når "
"funktionen :doc:`Pakker <../../product_management/configure/package>` er "
"aktiveret i :menuselection:`Lager --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:321
msgid ""
"After it is enabled, the :guilabel:`Put in Pack` button is available on all "
"inventory operations (e.g. receipt, pickings, internal transfers, delivery "
"orders, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Efter den er aktiveret, er knappen :guilabel:`Læg i pakke` tilgængelig på "
"alle lageroperationer (f.eks. modtagelse, pluk, interne overførsler, "
"leveringsordrer osv.)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:324
msgid ""
"To automatically print the package label when the :guilabel:`Put in Pack` "
"button is clicked, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> "
"Operation Types`. Select the desired operation type, and tick "
"the :guilabel:`Package Label` checkbox in the :guilabel:`Hardware` tab. "
"Labels can be printed in :guilabel:`PDF` or :guilabel:`ZPL` file formats, as "
"defined in the :guilabel:`Print label as` field."
msgstr ""
"For automatisk at udskrive pakkelabelen, når knappen :guilabel:`Læg i pakke` "
"klikkes, gå til :menuselection:`Lager --> Konfiguration --> "
"Operationstyper`. Vælg den ønskede operationstype, og markér "
"afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Pakkelabel` under fanen :guilabel:`Hardware`. "
"Labeler kan udskrives i filformaterne :guilabel:`PDF` eller :guilabel:`ZPL`, "
"som defineret i feltet :guilabel:`Udskriv label som`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:0
msgid "PDF of package barcode and package date."
msgstr "PDF af pakke-stregkode og pakkedato."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:3
msgid "Sendcloud integration"
msgstr "Sendcloud-integration"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:5
msgid ""
"Sendcloud is a shipping service aggregator that facilitates the integration "
"of European shipping carriers with Odoo. Once integrated, users can select "
"shipping carriers on inventory operations in their Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Sendcloud er en aggregator af forsendelsestjenester, der letter "
"integrationen af europæiske fragtselskaber med Odoo. Når integrationen er på "
"plads, kan brugere vælge fragtselskaber på lageroperationer i deres Odoo-"
"database."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:10
msgid "Setup in Sendcloud"
msgstr "Opsætning i Sendcloud"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:15
msgid ""
"To get started, `create or log in to a Sendcloud account <https://"
"account.sendcloud.com/signup/ ?"
"utm_source=odoo&utm_medium=partnerships&utm_campaign=partner_integrations_page>`_."
msgstr ""
"For at komme i gang skal du `oprette eller logge ind på en Sendcloud-konto "
"<https://account.sendcloud.com/signup/ ?"
"utm_source=odoo&utm_medium=partnerships&utm_campaign=partner_integrations_page>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:18
msgid ""
"On the Sendcloud platform, follow the `Sendcloud integration documentation "
"<https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/articles/360059470491-Odoo-Native-"
"integration>`_ to configure the account and generate the connector "
"credentials."
msgstr ""
"På Sendcloud-platformen skal du følge `Sendcloud-integrationsdokumentationen "
"<https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/articles/360059470491-Odoo-Native-"
"integration>`_ for at konfigurere kontoen og generere connector-"
"legitimationsoplysningerne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:23
msgid ""
"For new account creation, Sendcloud will ask for a :abbr:`VAT (Value-Added "
"Tax Identification)` number or :abbr:`EORI (Economic Operators' Registration "
"and Identification)` number. After completing the account setup, activate "
"(or deactivate) the shipping carriers that will be used in the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Ved oprettelse af ny konto vil Sendcloud bede om et :abbr:`VAT "
"(momsregistrerings)`nummer eller et :abbr:`EORI (registrerings- og "
"identifikationsnummer for økonomiske operatører)`nummer. Efter afslutning af "
"kontoopsætningen skal de fragtselskaber, der skal bruges i Odoo-databasen, "
"aktiveres (eller deaktiveres)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:29
msgid ""
"Odoo integration of Sendcloud works on free Sendcloud plans *only* if a bank "
"account is linked, since Sendcloud won't ship for free. To use shipping "
"rules, or individual custom carrier contacts, a paid plan of Sendcloud is "
"**required**."
msgstr ""
"Odoo-integration af Sendcloud fungerer kun på gratis Sendcloud-planer, "
"*hvis* en bankkonto er tilknyttet, da Sendcloud ikke sender gratis. For at "
"bruge forsendelsesregler eller individuelle tilpassede "
"fragtselskabskontakter er en betalt Sendcloud-plan **påkrævet**."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:34
msgid ""
"`Magic Sheet - Connect Sendcloud [PDF] <https://drive.google.com/drive/"
"folders/1Cj_bbIn2gOA6HNDFEI8AhjUvcxe2wSMf>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Magic Sheet - Connect Sendcloud [PDF] <https://drive.google.com/drive/"
"folders/1Cj_bbIn2gOA6HNDFEI8AhjUvcxe2wSMf>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:40
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:185
msgid "Warehouse configuration"
msgstr "Lagerkonfiguration"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:42
msgid ""
"Once logged into the Sendcloud account, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings "
"--> Shipping --> Addresses`, and fill in the field for :guilabel:`Warehouse "
"address`."
msgstr ""
"Når du er logget ind på Sendcloud-kontoen, gå "
"til :menuselection:`Indstillinger --> Forsendelse --> Adresser`, og udfyld "
"feltet for :guilabel:`Lageradresse`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Adding addresses in the Sendcloud settings."
msgstr "Tilføjelse af adresser i Sendcloud-indstillingerne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:49
msgid ""
"To allow Sendcloud to process returns as well, a :guilabel:`Return Address` "
"is required. Under the :guilabel:`Miscellaneous section`, there is a field "
"called :guilabel:`Address Name (optional)`. The Odoo warehouse name should "
"be entered here, and the characters should be exactly the same."
msgstr ""
"For at tillade Sendcloud også at behandle returneringer kræves "
"en :guilabel:`Returadresse`. Under afsnittet :guilabel:`Diverse` findes et "
"felt kaldet :guilabel:`Adressenavn (valgfrit)`. Odoo-lagernavnet skal "
"indtastes her, og tegnene skal være nøjagtig de samme."

