msgid ""
":guilabel:`Authorization (O Auth)`: Used to generate the authorization token "
"to request information from the UPS API."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Authorization (O Auth)`: Bruges til at generere "
"autorisationstoken til at anmode om information fra UPS API."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Address Validation`: Validates addresses at the street level in "
"the United States and Puerto Rico."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Address Validation`: Validerer adresser på gadeniveau i USA og "
"Puerto Rico."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:129
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Locator`: Enables search for UPS shipping locations based on type "
"and available services."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Locator`: Gør det muligt at søge efter UPS fragtlokationer "
"baseret på type og tilgængelige tjenester."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Paperless Documents`: Enables the upload of document images to "
"link to shipments."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Paperless Documents`: Gør det muligt at uploade dokumentbilleder "
"til at linke til forsendelser."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:132
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shipping`: Enables UPS shipping services, such as preparing "
"packages for shipment, managing returns, and cancelling scheduled shipments."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Shipping`: Aktiverer UPS fragttjenester, såsom forberedelse af "
"pakker til forsendelse, håndtering af returneringer og annullering af "
"planlagte forsendelser."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:134
msgid ":guilabel:`Rating`: Compare delivery services and shipping rates."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Rating`: Sammenlign leveringstjenester og fragtpriser."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:136
msgid "Finally, click :guilabel:`Save` and accept UPS's terms and conditions."
msgstr ""
"Klik til sidst på :guilabel:`Gem`, og accepter UPS's vilkår og betingelser."

