msgstr ""
"På siden :guilabel:`Fragtmetoder` skal du klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:173
