msgstr ""
":guilabel:`UPS-pakketype`: (*påkrævet*) Vælg den :doc:`pakketype <../../"
"product_management/configure/package>`, der understøttes for "
"forsendelsesservicen, fra rullelisten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:192
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Package Weight Unit`: The unit of measure for the package weight."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pakkevægtenhed`: Måleenheden for pakkevægten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:193
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Package Size Unit`: The unit of measure for the package "
"dimensions."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pakkestørrelsesenhed`: Måleenheden for pakkedimensionerne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:194
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Label Format`: Choose the label format shipping "
"labels: :guilabel:`PDF`, :guilabel:`ZPL`, :guilabel:`EPL`, "
"or :guilabel:`SPL`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Etiketformat`: Vælg etiketformatet for "
"forsendelsesetiketter: :guilabel:`PDF`, :guilabel:`ZPL`, :guilabel:`EPL` "
"eller :guilabel:`SPL`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:None
msgid "Show the \"UPS Configuration\" tab on the Shipping Methods form."
msgstr "Vis fanen \"UPS-konfiguration\" på forsendelsesmetodeformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:201
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Options` section, the following features are available:"
msgstr ""
"I afsnittet :guilabel:`Valgmuligheder` er følgende funktioner tilgængelige:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:203
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bill My Account`: Charge the user's UPS account for shipping in "
"the *eCommerce* app."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fakturer min konto`: Opkræv brugerens UPS-konto for forsendelse i "
"appen *Webshop*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:204
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Collect on Delivery`: Collect payment from customers for shipping "
"after the shipment is delivered."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Opkræv ved levering`: Opkræv betaling fra kunder for forsendelse, "
"efter at forsendelsen er leveret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:206
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Generate Return Label`: Print the return label for the order "
"after the delivery order is validated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Generer returetiket`: Udskriv returetiketten for ordren, efter at "
"leveringsordren er valideret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials.rst:208
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Duties paid by`: Select whether duties or other fees are charged "
"to the :guilabel:`Sender` or :guilabel:`Recipient` of the order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Told betalt af`: Vælg, om told eller andre gebyrer opkræves "
"af :guilabel:`Afsender` eller :guilabel:`Modtager` af ordren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:3
msgid "USPS integration"
msgstr "Integrace USPS"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:7
msgid ""
"Integrating a USPS account with Odoo's **Inventory** app makes it possible "
"to calculate delivery rates and generate delivery labels within Odoo. This "
"is accomplished by enabling the USPS shipping connector, then configuring at "
"least one delivery method."
msgstr ""
"Integrace účtu USPS s aplikací **Lager** umožňuje vypočítat sazby dodání a "
"generovat štítky dodání přímo v Odoo. Toho je dosaženo povolením konektoru "
"USPS a následným nakonfigurováním alespoň jedné metody dodání."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:14
msgid ""
"To enable the USPS shipping connector, open the :menuselection:`Apps` app "
"from the main Odoo dashboard. In the :guilabel:`Search` field, search for "
"`USPS`  and click :guilabel:`Install`."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li povolit konektor USPS, otevřete aplikaci :menuselection:`Aplikace` "
"z hlavního Odoo dashboardu. Do pole :guilabel:`Hledat` zadejte `USPS` a "
"klikněte na :guilabel:`Instalovat`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:17
msgid ""
"After the shipping connector is installed, the USPS connector is enabled by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"Po instalaci konektoru dodání je konektor USPS ve výchozím nastavení povolen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:20
msgid "Configure USPS business account"
msgstr "Konfigurer USPS-forretningskonto"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:22
msgid ""
"A USPS business account is required to obtain the information needed "
"to :ref:`fill out the fields in the delivery method form <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/usps-configuration>`. To create a new account, navigate "
"to USPS's `Create Your USPS.com Account <https://reg.usps.com/entreg/"
"RegistrationAction_input>`_ page, select the :guilabel:`Business Account` "
"option, then follow the steps."
msgstr ""
"En USPS-forretningskonto er påkrævet for at få de nødvendige oplysninger til "
"at :ref:`udfylde felterne i leveringsmetodeformularen <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/usps-configuration>`. For at oprette en ny konto skal du "
"gå til USPS's `Create Your USPS.com Account <https://reg.usps.com/entreg/"
"RegistrationAction_input>`_-side, vælge :guilabel:`Business Account`-"
"indstillingen og derefter følge trinnene."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:29
msgid "Create a developer app"
msgstr "Opret en udviklerapp"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:31
msgid ""
"After the USPS Business Customer Onboarding Portal (COP) is set up, `sign in "
"to the USPS COP <https://cop.usps.com/>`_ to manage business account "
"information and access the USPS APIs."
msgstr ""
"Når USPS Business Customer Onboarding Portal (COP) er oprettet, skal du "
"`logge ind på USPS COP <https://cop.usps.com/>`_ for at administrere "
"forretningskontooplysninger og få adgang til USPS API'erne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:34
msgid ""
"On this page, make note of the :guilabel:`Customer Registration ID (CRID)`, "
"the :guilabel:`Master Mailer ID`, and the :guilabel:`Label Mailer ID`."
msgstr ""
"På denne side skal du notere :guilabel:`Customer Registration ID "
"(CRID)`, :guilabel:`Master Mailer ID` og :guilabel:`Label Mailer ID`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:37
msgid "Click the :guilabel:`My Apps` link at the top of the screen."
msgstr "Klik på linket :guilabel:`My Apps` øverst på skærmen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:39
msgid ""
"Open the :guilabel:`Developer Apps` tab. Click the :guilabel:`Add App` "
"button. In the *Add App* pop-up window, specify an :guilabel:`App Name`. "
"Select the APIs to use. Finally, click the :guilabel:`Add App` button."
msgstr ""
"Åbn fanen :guilabel:`Developer Apps`. Klik på knappen :guilabel:`Add App`. I "
"pop op-vinduet *Add App* skal du angive et :guilabel:`App Name`. Vælg de "
"API'er, der skal bruges. Klik til sidst på knappen :guilabel:`Add App`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:43
msgid ""
"A window opens, titled after the app name. Keep this window open as the "
"delivery method is configured. The :guilabel:`Consumer Key` "
"and :guilabel:`Consumer Secret` will be necessary in the delivery method "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Et vindue åbnes med appnavnet som titel. Hold dette vindue åbent, mens "
"leveringsmetoden konfigureres. :guilabel:`Consumer Key` "
"og :guilabel:`Consumer Secret` er nødvendige i leveringsmetodeformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:50
msgid ""
"Once the USPS shipping connector is enabled, at least one delivery method "
"must be configured. After doing so, the delivery method can be included in "
"sales orders (SOs) and used to compute delivery costs and print shipping "
"labels."
msgstr ""
"Når USPS-forsendelsesforbindelsen er aktiveret, skal mindst én "
"leveringsmetode konfigureres. Herefter kan leveringsmetoden inkluderes i "
"salgsordrer (SO'er) og bruges til at beregne leveringsomkostninger og "
"udskrive forsendelsesetiketter."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:55
msgid ""
"The USPS shipping connector automatically creates two default delivery "
"methods: :guilabel:`USPS Domestic` and :guilabel:`USPS International`. These "
"methods are preconfigured with test credentials, allowing them to be used "
"for testing purposes."
msgstr ""
"USPS-forsendelsesforbindelsen opretter automatisk to "
"standardleveringsmetoder: :guilabel:`USPS Domestic` og :guilabel:`USPS "
"International`. Disse metoder er forudkonfigureret med "
"testlegitimationsoplysninger, hvilket gør det muligt at bruge dem til "
"testformål."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:59
msgid ""
"To create actual shipments using the default delivery methods, the test "
"credentials must be replaced with credentials from a valid USPS account."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette faktiske forsendelser ved hjælp af standardleveringsmetoderne "
"skal testlegitimationsoplysningerne erstattes med legitimationsoplysninger "
"fra en gyldig USPS-konto."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:62
msgid ""
"Open or create a new delivery method. Navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory "
"--> Configuration --> Delivery Methods`, then open an existing USPS delivery "
"method to display its form. Alternatively, click :guilabel:`New` to open a "
"blank form and configure a new delivery method."
msgstr ""
"Åbn eller opret en ny leveringsmetode. Gå til :menuselection:`Lager --> "
"Konfiguration --> Leveringsmetoder`, og åbn derefter en eksisterende USPS-"
"leveringsmetode for at vise dens formular. Alternativt kan du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Ny` for at åbne en tom formular og konfigurere en ny "
"leveringsmetode."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:None
msgid "The USPS Domestic delivery method, fully configured."
msgstr "USPS Domestic-leveringsmetoden, fuldt konfigureret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:72
msgid ""
"The fields at the top of the delivery method form configure how the method "
"operates in Odoo. In the :guilabel:`Provider` field, select :guilabel:`USPS` "
"from the drop-down menu if it is not already selected."
msgstr ""
"Felterne øverst i leveringsmetodeformularen konfigurerer, hvordan metoden "
"fungerer i Odoo. I feltet :guilabel:`Udbyder` skal du vælge :guilabel:`USPS` "
"fra rullemenuen, hvis det ikke allerede er valgt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:76
msgid ""
"The remaining fields in this section are general to all delivery providers. "
"For details on how to fill them out, see :doc:`third_party_shipper`."
msgstr ""
"De resterende felter i dette afsnit er generelle for alle leveringsudbydere. "
"Se :doc:`third_party_shipper` for detaljer om, hvordan de udfyldes."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:82
msgid "USPS Configuration tab"
msgstr "Fanen USPS Configuration"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:84
msgid ""
"The options in the *USPS Configuration* tab are used to connect the method "
"to a USPS account and to configure the delivery details associated with it."
msgstr ""
"Indstillingerne på fanen *USPS Configuration* bruges til at forbinde metoden "
"til en USPS-konto og til at konfigurere de leveringsdetaljer, der er knyttet "
"til den."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:87
msgid "Fill out the following fields in the form:"
msgstr "Udfyld følgende felter i formularen:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`EPS Number`: The Enterprise Payment System (EPS) account number "
"identifies the payment account and is used for electronic funds transfers. "
"After a payment account is added in the |COP| tool, the EPS number will "
"display, or it can be retrieved from the `USPS Business Customer Gateway "
"<https://epay.usps.com/paymod/>`_."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`EPS Number`: Enterprise Payment System (EPS)-kontonummeret "
"identificerer betalingskontoen og bruges til elektroniske pengeoverførsler. "
"Når en betalingskonto er tilføjet i |COP|-værktøjet, vises EPS-nummeret, "
"eller det kan hentes fra `USPS Business Customer Gateway <https://"
"epay.usps.com/paymod/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`CRID`: The CRID is a number that identifies the physical business "
"address across all USPS systems and applications."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`CRID`: CRID er et nummer, der identificerer den fysiske "
"forretningsadresse på tværs af alle USPS-systemer og -applikationer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`MID`: Fill in the :guilabel:`Master Mailer ID` listed in the |"
"COP|."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`MID`: Udfyld :guilabel:`Master Mailer ID`, som er angivet i |COP|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:96
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Manifest MID`: Fill in the :guilabel:`Label Mailer ID` listed in "
"the |COP|."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Manifest MID`: Udfyld :guilabel:`Label Mailer ID`, som er angivet "
"i |COP|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:97
msgid ""
":guilabel:`USPS API Key`: Enter the :guilabel:`Consumer Key` credential for "
"the app created in the USPS |COP| tool."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`USPS API Key`: Indtast "
"legitimationsoplysningen :guilabel:`Consumer Key` for den app, der er "
"oprettet i USPS |COP|-værktøjet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:99
msgid ""
":guilabel:`USPS API Secret`: Enter the :guilabel:`Consumer Secret` "
"credential for the app created in the USPS |COP| tool."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`USPS API Secret`: Indtast "
"legitimationsoplysningen :guilabel:`Consumer Secret` for den app, der er "
"oprettet i USPS |COP|-værktøjet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:101
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Label Format`: Select the file format that generated labels "
"should use."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Labeletiketformat`: Vælg det filformat, som genererede etiketter "
"skal bruge."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:102
msgid ""
":guilabel:`USPS Package Type`: Select or create the package type to use for "
"shipping."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`USPS-pakketype`: Vælg eller opret den pakketype, der skal bruges "
"til forsendelse."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:103
msgid ""
":guilabel:`USPS Domestic Service` or :guilabel:`USPS International Service`: "
"Select the service level that should be used to generate shipping labels."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`USPS indenrigs service` eller :guilabel:`USPS international "
"service`: Vælg det serviceniveau, der skal bruges til at generere "
"forsendelsesetiketter."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:105
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Nature`: Select whether the delivery method "
"is :guilabel:`Domestic` or :guilabel:`International`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Leveringstype`: Vælg om leveringsmetoden er :guilabel:`Indenrigs` "
"eller :guilabel:`International`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:107
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Content Type`: Select the type of content that will be shipped in "
"packages with this delivery method."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Indholdstype`: Vælg den indholdtype, der skal sendes i pakker med "
"denne leveringsmetode."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:110
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Options` section, configure the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"I afsnittet :guilabel:`Indstillinger` skal du konfigurere følgende felter:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Domestic Rating Indicator` or :guilabel:`International Rating "
"Indicator`: Select the rating indicator that works best for shipping needs. "
"USPS uses specific indicators, pricing groups, and automated classification "
"systems to distinguish between domestic and international shipments for "
"rating purposes. These systems help ensure accurate postage calculations "
"based on factors such as destination, package weight, dimensions, and "
"selected mail class."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Indenrigs vurderingsindikator` eller :guilabel:`International "
"vurgeringsindikator`: Vælg den vurderingsindikator, der passer bedst til "
"forsendelsesbehov. USPS bruger specifikke indikatorer, prisgrupper og "
"automatiserede klassificeringssystemer til at skelne mellem indenrigs og "
"internationale forsendelser til vurderingsformål. Disse systemer hjælper med "
"at sikre nøjagtige portoberegninger baseret på faktorer som destination, "
"pakkevægt, dimensioner og valgt postklasse."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:117
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Processing Category`: Select a packaging processing category."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Behandlingskategori`: Vælg en behandlingskategori for emballage."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Generate Return Label`: For domestic shipments only. Select this "
"checkbox to automatically generate a return label when the delivery is "
"validated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Generer returetiket`: Kun til indenrigs forsendelser. Marker "
"dette afkrydsningsfelt for automatisk at generere en returetiket, når "
"leveringen valideres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:122
msgid "Turn on the USPS delivery method"
msgstr "Aktivér USPS-leveringsmetoden"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:124
msgid ""
"After the USPS connection is set up, use the smart buttons at the top of the "
"form to publish, turn on production mode, or activate debug logging."
msgstr ""
"Når USPS-forbindelsen er oprettet, skal du bruge de smarte knapper øverst på "
"formularen til at udgive, aktivere produktionstilstand eller aktivere "
"fejllogning."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unpublished` / :guilabel:`Published`: Determines whether the "
"delivery method is available on the **eCommerce** website."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ikke udgivet` / :guilabel:`Udgivet`: Bestemmer om "
"leveringsmetoden er tilgængelig på **Webshop**-hjemmesiden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:129
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Test Environment` / :guilabel:`Production Environment`: "
"Determines whether the delivery method creates :guilabel:`Test` labels, "
"which are canceled immediately,  or :guilabel:`Production` labels, which are "
"real shipping labels charged to the USPS account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Testmiljø` / :guilabel:`Produktionsmiljø`: Bestemmer om "
"leveringsmetoden opretter :guilabel:`Test`-etiketter, som annulleres med det "
"samme, eller :guilabel:`Produktions`-etiketter, som er rigtige "
"forsendelsesetiketter, der debiteres USPS-kontoen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:132
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No Debug` / :guilabel:`Debug Requests`: Determines whether API "
"requests and responses are logged in Odoo (:doc:`turn on developer mode "
"<../../../../general/developer_mode>` and go to :menuselection:`Settings app "
"--> Technical --> Logging`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ingen fejlfinding` / :guilabel:`Fejlfind anmodninger`: Bestemmer "
"om API-anmodninger og -svar logges i Odoo (:doc:`aktivér udviklertilstand "
"<../../../../general/developer_mode>` og gå "
"til :menuselection:`Indstillinger-appen --> Teknisk --> Logning`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:3
msgid "Zebra label configuration"
msgstr "Zebra-etiketkonfiguration"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:7
msgid ""
"In Odoo, labels printed in the Zebra Programming Language (ZPL) file format "
"are designed to fit a four-by-six inch label. To resize (or reformat) text "
"to fit a variety of |ZPL| label sizes, :ref:`navigate to the ZPL label view "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/zpl-view>`, and alter the |ZPL| code."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo er etiketter, der udskrives i Zebra Programming Language (ZPL) "
"filformatet, designet til at passe til en fire gange seks tommer etiket. For "
"at ændre størrelse (eller omformatere) tekst, så den passer til forskellige |"
"ZPL| etiketstørrelser, skal du :ref:`navigere til ZPL-etiketvisningen "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/zpl-view>` og ændre |ZPL| koden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:13
msgid ""
"When customizing code in Odoo, please note that upgrading the database to "
"newer versions may break custom |ZPL| code. **Customers are responsible for "
"maintaining their custom code**."
msgstr ""
"Når kode tilpasses i Odoo, skal du være opmærksom på, at opgradering af "
"databasen til nyere versioner kan ødelægge tilpasset |ZPL| kode. **Kunder er "
"ansvarlige for at vedligeholde deres tilpassede kode**."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:16
msgid ""
"Refer to the following sections for explanations, and example code, for "
"frequently requested Zebra label customizations."
msgstr ""
"Se følgende afsnit for forklaringer og eksempelkode til ofte ønskede Zebra-"
"etikettilpasninger."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:19
msgid ":ref:`Adjust margins <inventory/shipping_receiving/margin>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Juster margener <inventory/shipping_receiving/margin>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:20
msgid ":ref:`Enlarge/minimize barcodes <inventory/shipping_receiving/resize>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Forstør/minimer stregkoder <inventory/shipping_receiving/resize>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:21
msgid ":ref:`Rotate elements <inventory/shipping_receiving/rotate>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Rotér elementer <inventory/shipping_receiving/rotate>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:26
msgid "Navigate to ZPL label view"
msgstr "Navigér til ZPL-etiketvisning"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:28
msgid ""
"To begin customizing a Zebra label in Odoo, turn on :ref:`developer mode "
"<developer-mode>`, and on the main Odoo dashboard, type `Reports`. From the "
"search results that appear in the resulting pop-up window, "
"choose :guilabel:`Settings / Technical / Reporting / Reports` to open "
"the :guilabel:`Reports` page."
msgstr ""
"For at begynde at tilpasse en Zebra-etiket i Odoo skal du "
"aktivere :ref:`udviklertilstand <developer-mode>`, og på Odoos "
"hoveddashboard skal du skrive `Reports`. Fra søgeresultaterne, der vises i "
"pop-up-vinduet, skal du vælge :guilabel:`Indstillinger / Teknisk / "
"Rapportering / Rapporter` for at åbne siden :guilabel:`Rapporter`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:34
msgid ""
"To manually navigate to the :guilabel:`Reports` page, go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> Reporting: Reports`."
msgstr ""
"For at navigere manuelt til siden :guilabel:`Rapporter` skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Indstillinger-app --> Teknisk --> Rapportering: "
"Rapporter`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:None
msgid "Show global search result for \"Reports\"."
msgstr "Vis globalt søgeresultat for \"Reports\"."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:41
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Reports` page, in the :guilabel:`Search...` bar, type "
"`ZPL`, and hit :kbd:`Enter`. Upon doing so, Odoo presents a list of "
"available Zebra labels in Odoo. Select the desired Zebra label from the list "
"to modify it on a separate page."
msgstr ""
"På siden :guilabel:`Rapporter` skal du i søgefeltet :guilabel:`Søg...` "
"skrive `ZPL` og trykke på :kbd:`Enter`. Herefter viser Odoo en liste over "
"tilgængelige Zebra-etiketter i Odoo. Vælg den ønskede Zebra-etiket fra "
"listen for at redigere den på en separat side."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:46
msgid "Printable ZPL labels in Odoo:"
msgstr "Printbare ZPL-etiketter i Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:48
msgid ":ref:`lot/serial number <inventory/shipping_receiving/lot-sn-labels>`"
msgstr ":ref:`parti-/serienummer <inventory/shipping_receiving/lot-sn-labels>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:49
msgid "operation type"
msgstr "operationstype"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:50
msgid "package barcode"
msgstr "pakkestregkode"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:51
msgid ":ref:`product label <inventory/shipping_receiving/product-labels>`"
msgstr ":ref:`produktetiket <inventory/shipping_receiving/product-labels>`"

