#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:110
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Max`: The maximum quantity at which the stock is replenished."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Max`: Den maksimale mængde, som lageret genopfyldes til."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:115
