"vælge |adjust| i øverste højre hjørne og vælge den ønskede kolonne fra "
"rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:142
msgid "0/0/1 reordering rule"
msgstr "0/0/1 genbestillingsregel"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:144
msgid ""
"The *0/0/1* reordering rule is a specialty rule used to replenish a product "
"that is not kept on-hand, each time a sales order (SO) is confirmed for that "
"product."
msgstr ""
"Genbestillingsreglen *0/0/1* er en specialregel, der bruges til at "
"genopfylde et produkt, som ikke opbevares på lager, hver gang en salgsordre "
"bekræftes for det pågældende produkt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:148
msgid ""
"The 0/0/1 reordering rule is similar to the *Replenish on Order (MTO)* "
"route, in that both workflows are used to replenish a product upon "
"confirmation of an |SO|."
msgstr ""
"0/0/1 genbestillingsreglen ligner ruten *Genopfyld ved ordre (MTO)*, idet "
"begge arbejdsgange bruges til at genopfylde et produkt ved bekræftelse af en "
"|SO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:151
msgid ""
"The main difference between the two methods is that the *Replenish on Order* "
"route automatically reserves the product for the |SO| that caused it to be "
"replenished. This means the product **cannot** be used for a different |SO|."
msgstr ""
"Den væsentligste forskel mellem de to metoder er, at ruten *Genopfyld ved "
"ordre* automatisk reserverer produktet til den |SO|, der forårsagede "
"genopfyldningen. Det betyder, at produktet **ikke kan** bruges til en anden |"
"SO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:155
msgid ""
"The 0/0/1 reordering rule does not have this limitation. A product "
"replenished using the rule is not reserved for any specific |SO|, and can be "
"used as needed."
msgstr ""
"0/0/1 genbestillingsreglen har ikke denne begrænsning. Et produkt genopfyldt "
"ved hjælp af reglen er ikke reserveret til nogen specifik |SO|, og kan "
"bruges efter behov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:158
msgid ""
"Another key difference is that replenishment orders created by the "
"*Replenish on Order* route are linked to the original |SO| by a smart button "
"at the top of the order. When using the 0/0/1 reordering rule, a "
"replenishment order is created, but is not linked to the original |SO|."
msgstr ""
"En anden væsentlig forskel er, at genbestillingsordrer oprettet af ruten "
"*Genopfyld ved ordre* er linket til den oprindelige |SO| via en smart knap "
"øverst på ordren. Ved brug af 0/0/1 genbestillingsreglen oprettes en "
"genbestillingsordre, men den er ikke linket til den oprindelige |SO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:162
msgid ""
"See the :doc:`Replenish on Order (MTO) <mto>` documentation for a full "
"overview of the MTO route."
msgstr ""
"Se dokumentationen :doc:`Genopfyld ved ordre (MTO) <mto>` for et fuldt "
"overblik over MTO-ruten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:164
msgid ""
"To create a 0/0/1 reordering rule, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app "
"--> Products --> Products`, and select a product."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en 0/0/1 genbestillingsregel skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Produkter --> Produkter` og vælge et "
"produkt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:167
msgid ""
"At the top of the product's page, click the :icon:`fa-"
"refresh` :guilabel:`Reordering Rules` smart button to open "
"the :guilabel:`Reordering Rules` page for the product. On the resulting "
"page, click :guilabel:`New` to begin configuring a new reordering rule."
msgstr ""
"Øverst på produktets side skal du klikke på den smarte knap :icon:`fa-"
"refresh` :guilabel:`Genbestillingsregler` for at åbne "
"siden :guilabel:`Genbestillingsregler` for produktet. På den viste side skal "
"du klikke på :guilabel:`Ny` for at begynde at konfigurere en ny "
"genbestillingsregel."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:171
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Location` field of the new reordering rule, select the "
"location in which replenished products should be stored. By default, this "
"location is set to :guilabel:`WH/Stock`."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Lokation` for den nye genbestillingsregel skal du vælge "
"den lokation, hvor genopfyldte produkter skal opbevares. Som standard er "
"denne lokation indstillet til :guilabel:`WH/Lager`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:174
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Route` field, select the route the rule should use to "
"replenish the item. For example, if the product should be purchased from a "
"vendor, select the :guilabel:`Buy` route."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Rute` skal du vælge den rute, reglen skal bruge til at "
"genopfylde varen. Hvis produktet f.eks. skal købes fra en leverandør, skal "
"du vælge ruten :guilabel:`Køb`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:177
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Min` field and :guilabel:`Max` field, leave the values set "
"to `0.00`. In the :guilabel:`To Order` field, enter a value of `1.00`."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Min` og feltet :guilabel:`Maks` skal værdierne forblive "
"sat til `0.00`. I feltet :guilabel:`Til bestilling` indtastes en værdi på "
"`1.00`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:None
msgid "A 0/0/1 reordering rule."
msgstr "En 0/0/1 genbestillingsregel."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:183
msgid ""
"With the reordering rule configured using these values, each time an |SO| "
"causes the forecasted quantity of the product to fall below "
"the :guilabel:`Min` of `0.00`, the selected :guilabel:`Route` is used to "
"replenish the product in one-unit increments, back up to the :guilabel:`Max` "
"of `0.00`."
msgstr ""
"Med genbestillingsreglen konfigureret med disse værdier vil den "
"valgte :guilabel:`Rute` blive brugt til at genopfylde produktet i "
"intervaller på en enhed, op til :guilabel:`Maks` på `0.00`, hver gang en |"
"SO| medfører, at den forventede mængde af produktet falder "
"under :guilabel:`Min` på `0.00`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:188
msgid ""
"An item is configured with a 0/0/1 reordering rule that uses the *Buy* "
"route. Zero units are kept on-hand at any given time."
msgstr ""
"En vare er konfigureret med en 0/0/1 genbestillingsregel, der bruger ruten "
"*Køb*. Der opbevares nul enheder på lager til enhver tid."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:191
msgid ""
"A |SO| is confirmed for one unit, which causes the forecasted quantity to "
"drop to `-1.00`. This triggers the reordering rule, which automatically "
"creates a |PO| for one unit."
msgstr ""
"En |SO| bekræftes for en enhed, hvilket medfører, at den forventede mængde "
"falder til `-1.00`. Dette udløser genbestillingsreglen, som automatisk "
"opretter en |PO| for en enhed."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:194
msgid ""
"Once the product is received from the vendor, the forecasted quantity "
"returns to `0.00`. There is now one unit on-hand, but it is not reserved for "
"the |SO| which triggered its purchase. It can be used to fulfill that |SO|, "
"or reserved for a different order."
msgstr ""
"Når produktet er modtaget fra leverandøren, vender den forventede mængde "
"tilbage til `0.00`. Der er nu en enhed på lager, men den er ikke reserveret "
"til den |SO|, som udløste købet. Den kan bruges til at opfylde den "
"pågældende |SO|, eller reserveres til en anden ordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:201
msgid "Multiple"
msgstr "Flere"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:203
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Multiple` field on the replenishment report "
"(:menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations --> Replenishment`) defines "
"the unit used when replenishing a product. Odoo rounds the ordered quantity "
"*up* to the nearest multiple that meets or slightly exceeds "
"the :guilabel:`Max` quantity set on the reordering rule. If no multiples "
"apply, select :guilabel:`Units`."
msgstr ""
"Feltet :guilabel:`Multiplum` i genopfyldningsrapporten "
"(:menuselection:`Lager-app --> Operationer --> Genopfyldning`) definerer den "
"enhed, der bruges ved genopfyldning af et produkt. Odoo runder den bestilte "
"mængde *op* til det nærmeste multiplum, der opfylder eller lidt "
"overstiger :guilabel:`Maks.`-mængden angivet i genbestillingsreglen. Hvis "
"ingen multipler gælder, skal du vælge :guilabel:`Enheder`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:209
msgid ""
"A vendor sells soda only in cases of six cans, but your company tracks "
"quantities per can. Setting the :guilabel:`Multiple` to `6` ensures soda is "
"ordered in multiples of six (6, 12, 18...)."
msgstr ""
"En leverandør sælger kun sodavand i kasser med seks dåser, men din "
"virksomhed sporer mængder pr. dåse. Ved at indstille :guilabel:`Multiplum` "
"til `6` sikres det, at sodavand bestilles i multipler af seks (6, 12, 18...)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:213
msgid ""
"For a reordering rule with the :guilabel:`Min` = `10` and :guilabel:`Max` = "
"`40`:"
msgstr ""
"For en genbestillingsregel med :guilabel:`Min` = `10` og :guilabel:`Maks.` = "
"`40`:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:215
msgid ""
"If the forecasted quantity is `10`, the amount :guilabel:`To Order` is `30`, "
"a multiple of six that will bring the :guilabel:`On Hand` quantity to "
"exactly the maximum."
msgstr ""
"Hvis den forventede mængde er `10`, er beløbet :guilabel:`At bestille` `30`, "
"et multiplum af seks, der vil bringe mængden :guilabel:`På lager` til præcis "
"maksimum."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:217
msgid ""
"If the forecasted quantity is `8`, the quantity needed to reach the max is "
"`32`. But 32 is not a multiple of six, so Odoo rounds the :guilabel:`To "
"Order` quantity up to `36`. This will cause the :guilabel:`On Hand` quantity "
"to slightly exceed the maximum."
msgstr ""
"Hvis den forventede mængde er `8`, er den mængde, der er nødvendig for at nå "
"maks., `32`. Men 32 er ikke et multiplum af seks, så Odoo runder "
"mængden :guilabel:`At bestille` op til `36`. Dette vil få "
"mængden :guilabel:`På lager` til at overstige maksimum en smule."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:0
msgid "Reordering rule with the Multiple set to 6."
msgstr "Genbestillingsregel med Multiplum indstillet til 6."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:225
msgid ""
"If the maximum is exceeded, expect to see a :icon:`fa-warning` warning "
"indicating the possibility of excessive stock."
msgstr ""
"Hvis maksimum overskrides, kan du forvente at se en :icon:`fa-warning`-"
"advarsel, der indikerer muligheden for overskydende lager."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:231
msgid ""
"Multiples are based on defined :doc:`packagings <../../product_management/"
"configure/packaging>`. Only packaging types listed on the "
"product's :doc:`vendor pricelist <../../../purchase/products/pricelist>` "
"appear as options in the :guilabel:`Multiple` field when configuring "
"reordering rules."
msgstr ""
"Multipler er baseret på definerede :doc:`emballager <../../"
"product_management/configure/packaging>`. Kun emballagetyper, der er anført "
"på produktets :doc:`leverandørprisliste <../../../purchase/products/"
"pricelist>`, vises som valgmuligheder i feltet :guilabel:`Multiplum`, når du "
"konfigurerer genbestillingsregler."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:239
msgid "Trigger"
msgstr "Trigger"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:241
msgid ""
"A reordering rule's *trigger* can be set to *automatic* or *manual*. While "
"both function the same way, the difference between the two types of "
"reordering rules is how the rule is launched:"
msgstr ""
"En genbestillingsregels *udløser* kan indstilles til *automatisk* eller "
"*manuel*. Selvom begge fungerer på samme måde, er forskellen mellem de to "
"typer genbestillingsregler, hvordan reglen aktiveres:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:244
msgid ""
":ref:`Auto <inventory/warehouses_storage/auto-rr>`: A purchase or "
"manufacturing order is automatically created when the forecasted stock falls "
"below the reordering rule's minimum quantity. By default, "
"the :guilabel:`Auto` trigger is selected."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Auto <inventory/warehouses_storage/auto-rr>`: En indkøbs- eller "
"produktionsordre oprettes automatisk, når den forventede lagerbeholdning "
"falder under genbestillingsreglens minimumsantal. Som standard er "
"udløseren :guilabel:`Auto` valgt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:247
msgid ""
":ref:`Manual <inventory/warehouses_storage/manual-rr>`: "
"The :doc:`Replenishment report <report>` lists products needing "
"replenishment, showing current/forecasted stock, lead times, and arrival "
"dates. Users can review forecasts before clicking *Order*."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Manuel <inventory/warehouses_storage/manual-"
"rr>`: :doc:`Genopfyldningsrapporten <report>` viser produkter, der har behov "
"for genopfyldning, med aktuel/forventet lagerbeholdning, leveringstider og "
"ankomstdatoer. Brugere kan gennemgå prognoser, før de klikker på *Bestil*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:251
msgid ""
"To enable the :guilabel:`Trigger` field, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app "
"--> Operations --> Replenishment`. Then, click the |adjust|, located to the "
"far-right of the column titles, and tick the :guilabel:`Trigger` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"For at aktivere feltet :guilabel:`Udløser` skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Handlinger --> Genopfyldning`. Klik "
"derefter på |adjust|, som findes helt til højre for kolonnetitlerne, og "
"marker afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Udløser`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:255
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Trigger` column, select :guilabel:`Auto` "
"or :guilabel:`Manual`. Refer to the sections below to learn about the "
"different types of reordering rules."
msgstr ""
"I kolonnen :guilabel:`Udløser` vælges :guilabel:`Auto` "
"eller :guilabel:`Manuel`. Se nedenstående afsnit for at lære om de "
"forskellige typer genbestillingsregler."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:261
msgid "Auto"
msgstr "Automatisk"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:263
msgid ""
"*Automatic reordering rules*, enabled by setting the reordering "
"rule's :guilabel:`Trigger` field to :guilabel:`Auto`, generate purchase or "
"manufacturing orders when either:"
msgstr ""
"*Automatiske genbestillingsregler*, aktiveret ved at indstille "
"genbestillingsreglens :guilabel:`Udløser`-felt til :guilabel:`Auto`, "
"genererer indkøbs- eller produktionsordrer, når enten:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:266
msgid ""
"The scheduler runs, and the *Forecasted* quantity is below the minimum, or"
msgstr "Planlæggeren kører, og den *Forventede* mængde er under minimum, eller"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:267
msgid ""
"A |SO| is confirmed, and lowers the *Forecasted* quantity of the product "
"below the minimum."
msgstr ""
"En |SO| bekræftes og sænker den *Forventede* mængde af produktet under "
"minimum."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:269
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Buy` route is selected, then an |RFQ| is generated. To "
"view and manage |RFQs|, navigate to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Orders "
"--> Requests for Quotation`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis ruten :guilabel:`Køb` er valgt, genereres en |RFQ|. For at se og "
"administrere |RFQs| skal du gå til :menuselection:`Indkøb-app --> Ordrer --> "
"Tilbudsanmodninger`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:272
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Manufacture` route is selected, then an |MO| is generated. "
"To view and manage |MOs|, navigate to :menuselection:`Manufacturing app --> "
"Operations --> Manufacturing Orders`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis ruten :guilabel:`Producér` er valgt, genereres en |MO|. For at se og "
"administrere |MOs| skal du gå til :menuselection:`Produktion-app --> "
"Handlinger --> Produktionsordrer`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:275
msgid ""
"When no route is selected, Odoo selects the :guilabel:`Route` specified in "
"the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab of the product form."
msgstr ""
"Når ingen rute er valgt, vælger Odoo den :guilabel:`Rute`, der er angivet i "
"fanen :guilabel:`Lager` på produktformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:279
msgid "The scheduler is set to run once a day, by default."
msgstr "Planlæggeren er som standard indstillet til at køre en gang om dagen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:281
msgid ""
"To manually trigger a reordering rule before the scheduler runs, "
"ensure :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` is enabled, and "
"select :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations --> Run Scheduler`. "
"Then, click the purple :guilabel:`Run Scheduler` button on the pop-up window "
"that appears."
msgstr ""
"For at udløse en genbestillingsregel manuelt, før planlæggeren kører, skal "
"du sikre, at :ref:`udviklertilstand <developer-mode>` er aktiveret, og "
"vælge :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Handlinger --> Kør planlægger`. Klik "
"derefter på den lilla knap :guilabel:`Kør planlægger` i pop op-vinduet, der "
"vises."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:286
msgid "Be aware that this also triggers any other scheduled actions."
msgstr ""
"Vær opmærksom på, at dette også udløser alle andre planlagte handlinger."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:289
msgid ""
"The product, `Office Lamp`, has an automatic reordering rule set to trigger "
"when the forecasted quantity falls below the :guilabel:`Min Quantity` of "
"`5.00`. Since the current :guilabel:`Forecast` is `55.00`, the reordering "
"rule is **not** triggered."
msgstr ""
"Produktet `Office Lamp` har en automatisk genbestillingsregel sat til at "
"udløse, når den forventede mængde falder under :guilabel:`Min. mængde` på "
"`5,00`. Da den aktuelle :guilabel:`Prognose` er `55,00`, udløses "
"genbestillingsreglen **ikke**."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:0
msgid "Show automatic reordering rule from the Reordering Rule page."
msgstr "Vis automatisk genbestillingsregel fra siden Genbestillingsregler."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:299
msgid "Manual"
msgstr "Manuel"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:301
msgid ""
"*Manual reordering rules*, configured by setting the reordering "
"rule's :guilabel:`Trigger` field to :guilabel:`Manual`, list a product on "
"the :doc:`replenishment dashboard <report>` when the forecasted quantity "
"falls below a specified minimum. Products on this dashboard are called "
"*needs*, because they are needed to fulfill upcoming |SOs|, for which the "
"forecasted quantity is not enough."
msgstr ""
"*Manuelle genbestillingsregler*, der konfigureres ved at sætte "
"genbestillingsreglens :guilabel:`Udløser`-felt til :guilabel:`Manuel`, viser "
"et produkt på :doc:`genopfyldningsdashboardet <report>`, når den forventede "
"mængde falder under et angivet minimum. Produkter på dette dashboard kaldes "
"*behov*, fordi de er nødvendige for at opfylde kommende |SOs|, hvor den "
"forventede mængde ikke er nok."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:306
msgid ""
"The replenishment dashboard, accessible by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations --> Replenishment`, "
"considers order deadlines, forecasted stock levels, and lead times. It "
"displays needs **only** when it is time to reorder items, thanks to "
"the :guilabel:`To Reorder` filter."
msgstr ""
"Genopfyldningsdashboardet, tilgængeligt ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Handlinger --> Genopfyldning`, tager højde "
"for ordredeadlines, forventede lagerniveauer og leveringstider. Det viser "
"behov **kun**, når det er tid til at genbestille varer, takket være "
"filteret :guilabel:`Til genbestilling`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:311
msgid ""
"When a product appears on the replenishment dashboard, clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Order` button generates the purchase or manufacturing order "
"with the specified amounts :guilabel:`To Order`."
msgstr ""
"Når et produkt vises på genopfyldningsdashboardet, genererer et klik på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Bestil` indkøbs- eller produktionsordren med de angivne "
"mængder :guilabel:`Til bestilling`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:None
msgid ""
"Click the Order button on the replenishment dashboard to replenish stock."
msgstr ""
"Klik på knappen Bestil på genopfyldningsdashboardet for at genopfylde "
"lageret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:320
msgid "Route"
msgstr "Rute"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:322
msgid ""
"Odoo allows for multiple routes to be selected as replenishment methods "
"under the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab on each product form. For instance, it "
"is possible to select both :guilabel:`Buy` and :guilabel:`Manufacture`, "
"indicating to Odoo that the product can be bought or manufactured."
msgstr ""
"Odoo giver mulighed for at vælge flere ruter som genopfyldningsmetoder under "
"fanen :guilabel:`Lager` på hver produktformular. For eksempel er det muligt "
"at vælge både :guilabel:`Køb` og :guilabel:`Fremstil`, hvilket indikerer til "
"Odoo, at produktet kan købes eller fremstilles."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:328
msgid ""
":ref:`Set route on product form <inventory/warehouses_storage/set-method>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Angiv rute på produktformular <inventory/warehouses_storage/set-"
"method>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:330
msgid ""
"Odoo also enables users to set a preferred route for a product's reordering "
"rule. This is the replenishment method (e.g., buying or manufacturing) that "
"the rule defaults to, if multiple are available."
msgstr ""
"Odoo giver også brugere mulighed for at angive en foretrukken rute for et "
"produkts genbestillingsregel. Dette er genopfyldningsmetoden (f.eks. køb "
"eller fremstilling), som reglen som standard bruger, hvis flere er "
"tilgængelige."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:334
msgid ""
"To specify a preferred route, begin by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations --> Replenishment`."
msgstr ""
"For at angive en foretrukken rute skal du starte med at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Handlinger --> Genopfyldning`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:337
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`Route` column is hidden. To reveal it, select the "
"|adjust| to the far-right of the column titles, and "
"ticking :guilabel:`Route` from the drop-down menu that appears."
msgstr ""
"Som standard er kolonnen :guilabel:`Rute` skjult. For at vise den skal du "
"vælge |adjust| helt til højre for kolonnetitlerne og sætte flueben "
"ved :guilabel:`Rute` fra rullemenuen, der vises."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:340
msgid ""
"Click inside of the column on the row of a reordering rule, and a drop-down "
"menu shows all available routes for that rule. Select one to set it as the "
"preferred route."
msgstr ""
"Klik inde i kolonnen på rækken for en genbestillingsregel, og en rullemenu "
"viser alle tilgængelige ruter for den regel. Vælg en for at angive den som "
"den foretrukne rute."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:None
msgid "Select a preferred route from the drop-down."
msgstr "Vælg en foretrukken rute fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:347
msgid ""
"If multiple routes are enabled for a product but no preferred route is set "
"for its reordering rule, the product is reordered using the *Buy* route, "
"then *Manufacture*."
msgstr ""
"Hvis flere ruter er aktiveret for et produkt, men ingen foretrukken rute er "
"angivet for dets genbestillingsregel, genbestilles produktet ved hjælp af "
"ruten *Køb*, derefter *Fremstil*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:351
msgid "Advanced uses"
msgstr "Avanceret brug"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:353
msgid ""
"Pairing :guilabel:`Route` with one of the following fields on the "
"replenishment report unlocks advanced configurations of reordering rules. "
"Consider the following:"
msgstr ""
"Kombination af :guilabel:`Rute` med et af følgende felter på "
"genopfyldningsrapporten låser op for avancerede konfigurationer af "
"genbestillingsregler. Overvej følgende:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:358
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Vendor`: When the selected :guilabel:`Route` is :guilabel:`Buy`, "
"setting the :guilabel:`Vendor` field to one of the multiple vendors on the "
"vendor pricelist indicates to Odoo that the vendor is automatically "
"populated on |RFQs| when a reordering rule triggers the creation of a "
"purchase order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Leverandør`: Når den valgte :guilabel:`Rute` er :guilabel:`Køb`, "
"angiver indstilling af feltet :guilabel:`Leverandør` til en af flere "
"leverandører på leverandørprislisten til Odoo, at leverandøren automatisk "
"udfyldes på |RFQs|, når en genbestillingsregel udløser oprettelse af en "
"indkøbsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:365
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bill of Materials`: When the :guilabel:`Route` is set "
"to :guilabel:`Manufacture`, and there are multiple |BoMs| in use, specifying "
"the desired |BoM| in the replenishment report, draft manufacturing orders "
"are created with this |BoM| in use."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Stykliste`: Når :guilabel:`Rute` er sat til :guilabel:`Fremstil`, "
"og der er flere |BoMs| i brug, vil angivelse af den ønskede |BoM| i "
"genopfyldningsrapporten oprette kladdeproduktionsordrer med denne |BoM| i "
"brug."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:371
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Procurement Group`: This is a way to group related |POs| or |MOs| "
"that are tied to fulfilling a specific demand, like an |SO| or a project. It "
"helps organize and track which orders are linked to a particular demand."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Indkøbsgruppe`: Dette er en måde at gruppere relaterede |POs| "
"eller |MOs|, der er knyttet til opfyldelse af et specifikt behov, som en |"
"SO| eller et projekt. Det hjælper med at organisere og spore, hvilke ordrer "
"der er knyttet til et bestemt behov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:376
msgid ""
"Procurement groups link replenishment methods to demand, making smart "
"buttons to appear — similar to how smart buttons appear when using "
"the :doc:`MTO route <mto>`."
msgstr ""
"Indkøbsgrupper linker genopfyldningsmetoder til behov, hvilket gør, at "
"smarte knapper vises — på samme måde som smarte knapper vises, når du "
"bruger :doc:`MTO-ruten <mto>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:0
msgid "Showing smart button to PO."
msgstr "Visning af smart-knap til IO."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:382
msgid ""
"Sales order (demand) with a smart button linking to the related purchase "
"order (replenishment method)."
msgstr ""
"Salgsordre (efterspørgsel) med en smart-knap, der linker til den relaterede "
"indkøbsordre (genopfyldningsmetode)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:385
msgid "In the context of reordering rules:"
msgstr "I forbindelse med genbestillingsregler:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:387
msgid ""
"Reordering rules do not automatically assign a procurement group, which is "
"why there are no smart buttons that link |SOs| to |POs|, unlike "
"the :abbr:`MTO (Make to Order)` route."
msgstr ""
"Genbestillingsregler tildeler ikke automatisk en indkøbsgruppe, hvilket er "
"grunden til, at der ikke er smart-knapper, der linker |SOs| til |POs|, i "
"modsætning til :abbr:`MTO (Make to Order)` ruten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:389
msgid ""
"To enable smart buttons for products replenished by reordering rules "
"(not :abbr:`MTO (Make to Order)`), with specific quantities linked to "
"specific demands (e.g. |SOs|), assign a procurement group."
msgstr ""
"For at aktivere smart-knapper for produkter, der genopfyldes ved hjælp af "
"genbestillingsregler (ikke :abbr:`MTO (Make to Order)`), med specifikke "
"mængder linket til specifikke efterspørgsler (f.eks. |SOs|), skal du tildele "
"en indkøbsgruppe."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:392
msgid ""
"Without a procurement group, demands for the same product can be combined "
"into a single |RFQ|, even if the reordering rule is executed multiple times "
"for those demands. This allows for more efficient procurement by "
"consolidating demands into fewer orders."
msgstr ""
"Uden en indkøbsgruppe kan efterspørgsler efter samme produkt kombineres i en "
"enkelt |RFQ|, selvom genbestillingsreglen udføres flere gange for disse "
"efterspørgsler. Dette giver mulighed for mere effektiv indkøb ved at "
"konsolidere efterspørgsler i færre ordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:396
msgid ""
"Selecting a procurement group in the :guilabel:`Procurement Group` field on "
"the replenishment report ensures that all linked orders are grouped under "
"the same demand, based on the defined route."
msgstr ""
"Valg af en indkøbsgruppe i feltet :guilabel:`Indkøbsgruppe` på "
"genopfyldningsrapporten sikrer, at alle linkede ordrer grupperes under samme "
"efterspørgsel baseret på den definerede rute."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:401
msgid ""
"How can you set the *Procurement Group*, *Vendor*, and *Route* fields on the "
"replenishment report to generate a single |RFQ| for five different products "
"in sales order SO35, given they share the same vendor, Azure Interior, and "
"ensure other demands for these products are handled separately?"
msgstr ""
"Hvordan kan du indstille felterne *Indkøbsgruppe*, *Leverandør* og *Rute* på "
"genopfyldningsrapporten til at generere en enkelt |RFQ| for fem forskellige "
"produkter i salgsordre SO35, givet at de deler samme leverandør, Azure "
"Interior, og sikre at andre efterspørgsler efter disse produkter håndteres "
"separat?"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:408
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Procurement Group` to `SO35`, in the reordering rule for "
"all five products. This groups the demands for `SO35` in the same |RFQ| or |"
"MO|."
msgstr ""
"Indstil :guilabel:`Indkøbsgruppe` til `SO35` i genbestillingsreglen for alle "
"fem produkter. Dette grupperer efterspørgslerne for `SO35` i samme |RFQ| "
"eller |MO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:410
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Vendor` to `Azure Interior` to ensure the |RFQ| is "
"created for the same supplier."
msgstr ""
"Indstil :guilabel:`Leverandør` til `Azure Interior` for at sikre, at |RFQ| "
"oprettes til samme leverandør."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:412
msgid "Set the :guilabel:`Route` to :guilabel:`Buy` to generate an |RFQ|."
msgstr "Indstil :guilabel:`Rute` til :guilabel:`Køb` for at generere en |RFQ|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:413
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Order` button to generate a single |RFQ| for the five "
"products tied to `SO35`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på knappen :guilabel:`Bestil` for at generere en enkelt |RFQ| for de "
"fem produkter knyttet til `SO35`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:0
msgid ""
"After placing the order, remove `SO35` from the :guilabel:`Procurement "
"Group` field of the five products' reordering rules. This ensures future "
"demands for these products are managed separately and assigned to different |"
"RFQs| (the usual behavior)."
msgstr ""
"Efter placering af ordren skal du fjerne `SO35` fra "
"feltet :guilabel:`Indkøbsgruppe` i de fem produkters genbestillingsregler. "
"Dette sikrer, at fremtidige efterspørgsler efter disse produkter håndteres "
"separat og tildeles forskellige |RFQs| (den sædvanlige adfærd)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:421
msgid ":doc:`Just-in-time logic <just_in_time>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Just-in-time-logik <just_in_time>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:424
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:67
msgid "Horizon days"
msgstr "Horisontdage"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:426
msgid ""
"*Horizon days* allow users to extend the time window between today's date "
"and the forecasted date when calculating for the forecasted quantity. This "
"features allows users to plan and restock inventory proactively, rather than "
"following a just-in-time approach. The feature is meant to help users plan "
"replenishment in advance by increasing the :ref:`forecasted date <inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/forecasted-date>`."
msgstr ""
"*Horisontdage* giver brugere mulighed for at udvide tidsvinduet mellem dags "
"dato og den forventede dato, når der beregnes for den forventede mængde. "
"Denne funktion giver brugere mulighed for at planlægge og genopfylde lager "
"proaktivt i stedet for at følge en just-in-time-tilgang. Funktionen er "
"beregnet til at hjælpe brugere med at planlægge genopfyldning på forhånd ved "
"at øge den :ref:`forventede dato <inventory/warehouses_storage/forecasted-"
"date>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:432
msgid ""
"\\text{Forecasted date} = \\text{Current date} + \\text{Vendor Lead Time} + "
"\\text{Horizon Days}"
msgstr ""
"\\text{Forventet dato} = \\text{Aktuel dato} + \\text{Leverandørens "
"leveringstid} + \\text{Horisontdage}"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:437
msgid ""
"Since horizon days are only meant to be used with manual reordering rules, "
"find details about the feature in the :doc:`Replenishment report article "
"<report>`."
msgstr ""
"Da horisontdage kun er beregnet til brug med manuelle genbestillingsregler, "
"finder du detaljer om funktionen i :doc:`artiklen om genopfyldningsrapport "
"<report>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:441
msgid "Horizon days are configured on a company level."
msgstr "Horisontdage konfigureres på virksomhedsniveau."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:443
msgid ""
"The default horizon days setting can be set or updated by navigating to "
"the :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Advanced Scheduling`. Enter the "
"desired number of days in the :guilabel:`Replenishment Horizon` field, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Standardindstillingen for horisontdage kan indstilles eller opdateres ved at "
"navigere til :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Avanceret planlægning`. Indtast "
"det ønskede antal dage i feltet :guilabel:`Genopfyldningshorisont`, og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:None
msgid "The Replenishment Horizon setting in the Inventory app."
msgstr "Indstillingen Genopfyldningshorisont i Lager-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:451
msgid "Example of how horizon days affect replenishment planning"
msgstr "Eksempel på, hvordan horisontdage påvirker genopfyldningsplanlægning"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:453
msgid ""
"On the Replenishment report, there are currently two products listed due for "
"reordering: `Drawer, Black` and `Corner Desk`. This is based on their "
"current level of on-hand stock, and their forecasted stock level. The "
"default horizon days is set as `20`."
msgstr ""
"I genopfyldningsrapporten er der i øjeblikket anført to produkter, der skal "
"genbestilles: `Drawer, Black` og `Corner Desk`. Dette er baseret på deres "
"nuværende lagerbeholdning og deres forventede lagerniveau. "
"Standardhorisontdagene er indstillet til `20`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:None
msgid "Replenishment report with horizon days set at 20."
msgstr "Genopfyldningsrapport med horisontdage indstillet til 20."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:460
msgid ""
"However, by extending the horizon days to `30`, an additional product is "
"added to the list."
msgstr ""
"Ved at udvide horisontdagene til `30` tilføjes der dog et ekstra produkt til "
"listen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:None
msgid "Replenishment report with horizon days set at 30."
msgstr "Genopfyldningsrapport med horisontdage indstillet til 30."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:465
msgid ""
"This is because the additional product, `[FURN_0789] Individual Workplace`, "
"has a delivery scheduled in twenty-nine days, at which point their on-hand "
"stock levels will fall below the minimum needed on-hand."
msgstr ""
"Dette skyldes, at det ekstra produkt, `[FURN_0789] Individual Workplace`, "
"har en levering planlagt om niogtyve dage, hvorefter deres lagerbeholdning "
"vil falde under det minimum, der er nødvendigt på lager."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:3
msgid "Replenishment report"
msgstr "Genopfyldningsrapport"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:8
msgid ""
"The *replenishment report* is an interactive dashboard that "
"uses :doc:`manual reordering rules <reordering_rules>`, lead times, and "
"upcoming demands to forecast quantities of products that need restocking."
msgstr ""
"*Genbestillingsrapporten* er et interaktivt dashboard, der "
"bruger :doc:`manuelle genbestillingsregler <reordering_rules>`, "
"leveringstider og kommende behov til at forudsige mængder af produkter, der "
"skal genbestilles."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:12
msgid ""
"Reordering rules used on this dashboard are normal reordering rules, but the "
"user benefits from a monitoring menu with extra options to manage "
"suggestions for replenishment."
msgstr ""
"*Genbestillingsregler*, der bruges på dette dashboard, er normale "
"genbestillingsregler, men brugeren drager fordel af en overvågningsmenu med "
"ekstra muligheder for at administrere forslag til genbestilling."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:15
msgid ""
"This enables users to anticipate future needs, keep less products on hand "
"without the risk of running out, plan and consolidate orders."
msgstr ""
"Dette gør det muligt for brugere at forudse fremtidige behov, have færre "
"produkter på lager uden risiko for at løbe tør, planlægge og konsolidere "
"ordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:19
msgid "Navigate the replenishment report"
msgstr "Navigere i genbestillingsrapporten"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:21
msgid ""
"To access the replenishment report, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Operations --> Replenishment.`"
msgstr ""
"For at få adgang til genbestillingsrapporten skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Lager-appen --> Operationer --> Genbestilling.`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:25
msgid ""
"Automatic reordering rules are available on this menu as well, but are "
"hidden by default."
msgstr ""
"Automatiske genbestillingsregler er også tilgængelige i denne menu, men er "
"skjult som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:27
msgid ""
"The fields and features unique to the replenishment dashboard are displayed "
"below. For definitions of the other fields, go to the :ref:`Create "
"reordering rules section <inventory/warehouses_storage/rr-fields>`."
msgstr ""
"Felterne og funktionerne, der er unikke for genbestillingsdashboardet, vises "
"nedenfor. For definitioner af de andre felter skal du gå til :ref:`afsnittet "
"Opret genbestillingsregler <inventory/warehouses_storage/rr-fields>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:31
msgid ""
"By default, the quantity in the :guilabel:`To Order` field is the quantity "
"required to reach the set :guilabel:`Max Quantity`. However, "
"the :guilabel:`To Order` quantity can be adjusted by clicking on the field "
"and changing the value. To replenish a product manually, click :icon:`fa-"
"truck` :guilabel:`Order`."
msgstr ""
"Som standard er mængden i feltet :guilabel:`At bestille` den mængde, der "
"kræves for at nå den indstillede :guilabel:`Maks. mængde`. Dog kan "
"mængden :guilabel:`At bestille` justeres ved at klikke på feltet og ændre "
"værdien. For at genbestille et produkt manuelt skal du klikke på :icon:`fa-"
"truck` :guilabel:`Bestil`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:36
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-bell-slash` :guilabel:`Snooze` to temporarily deactivate the "
"reordering rule for the set period, hiding the entry from the replenishment "
"dashboard, when it is supposed to appear."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :icon:`fa-bell-slash` :guilabel:`Slumre` for midlertidigt at "
"deaktivere genbestillingsreglen i den angivne periode, hvilket skjuler "
"posten fra genbestillingsdashboardet, når den forventes at vises."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:40
msgid ""
"Defining a :guilabel:`Vendor` allows filtering or grouping demands by the "
"vendor. This simplifies the process of identifying products to order and can "
"reduce shipment costs. Click the :icon:`oi-settings-"
"adjust` :guilabel:`(adjust settings)` icon and select :guilabel:`Vendor` "
"from the drop-down list to view the field on the report."
msgstr ""
"Definition af en :guilabel:`Leverandør` gør det muligt at filtrere eller "
"gruppere behov efter leverandøren. Dette forenkler processen med at "
"identificere produkter, der skal bestilles, og kan reducere "
"forsendelsesomkostningerne. Klik på ikonet :icon:`oi-settings-"
"adjust` :guilabel:`(juster indstillinger)` og vælg :guilabel:`Leverandør` "
"fra rullelisten for at se feltet i rapporten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:None
msgid "Replenishment report that displays recommended quantities to order."
msgstr "Genbestillingsrapport, der viser anbefalede mængder at bestille."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:49
msgid "Order to max"
msgstr "Bestil til maks."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:51
msgid ""
"If a reordering rule does not forecast the product to arrive below the "
"minimum, the replenishment cannot be triggered, because it is seen as "
"*unnecessary*. However, there can be instances where a product needs to be "
"replenished even if it is not deemed *necessary*, such as when an order "
"needs to be maximized to obtain better discounts, or to save on delivery "
"costs."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en genbestillingsregel ikke forudsiger, at produktet ankommer under "
"minimum, kan genbestillingen ikke udløses, fordi den ses som *unødvendig*. "
"Der kan dog være tilfælde, hvor et produkt skal genbestilles, selvom det "
"ikke anses for *nødvendigt*, f.eks. når en ordre skal maksimeres for at opnå "
"bedre rabatter eller spare på leveringsomkostninger."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:56
msgid ""
"First, select one or more products by ticking the appropriate checkbox. "
"Then, click the :guilabel:`Replenish` button and select :guilabel:`Order to "
"Max`. Doing so creates a request for quotation (RFQ) for the first possible "
"replenishment date for each product for the maximum specified in the "
"reordering rule."
msgstr ""
"Vælg først et eller flere produkter ved at markere det relevante "
"afkrydsningsfelt. Klik derefter på knappen :guilabel:`Genbestil` og "
"vælg :guilabel:`Bestil til maks.`. Dette opretter en anmodning om tilbud "
"(RFQ) for den først mulige genbestillingsdato for hvert produkt til det "
"maksimum, der er angivet i genbestillingsreglen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:None
msgid "The Order to Max option on the replenishment dashboard."
msgstr "Muligheden Bestil til maks. på genbestillingsdashboardet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:69
msgid ""
"*Horizon days* determine how many days ahead Odoo checks if the forecasted "
"quantity will drop below reordering rule's minimum. The feature is meant to "
"help users plan replenishment in advance, by increasing the :ref:`forecasted "
"date <inventory/warehouses_storage/forecasted-date>` on "
"the :doc:`replenishment report <report>`. Horizon days look ahead a "
"specified number of days and trigger reordering rules as soon as the "
"forecasted quantity falls below the minimum within that window, even if no "
"replenishment is needed today."
msgstr ""
"*Horisontdage* bestemmer, hvor mange dage frem Odoo kontrollerer, om den "
"forventede mængde vil falde under genbestillingsreglens minimum. Funktionen "
"er beregnet til at hjælpe brugere med at planlægge genopfyldning på forhånd "
"ved at øge den :ref:`forventede dato <inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"forecasted-date>` i :doc:`genopfyldningsrapporten <report>`. Horisontdage "
"ser frem et bestemt antal dage og udløser genbestillingsregler, så snart den "
"forventede mængde falder under minimum inden for det vindue, selvom der ikke "
"er behov for genopfyldning i dag."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:77
msgid ""
"Setting horizon days to `7` ensures all manual reordering rules set to "
"trigger within the next seven days appear on the replenishment report, "
"allowing users to review and decide which products to order in advance."
msgstr ""
"Indstilling af horisontdage til `7` sikrer, at alle manuelle "
"genbestillingsregler, der er indstillet til at udløse inden for de næste syv "
"dage, vises i genbestillingsrapporten, hvilket gør det muligt for brugere at "
"gennemgå og beslutte, hvilke produkter der skal bestilles på forhånd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:81
msgid ""
"To set horizon days, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations --> "
"Replenishment`, and click :icon:`fa-angle-double-right` :icon:`fa-"
"folder` :guilabel:`Manual` in the left sidebar. In the menu that appears, "
"set the number of :guilabel:`Horizon` days."
msgstr ""
"For at indstille horisontdage skal du gå til :menuselection:`Lager-appen --> "
"Operationer --> Genbestilling` og klikke på :icon:`fa-angle-double-"
"right` :icon:`fa-folder` :guilabel:`Manuel` i venstre sidebjælke. I den "
"menu, der vises, skal du indstille antallet af :guilabel:`Horisont`-dage."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:86
msgid "Current date: Feb 18"
msgstr "Aktuel dato: 18. feb."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:87
msgid "On hand quantity: 10"
msgstr "Lagerbeholdning: 10"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:88
msgid "Reordering rule: Min: 5, Max 10"
msgstr "Genbestillingsregel: Min: 5, Maks: 10"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:89
msgid "Vendor lead time: 1 day"
msgstr "Leverandørens leveringstid: 1 dag"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:91
msgid ""
"8 units are needed for an |SO| on Feb 23. That means, on Feb 23, there will "
"only be 2 units in stock."
msgstr ""
"8 enheder er nødvendige til en |SO| den 23. februar. Det betyder, at der den "
"23. februar kun vil være 2 enheder på lager."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/report.rst:94
msgid "**Without horizon days**"
msgstr "**Uden horisontdage**"

