msgstr ":doc:`Forskel mellem MTO og genbestillingsregler <../replenishment>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:24
msgid ""
"The initial configuration for both replenishment strategies is the same. "
"First go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"In the :guilabel:`Warehouse` section, activate :guilabel:`Storage "
"Locations`. Then, click :guilabel:`Save` to apply the setting."
msgstr ""
"Den indledende konfiguration er den samme for begge "
"genopfyldningsstrategier. Gå først til :menuselection:`Lager-app --> "
"Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`. I afsnittet :guilabel:`Lagersted` skal du "
"aktivere :guilabel:`Lagerlokationer`. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Gem` for "
"at anvende indstillingen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:None
msgid "Enable Storage Locations in Inventory settings."
msgstr "Aktivér lagerlokationer i lagerindstillingerne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:35
msgid ""
"Configure the settings for the central warehouse and connecting storage "
"locations by going to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> "
"Warehouses`."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurér indstillingerne for det centrale lagersted og tilsluttede "
"lagerlokationer ved at gå til :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Konfiguration --"
"> Lagersteder`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:39
msgid ""
"Each central warehouse and other locations *must* have its own warehouse. "
"For example, each shop is considered a local warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Hvert centralt lagersted og andre lokationer *skal* have sit eget lagersted. "
"For eksempel betragtes hver butik som et lokalt lagersted."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:42
msgid ""
"Select an existing warehouse, or create a new one to be resupplied from the "
"central warehouse, by clicking :guilabel:`New`. Then, give the warehouse a "
"name and a :guilabel:`Short Name`, which will appear on that warehouse's "
"transfers."
msgstr ""
"Vælg et eksisterende lagersted, eller opret et nyt, der skal genopfyldes fra "
"det centrale lagersted, ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Ny`. Giv derefter "
"lagerstedet et navn og et :guilabel:`Kort navn`, som vil vises på "
"lagerstedets overførsler."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:46
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Warehouse Configuration` tab, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Resupply From` field. Check the box next to the central "
"warehouse's name. If the warehouse can be resupplied by more than one "
"warehouse, make sure to check those warehouses' boxes too. Now, Odoo knows "
"which warehouses can resupply this warehouse."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Konfiguration af lagersted` skal du finde "
"feltet :guilabel:`Genopfyld fra`. Markér afkrydsningsfeltet ved siden af det "
"centrale lagersteds navn. Hvis lagerstedet kan genopfyldes af mere end ét "
"lagersted, skal du sørge for også at markere disse lagersteder. Nu ved Odoo, "
"hvilke lagersteder der kan genopfylde dette lagersted."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:52
msgid ""
"The central warehouse that will supply the shops is called `Central "
"warehouse`. The :guilabel:`Resupply From` field is set to this warehouse on "
"the shop's warehouse configuration page."
msgstr ""
"Det centrale lagersted, der leverer til butikkerne, hedder `Centralt "
"lagersted`. Feltet :guilabel:`Genopfyld fra` er indstillet til dette "
"lagersted på butikkens konfigurationsside for lagersted."

