"downloadede XML-fil. Alternativt kan brugere trække og slippe filen ind "
"i :guilabel:`Tilbud`-dashboardet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/edi.rst:113
msgid ""
"Doing so automatically generates a sales order with the customer populated "
"as the buyer and all product lines, quantities, and prices pre-filled. This "
"process ensures efficient and accurate data exchange between the two "
"databases."
msgstr ""
"Dette genererer automatisk en salgsordre med kunden udfyldt som køber og "
"alle produktlinjer, mængder og priser forudfyldt. Denne proces sikrer "
"effektiv og præcis dataudveksling mellem de to databaser."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/edi.rst:120
msgid "Uploaded SO in the seller's database."
msgstr "Uploadet SO i sælgerens database."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:3
msgid "Procurement expenses report"
msgstr "Rapport over indkøbsomkostninger"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:12
msgid ""
"With the *Purchase* application, users can monitor procurement expenses over "
"time. This report helps companies track and analyze spending, identify cost-"
"saving opportunities, and ensure efficient budget management."
msgstr ""
"Med *Indkøb*-applikationen kan brugere overvåge indkøbsomkostninger over "
"tid. Denne rapport hjælper virksomheder med at spore og analysere forbrug, "
"identificere muligheder for besparelser og sikre effektiv budgetstyring."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:17
msgid "Create procurement expenses report"
msgstr "Opret rapport over indkøbsomkostninger"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:19
msgid ""
"To create a |per|, first navigate to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> "
"Reporting --> Purchase` to open the :guilabel:`Purchase Analysis` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en |per| skal du først navigere til :menuselection:`Indkøb --"
"> Rapportering --> Indkøb` for at åbne :guilabel:`Indkøbsanalyse`-"
"dashboardet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:22
msgid ""
"By default, the dashboard displays a line chart overview of "
"the :guilabel:`Untaxed Total` of :guilabel:`Purchase Orders` (POs) with "
"a :guilabel:`Confirmation Date` for the current month, or of Requests for "
"Quotation (RFQs) with a status of *Draft*, *Sent*, or *Cancelled*."
msgstr ""
"Som standard viser dashboardet en linjediagramoversigt over :guilabel:`Beløb "
"ekskl. moms` for :guilabel:`Indkøbsordrer` (PO'er) med "
"en :guilabel:`Bekræftelsesdato` for den aktuelle måned, eller for "
"tilbudsanmodninger (RFQ'er) med status *Kladde*, *Sendt* eller *Annulleret*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:27
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:25
msgid "Add filters and groups"
msgstr "Tilføj filtre og grupperinger"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:29
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:27
msgid ""
"On the top-right, click the :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`(pivot)` icon "
"to switch to pivot view."
msgstr ""
"Øverst til højre skal du klikke på ikonet :icon:`oi-view-"
"pivot` :guilabel:`(pivot)` for at skifte til pivotvisning."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:32
msgid ""
"While the |per| can also be :ref:`viewed <purchase/view-results>` as "
"a :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`(bar chart)`, :icon:`fa-line-"
"chart` :guilabel:`(line chart)`, or :icon:`fa-pie-chart` :guilabel:`(pie "
"chart)`, the pivot view provides the most detailed view of the data, and is "
"the recommended starting point."
msgstr ""
"Selvom |per| også kan :ref:`vises <purchase/view-results>` som :icon:`fa-bar-"
"chart` :guilabel:`(søjlediagram)`, :icon:`fa-line-"
"chart` :guilabel:`(linjediagram)` eller :icon:`fa-pie-"
"chart` :guilabel:`(cirkeldiagram)`, giver pivotvisningen den mest "
"detaljerede visning af dataene og er det anbefalede udgangspunkt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:37
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:29
msgid ""
"Remove any default filters from the :guilabel:`Search...` bar. Then, click "
"the |caret| to open the drop-down menu that contains "
"the :guilabel:`Filters`, :guilabel:`Group By`, and :guilabel:`Favorites` "
"columns."
msgstr ""
"Fjern eventuelle standardfiltre fra søgefeltet :guilabel:`Søg...`. Klik "
"derefter på |caret| for at åbne rullemenuen, der indeholder "
"kolonnerne :guilabel:`Filtre`, :guilabel:`Gruppér efter` "
"og :guilabel:`Favoritter`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:42
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:34
msgid ""
"Unless otherwise specified, the report displays data from both |RFQs| and |"
"POs|. This can be changed by selecting either :guilabel:`Requests for "
"Quotation` or :guilabel:`Purchase Orders` under the :guilabel:`Filters` "
"column."
msgstr ""
"Medmindre andet er angivet, viser rapporten data fra både |RFQs| og |POs|. "
"Dette kan ændres ved at vælge enten :guilabel:`Tilbudsanmodninger` "
"eller :guilabel:`Indkøbsordrer` under kolonnen :guilabel:`Filtre`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:46
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Filters` column, select a time frame to use for "
"comparison. The report can be filtered by either :guilabel:`Order Date` "
"or :guilabel:`Confirmation Date`. Choose one from the list, and click the |"
"caret| to specify the date range, either by month, quarter, or year."
msgstr ""
"Under kolonnen :guilabel:`Filtre` skal du vælge en tidsramme, der skal "
"bruges til sammenligning. Rapporten kan filtreres efter "
"enten :guilabel:`Ordredato` eller :guilabel:`Bekræftelsesdato`. Vælg en fra "
"listen, og klik på |caret| for at angive datointervallet, enten efter måned, "
"kvartal eller år."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:50
msgid ""
"Next, under the :guilabel:`Group by` column, select :guilabel:`Vendor`. "
"Then, select :guilabel:`Product Category`, which is also located in "
"the :guilabel:`Group By` column."
msgstr ""
"Dernæst skal du under kolonnen :guilabel:`Gruppér efter` "
"vælge :guilabel:`Leverandør`. Vælg derefter :guilabel:`Produktkategori`, som "
"også findes i kolonnen :guilabel:`Gruppér efter`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:54
msgid ""
"The selections under the :guilabel:`Group By` heading can be altered, "
"depending on the needs of the individual company. For example, "
"selecting :guilabel:`Product`, instead of :guilabel:`Product Category`, "
"provides a more in depth look at the performance of specific items, in place "
"of an entire category."
msgstr ""
"Valgene under overskriften :guilabel:`Gruppér efter` kan ændres afhængigt af "
"den enkelte virksomheds behov. For eksempel giver valg "
"af :guilabel:`Produkt` i stedet for :guilabel:`Produktkategori` et mere "
"dybdegående indblik i specifikke varers præstation i stedet for en hel "
"kategori."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:59
msgid ""
"Next, make a selection under the :guilabel:`Comparison` heading that "
"appears. These options are only available after the date range is selected "
"under the :guilabel:`Filters` column, and vary based on that "
"range. :guilabel:`Previous Period` adds a comparison to the previous period, "
"such as the last month or quarter. :guilabel:`Previous Year` compares the "
"same time period from the previous year."
msgstr ""
"Dernæst skal du foretage et valg under "
"overskriften :guilabel:`Sammenligning`, der vises. Disse muligheder er kun "
"tilgængelige, efter datointervallet er valgt under "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Filtre`, og varierer baseret på dette "
"interval. :guilabel:`Forrige periode` tilføjer en sammenligning med den "
"forrige periode, såsom sidste måned eller kvartal. :guilabel:`Forrige år` "
"sammenligner samme tidsperiode fra det foregående år."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:65
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:60
msgid ""
"While multiple time-based filters can be added at once, only one comparison "
"can be selected at a time."
msgstr ""
"Selvom flere tidsbaserede filtre kan tilføjes på én gang, kan kun én "
"sammenligning vælges ad gangen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:73
msgid ""
"The drop-down menu of filters, group by and comparison options for the "
"procurement expenses\n"
"report."
msgstr ""
"Rullemenuen med filtre, gruppér efter og sammenligningsindstillinger til "
"rapporten over indkøbsomkostninger."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:73
msgid ""
"The filter for Q2, comparison for **Previous Period**, and group-by for "
"**Vendor** and **Product Category** were selected."
msgstr ""
"Filteret for Q2, sammenligning for **Forrige periode** og gruppering efter "
"**Leverandør** og **Produktkategori** blev valgt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:77
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:68
msgid "Add measures"
msgstr "Tilføj mål"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:79
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:70
msgid ""
"After selecting the :guilabel:`Filters`, :guilabel:`Group by`, "
"and :guilabel:`Comparison` settings, click out of the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Efter valg af indstillingerne :guilabel:`Filtre`, :guilabel:`Gruppér efter` "
"og :guilabel:`Sammenligning`, klik uden for rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:82
msgid ""
"By default, the report displays data with the following "
"measures: :guilabel:`Order`, :guilabel:`Total`, :guilabel:`Untaxed Total`, "
"and :guilabel:`Count`. Click :guilabel:`Measures` at the top-left to open "
"the drop-down list of available measures."
msgstr ""
"Som standard viser rapporten data med følgende "
"mål: :guilabel:`Ordre`, :guilabel:`Total`, :guilabel:`Total ekskl. moms` "
"og :guilabel:`Antal`. Klik på :guilabel:`Mål` øverst til venstre for at åbne "
"rullelisten over tilgængelige mål."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:86
msgid ""
"Click the following specific measures to include additional columns for the "
"procurement expenses report:"
msgstr ""
"Klik på følgende specifikke mål for at inkludere yderligere kolonner til "
"indkøbsomkostningsrapporten:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Total` and :guilabel:`Untaxed Total`: can include one or both "
"measures. These are included for overall spending analysis."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Total` og :guilabel:`Total ekskl. moms`: kan inkludere et eller "
"begge mål. Disse er inkluderet til overordnet forbrugsanalyse."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/procurement_expenses_report.rst:91
msgid ":guilabel:`Average Cost`: included to evaluate cost efficiency."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gennemsnitlig pris`: inkluderet til evaluering af "
"omkostningseffektivitet."

