":guilabel:`Gennemsnitlig ordreværdi`: angiver det gennemsnitlige "
"indkøbsbeløb pr. ordre i den valgte periode."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/purchase_dashboard.rst:47
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Number of orders`: indicates the number of purchase orders during "
"the selected period."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Antal ordrer`: angiver antallet af indkøbsordrer i den valgte "
