msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mest købte produkter`: viser de ti produkter med det højeste "
"samlede købsbeløb i faldende rækkefølge."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/purchase_dashboard.rst:92
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Purchase Orders by Buyer`: shows the percentage of purchases by "
"buyer."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Indkøbsordrer efter køber`: viser procentdelen af indkøb efter "
"køber."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:3
msgid "Suggest quantities based on historical demand"
msgstr "Foreslå antal baseret på historisk efterspørgsel"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:7
msgid ""
"For a straightforward push-based replenishment strategy, the *Suggest* "
"feature recommends quantities to order on requests for quotations (RFQs) "
"based on historical demand."
msgstr ""
"For en ligetil push-baseret genopfyldningsstrategi anbefaler funktionen "
"*Foreslå* mængder til bestilling på tilbudsanmodninger (RFQ'er) baseret på "
"historisk efterspørgsel."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:11
msgid "Key parameters"
msgstr "Nøgleparametre"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:13
msgid "*Replenish for*: future coverage window (days)."
msgstr "*Genopfyld til*: fremtidig dækningsperiode (dage)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:14
msgid ""
"*Based on*: period that defines historical demand: last 7 days, 30 days, 3 "
"months, 12 months, or the same month or quarter the previous year."
msgstr ""
"*Baseret på*: periode, der definerer historisk efterspørgsel: sidste 7 dage, "
"30 dage, 3 måneder, 12 måneder eller samme måned eller kvartal det "
"foregående år."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:16
msgid ""
"*Factor*: growth or decline factor (default 100%). After obtaining the total "
"from the period, multiply the historical demand by this percentage to "
"determine how much of the demand should be replenished. (e.g., input `120%` "
"if sales are projected to grow 20% more than the previous period)"
msgstr ""
"*Faktor*: vækst- eller faldsfaktor (standard 100%). Efter at have opnået "
"totalen fra perioden ganges den historiske efterspørgsel med denne "
"procentsats for at bestemme, hvor meget af efterspørgslen der skal "
"genopfyldes. (f.eks. indtast `120%`, hvis salget forventes at vokse 20% mere "
"end den foregående periode)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:21
msgid "Demand calculation"
msgstr "Efterspørgselsberegning"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:23
msgid ""
"To estimate demand, Odoo sums all :ref:`validated deliveries <inventory/"
"delivery/one-step>`, :ref:`components consumed in manufacturing orders "
"<manufacturing/basic_setup/setup-components>` (MOs), or used "
"to :doc:`resupply subcontractors <../../manufacturing/subcontracting/"
"subcontracting_resupply>` coming from the warehouse specified on the RFQ in "
"the *Based on* period. The *average daily demand* is this sum of outgoing "
"moves divided by the number of days in the *Based on* period, multiplied by "
"*Factor*. The *estimated demand* is the *average daily demand* multiplied by "
"*Replenish For* days."
msgstr ""
"For at estimere efterspørgslen summerer Odoo alle :ref:`validerede "
"leveringer <inventory/delivery/one-step>`, :ref:`komponenter forbrugt i "
"produktionsordrer <manufacturing/basic_setup/setup-components>` (MO'er) "
"eller brugt til at :doc:`genforsynes underleverandører <../../manufacturing/"
"subcontracting/subcontracting_resupply>`, der kommer fra det lager, der er "
"angivet på tilbudsanmodningen i perioden *Baseret på*. Den *gennemsnitlige "
"daglige efterspørgsel* er denne sum af udgående bevægelser divideret med "
"antallet af dage i perioden *Baseret på*, ganget med *Faktor*. Den "
"*estimerede efterspørgsel* er den *gennemsnitlige daglige efterspørgsel* "
"ganget med *Genopfyld for* dage."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:31
msgid ""
"Average~Daily~Demand = \\frac{Delivered~or~Consumed~Items}{Based~on~Days} "
"\\times Factor\n"
"\\\\ \\\\ Estimated~Demand = Average~Daily~Demand \\times Replenish~for~Days"
msgstr ""
"Average~Daily~Demand = \\frac{Delivered~or~Consumed~Items}{Based~on~Days} "
"\\times Factor\n"
"\\\\ \\\\ Estimated~Demand = Average~Daily~Demand \\times Replenish~for~Days"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:38
msgid ""
"Only :guilabel:`Assigned` or :guilabel:`Confirmed` moves are taken into "
"account in the *average daily demand* calculations, sales quotations or "
"manufacturing orders in :guilabel:`Draft` are not taken into account until "
"validated."
msgstr ""
"Kun :guilabel:`Tildelte` eller :guilabel:`Bekræftede` bevægelser tages i "
"betragtning i beregningerne af *gennemsnitlig daglig efterspørgsel*. "
"Salgstilbud eller produktionsordrer i :guilabel:`Kladde` tages ikke i "
"betragtning, før de valideres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:43
msgid ""
"In a multi-warehouse setup, internal deliveries are also counted in demand "
"estimation. In the case of a central warehouse dispatching products to "
"individual stores, the *average daily demand* of the central warehouse will "
"include internal transfers to individual stores."
msgstr ""
"I en opsætning med flere lagre tælles interne leveringer også med i "
"efterspørgselsestimatet. I tilfælde af et centralt lager, der afsender "
"produkter til individuelle butikker, vil den *gennemsnitlige daglige "
"efterspørgsel* for det centrale lager inkludere interne overførsler til "
"individuelle butikker."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:49
msgid "Recommended quantity"
msgstr "Anbefalet mængde"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:51
msgid ""
"To find the suggested quantity, Odoo deducts the *estimated demand* from the "
"current stock available quantity and all incoming shipments."
msgstr ""
"For at finde den foreslåede mængde trækker Odoo den *estimerede "
"efterspørgsel* fra den aktuelle tilgængelige lagerbeholdning og alle "
"indgående forsendelser."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:54
msgid ""
"Recommended~Quantity = Estimated~Demand - (Available~Stock + Incoming~Stock)"
msgstr ""
"Recommended~Quantity = Estimated~Demand - (Available~Stock + Incoming~Stock)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:60
msgid ""
"In :ref:`example 1 <purchase/advanced/example-suggestion>`, Odoo recommends "
"`19` units to *Replenish for* `14` days *Based on* the past month's `40` "
"delivered units."
msgstr ""
"I :ref:`eksempel 1 <purchase/advanced/example-suggestion>` anbefaler Odoo "
"`19` enheder til *Genopfyld til* `14` dage *Baseret på* den seneste måneds "
"`40` leverede enheder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:64
msgid "Prerequisite setup"
msgstr "Nødvendig opsætning"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:66
msgid ""
"**Purchase** and **Inventory** apps must be :ref:`installed <general/"
"install>`."
msgstr ""
"**Indkøb** og **Lager** apps skal være :ref:`installeret <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:67
msgid ""
":ref:`Validate at least one delivery order <inventory/delivery/one-step>` "
"for each product."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Valider mindst én leveringsordre <inventory/delivery/one-step>` for "
"hvert produkt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:69
msgid ""
"Ensures there is a past delivery record so the system can calculate average "
"daily demand."
msgstr ""
"Sikrer, at der er en tidligere leveringsregistrering, så systemet kan "
"beregne gennemsnitlig daglig efterspørgsel."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:71
msgid ""
":ref:`Add a vendor to the vendor pricelist <purchase/manage_deals/vendor-"
"pricelist>` with a purchase price for each product."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Tilføj en leverandør til leverandørprislisten <purchase/manage_deals/"
"vendor-pricelist>` med en indkøbspris for hvert produkt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:74
msgid ""
"The *Suggest* feature is vendor-specific, so each product needs a matching "
"vendor for accurate purchase quantity and price calculations."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen *Foreslå* er leverandørspecifik, så hvert produkt skal have en "
"matchende leverandør for nøjagtige beregninger af indkøbsmængde og pris."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:77
msgid ""
"Set the *Product Type* to *Goods* and ensure the product is :ref:`Tracked by "
"quantity <inventory/product_management/manufacture>`."
msgstr ""
"Sæt *Produkttype* til *Varer* og sørg for, at produktet er :ref:`Sporet "
"efter mængde <inventory/product_management/manufacture>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:80
msgid ""
"Ensures the system can manage stock levels and calculate recommended "
"replenishment quantities for tangible items."
msgstr ""
"Sikrer, at systemet kan håndtere lagerniveauer og beregne anbefalede "
"genopfyldningsmængder for håndgribelige varer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:84
msgid "Suggest quantities to order"
msgstr "Foreslå mængder til bestilling"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:86
msgid ""
"To suggest quantities based on past sales, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Purchase` app. Create a :guilabel:`New` |RFQ| or select "
"an existing one."
msgstr ""
"For at foreslå mængder baseret på tidligere salg skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Indkøb`-appen. Opret en :guilabel:`Ny` |RFQ| eller vælg "
"en eksisterende."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:89
msgid "In the |RFQ|, set the :guilabel:`Vendor` field to the chosen supplier."
msgstr ""
"I |RFQ| skal du sætte feltet :guilabel:`Leverandør` til den valgte "
"leverandør."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:91
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Products` tab, click the :guilabel:`Catalog` button to "
"view that vendor's items."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Produkter` skal du klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Katalog` "
"for at se den pågældende leverandørs varer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:94
msgid ""
"Verify that each product in the catalog is configured with the chosen vendor "
"and that the Purchase Order is in the |RFQ| stage"
msgstr ""
"Kontrollér, at hvert produkt i kataloget er konfigureret med den valgte "
"leverandør, og at indkøbsordren er i |RFQ|-fasen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:98
msgid ""
"By default, products listed in the product catalog are filtered by vendor."
msgstr "Som standard filtreres produkter i produktkataloget efter leverandør."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:100
msgid ""
"Remove the filter in the search bar to view all items or use the built-"
"in :icon:`oi-group` :guilabel:`Group By` for :guilabel:`Product Category`."
msgstr ""
"Fjern filteret i søgefeltet for at se alle varer, eller brug den "
"indbyggede :icon:`oi-group` :guilabel:`Gruppér efter` "
"for :guilabel:`Produktkategori`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:103
msgid ""
"Inside the :guilabel:`Catalog`, toggle :guilabel:`Suggest` in the left "
"sidebar to activate the feature. Complete its fields as follows:"
msgstr ""
"I :guilabel:`Katalog` skal du aktivere :guilabel:`Foreslå` i venstre "
"sidepanel for at aktivere funktionen. Udfyld felterne som følger:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:106
msgid ":guilabel:`Replenish for`: Number of days intended to stock products."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Genopfyld til`: Antal dage produkter er beregnet til at være på "
"lager."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:107
msgid ":guilabel:`Based on`: There are two inputs:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Baseret på`: Der er to indtastninger:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:109
msgid ""
"Period: select the time frame that represents historical demand "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`Last 30 Days`, :guilabel:`April 2024`)."
msgstr ""
"Periode: vælg den tidsramme, der repræsenterer historisk efterspørgsel "
"(f.eks. :guilabel:`Sidste 30 dage`, :guilabel:`April 2024`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:112
msgid ""
"Growth factor %: scale the demand up or down (e.g., 120% for 20% growth, 30% "
"for 70% drop)."
msgstr ""
"Vækstfaktor %: skalér efterspørgslen op eller ned (f.eks. 120 % for 20 % "
"vækst, 30 % for 70 % fald)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:114
msgid ""
"The total in the bottom shows the order value. Odoo multiplies the vendor's "
"*Unit Price* by the suggested quantity."
msgstr ""
"Totalen nederst viser ordreværdien. Odoo ganger leverandørens *enhedspris* "
"med den foreslåede mængde."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:117
msgid ""
"Once the parameters are confirmed, click :guilabel:`Add All` to add all "
"suggestions to the order. Adjust amounts if needed, then "
"click :guilabel:`Back to Quotation` to confirm the final numbers on the |"
"RFQ|."
msgstr ""
"Når parametrene er bekræftet, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj alle` for "
"at tilføje alle forslag til ordren. Justér beløbene, hvis det er nødvendigt, "
"og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Tilbage til tilbud` for at bekræfte de "
"endelige tal på |RFQ|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:124
msgid "Example Workflow"
msgstr "Eksempel på arbejdsgang"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:127
msgid "Recommend at 100% growth"
msgstr "Anbefal ved 100 % vækst"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:129
msgid ""
"A company needs to replenish orchids for 14 days, referencing the last 30 "
"days of historical data, assuming the revenue growth is the same this month, "
"at 100%."
msgstr ""
"En virksomhed skal genopfylde orkidéer i 14 dage med reference til de sidste "
"30 dages historiske data under antagelse af, at omsætningsvæksten er den "
"samme denne måned, på 100 %."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:132
msgid "Delivered/consumed within the period:"
msgstr "Leveret/forbrugt inden for perioden:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:134
msgid "20 units delivered 15 days ago in a `WH/OUT` operation."
msgstr "20 enheder leveret for 15 dage siden i en `WH/OUT`-operation."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:135
msgid "20 units delivered 1 day ago"
msgstr "20 enheder leveret for 1 dag siden"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:136
msgid "Total: 40 units in the last 30 days"
msgstr "I alt: 40 enheder i de sidste 30 dage"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:139
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:173
msgid "Variables"
msgstr "Variabler"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:141
msgid "Replenish for: 14 days"
msgstr "Genopfyld til: 14 dage"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:142
msgid "Based on: 30 days"
msgstr "Baseret på: 30 dage"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:144
msgid "total delivered/consumed in the period: 40 units"
msgstr "samlet leveret/forbrugt i perioden: 40 enheder"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:146
msgid "Factor: 100%"
msgstr "Faktor: 100 %"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:148
msgid "Average~Daily~Demand = \\frac{40}{30}  \\approx 1.33 \\text{ units/day}"
msgstr ""
"Gennemsnitlig~daglig~efterspørgsel = \\frac{40}{30}  \\approx 1,33 "
"\\text{ enheder/dag}"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:153
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:187
msgid "Suggested quantity"
msgstr "Foreslået antal"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:155
msgid ""
"Suggested~Quantity = 1.33 \\times 14 \\approx 18.67 \\text{ (rounded to 19 "
"units)}"
msgstr ""
"Foreslået~antal = 1,33 \\times 14 \\approx 18,67 \\text{ (afrundet til 19 "
"enheder)}"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:162
msgid "Suggestion to purchase 19 units."
msgstr "Forslag om at købe 19 enheder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:162
msgid ""
"Suggestion to purchase 19 orchids. Since the *Unit Price* is $3, :math:`$3 "
"\\times 19 = $57`, which is the total amount displayed."
msgstr ""
"Forslag om at købe 19 orkidéer. Da *enhedsprisen* er $3, :math:`$3 \\times "
"19 = $57`, hvilket er det samlede beløb, der vises."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:166
msgid "Planning for Mother's Day"
msgstr "Planlægning til mors dag"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:168
msgid ""
"To better plan for the upcoming Mother's day week, the company changes "
"*Based on* to the same month last year (May 2024). As the business has grown "
"since then, they also decide to add a 120% growth factor."
msgstr ""
"For bedre at planlægge den kommende uge med mors dag ændrer virksomheden "
"*Baseret på* til samme måned sidste år (maj 2024). Da forretningen er vokset "
"siden da, beslutter de også at tilføje en vækstfaktor på 120%."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:175
msgid "Replenish for 7 days"
msgstr "Genbestil i 7 dage"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:176
msgid "Based on: May 2024,"
msgstr "Baseret på: maj 2024,"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:178
msgid "total delivered/consumed in the entire May 2024 month: 361 units"
msgstr "i alt leveret/forbrugt i hele maj 2024-måneden: 361 enheder"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:180
msgid "Factor: 120%"
msgstr "Faktor: 120%"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:182
msgid ""
"Average~Daily~Demand = \\frac{361}{30} \\times 1.20 \\approx 14.44 "
"\\text{ units/day}"
msgstr ""
"Gennemsnitlig~daglig~efterspørgsel = \\frac{361}{30} \\times 1,20 \\approx "
"14,44 \\text{ enheder/dag}"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:189
msgid ""
"Suggested~Quantity = 14.44 \\times 7 \\approx 101.08 \\text{ (rounded up to "
"102 units)}"
msgstr ""
"Foreslået~mængde = 14,44 \\times 7 \\approx 101,08 \\text{ (rundet op til "
"102 enheder)}"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:196
msgid "Suggestion to purchase 102 orchids."
msgstr "Forslag om at købe 102 orkidéer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:196
msgid ""
"Suggestion to purchase 102 orchids. Each orchid costs $3 with the chosen "
"vendor, so :math:`$3 \\times 102 = $306`."
msgstr ""
"Forslag om at købe 102 orkidéer. Hver orkidé koster $3 hos den valgte "
"leverandør, så :math:`$3 \\times 102 = $306`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:202
msgid "Best practices"
msgstr "Bedste praksis"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:204
msgid "Validate historical data"
msgstr "Validér historiske data"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:206
msgid ""
"Forecasts are based on validated delivery orders, manufacturing orders, and "
"other inventory actions that consume quantities. For delivery orders, the "
"*Effective Date* field is considered the date the quantities were consumed."
msgstr ""
"Prognoser er baseret på validerede leveringsordrer, produktionsordrer og "
"andre lageraktioner, der forbruger mængder. For leveringsordrer betragtes "
"feltet *Effektiv dato* som den dato, hvor mængderne blev forbrugt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:0
msgid "Example of effective date field."
msgstr "Eksempel på felt for effektiv dato."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:213
msgid "Maintain accurate vendor pricelists"
msgstr "Vedligehold nøjagtige leverandørprislister"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:215
msgid ""
"Review and update vendor pricelists to reflect the latest pricing and "
"supplier information to ensure correct suggestions."
msgstr ""
"Gennemgå og opdatér leverandørprislister for at afspejle de seneste priser "
"og leverandøroplysninger for at sikre korrekte forslag."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:218
msgid "Test sales projections based on seasonality"
msgstr "Test salgsprognoser baseret på sæsonudsving"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:220
msgid ""
"Reference prior months or quarters to capture seasonal fluctuations and "
"experiment with growth and decline factors to project sales."
msgstr ""
"Henvis til tidligere måneder eller kvartaler for at fange sæsonudsving, og "
"eksperimenter med vækst- og faldfaktorer for at fremskrive salg."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:223
msgid "Review suggestions critically"
msgstr "Gennemgå forslag kritisk"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:225
msgid ""
"Although the tool provides a baseline recommendation, always apply business "
"judgment. Market changes, promotions, and upcoming events can affect actual "
"demand."
msgstr ""
"Selvom værktøjet giver en grundlæggende anbefaling, skal du altid anvende "
"forretningsmæssig vurdering. Markedsændringer, kampagner og kommende "
"begivenheder kan påvirke den faktiske efterspørgsel."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:3
msgid "Vendor costs report"
msgstr "Rapport over leverandøromkostninger"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:10
msgid ""
"With the *Purchase* application, users can track the fluctuation of vendor "
"costs over time. This allows users to identify the most expensive vendors, "
"and track seasonal changes."
msgstr ""
"Med *Indkøb*-applikationen kan brugere spore udsving i "
"leverandøromkostninger over tid. Dette gør det muligt for brugere at "
"identificere de dyreste leverandører og spore sæsonændringer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:14
msgid "Create vendor costs reports"
msgstr "Opret rapporter over leverandøromkostninger"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:16
msgid ""
"To create a vendor costs report, first navigate to :menuselection:`Purchase "
"app --> Reporting --> Purchase` to open the :guilabel:`Purchase Analysis` "
"dashboard. By default, the dashboard displays a line chart overview of "
"the :guilabel:`Untaxed Total` of POs (Purchase Orders) with "
"a :guilabel:`Confirmation Date` for the current month, or of RFQs (Requests "
"for Quotation) with a status of *Draft*, *Sent, or *Cancelled*."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en rapport over leverandøromkostninger skal du først navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Indkøb-app --> Rapportering --> Indkøb` for at åbne "
"dashboardet :guilabel:`Indkøbsanalyse`. Som standard viser dashboardet en "
"kurvediagramsoversigt over :guilabel:`Beløb ekskl. moms` for indkøbsordrer "
"med en :guilabel:`Bekræftelsesdato` for den aktuelle måned, eller af "
"tilbudsanmodninger med status *Kladde*, *Sendt* eller *Annulleret*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:38
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Filters` column, select a date range to use for "
"comparison. The report can be filtered by either :guilabel:`Order Date` "
"or :guilabel:`Confirmation Date`. Choose one from the list, and click the |"
"caret| to specify the date range, either by month, quarter, or year."
msgstr ""
"Under kolonnen :guilabel:`Filtre` skal du vælge et datointerval til "
"sammenligning. Rapporten kan filtreres efter enten :guilabel:`Ordredato` "
"eller :guilabel:`Bekræftelsesdato`. Vælg en fra listen, og klik på |caret| "
"for at angive datointervallet, enten efter måned, kvartal eller år."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:42
msgid ""
"Next, under the :guilabel:`Group by` column, select :guilabel:`Vendor`. "
"Then, select :guilabel:`Product`, which is also located in "
"the :guilabel:`Group By` column."
msgstr ""
"Dernæst skal du under kolonnen :guilabel:`Gruppér efter` "
"vælge :guilabel:`Leverandør`. Vælg derefter :guilabel:`Produkt`, som også "
"findes i kolonnen :guilabel:`Gruppér efter`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:46
msgid ""
"Selecting :guilabel:`Product` is **not** required for this report. However, "
"it is recommended, as it provides additional insight into the performance of "
"individual vendors. Additional selections can be made under "
"the :guilabel:`Group by` heading as well, including :guilabel:`Product "
"Category`, :guilabel:`Status`, and :guilabel:`Purchase Representative`."
msgstr ""
"Valg af :guilabel:`Produkt` er **ikke** påkrævet for denne rapport. Det "
"anbefales dog, da det giver yderligere indsigt i individuelle leverandørers "
"præstation. Yderligere valg kan også foretages under "
"overskriften :guilabel:`Gruppér efter`, "
"herunder :guilabel:`Produktkategori`, :guilabel:`Status` "
"og :guilabel:`Indkøbsrepræsentant`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:51
msgid ""
"To ensure the report is generated correctly, make sure "
"that :guilabel:`Vendor` is the **first** selection made under "
"the :guilabel:`Group By` column."
msgstr ""
"For at sikre at rapporten genereres korrekt, skal du sørge for "
"at :guilabel:`Leverandør` er det **første** valg foretaget under "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Gruppér efter`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:54
msgid ""
"Next, make a selection under the :guilabel:`Comparison` heading. These "
"options are only available after the date range is selected under "
"the :guilabel:`Filters` column, and vary based on that "
"range. :guilabel:`Previous Period` adds a comparison to the previous period, "
"such as the last month or quarter. :guilabel:`Previous Year` compares the "
"same time period from the previous year."
msgstr ""
"Vyberte dále položku pod nadpisem :guilabel:`Comparison`. Tyto možnosti jsou "
"dostupné pouze po výběru časového rozsahu v sloupci :guilabel:`Filters` a "
"liší se podle daného rozsahu. :guilabel:`Previous Period` přidá srovnání s "
"předchozím obdobím, například minulým měsícem nebo "
"čtvrtletím. :guilabel:`Previous Year` srovnává stejné časové období z "
"předchozího roku."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:None
msgid ""
"The drop-down menu of filters, group by and comparison options for the "
"vendor costs report."
msgstr ""
"Rozevírací nabídka filtrů, možností seskupení a srovnání pro sestavu nákladů "
"dodavatele."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:73
msgid ""
"By default, the report displays with the following "
"measures: :guilabel:`Order`, :guilabel:`Total`, :guilabel:`Untaxed Total`, "
"and :guilabel:`Count`. Click :guilabel:`Measures` at the top-left to open "
"the drop-down list of available measures. Click :guilabel:`Average Cost` to "
"add it to the report. Select any additional measures to add to the report, "
"or click on any of the already selected measures to remove them, if desired."
msgstr ""
"Sestava se standardně zobrazuje s následujícími "
"mírami: :guilabel:`Order`, :guilabel:`Total`, :guilabel:`Untaxed Total` "
"a :guilabel:`Count`. Klikněte na :guilabel:`Measures` v levém horním rohu a "
"otevřete rozevírací seznam dostupných měr. Klikněte na :guilabel:`Average "
"Cost` a přidejte ji do sestavy. Vyberte další měry, které chcete přidat do "
"sestavy, nebo klikněte na některou z již vybraných měr a odeberte ji, pokud "
"je to žádoucí."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:80
msgid ""
"It is recommended to run the report with at least :guilabel:`Average "
"Cost`, :guilabel:`Total`, or :guilabel:`Untaxed Total` selected from "
"the :guilabel:`Measures` list. Additional measures, such as :guilabel:`Days "
"to Receive`, can be added to provide additional insights."
msgstr ""
"Doporučuje se spustit sestavu alespoň s :guilabel:`Average "
"Cost`, :guilabel:`Total` nebo :guilabel:`Untaxed Total` vybranou ze "
"seznamu :guilabel:`Measures`. Další měry, jako například :guilabel:`Days to "
"Receive`, lze přidat pro získání dalších poznatků."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:87
msgid ""
"After all of the :ref:`filters and measures have been selected <purchase/"
"vender-cost-report-filters>`, the report generates in the pivot view. "
"Click :guilabel:`Insert in Spreadsheet` to add the pivot view into an "
"editable spreadsheet format within the *Documents* app."
msgstr ""
"Po :ref:`výběru všech filtrů a měr <purchase/vender-cost-report-filters>` se "
"sestava vygeneruje v kontingenčním zobrazení. Klikněte na :guilabel:`Insert "
"in Spreadsheet` a přidejte kontingenční zobrazení do upravitelného formátu "
"tabulky v aplikaci *Dokumenter*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:93
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Insert in Spreadsheet` option is only available if the "
"*Documents Spreadsheet* module is installed."
msgstr ""
"Možnost :guilabel:`Insert in Spreadsheet` je dostupná pouze v případě, že je "
"nainstalován modul *Documents Spreadsheet*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:None
msgid ""
"A sample of a vendor costs report with the measures set as total and average "
"costs."
msgstr ""
"Ukázka sestavy nákladů dodavatele s mírami nastavenými jako celkové a "
"průměrné náklady."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/vendor_costs_report.rst:101
msgid ""
"The vendor costs report is also available in *graph* view. Click "
"the :icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`(area chart)` icon to change to graph "
"view. Click the corresponding icon at the top of the report to switch to "
"a :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`(bar chart)`, :icon:`fa-line-"
"chart` :guilabel:`(line chart)`, or :icon:`fa-pie-chart` :guilabel:`(pie "
"chart)`."
msgstr ""
"Sestava nákladů dodavatele je také dostupná v zobrazení *graf*. Klikněte na "
"ikonu :icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`(area chart)` a přepněte do zobrazení "
"grafu. Klikněte na odpovídající ikonu v horní části sestavy a přepněte "
"na :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`(bar chart)`, :icon:`fa-line-"
"chart` :guilabel:`(line chart)` nebo :icon:`fa-pie-chart` :guilabel:`(pie "
"chart)`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals.rst:5
msgid "Manage deals"
msgstr "Administrer handler"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:3
msgid "Blanket orders"
msgstr "Rámcové objednávky"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:13
msgid ""
"Blanket orders are long-term purchase agreements between a company and a "
"vendor to deliver products on a recurring basis with predetermined pricing."
msgstr ""
"Rámcové objednávky jsou dlouhodobé nákupní dohody mezi společností a "
"dodavatelem o dodávání produktů na opakovaném základě s předem stanovenými "
"cenami."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:16
msgid ""
"Blanket orders are helpful when products are consistently purchased from the "
"same vendor, but in different quantities, and at different times."
msgstr ""
"Rámcové objednávky jsou užitečné v případě, že jsou produkty pravidelně "
"nakupovány od stejného dodavatele, ale v různém množství a v různých časech."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:19
msgid ""
"By simplifying the ordering process, blanket orders not only save time, they "
"also save money, since they can be advantageous when negotiating bulk "
"pricing with vendors."
msgstr ""
"Zjednodušením objednávkového procesu rámcové objednávky nejen šetří čas, ale "
"i peníze, protože mohou být výhodné při vyjednávání hromadných cen s "
"dodavateli."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:23
msgid "Create a new blanket order"
msgstr "Vytvoření nové rámcové objednávky"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:25
msgid ""
"To create blanket orders, enable the *Purchase Agreements* feature from the "
"*Purchase* app settings. Navigate to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and under the :guilabel:`Orders` section, click "
"the checkbox for :guilabel:`Purchase Agreements`. Then "
"click :guilabel:`Save` to implement the changes."
msgstr ""
"Pro vytváření rámcových objednávek povolte funkci *Purchase Agreements* v "
"nastavení aplikace *Indkøb*. Přejděte do :menuselection:`Purchase app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` a v sekci :guilabel:`Orders` zaškrtněte políčko "
"u :guilabel:`Purchase Agreements`. Poté klikněte na :guilabel:`Save` a "
"implementujte změny."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:31
msgid ""
"In addition to creating blanket orders, the *Purchase Agreements* setting "
"also allows users to create alternative requests for quotation (RfQs)."
msgstr ""
"Kromě vytváření rámcových objednávek umožňuje nastavení *Purchase "
"Agreements* uživatelům také vytvářet alternativní žádosti o cenovou nabídku "
"(RfQ)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:None
msgid "Purchase Agreements enabled in the Purchase app settings."
msgstr "Purchase Agreements povoleny v nastavení aplikace Indkøb."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:37
msgid ""
"To create a blanket order, go to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Orders --> "
"Purchase Agreements`, and click :guilabel:`New`. This opens a new purchase "
"agreement form."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en rammeordre skal du gå til :menuselection:`Indkøb-app --> "
"Ordrer --> Indkøbsaftaler` og klikke på :guilabel:`Ny`. Dette åbner en ny "
"formular til indkøbsaftale."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:40
msgid ""
"Configure the following fields in the new purchase agreement form to "
"establish predetermined rules for the recurring long-term agreement:"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurer følgende felter i den nye formular til indkøbsaftale for at "
"fastlægge forudbestemte regler for den tilbagevendende langsigtede aftale:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:43
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Vendor`: the supplier to whom this agreement is tied, either once "
"or on a recurring basis. The vendor can be selected directly from the drop-"
"down menu next to this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vendor`: dodavatel, ke kterému je tato dohoda vázána, buď "
"jednorázově nebo opakovaně. Dodavatele lze vybrat přímo z rozevírací nabídky "
"vedle tohoto pole."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:45
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Buyer`: the user assigned to this specific blanket order. By "
"default, this is the user who created the agreement; the user can be changed "
"directly from the drop-down menu next to this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Køber`: brugeren tildelt denne specifikke rammeordre. Som "
"standard er dette den bruger, der oprettede aftalen; brugeren kan ændres "
"direkte fra rullemenuen ved siden af dette felt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Agreement Type`: the type of purchase agreement this blanket "
"order is classified as. Use the drop-down menu to choose :guilabel:`Blanket "
"Order` if not already selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Aftaletype`: den type indkøbsaftale, som denne rammeordre er "
"klassificeret som. Brug rullemenuen til at vælge :guilabel:`Rammeordre`, "
"hvis den ikke allerede er valgt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:50
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Currency`: the agreed-upon currency to be used for this exchange. "
"If multiple currencies have been activated in the database, the currency can "
"be changed from the drop-down menu next to this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Currency`: dohodnutá měna, která má být použita pro tuto "
"transakci. Pokud byly v databázi aktivovány více měn, lze měnu změnit z "
"rozevírací nabídky vedle tohoto pole."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:53
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Agreement Validity`: the date range this agreement should be "
"valid for. If this blanket order should not expire, leave this field blank."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Aftalens gyldighed`: det datointerval, som denne aftale skal være "
"gyldig for. Hvis denne rammeordre ikke skal udløbe, skal du lade feltet stå "
"tomt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:55
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reference`: the source purchase order (PO) that this blanket "
"order is tied to. If this blanket order should not be tied to any existing |"
"PO|, leave this field blank."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Reference`: den oprindelige indkøbsordre (PO), som denne "
"rammeordre er knyttet til. Hvis denne rammeordre ikke skal være knyttet til "
"nogen eksisterende |PO|, skal du lade feltet stå tomt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:57
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Operation Type`: the operation type that should be applied to "
"this order once it is delivered."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Operationstype`: den operationstype, der skal anvendes på denne "
"ordre, når den er leveret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: the company assigned to this specific blanket order. By "
"default, this is the company that the user creating the blanket order is "
"listed under. If the database is not a multi-company database, this field "
"**cannot** be changed, and defaults to the only company listed in the "
"database."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Company`: společnost přiřazená k této konkrétní rámcové "
"objednávce. Standardně se jedná o společnost, pod kterou je veden uživatel "
"vytvářející rámcovou objednávku. Pokud database není vícespolečnostní, toto "
"pole **nelze** změnit a je nastaveno na jedinou společnost uvedenou v "
"databázi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:None
msgid "New blanket order purchase agreement with added products."
msgstr "Nová rámcová objednávka s přidanými produkty."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:67
msgid ""
"Once all relevant fields have been filled out, click :guilabel:`Add a line` "
"to add products under the :guilabel:`Product` column. Then, in "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` column, change the quantity of each product, and "
"set a price in the :guilabel:`Unit Price` column."
msgstr ""
"Når alle relevante felter er udfyldt, klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` "
"for at tilføje produkter under kolonnen :guilabel:`Produkt`. Skift derefter "
"mængden af hvert produkt i kolonnen :guilabel:`Mængde`, og angiv en pris i "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Enhedspris`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:72
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:48
msgid ""
"When adding products to a new blanket order, the pre-existing prices of "
"products are not automatically added to the product lines. Instead, the "
"prices **must** be manually assigned, by changing the value in "
"the :guilabel:`Unit Price` column to an agreed-upon price with the listed "
"vendor. Otherwise, the price will remain `0`."
msgstr ""
"Når der tilføjes produkter til en ny rammeordre, tilføjes de eksisterende "
"produktpriser ikke automatisk til produktlinjerne. I stedet **skal** "
"priserne tildeles manuelt ved at ændre værdien i "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Enhedspris` til en aftalt pris med den anførte "
"leverandør. Ellers forbliver prisen `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:77
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Confirm` to save this new purchase agreement."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Bekræft` for at gemme denne nye indkøbsaftale."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:79
msgid ""
"Once confirmed, the blanket order's stage changes from :guilabel:`Draft` "
"to :guilabel:`Confirmed`, meaning this agreement can be selected and used "
"when creating new |RfQs|."
msgstr ""
"Når den er bekræftet, ændres rammeordrens trin fra :guilabel:`Udkast` "
"til :guilabel:`Bekræftet`, hvilket betyder, at denne aftale kan vælges og "
"bruges, når der oprettes nye |RfQs|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:83
msgid ""
"After creating and confirming a blanket order, products, quantities, and "
"prices can still be edited, added, and removed from the purchase agreement."
msgstr ""
"Efter oprettelse og bekræftelse af en rammeordre kan produkter, mængder og "
"priser stadig redigeres, tilføjes og fjernes fra indkøbsaftalen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:87
msgid "Create a new |RfQ| from the blanket order"
msgstr "Opret en ny |RfQ| fra rammeordren"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:89
msgid ""
"After confirming a blanket order, new quotations can be created directly "
"from the blanket order form. |RfQs| using this form are pre-populated with "
"information based on the rules set in the form. The total quantities of "
"products ordered through linked |RfQs| are automatically updated in "
"the :guilabel:`Ordered` field on the agreement."
msgstr ""
"Efter bekræftelse af en rammeordre kan nye tilbud oprettes direkte fra "
"rammeordreformularen. |RfQs|, der bruger denne formular, er forududfyldt med "
"oplysninger baseret på reglerne fastsat i formularen. De samlede mængder af "
"produkter bestilt gennem linkede |RfQs| opdateres automatisk i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Bestilt` i aftalen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:94
msgid ""
"Additionally, new quotations are automatically linked to this blanket order "
"form, via the :guilabel:`RFQs/Orders` smart button at the top-right of the "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Derudover linkes nye tilbud automatisk til denne rammeordreformular via den "
"smarte knap :guilabel:`Tilbudsanmodninger/Ordrer` øverst til højre i "
"formularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:97
msgid ""
"To create a new quotation from the blanket order form, click "
"the :guilabel:`New Quotation` button. This opens a new |RfQ|, that is pre-"
"populated with the correct information, depending on the settings configured "
"on the blanket order form."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette et nyt tilbud fra rammeordreformularen skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Nyt tilbud`. Dette åbner en ny |RfQ|, der er forudfyldt "
"med de korrekte oplysninger afhængigt af de indstillinger, der er "
"konfigureret på rammeordreformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:101
msgid ""
"From the new |RfQ| form, click :guilabel:`Send by Email` to compose and send "
"an email to the listed vendor. Click :guilabel:`Print RFQ` to generate a "
"printable PDF of the quotation; or, once ready, click :guilabel:`Confirm "
"Order` to confirm the |PO|."
msgstr ""
"Fra den nye |RfQ|-formular skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Send via e-mail` for "
"at skrive og sende en e-mail til den anførte leverandør. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Udskriv tilbudsanmodning` for at generere en printbar PDF af "
"tilbuddet; eller når du er klar, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Bekræft ordre` "
"for at bekræfte |PO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:None
msgid "New quotation with copied products and rules from blanket order."
msgstr "Nyt tilbud med kopierede produkter og regler fra rammeordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:108
msgid ""
"Once the |PO| has been confirmed, click back to the blanket order form (via "
"the breadcrumbs, at the top of the page). From the blanket order form, there "
"is now one |RfQ| listed in the :guilabel:`RFQs/Orders` smart button at the "
"top-right of the form. Click the :guilabel:`RFQs/Orders` smart button to see "
"the |PO| that was just created."
msgstr ""
"Når |PO| er bekræftet, skal du klikke tilbage til rammeordreformularen (via "
"brødkrummerne øverst på siden). Fra rammeordreformularen er der nu en |RfQ| "
"anført i den smarte knap :guilabel:`Tilbudsanmodninger/ordrer` øverst til "
"højre på formularen. Klik på den smarte knap :guilabel:`Tilbudsanmodninger/"
"ordrer` for at se den |PO|, der lige blev oprettet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:None
msgid "RFQs and Orders smart button from blanket order form."
msgstr "Smart knap for tilbudsanmodninger og ordrer fra rammeordreformular."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:119
msgid ""
"Once a blanket order is confirmed, a new vendor line is added under "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase` tab of the products included in the order."
msgstr ""
"Når en rammeordre er bekræftet, tilføjes en ny leverandørlinje under "
"fanen :guilabel:`Indkøb` for de produkter, der er inkluderet i ordren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:122
msgid ""
"This makes blanket orders useful with :doc:`automated replenishment <../../"
"purchase/products/reordering>`, because information about "
"the :guilabel:`Vendor`, :guilabel:`Price`, and the :guilabel:`Agreement` are "
"referenced on the vendor line. This information dictates when, where, and at "
"what price the product should be replenished."
msgstr ""
"Dette gør rammeordrer nyttige sammen med :doc:`automatisk genopfyldning "
"<../../purchase/products/reordering>`, fordi oplysninger "
"om :guilabel:`Leverandør`, :guilabel:`Pris` og :guilabel:`Aftale` refereres "
"på leverandørlinjen. Disse oplysninger bestemmer, hvornår, hvor og til "
"hvilken pris produktet skal genopfyldes."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:None
msgid "Product form with replenishment agreement linked to blanket order."
msgstr "Produktformular med genopfyldningsaftale knyttet til rammeordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/blanket_orders.rst:131
msgid ":doc:`calls_for_tenders`"
msgstr ":doc:`calls_for_tenders`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:3
msgid "Call for tenders"
msgstr "Udbud"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:12
msgid ""
"Sometimes, companies might want to invite vendors to submit offers for "
"similar goods or services all at once. This helps companies select the "
"cheapest, fastest vendors for their specific business needs."
msgstr ""
"Nogle gange ønsker virksomheder at invitere leverandører til at indsende "
"tilbud på lignende varer eller tjenester på én gang. Dette hjælper "
"virksomheder med at vælge de billigste, hurtigste leverandører til deres "
"specifikke forretningsbehov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:16
msgid ""
"In Odoo, this can be done by creating alternative requests for quotation "
"(RfQs) for different vendors. Once a response is received from each vendor, "
"the product lines from each |RfQ| can be compared, and a decision can be "
"made for which products to purchase from which vendors."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo kan dette gøres ved at oprette alternative tilbudsanmodninger for "
"forskellige leverandører. Når der er modtaget svar fra hver leverandør, kan "
"produktlinjerne fra hver |RfQ| sammenlignes, og der kan træffes en "
"beslutning om, hvilke produkter der skal købes fra hvilke leverandører."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:21
msgid ""
"Sometimes referred to as a *call for tender*, this process is primarily used "
"by organizations in the public sector, who are legally bound to use it when "
"making a purchase. However, private companies can also use alternative |"
"RfQs| to spend money efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Nogle gange omtalt som et *udbud*, denne proces bruges primært af "
"organisationer i den offentlige sektor, som er juridisk forpligtet til at "
"bruge den ved køb. Private virksomheder kan dog også bruge alternative |"
"RfQs| til at bruge penge effektivt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:28
msgid ""
"To create alternative |RfQs|, the *Purchase Agreements* feature **must** be "
"enabled in the *Purchase* app settings. To enable the feature, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Configuration --> Settings`. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Orders` section, click the checkbox for :guilabel:`Purchase "
"Agreements`."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette alternative |RfQs| **skal** funktionen *Indkøbsaftaler* være "
"aktiveret i indstillingerne for *Indkøb*-appen. For at aktivere funktionen "
"skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Indkøb-app --> Konfiguration --> "
"Indstillinger`. Under sektionen :guilabel:`Ordrer` skal du klikke på "
"afkrydsningsfeltet for :guilabel:`Indkøbsaftaler`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:33
msgid "Then, click :guilabel:`Save` to apply the change."
msgstr "Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Gem` for at anvende ændringen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:42
msgid "Create an |RfQ|"
msgstr "Opret en |RfQ|"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:44
msgid ""
"To create a new |RfQ|, follow the instructions in the :doc:`rfq` "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en ny |RfQ|, følg instruktionerne i :doc:`rfq`-"
"dokumentationen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:47
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorial: Purchase Basics and Your First Request for Quotation "
"<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o_uI718P1Dc>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo-tutorial: Indkøbsgrundlæggende og din første anmodning om tilbud "
"<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o_uI718P1Dc>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:53
msgid "Create alternative |RfQs|"
msgstr "Opret alternative |RfQs|"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:55
msgid ""
"Once a |PO| is created and sent to a vendor, alternative |RfQs| can be "
"created for additional vendors to compare prices, delivery times, and other "
"factors, to help make a decision for the order."
msgstr ""
"Når en |PO| er oprettet og sendt til en leverandør, kan alternative |RfQs| "
"oprettes for yderligere leverandører for at sammenligne priser, "
"leveringstider og andre faktorer, som hjælper med at træffe en beslutning om "
"ordren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:58
msgid ""
"To create alternative |RfQs| from the original, click "
"the :guilabel:`Alternatives` tab. Then, click :guilabel:`Create "
"Alternative`. When clicked, a :guilabel:`Create alternative` pop-up window "
"appears."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette alternative |RfQs| fra den oprindelige skal du klikke på "
"fanen :guilabel:`Alternativer`. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Opret "
"alternativ`. Når der klikkes, vises et pop op-vindue :guilabel:`Opret "
"alternativ`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:None
msgid "Calls for tenders pop-up to create alternative quotation."
msgstr "Pop op-vindue til udbud for at oprette alternativt tilbud."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:66
msgid ""
"From this window, select an alternative vendor from the drop-down menu next "
"to the :guilabel:`Vendor` field, to whom the alternative quotation is "
"assigned."
msgstr ""
"I dette vindue skal du vælge en alternativ leverandør fra rullemenuen ved "
"siden af feltet :guilabel:`Leverandør`, som det alternative tilbud tildeles "
"til."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:69
msgid ""
"Next to this, there is a :guilabel:`Copy Products` checkbox that is selected "
"by default. When selected, the product quantities of the original |RfQ| are "
"copied over to the alternative. For this first alternative quotation, leave "
"the checkbox checked. Once finished, click :guilabel:`Create Alternative`. "
"This opens a new |RfQ| form."
msgstr ""
"Ved siden af dette er der et afkrydsningsfelt :guilabel:`Kopier produkter`, "
"som er markeret som standard. Når det er markeret, kopieres produktmængderne "
"fra den oprindelige |RfQ| over til alternativet. For dette første "
"alternative tilbud skal du lade afkrydsningsfeltet være markeret. Når du er "
"færdig, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Opret alternativ`. Dette åbner en ny |"
"RfQ|-formular."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:74
msgid ""
"Since the :guilabel:`Create Alternative` checkbox was left checked, the new "
"form is already pre-populated with the same products, quantities, and other "
"details as the previous, original |RfQ|."
msgstr ""
"Da afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Opret alternativ` blev efterladt markeret, "
"er den nye formular allerede forudfyldt med de samme produkter, mængder og "
"andre detaljer som den tidligere, oprindelige |RfQ|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:78
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Copy Products` checkbox is selected while creating an "
"alternative quotation, additional products do **not** need to be added, "
"unless desired."
msgstr ""
"Når afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Kopier produkter` er markeret, mens du "
"opretter et alternativt tilbud, behøver yderligere produkter **ikke** at "
"blive tilføjet, medmindre det ønskes."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:81
msgid ""
"However, if a chosen vendor is listed in the :guilabel:`Vendor` column under "
"a specific product form included in the order, the values set on the product "
"form carry over to the |RfQ|, and **must** be changed manually, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en valgt leverandør dog er opført i kolonnen :guilabel:`Leverandør` "
"under en specifik produktformular inkluderet i ordren, overføres værdierne "
"indstillet på produktformularen til |RfQ|, og **skal** ændres manuelt, hvis "
"nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:85
msgid ""
"Once ready, create a second alternative quotation by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Alternatives` tab, followed by :guilabel:`Create Alternative`."
msgstr ""
"Når du er klar, skal du oprette et andet alternativt tilbud ved at klikke på "
"fanen :guilabel:`Alternativer`, efterfulgt af :guilabel:`Opret alternativ`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:88
msgid ""
"This opens the :guilabel:`Create alternative` pop-up window. Once again, "
"choose a different vendor from the drop-down menu next "
"to :guilabel:`Vendor`. For this particular |RfQ|, however, *uncheck* "
"the :guilabel:`Copy Products` checkbox. Doing so removes all products on the "
"new alternative |RfQ|, leaving it blank. The specific products which should "
"be ordered from this particular vendor can be added in as needed."
msgstr ""
"Dette åbner pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Opret alternativ`. Vælg endnu en gang "
"en anden leverandør fra rullemenuen ved siden af :guilabel:`Leverandør`. For "
"denne særlige |RfQ| skal du dog *fjerne markeringen* af "
"afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Kopier produkter`. Dette fjerner alle "
"produkter på den nye alternative |RfQ|, så den er tom. De specifikke "
"produkter, der skal bestilles fra denne særlige leverandør, kan tilføjes "
"efter behov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:94
msgid "Once ready, click :guilabel:`Create Alternative`."
msgstr "Når du er klar, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Opret alternativ`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:97
msgid ""
"If an alternative quotation should be removed from "
"the :guilabel:`Alternatives` tab, they can be individually removed by "
"clicking on the :guilabel:`X (remove)` icon at the end of their row."
msgstr ""
"Hvis et alternativt tilbud skal fjernes fra fanen :guilabel:`Alternativer`, "
"kan de fjernes individuelt ved at klikke på ikonet :guilabel:`X (fjern)` i "
"slutningen af deres række."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:100
msgid ""
"This creates a third, new |RfQ|. But, since the product quantities of the "
"original |RfQ| were **not** copied over, the product lines are empty, and "
"new products can be added as needed by clicking :guilabel:`Add a product`, "
"and selecting the desired products from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Dette opretter en tredje, ny |RfQ|. Men da produktmængderne fra den "
"oprindelige |RfQ| **ikke** blev kopieret, er produktlinjerne tomme, og nye "
"produkter kan tilføjes efter behov ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj et "
"produkt` og vælge de ønskede produkter fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:104
msgid ""
"Once the desired number of specific products are added, "
"click :guilabel:`Send by Email`."
msgstr ""
"Når det ønskede antal specifikke produkter er tilføjet, skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Send via e-mail`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:None
msgid "Blank alternative quotation with alternatives in breadcrumbs."
msgstr "Tomt alternativt tilbud med alternativer i brødkrummer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:110
msgid ""
"This opens a :guilabel:`Compose Email` pop-up window, wherein the message to "
"the vendor can be customized, and attachments can be added, if necessary. "
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr ""
"Dette åbner et pop op-vindue :guilabel:`Skriv e-mail`, hvor beskeden til "
"leverandøren kan tilpasses, og vedhæftninger kan tilføjes, hvis nødvendigt. "
"Når du er klar, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Send`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:113
msgid ""
"From this newest form, click the :guilabel:`Alternatives` tab. Under this "
"tab, all three |RfQs| can be seen in the :guilabel:`Reference` column. "
"Additionally, the vendors are listed under the :guilabel:`Vendor` column, "
"and the order :guilabel:`Total` (and :guilabel:`Status`) of the orders are "
"in the rows, as well."
msgstr ""
"Fra denne nyeste formular skal du klikke på fanen :guilabel:`Alternativer`. "
"Under denne fane kan alle tre |RfQs| ses i kolonnen :guilabel:`Reference`. "
"Derudover er leverandørerne opført under kolonnen :guilabel:`Leverandør`, og "
"ordre-:guilabel:`Total` (og :guilabel:`Status`) for ordrerne er også i "
"rækkerne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:118
msgid ""
"The date in the :guilabel:`Expected Arrival` column is calculated for each "
"vendor, based on any pre-configured lead times in the vendor and product "
"forms."
msgstr ""
"Datoen i kolonnen :guilabel:`Forventet ankomst` beregnes for hver leverandør "
"baseret på eventuelle forudkonfigurerede leveringstider i leverandør- og "
"produktformularerne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:124
msgid "Link new |RfQ| to existing quotations"
msgstr "Knyt nye |RfQ| til eksisterende tilbud"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:126
msgid ""
"Even if a quotation is not created directly from "
"the :guilabel:`Alternatives` tab of another |RfQ|, it can still be linked to "
"existing |RfQs|."
msgstr ""
"Selvom et tilbud ikke oprettes direkte fra fanen :guilabel:`Alternativer` i "
"en anden |RfQ|, kan det stadig knyttes til eksisterende |RfQs|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:129
msgid ""
"To do that, begin by creating a new |RfQ|. Navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> New`. Fill out the |RfQ|, according to "
"the :ref:`previous instructions <purchase/manage_deals/create-rfq>`."
msgstr ""
"For at gøre dette skal du starte med at oprette en ny |RfQ|. Naviger "
"til :menuselection:`Indkøb-app --> Ny`. Udfyld |RfQ| i overensstemmelse med "
"de :ref:`tidligere instruktioner <purchase/manage_deals/create-rfq>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:132
msgid ""
"Then, once ready, click the :guilabel:`Alternatives` tab. Since this new |"
"RfQ| was created separately, there are no other orders linked yet."
msgstr ""
"Når du er klar, skal du klikke på fanen :guilabel:`Alternativer`. Da denne "
"nye |RfQ| blev oprettet separat, er der endnu ingen andre ordrer knyttet til."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:135
msgid ""
"However, to link this |RfQ| with existing alternatives, "
"click :guilabel:`Link to Existing RfQ` on the first line in "
"the :guilabel:`Vendor` column."
msgstr ""
"For at knytte denne |RfQ| til eksisterende alternativer skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Knyt til eksisterende tilbudsanmodning` på den første linje i "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Leverandør`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:None
msgid "Pop-up to link new quotation to existing RFQs."
msgstr "Pop-up til at knytte nyt tilbud til eksisterende tilbudsanmodninger."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:142
msgid ""
"This opens an :guilabel:`Add: Alternative POs` pop-up window. Select the "
"desired previously-created |RfQs|, and click :guilabel:`Select`. All of "
"these orders are now copied to this |RfQ|, and can be found under "
"the :guilabel:`Alternatives` tab."
msgstr ""
"Dette åbner et pop-op-vindue med :guilabel:`Tilføj: alternative "
"indkøbsordrer`. Vælg de ønskede tidligere oprettede |RfQs|, og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Vælg`. Alle disse ordrer kopieres nu til denne |RfQ| og kan "
"findes under fanen :guilabel:`Alternativer`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:147
msgid ""
"If a large number of |POs| are being processed, and the previous |POs| can't "
"be located, click the :icon:`fa-chevron-down` :guilabel:`(chevron)` icon to "
"the right of the search bar, at the top of the pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Hvis et stort antal |POs| behandles, og de tidligere |POs| ikke kan "
"lokaliseres, skal du klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-chevron-"
"down` :guilabel:`(chevron)` til højre for søgelinjen øverst i pop-op-vinduet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:151
msgid ""
"Then, under the :guilabel:`Group By` section, click :guilabel:`Vendor`. "
"Vendors are displayed in their own nested drop-down lists, and each vendor's "
"list can be expanded to view open |POs| for that vendor."
msgstr ""
"Under afsnittet :guilabel:`Gruppér efter` skal du derefter klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Leverandør`. Leverandører vises i deres egne indlejrede "
"rullemenuer, og hver leverandørs liste kan udvides for at se åbne |POs| for "
"den pågældende leverandør."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:158
msgid "Compare product lines"
msgstr "Sammenlign produktlinjer"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:160
msgid ""
"Alternative |RfQs| can be compared side-by-side, in order to determine which "
"vendors offer the best deals on the products included in the orders."
msgstr ""
"Alternative |RfQs| kan sammenlignes side om side for at afgøre, hvilke "
"leverandører tilbyder de bedste tilbud på de produkter, der er inkluderet i "
"ordrerne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:163
msgid ""
"To compare alternative |RfQs|, navigate to the :menuselection:`Purchase` "
"app, and select one of the previously-created |RfQs|."
msgstr ""
"For at sammenligne alternative |RfQs| skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Indkøb`-appen og vælge en af de tidligere oprettede |"
"RfQs|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:166
msgid ""
"Then, click the :guilabel:`Alternatives` tab to see all linked |RfQs|. Next, "
"under the :guilabel:`Create Alternative` option, click :guilabel:`Compare "
"Product Lines`. This navigates to the :guilabel:`Compare Order Lines` page."
msgstr ""
"Klik derefter på fanen :guilabel:`Alternativer` for at se alle tilknyttede |"
"RfQs|. Under indstillingen :guilabel:`Opret alternativ` skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Sammenlign produktlinjer`. Dette navigerer til "
"siden :guilabel:`Sammenlign ordrelinjer`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:None
msgid "Compare Product Lines page for alternative RFQs."
msgstr "Siden Sammenlign produktlinjer for alternative tilbudsanmodninger."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:174
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Compare Order Lines` page, by default, groups "
"by :guilabel:`Product`. Each product included in any of the |RfQs| is "
"displayed in its own nested drop-down list, and features all of the |PO| "
"numbers in the :guilabel:`Reference` column."
msgstr ""
"Siden :guilabel:`Sammenlign ordrelinjer` grupperer som standard "
"efter :guilabel:`Produkt`. Hvert produkt, der er inkluderet i nogen af |"
"RfQs|, vises i sin egen indlejrede rullemenuliste og indeholder alle |PO|-"
"numrene i kolonnen :guilabel:`Reference`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:179
msgid ""
"To remove product lines from the :guilabel:`Compare Order Lines` page, "
"click :guilabel:`Clear` at the far-right end of that product line's row."
msgstr ""
"For at fjerne produktlinjer fra siden :guilabel:`Sammenlign ordrelinjer` "
"skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Ryd` i højre ende af den pågældende "
"produktlinjes række."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:182
msgid ""
"Doing so removes this specific product as a selectable option from the page, "
"and changes the :guilabel:`Total` price of that product on the page to `0`."
msgstr ""
"Dette fjerner dette specifikke produkt som en valgmulighed fra siden og "
"ændrer :guilabel:`Total`prisen for det produkt på siden til `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:185
msgid ""
"Additionally, on the |RfQ| form, in which that product was included, its "
"ordered quantity is also changed to `0`."
msgstr ""
"Derudover ændres den bestilte mængde også til `0` på |RfQ|-formularen, hvor "
"produktet var inkluderet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:188
msgid ""
"Once the best offers have been identified, individual products can be "
"selected by clicking the :guilabel:`Choose` button at the end of each "
"corresponding row."
msgstr ""
"Når de bedste tilbud er identificeret, kan individuelle produkter vælges ved "
"at klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Vælg` i slutningen af hver tilsvarende række."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:191
msgid ""
"Once all desired products have been chosen, click :guilabel:`Requests for "
"Quotation` (in the breadcrumbs, at the top of the page) to navigate back to "
"an overview of all |RfQs|."
msgstr ""
"Når alle ønskede produkter er valgt, klik på :guilabel:`Tilbudsanmodninger` "
"(i brødkrummestien øverst på siden) for at navigere tilbage til en oversigt "
"over alle |RfQs|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:197
msgid "Cancel (or keep) alternatives"
msgstr "Annuller (eller behold) alternativer"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:199
msgid ""
"Once the desired products have been chosen from the :guilabel:`Compare Order "
"Lines` page, the remaining |RfQs|, from which no products were chosen, can "
"be cancelled."
msgstr ""
"Når de ønskede produkter er valgt fra siden :guilabel:`Sammenlign "
"ordrelinjer`, kan de resterende |RfQs|, som der ikke blev valgt produkter "
"fra, annulleres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:202
msgid ""
"The cost in the :guilabel:`Total` column for each product that wasn't chosen "
"is automatically set to `0`, indicated at the far-right of each "
"corresponding row."
msgstr ""
"Omkostningen i kolonnen :guilabel:`I alt` for hvert produkt, der ikke blev "
"valgt, sættes automatisk til `0`, som angivet til højre for hver tilsvarende "
"række."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:205
msgid ""
"Although they haven't been cancelled yet, this indicates that each of those "
"orders can be cancelled without having an effect on the other live orders, "
"once those orders have been confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Selvom de endnu ikke er blevet annulleret, indikerer dette, at hver af disse "
"ordrer kan annulleres uden at påvirke de andre aktive ordrer, når disse "
"ordrer er bekræftet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:None
msgid "Cancelled quotations in the Purchase app overview."
msgstr "Annullerede tilbud i oversigten over Indkøb-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:212
msgid ""
"To confirm an |RfQ| for which products were selected, click into an |RfQ|, "
"and click :guilabel:`Confirm Order`."
msgstr ""
"For at bekræfte en |RfQ|, som der blev valgt produkter for, klik ind i en |"
"RfQ|, og klik på :guilabel:`Bekræft ordre`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:215
msgid ""
"This causes a :guilabel:`What about the alternative Requests for Quotations?"
"` pop-up window to appear."
msgstr ""
"Dette får et pop op-vindue :guilabel:`Hvad med de alternative "
"tilbudsanmodninger?` til at vises."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:218
msgid ""
"To view a detailed form of one of the |RfQs| listed, click the line item for "
"that quotation. This opens an :guilabel:`Open: Alternative POs` pop-up "
"window, from which all details of that particular |RfQ| can be viewed."
msgstr ""
"For at se en detaljeret formular for en af de listede |RfQs|, klik på "
"linjeelementet for det pågældende tilbud. Dette åbner et pop op-"
"vindue :guilabel:`Åbn: Alternative indkøbsordrer`, hvorfra alle detaljer for "
"den pågældende |RfQ| kan ses."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:222
msgid "Once ready, click :guilabel:`Close` to close the pop-up window."
msgstr "Når du er klar, klik på :guilabel:`Luk` for at lukke pop op-vinduet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:224
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`What about the alternative Requests for Quotations?` pop-"
"up window, two options are presented: :guilabel:`Cancel Alternatives` "
"and :guilabel:`Keep Alternatives`."
msgstr ""
"I pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Hvad med de alternative tilbudsanmodninger?` "
"præsenteres to muligheder: :guilabel:`Annuller alternativer` "
"og :guilabel:`Behold alternativer`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:227
msgid "If this |PO| should **not** be confirmed, click :guilabel:`Discard`."
msgstr "Hvis denne |PO| **ikke** skal bekræftes, klik på :guilabel:`Kassér`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:229
msgid ""
"Selecting :guilabel:`Cancel Alternatives` automatically cancels the "
"alternative |RfQs|. Selecting :guilabel:`Keep Alternatives` keeps the "
"alternative |RfQs| open, so they can still be accessed, if any additional "
"product quantities need to be ordered later."
msgstr ""
"Valg af :guilabel:`Annuller alternativer` annullerer automatisk de "
"alternative |RfQs|. Valg af :guilabel:`Behold alternativer` holder de "
"alternative |RfQs| åbne, så de stadig kan tilgås, hvis yderligere "
"produktmængder skal bestilles senere."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:233
msgid ""
"Once all products are ordered, select :guilabel:`Cancel Alternatives` from "
"whichever |PO| is open at that time."
msgstr ""
"Når alle produkter er bestilt, vælg :guilabel:`Annuller alternativer` fra "
"den |PO|, der er åben på det tidspunkt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:None
msgid "Keep or cancel pop-up for alternative RFQs."
msgstr "Behold eller annuller pop op for alternative tilbudsanmodninger."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:240
msgid ""
"Finally, using the breadcrumbs at the top of the page, "
"click :guilabel:`Requests for Quotation` to navigate back to an overview of "
"all |RfQs|."
msgstr ""
"Til sidst, brug brødkrummestien øverst på siden, klik "
"på :guilabel:`Tilbudsanmodninger` for at navigere tilbage til en oversigt "
"over alle |RfQs|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:243
msgid ""
"The cancelled orders can be seen, greyed out and listed with "
"a :guilabel:`Cancelled` status, under the :guilabel:`Status` column at the "
"far-right of their respective rows."
msgstr ""
"De annullerede ordrer kan ses, gråtonet og listet med "
"status :guilabel:`Annulleret`, under kolonnen :guilabel:`Status` til højre i "
"deres respektive rækker."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:246
msgid ""
"Now that all product quantities have been ordered, the purchase process can "
"be completed, and the products can be received into the warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Nu hvor alle produktmængder er bestilt, kan indkøbsprocessen gennemføres, og "
"produkterne kan modtages på lageret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:250
msgid ":doc:`blanket_orders`"
msgstr ":doc:`blanket_orders`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:3
msgid "Control policies"
msgstr "Kontrolpolitikker"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:10
msgid ""
"In Odoo's **Purchase** app, the *Control Policy* determines the quantities "
"billed by vendors on every purchase order (PO). For example, choosing *On "
"ordered quantities* means the bill is based on ordered items, even if they "
"have not been received yet."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo aplikaci **Indkøb** afgør *kontrolpolitikken*, hvilke mængder "
"leverandører fakturerer på hver indkøbsordre (IO). Valg af *På bestilte "
"mængder* betyder f.eks., at fakturaen er baseret på bestilte varer, selv "
"hvis de endnu ikke er modtaget."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:14
msgid "The control policy is selected on the *Product* record."
msgstr "Kontrolpolitikken vælges på *produkt*-posten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:19
msgid ""
"To configure the control policy for a product, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Products --> Products`, then click on a "
"product record to open it. Click to the :guilabel:`Purchase` tab. Scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Vendor Bills` section. Under :guilabel:`Control Policy`, tick "
"the radio button for either :guilabel:`On ordered quantities` "
"or :guilabel:`On recieved quantities`."
msgstr ""
"For at konfigurere kontrolpolitikken for et produkt skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Indkøb app --> Produkter --> Produkter`, og derefter "
"klikke på en produktpost for at åbne den. Klik på fanen :guilabel:`Indkøb`. "
"Rul ned til sektionen :guilabel:`Leverandørfakturaer`. "
"Under :guilabel:`Kontrolpolitik` skal du markere radioknappen for "
"enten :guilabel:`På bestilte mængder` eller :guilabel:`På modtagne mængder`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:24
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On ordered quantities`: Creates a vendor bill as soon as a |PO| "
"is confirmed. The products and quantities in the |PO| are used to generate a "
"draft bill."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`På bestilte mængder`: Opretter en leverandørfaktura, så snart en |"
"PO| er bekræftet. Produkterne og mængderne i |PO| bruges til at generere en "
"kladdefaktura."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:26
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On received quantities`: A bill is created only *after* part of "
"the total order has been received. The products and quantities received are "
"used to generate a draft bill. An error message appears if creation of a "
"vendor bill is attempted without receiving anything."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`På modtagne mængder`: En faktura oprettes først *efter*, at en "
"del af den samlede ordre er modtaget. De modtagne produkter og mængder "
"bruges til at generere en kladdefaktura. En fejlmeddelelse vises, hvis man "
"forsøger at oprette en leverandørfaktura uden at have modtaget noget."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:30
msgid ""
"The default control policy for a product is determined by "
"the :guilabel:`Product Type`:"
msgstr ""
"Standardkontrolpolitikken for et produkt bestemmes "
"af :guilabel:`produkttypen`:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:32
msgid "**Services**: The default control policy is *On ordered quantities*."
msgstr "**Tjenester**: Standardkontrolpolitikken er *På bestilte mængder*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:33
msgid "**Goods**: The default control policy is *On delivered quantities*"
msgstr "**Varer**: Standardkontrolpolitikken er *På leverede mængder*"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:36
msgid "Pay vendor bills with 3-way matching"
msgstr "Betal leverandørfakturaer med 3-vejs matching"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:38
msgid ""
"The *3-way matching* feature ensures vendor bills are only paid once some, "
"or all, of the products included in the |PO| have been received."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen *3-vejs matching* sikrer, at leverandørfakturaer først betales, "
"når nogle eller alle produkter inkluderet i |PO| er modtaget."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:41
msgid ""
"To activate *3-way matching*, navigate to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and scroll down to the :guilabel:`Invoicing` "
"section. Then, tick the checkbox for :guilabel:`3-way matching` to enable "
"the feature, and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"For at aktivere *3-vejs matching* skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Indkøb-app --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger` og rulle "
"ned til sektionen :guilabel:`Fakturering`. Derefter skal du markere "
"afkrydsningsfeltet for :guilabel:`3-vejs matching` for at aktivere "
"funktionen og klikke på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:None
msgid "Enabled 3-way matching feature in Purchase app settings."
msgstr "Aktiveret 3-vejs matching-funktion i Indkøb-app-indstillinger."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:48
msgid ""
"When *3-way matching* is enabled, vendor bills display a :guilabel:`Should "
"Be Paid` field under the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab. When a new vendor bill "
"is created, the field is set to :guilabel:`Yes`, since a bill **cannot** be "
"created until at least some of the products included in a |PO| have been "
"received."
msgstr ""
"Når *3-vejs matching* er aktiveret, viser leverandørfakturaer "
"et :guilabel:`Skal betales`-felt under fanen :guilabel:`Øvrige oplysninger`. "
"Når en ny leverandørfaktura oprettes, er feltet sat til :guilabel:`Ja`, da "
"en faktura **ikke kan** oprettes, før mindst nogle af produkterne inkluderet "
"i en |PO| er modtaget."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:53
msgid ""
"To create a vendor bill from a |PO|, navigate to :menuselection:`Purchase "
"app --> Orders --> Purchase Orders`. From the :guilabel:`Purchase Orders` "
"page, select the desired |PO| from the list. Then, click :guilabel:`Create "
"Bill`. Doing so opens a new draft :guilabel:`Vendor Bill` form, in "
"the :guilabel:`Draft` stage. Click the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab, and "
"locate the :guilabel:`Should Be Paid` field."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en leverandørfaktura fra en |PO| skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Indkøb-app --> Ordrer --> Indkøbsordrer`. Fra "
"siden :guilabel:`Indkøbsordrer` skal du vælge den ønskede |PO| fra listen. "
"Derefter skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Opret faktura`. Dette åbner en ny "
"kladde :guilabel:`Leverandørfaktura`-formular i stadiet :guilabel:`Kladde`. "
"Klik på fanen :guilabel:`Øvrige oplysninger` og find feltet :guilabel:`Skal "
"betales`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:60
msgid ""
"The |PO| selected from the list **must not** be billed yet, or "
"an :guilabel:`Invalid Operation` pop-up window appears."
msgstr ""
"Den |PO|, der vælges fra listen, må **ikke** være faktureret endnu, ellers "
"vises et pop op-vindue med :guilabel:`Ugyldig handling`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:0
msgid "Invalid Operation pop-up window for billed Purchase Order."
msgstr "Pop op-vindue med ugyldig handling for faktureret indkøbsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:66
msgid ""
"Click the drop-down menu next to :guilabel:`Should Be Paid` to view the "
"available options: :guilabel:`Yes`, :guilabel:`No`, "
"and :guilabel:`Exception`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på rullemenuen ved siden af :guilabel:`Skal betales` for at se de "
"tilgængelige muligheder: :guilabel:`Ja`, :guilabel:`Nej` "
"og :guilabel:`Undtagelse`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:None
msgid "Should Be Paid field status on draft vendor bill."
msgstr "Status for feltet Skal betales på kladde-leverandørfaktura."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:73
msgid ""
"If the total quantity of products from a |PO| has not been received, Odoo "
"only includes the products that *have* been received in the draft vendor "
"bill."
msgstr ""
"Hvis den samlede mængde produkter fra en |PO| ikke er modtaget, inkluderer "
"Odoo kun de produkter, der *er* modtaget, i kladde-leverandørfakturaen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:76
msgid ""
"Draft vendor bills can be edited to increase the billed quantity, change the "
"price of the products in the bill, and add additional products to the bill."
msgstr ""
"Kladde-leverandørfakturaer kan redigeres for at øge den fakturerede mængde, "
"ændre prisen på produkterne i fakturaen og tilføje yderligere produkter til "
"fakturaen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:79
msgid ""
"If the draft bill's information is changed, the :guilabel:`Should Be Paid` "
"field status is set to :guilabel:`Exception`. This means that Odoo notices "
"the discrepancy, but does not block the changes or display an error message, "
"since there might be a valid reason for making changes to the draft bill."
msgstr ""
"Hvis kladdefakturaens oplysninger ændres, sættes statussen for "
"feltet :guilabel:`Skal betales` til :guilabel:`Undtagelse`. Dette betyder, "
"at Odoo opdager uoverensstemmelsen, men ikke blokerer ændringerne eller "
"viser en fejlmeddelelse, da der kan være en gyldig grund til at foretage "
"ændringer i kladdefakturaen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:84
msgid ""
"To process the vendor bill, select a date in the :guilabel:`Bill Date` "
"field, and click :guilabel:`Confirm`, followed by :guilabel:`Register "
"Payment`."
msgstr ""
"For at behandle kreditorfakturaen skal du vælge en dato i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Fakturadato` og klikke på :guilabel:`Bekræft` efterfulgt "
"af :guilabel:`Registrer betaling`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:87
msgid ""
"This opens a :guilabel:`Register Payment` pop-up window. From this window, "
"accounting information is pre-populated based on the database's accounting "
"settings. Click :guilabel:`Create Payment` to process the vendor bill."
msgstr ""
"Dette åbner et pop op-vindue med :guilabel:`Registrer betaling`. I dette "
"vindue er regnskabsoplysningerne udfyldt på forhånd baseret på databasens "
"regnskabsindstillinger. Klik på :guilabel:`Opret betaling` for at behandle "
"kreditorfakturaen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:91
msgid ""
"Once payment has been registered for a vendor bill, and the bill displays "
"the green :guilabel:`Paid` banner, the :guilabel:`Should Be Paid` field "
"status is set to :guilabel:`No`."
msgstr ""
"Når betaling er registreret for en kreditorfaktura, og fakturaen viser det "
"grønne :guilabel:`Betalt` banner, er status for feltet :guilabel:`Skal "
"betales` sat til :guilabel:`Nej`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:95
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Should Be Paid` status on bills is automatically set by Odoo. "
"However, the status can be manually changed by clicking the field's drop-"
"down menu inside the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab."
msgstr ""
"Status for :guilabel:`Skal betales` på fakturaer sættes automatisk af Odoo. "
"Status kan dog ændres manuelt ved at klikke på feltets rullemenу under "
"fanen :guilabel:`Andre oplysninger`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:100
msgid "View a purchase order's billing status"
msgstr "Vis faktureringsstatus for en indkøbsordre"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:102
msgid ""
"Once a |PO| is confirmed, its :guilabel:`Billing Status` can be viewed under "
"the :guilabel:`Other Information` tab on the |PO| form."
msgstr ""
"Når en |PO| er bekræftet, kan dens :guilabel:`Faktureringsstatus` ses under "
"fanen :guilabel:`Andre oplysninger` på |PO|-formularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:105
msgid ""
"To view the :guilabel:`Billing Status` of a |PO|, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Orders --> Purchase Orders`, and select "
"a |PO| to view."
msgstr ""
"For at se :guilabel:`Faktureringsstatus` for en |PO| skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Indkøb-app --> Ordrer --> Indkøbsordrer` og vælge en |"
"PO| at se."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:108
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Other Information` tab, and locate "
"the :guilabel:`Billing Status` field."
msgstr ""
"Klik på fanen :guilabel:`Andre oplysninger` og find "
"feltet :guilabel:`Faktureringsstatus`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:None
msgid "Billing status field on a purchase order form."
msgstr "Faktureringsstatus-felt på en indkøbsordreformular."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:113
msgid ""
"The table below details the different values the :guilabel:`Billing Status` "
"field could read, and when they are displayed, depending on the *Bill "
"Control* policy used."
msgstr ""
"Tabellen nedenfor beskriver de forskellige værdier, som "
"feltet :guilabel:`Faktureringsstatus` kan vise, og hvornår de vises, "
"afhængigt af den anvendte *Fakturastyring*-politik."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:120
msgid "Billing Status"
msgstr "Fakturastatus"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:121
msgid "On received quantities"
msgstr "På leverede mængder"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:122
msgid "On ordered quantities"
msgstr "På bestilte mængder"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:123
msgid "Nothing to Bill"
msgstr "Intet at fakturere"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:124
msgid "PO confirmed; no products received"
msgstr "Indkøbsordre bekræftet; ingen produkter modtaget"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:125
msgid "*Not applicable*"
msgstr "*Ikke relevant*"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:126
msgid "Waiting Bills"
msgstr "Afventer faktura"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:127
msgid "All/some products received; bill not created"
msgstr "Alle/nogle produkter modtaget; faktura ikke oprettet"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:128
msgid "PO confirmed"
msgstr "Indkøbsordre bekræftet"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:129
msgid "Fully Billed"
msgstr "Fuldt faktureret"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:130
msgid "All/some products received; draft bill created"
msgstr "Alle/nogle produkter modtaget; kladdefaktura oprettet"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:131
msgid "Draft bill created"
msgstr "Kladdefaktura oprettet"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/control_bills.rst:134
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:220
msgid ":doc:`manage`"
msgstr ":doc:`manage`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:3
msgid "Manage vendor bills"
msgstr "Administrer kreditorfakturaer"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:12
msgid ""
"A *vendor bill* is an invoice received for products and/or services "
"purchased by a company from a vendor. Vendor bills record payables as they "
"arrive from vendors, and can include amounts owed for the goods and/or "
"services purchased, sales taxes, freight and delivery charges, and more."
msgstr ""
"En *kreditorfaktura* er en faktura modtaget for produkter og/eller tjenester "
"købt af en virksomhed fra en kreditor. Kreditorfakturaer registrerer "
"kreditorer, efterhånden som de ankommer fra kreditorer, og kan omfatte "
"skyldige beløb for de købte varer og/eller tjenester, moms, fragt- og "
"leveringsomkostninger og mere."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:16
msgid ""
"In Odoo, a vendor bill can be created at different points in the purchasing "
"process, depending on the *bill control* policy selected on the product's "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo kan en leverandørfaktura oprettes på forskellige tidspunkter i "
"indkøbsprocessen, afhængigt af den *fakturakontrols*politik, der er valgt i "
"produktets indstillinger."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:20
msgid "Bill control policies"
msgstr "Politikker for fakturastyring"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:22
msgid ""
"To configure a product's bill control policy, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Products Products`, and click on the "
"desired product to open it. Then, click on the :guilabel:`Purchase` tab. "
"Under the *Vendor Bills* section, the *Control Policy* field lists two "
"policy options:"
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li nakonfigurovat zásadu kontroly faktur produktu, přejděte "
"do :menuselection:`Indkøb --> Produkter Produkter` a klikněte na požadovaný "
"produkt a otevřete jej. Poté klikněte na kartu :guilabel:`Indkøb`. V sekci "
"*Leverandørfakturaer* pole *Kontrolpolitik* uvádí dvě možnosti zásad:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:26
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On ordered quantities`: creates a vendor bill as soon as a "
"purchase order is confirmed. The products and quantities in the purchase "
"order are used to generate a draft bill."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ved bestilte mængder`: vytvoří fakturu dodavatele, jakmile je "
"indkøbsordre bekræftet. Produkty a množství v indkøbsordren slouží k "
"vygenerování konceptu faktury."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:28
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On received quantities`: a bill is only created **after** all (or "
"part) of the total order has been received. The products and quantities "
"received are used to generate a draft bill."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ved modtagne mængder`: faktura se vytvoří **až poté**, co je "
"přijata celá (nebo část) celkové objednávky. Přijaté produkty a množství "
"slouží k vygenerování konceptu faktury."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:None
msgid "Bill control policies on a product record."
msgstr "Zásady kontroly faktur v záznamu produktu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:34
msgid "Once a policy is selected, click :guilabel:`Save` to save the changes."
msgstr ""
"Når en politik er valgt, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Gem` for at gemme "
"ændringerne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:37
msgid "3-way matching"
msgstr "Trevejsafstemning"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:39
msgid ""
"The *3-way matching* policy ensures vendor bills are only paid once all (or "
"some) products in a purchase order (PO) have been received."
msgstr ""
"Politikken for *3-vejs-matching* sikrer, at kreditorfakturaer først betales, "
"når alle (eller nogle) produkter i en indkøbsordre (PO) er modtaget."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:42
msgid ""
"To activate 3-way matching, navigate to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and scroll to the :guilabel:`Invoicing` section."
msgstr ""
"For at aktivere 3-vejs-matching skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Indkøb-"
"app --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger` og rulle til "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Fakturering`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:45
msgid ""
"Tick the checkbox next to :guilabel:`3-way matching`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Sæt kryds i afkrydsningsfeltet ved siden af :guilabel:`3-vejs-matching` og "
"klik på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:48
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`3-way matching` feature is **only** intended to work with "
"the :guilabel:`Bill Control` policy set to :guilabel:`Received quantities`."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen :guilabel:`3-vejs-matching` er **kun** beregnet til at fungere "
"med politikken :guilabel:`Fakturastyring` sat til :guilabel:`Modtagne "
"mængder`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:52
msgid "Manage vendor bills in Accounting"
msgstr "Administrer kreditorfakturaer i Regnskab"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:54
msgid ""
"Vendor bills can also be created directly from the *Accounting* app, without "
"having to create a purchase order first."
msgstr ""
"Leverandørfakturaer kan også oprettes direkte fra *Regnskab*-appen uden "
"først at skulle oprette en indkøbsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:57
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Vendors --> Bills`, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. Doing so reveals a blank :guilabel:`Vendor Bill` form."
msgstr ""
"Naviger til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Leverandører --> Fakturaer`, og "
"klik på :guilabel:`Ny`. Dette åbner en tom :guilabel:`Leverandørfaktura`-"
"formular."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:60
msgid ""
"Add a vendor in the :guilabel:`Vendor` field. Then, in "
"the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line` to add "
"products."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj en leverandør i feltet :guilabel:`Leverandør`. Klik derefter "
"på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` under fanen :guilabel:`Fakturalinjer` for at "
"tilføje produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:63
msgid ""
"Select a product from the drop-down menu in the :guilabel:`Product` field, "
"and enter the quantity to order in the :guilabel:`Quantity` field."
msgstr ""
"Vælg et produkt fra rullemenuen i feltet :guilabel:`Produkt`, og indtast "
"mængden, der skal bestilles, i feltet :guilabel:`Antal`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:66
msgid ""
"Select a :guilabel:`Bill Date`, and configure any other necessary "
"information. Finally, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the bill."
msgstr ""
"Vælg en :guilabel:`Fakturadato`, og konfigurer eventuelle andre nødvendige "
"oplysninger. Klik til sidst på :guilabel:`Bekræft` for at bekræfte fakturaen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:69
msgid ""
"Once confirmed, click the :guilabel:`Journal Items` tab to view "
"the :guilabel:`Account` journals. These journals are populated based on the "
"configuration on the corresponding :guilabel:`Vendor` "
"and :guilabel:`Product` forms."
msgstr ""
"Når fakturaen er bekræftet, skal du klikke på "
"fanen :guilabel:`Journalposter` for at se :guilabel:`Konto`-journalerne. "
"Disse journaler udfyldes baseret på konfigurationen på de "
"tilsvarende :guilabel:`Leverandør`- og :guilabel:`Produkt`-formularer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:73
msgid ""
"If necessary, click :guilabel:`Credit Note` to add a credit note to the "
"bill. Additionally, a :guilabel:`Bill Reference` number can be added."
msgstr ""
"Hvis det er nødvendigt, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Kreditnota` for at "
"tilføje en kreditnota til fakturaen. Derudover kan "
"et :guilabel:`Fakturareference`-nummer tilføjes."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:76
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Register Payment`, followed "
"by :guilabel:`Create Payment`, to complete the :guilabel:`Vendor Bill`."
msgstr ""
"Når du er klar, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Registrer betaling`, efterfulgt "
"af :guilabel:`Opret betaling`, for at "
"færdiggøre :guilabel:`Leverandørfakturaen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:80
msgid ""
"To link a draft bill to an existing purchase order, click the drop-down menu "
"next to :guilabel:`Auto-Complete` *before* clicking :guilabel:`Confirm`, and "
"select a |PO| from the menu."
msgstr ""
"For at knytte en udkast til faktura til en eksisterende indkøbsordre skal du "
"klikke på rullemenuen ved siden af :guilabel:`Autofuldførelse` *før* du "
"klikker på :guilabel:`Bekræft`, og vælge en |PO| fra menuen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:83
msgid "The bill auto-populates with the information from the chosen |PO|."
msgstr "Fakturaen udfyldes automatisk med oplysningerne fra den valgte |PO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:0
msgid "Auto-complete drop-down list on draft vendor bill."
msgstr "Autofuldførelse-rullemenu på leverandørfaktura i udkast."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:90
msgid "Batch billing"
msgstr "Batchfakturering"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:92
msgid ""
"Vendor bills can be processed and managed in batches in the *Accounting* app."
msgstr ""
"Leverandørfakturaer kan behandles og administreres i batches i *Regnskab*-"
"appen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:94
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Vendors --> Bills`. Then, "
"click the :guilabel:`checkbox` in the top-left corner, beside "
"the :guilabel:`Number` column, under the :guilabel:`New` button."
msgstr ""
"Naviger til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Leverandører --> Fakturaer`. Klik "
"derefter på :guilabel:`afkrydsningsfeltet` i øverste venstre hjørne ved "
"siden af kolonnen :guilabel:`Nummer` under knappen :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:98
msgid ""
"This selects all existing vendor bills with a :guilabel:`Status` "
"of :guilabel:`Posted` or :guilabel:`Draft`."
msgstr ""
"Dette vælger alle eksisterende leverandørfakturaer med en :guilabel:`Status` "
"som :guilabel:`Bogført` eller :guilabel:`Udkast`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:101
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-print` :guilabel:`Print` button to print the selected "
"invoices or bills."
msgstr ""
"Klik på knappen :icon:`fa-print` :guilabel:`Udskriv` for at udskrive de "
"valgte fakturaer eller regninger."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:103
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Register Payment` to create and process payments for "
"multiple vendor bills at once."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Registrer betaling` for at oprette og behandle betalinger "
"for flere leverandørfakturaer på én gang."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:106
msgid ""
"Only payments with their :guilabel:`Status` listed as :guilabel:`Posted` can "
"be billed in batches. Payments in the :guilabel:`Draft` stage **must** be "
"posted before they can be included in a batch billing."
msgstr ""
"Kun betalinger med deres :guilabel:`Status` angivet som :guilabel:`Bogført` "
"kan faktureres i batches. Betalinger i :guilabel:`Udkast`-fasen **skal** "
"bogføres, før de kan inkluderes i en batchfakturering."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:110
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Register Payment` opens a :guilabel:`Register Payment` "
"pop-up window. From the pop-up window, select the :guilabel:`Journal` the "
"bills should post to, choose a :guilabel:`Payment Date`, and select "
"a :guilabel:`Payment Method`."
msgstr ""
"Ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Registrer betaling` åbnes et pop op-vindue "
"med :guilabel:`Registrer betaling`. Fra pop op-vinduet skal du vælge "
"den :guilabel:`Journal`, fakturaerne skal bogføres til, vælge "
"en :guilabel:`Betalingsdato` og vælge en :guilabel:`Betalingsmetode`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:114
msgid ""
"There is also the option to :guilabel:`Group Payments` together from this "
"pop-up window, as well. If this checkbox is ticked, only one payment is "
"created, instead of one per bill. This option only appears if the *Batch "
"Payments* feature is enabled in the settings of "
"the :menuselection:`Accounting` app."
msgstr ""
"Der er også mulighed for at :guilabel:`Gruppere betalinger` sammen fra dette "
"pop op-vindue. Hvis dette afkrydsningsfelt er markeret, oprettes kun én "
"betaling i stedet for én pr. faktura. Denne indstilling vises kun, hvis "
"funktionen *Batchbetalinger* er aktiveret i indstillingerne "
"for :menuselection:`Regnskab`-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:119
msgid ""
"Once ready, click the :guilabel:`Create Payment` button. This creates a list "
"of journal entries on a separate page. The journal entries on this list are "
"all tied to their corresponding vendor bills."
msgstr ""
"Når du er klar, klik på knappen :guilabel:`Opret betaling`. Dette opretter "
"en liste over posteringer på en separat side. Posteringerne på denne liste "
"er alle knyttet til deres tilsvarende leverandørfakturaer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:None
msgid "Batch billing register payment pop-up window."
msgstr "Pop-up-vindue til registrering af batchbetaling."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/manage.rst:127
msgid ":doc:`control_bills`"
msgstr ":doc:`control_bills`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:3
msgid "Purchase templates"
msgstr "Indkøbsskabeloner"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:10
msgid ""
"*Purchase templates* are an agreement type that allow for the repeated "
"creation of requests for quotations (RFQs) for recurring purchases. Products "
"can then be added and quantities can be changed, as needed. |Pts| can be "
"used for multiple vendors, saving time and simplifying the |RFQ| process."
msgstr ""
"*Indkøbskabeloner* er en aftaletype, der giver mulighed for gentagen "
"oprettelse af tilbudsanmodninger for tilbagevendende køb. Produkter kan "
"derefter tilføjes, og mængder kan ændres efter behov. |Pts| kan bruges til "
"flere leverandører, hvilket sparer tid og forenkler |RFQ|-processen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:14
msgid ""
"|Pts| differ from *blanket orders* in that a :doc:`blanket order "
"<blanket_orders>` is a large order split into several deliveries, therefore "
"all |RFQs| must be for the same vendor. |PTs| can be replicated for multiple "
"vendors, and can copy over quantities, which is useful when placing frequent "
"orders."
msgstr ""
"|Pts| adskiller sig fra *rammeordrer* ved, at en :doc:`rammeordre "
"<blanket_orders>` er en stor ordre opdelt i flere leverancer, derfor skal "
"alle |RFQs| være til samme leverandør. |PTs| kan replikeres til flere "
"leverandører og kan kopiere mængder, hvilket er nyttigt ved hyppige ordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:22
msgid ""
"First, navigate to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Orders` section, tick "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase Agreements` checkbox. Click :guilabel:`Save` to save "
"the changes."
msgstr ""
"Gå først til :menuselection:`Indkøb --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`. "
"Under sektionen :guilabel:`Ordrer` skal du markere "
"afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Indkøbsaftaler`. Klik på :guilabel:`Gem` for "
"at gemme ændringerne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:None
msgid "The Purchase agreements setting in the Purchase app."
msgstr "Indstillingen Indkøbsaftaler i Indkøb-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:30
msgid "Create a new template"
msgstr "Opret ny skabelon"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:32
msgid ""
"Navigate :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Orders --> Purchase Agreements` "
"and click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Indkøb --> Ordrer --> Indkøbsaftaler`, og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:34
msgid "Select a :guilabel:`Vendor` from the drop-down list."
msgstr "Vælg en :guilabel:`Leverandør` fra rullelisten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:37
msgid ""
"To make this template available to use with multiple vendors, leave "
"the :guilabel:`Vendor` field blank."
msgstr ""
"For at gøre denne skabelon tilgængelig til brug med flere leverandører skal "
"du lade feltet :guilabel:`Leverandør` stå tomt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:40
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Agreement Type` field, select :guilabel:`Purchase "
"Template` from the drop-down."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Aftaletype` skal du vælge :guilabel:`Indkøbsskabelon` "
"fra rullelisten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:42
msgid ""
"Confirm the information in the remaining fields is correct, or update as "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"Bekræft, at oplysningerne i de resterende felter er korrekte, eller opdater "
"efter behov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:44
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Products` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line`, and select "
"the desired product. Update the :guilabel:`Quantity`, and set "
"the :guilabel:`Unit Price`."
msgstr ""
"På fanen :guilabel:`Produkter` skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` "
"og vælge det ønskede produkt. Opdater :guilabel:`Mængde`, og "
"indstil :guilabel:`Enhedspris`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:53
msgid "After adding all necessary products, click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Når alle nødvendige produkter er tilføjet, klik på :guilabel:`Bekræft`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:56
msgid "Create a new RFQ from a purchase template"
msgstr "Opret en ny tilbudsanmodning fra en indkøbsskabelon"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:58
msgid ""
"After confirming a |pt|, new quotations can be created directly from the |"
"pt| form. |RFQs| using this form are pre-populated with information based on "
"the rules set in the form. Additionally, new quotations are automatically "
"linked to this |pt| form, via the :icon:`fa-list-alt` :guilabel:`RFQs/"
"Orders` smart button at the top of the form."
msgstr ""
"Efter bekræftelse af en |pt| kan nye tilbud oprettes direkte fra |pt|-"
"formularen. |RFQs|, der bruger denne formular, er forudfyldt med information "
"baseret på reglerne angivet i formularen. Desuden linkes nye tilbud "
"automatisk til denne |pt|-formular via den smarte knap :icon:`fa-list-"
"alt` :guilabel:`Tilbudsanmodninger/ordrer` øverst på formularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:63
msgid ""
"To :ref:`create a new quotation <purchase/manage_deals/create-new-rfq>`, "
"click :guilabel:`New Quotation`. This opens a new |RFQ|, that is pre-"
"populated with the correct information, depending on the settings configured "
"on the |pt| form."
msgstr ""
"For at :ref:`oprette et nyt tilbud <purchase/manage_deals/create-new-rfq>` "
"skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Nyt tilbud`. Dette åbner en ny |RFQ|, der er "
"forudfyldt med de korrekte oplysninger afhængigt af de indstillinger, der er "
"konfigureret på |pt|-formularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:67
msgid ""
"If there was no vendor identified on the |pt|, choose a :guilabel:`Vendor` "
"from the drop-down list. Products can be added to the |RFQ| by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Add a product` in the :guilabel:`Products` tab. To "
"remove a product, click the :icon:`fa-trash-o` :guilabel:`(trash)` icon at "
"the far-right of the product line."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der ikke blev angivet en leverandør på |pt|, skal du vælge "
"en :guilabel:`Leverandør` fra rullelisten. Produkter kan tilføjes til |RFQ| "
"ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj et produkt` på "
"fanen :guilabel:`Produkter`. For at fjerne et produkt skal du klikke på "
"ikonet :icon:`fa-trash-o` :guilabel:`(papirkurv)` helt til højre på "
"produktlinjen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:72
msgid ""
"From the new |RFQ| form, click :guilabel:`Send by Email` to compose and send "
"an email to the listed vendor. Click :guilabel:`Print RFQ` to generate a "
"printable PDF of the quotation; or, once ready, click :guilabel:`Confirm "
"Order` to confirm the purchase order."
msgstr ""
"Fra den nye |RFQ|-formular skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Send via e-mail` for "
"at skrive og sende en e-mail til den anførte leverandør. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Udskriv tilbudsanmodning` for at generere en PDF til "
"udskrivning af tilbuddet, eller klik på :guilabel:`Bekræft ordre`, når du er "
"klar, for at bekræfte indkøbsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:76
msgid ""
"After confirming the order, return to the |pt| via the breadcrumbs. "
"The :icon:`fa-list-alt` :guilabel:`RFQs/Orders` smart button has been "
"updated to list the confirmed order."
msgstr ""
"Efter bekræftelse af ordren skal du vende tilbage til |pt| via "
"brødkrummerne. Den smarte knap :icon:`fa-list-"
"alt` :guilabel:`Tilbudsanmodninger/Ordrer` er blevet opdateret til at vise "
"den bekræftede ordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/purchase_templates.rst:None
msgid "The RFQ smart button on a purchase template."
msgstr "Den smarte knap for tilbudsanmodninger på en indkøbsskabelon."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:3
msgid "Requests for quotation"
msgstr "Anmodninger for tilbud"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:10
msgid ""
"Odoo's requests for quotation (RFQs) feature in the **Purchase** app "
"standardizes ordering products from multiple vendors with varying prices and "
"delivery times."
msgstr ""
"Odoos funktion til tilbudsanmodninger i **Indkøb**-appen standardiserer "
"bestilling af produkter fra flere leverandører med varierende priser og "
"leveringstider."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:13
msgid ""
"|RFQs| are documents companies send to vendors requesting product pricing. "
"In Odoo, once the vendor approves the |RFQ|, the purchase order (PO) is "
"confirmed to align on lead times and pricing."
msgstr ""
"|RFQs| er dokumenter, som virksomheder sender til leverandører for at anmode "
"om produktpriser. Når leverandøren godkender |RFQ| i Odoo, bekræftes "
"indkøbsordren for at tilpasse leveringstider og priser."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:22
msgid ""
"To auto-populate product information and prices on an |RFQ|, configure "
"products by going to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Products --> "
"Products`. Select an existing product, or create a new one by "
"selecting :guilabel:`New`. Doing so opens the product form, where sales and "
"purchasing data can be configured."
msgstr ""
"For automatisk at udfylde produktoplysninger og priser på en |RFQ| skal du "
"konfigurere produkter ved at gå til :menuselection:`Indkøb-app --> Produkter "
"--> Produkter`. Vælg et eksisterende produkt, eller opret et nyt ved at "
"vælge :guilabel:`Ny`. Dette åbner produktformularen, hvor salgs- og "
"indkøbsdata kan konfigureres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:27
msgid ""
"To configure purchasable products, tick the :guilabel:`Purchase` checkbox, "
"under the product name. Next, go to the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab, and "
"enable the :guilabel:`Buy` route."
msgstr ""
"For at konfigurere produkter, der kan købes, skal du markere "
"afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Indkøb` under produktnavnet. Gå derefter til "
"fanen :guilabel:`Lager`, og aktivér ruten :guilabel:`Køb`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:31
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Inventory` tab and routes are only visible if using "
"the :doc:`Inventory app <../../inventory>`."
msgstr ""
"Fanen :guilabel:`Lager` og ruter er kun synlige, hvis du bruger :doc:`Lager-"
"appen <../../inventory>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:35
msgid ""
":doc:`Configure product types and track quantities <../../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Konfigurer produkttyper og spor mængder <../../../inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/product_management/configure>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:None
msgid "Required configuration for purchasable products."
msgstr "Nødvendig konfiguration for produkter, der kan købes."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:45
msgid "Vendor pricelist"
msgstr "Leverandørens prisliste"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:47
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Purchase` tab of the product form, click :guilabel:`Add a "
"line` to input the vendor and their price, to have this information auto-"
"populate on an |RFQ| each time the product is listed."
msgstr ""
"På fanen :guilabel:`Indkøb` i produktformularen skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` for at indtaste leverandøren og deres pris, "
"så disse oplysninger automatisk udfyldes på en |RFQ|, hver gang produktet "
"angives."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:52
msgid ":doc:`../products/pricelist`"
msgstr ":doc:`../products/pricelist`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:54
msgid ""
"Default columns include :guilabel:`Quantity`, :guilabel:`Unit Price`, "
"and :guilabel:`Delivery Lead Time`, but other columns "
"like, :guilabel:`Vendor Product Code` or :guilabel:`Discount (%)`, can also "
"be enabled."
msgstr ""
"Standardkolonner inkluderer :guilabel:`Mængde`, :guilabel:`Enhedspris` "
"og :guilabel:`Leveringstid`, men andre kolonner "
"som :guilabel:`Leverandørproduktskode` eller :guilabel:`Rabat (%)` kan også "
"aktiveres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:58
msgid ""
"To enable or disable columns, click the :icon:`oi-settings-"
"adjust` :guilabel:`(additional options)` icon on the right side of the "
"header row to reveal a drop-down menu of additional columns that can be "
"added (or removed) from the :guilabel:`Purchase` tab."
msgstr ""
"For at aktivere eller deaktivere kolonner skal du klikke på ikonet :icon:`oi-"
"settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(yderligere muligheder)` på højre side af "
"overskriftrækken for at afsløre en rullemenu med yderligere kolonner, der "
"kan tilføjes (eller fjernes) fra fanen :guilabel:`Indkøb`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:63
msgid ""
"Alternatively, prices and delivery lead times for existing products can be "
"added by going to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Configuration --> Vendor "
"Pricelists`. Click :guilabel:`New` in the top-left corner. In "
"the :guilabel:`Vendor` section of the pricelist form that appears, add the "
"product information as it pertains to the vendor."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt kan priser og leveringstider for eksisterende produkter tilføjes "
"ved at gå til :menuselection:`Indkøb-app --> Konfiguration --> "
"Leverandørprislister`. Klik på :guilabel:`Ny` i øverste venstre hjørne. I "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Leverandør` på den prislisteformular, der vises, skal "
"du tilføje produktoplysningerne, som de vedrører leverandøren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:69
msgid "Order products"
msgstr "Bestil produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:71
msgid ""
"With products and prices configured, follow these steps to create and send |"
"RFQs| to make purchases for the company."
msgstr ""
"Med produkter og priser konfigureret skal du følge disse trin for at oprette "
"og sende |RFQs| for at foretage indkøb for virksomheden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:75
msgid "|RFQ| dashboard"
msgstr "|RFQ|-dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:77
msgid ""
"To get started, navigate to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Orders --> "
"Requests for Quotation`."
msgstr ""
"For at komme i gang skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Indkøb-app --> "
"Ordrer --> Tilbudsanmodninger`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:79
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Requests for Quotation` dashboard displays an overview of the "
"company's |RFQs|, |POs|, and their status. The top of the screen breaks down "
"all |RFQs| in the company, as well as individual ones (where the user is the "
"buyer) with a summary of their status."
msgstr ""
"Dashboardet :guilabel:`Tilbudsanmodninger` viser en oversigt over "
"virksomhedens |RFQs|, |POs| og deres status. Øverst på skærmen opdeles alle |"
"RFQs| i virksomheden samt individuelle (hvor brugeren er indkøber) med et "
"resume af deres status."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:83
msgid ""
"The top-right corner also provides a report of the company's recent "
"purchases by total value, lead times, and number of |RFQs| sent."
msgstr ""
"Det øverste højre hjørne giver også en rapport over virksomhedens seneste "
"indkøb efter samlet værdi, leveringstider og antal sendte |RFQs|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:86
msgid "Additionally, the dashboard includes buttons for:"
msgstr "Desuden inkluderer dashboardet knapper til:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:88
msgid ""
":guilabel:`To Send`: orders in the |RFQ| stage that have not been sent to "
"the vendor."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`At sende`: ordrer i |RFQ|-fasen, der ikke er blevet sendt til "
"leverandøren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Waiting`: |RFQs| that have been sent by email, and are waiting on "
"vendor confirmation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Afventer`: |RFQs|, der er blevet sendt via e-mail og afventer "
"leverandørens bekræftelse."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:90
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Late`: |RFQs| or |POs| where the :guilabel:`Order Deadline` has "
"passed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`For sent`: |RFQs| eller |POs|, hvor :guilabel:`ordrefristen` er "
"overskredet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:None
msgid "RFQ dashboard with orders and order statuses."
msgstr "Anmodning om tilbud-dashboard med ordrer og ordrestatus."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:95
msgid ""
"In addition to view options, the :guilabel:`Requests for Quotation` "
"dashboard provides :guilabel:`Filters` and :guilabel:`Group By` options, "
"accessible via the search bar drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Ud over visningsmuligheder giver :guilabel:`Anmodninger om tilbud`-"
"dashboardet :guilabel:`filtre` og :guilabel:`gruppér efter`-muligheder, "
"tilgængelige via søgefeltets rullemenu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:99
msgid ":doc:`../../../essentials/search`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../essentials/search`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:104
msgid "Create a new |RFQ|"
msgstr "Opret en ny |RFQ|"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:106
msgid ""
"To create a new |RFQ|, click the :guilabel:`New` button on the top-left "
"corner of the :guilabel:`Requests for Quotation` dashboard to reveal a new |"
"PO| form."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en ny |RFQ|, klik på knappen :guilabel:`Ny` i øverste venstre "
"hjørne af :guilabel:`Anmodninger om tilbud`-dashboardet for at vise en ny |"
"PO|-formular."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:109
msgid "Start by assigning a :guilabel:`Vendor`."
msgstr "Begynd med at tildele en :guilabel:`leverandør`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:111
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Vendor Reference` field points to the sales and delivery "
"order numbers sent by the vendor. This comes in handy once products are "
"received, and the |PO| needs to be matched to the delivery order."
msgstr ""
"Feltet :guilabel:`leverandørreference` henviser til salgs- og "
"leveringsordrenumrene sendt af leverandøren. Dette er nyttigt, når produkter "
"modtages, og |PO| skal matches med leveringsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:115
msgid ""
"With the :doc:`Purchase Agreements feature <blanket_orders>` activated, "
"the :guilabel:`Blanket Order` field appears, referring to long-term purchase "
"agreements on recurring orders with set pricing. To view and configure "
"blanket orders, head to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Orders --> Purchase "
"agreements`."
msgstr ""
"Med funktionen :doc:`rammeaftaler <blanket_orders>` aktiveret vises "
"feltet :guilabel:`rammeordre`, som henviser til langsigtede indkøbsaftaler "
"på tilbagevendende ordrer med fastsat prissætning. For at se og konfigurere "
"rammeordrer, gå til :menuselection:`Indkøb --> Ordrer --> Indkøbsaftaler`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:121
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Purchase agreements` view only appears if "
"the :guilabel:`Blanket Order` setting is enabled. To do so, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Configuration --> Settings`, then tick "
"the :guilabel:`Blanket Orders` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Visningen :guilabel:`indkøbsaftaler` vises kun, hvis "
"indstillingen :guilabel:`rammeordre` er aktiveret. For at gøre dette, "
"naviger til :menuselection:`Indkøb --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, og "
"sæt derefter flueben ved :guilabel:`rammeordrer`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:125
msgid ""
"Next, configure an :guilabel:`Order Deadline`, which is the date by which "
"the vendor must confirm their agreement to supply the products."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurer dernæst en :guilabel:`ordrefrist`, som er den dato, hvorpå "
"leverandøren skal bekræfte deres accept af at levere produkterne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:129
msgid ""
"After the :guilabel:`Order Deadline` is exceeded, the |RFQ| is marked as "
"late, but the products can still be ordered."
msgstr ""
"Efter at :guilabel:`ordrefristen` er overskredet, markeres |RFQ| som "
"forsinket, men produkterne kan stadig bestilles."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:132
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Expected Arrival` is automatically calculated based on "
"the :guilabel:`Order Deadline` and vendor lead time. Tick the checkbox "
"for :guilabel:`Ask confirmation` to ask the vendor to confirm the shipping "
"date by email."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forventet ankomst` beregnes automatisk baseret "
"på :guilabel:`ordrefristen` og leverandørens leveringstid. Sæt flueben "
"ved :guilabel:`bed om bekræftelse` for at bede leverandøren om at bekræfte "
"forsendelsesdatoen via e-mail."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:136
msgid ""
"With the :doc:`Storage Locations feature <../../inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"inventory_management/use_locations>` activated, the :guilabel:`Deliver to` "
"field appears, which specifies which warehouse operation (set in the "
"**Inventory** app) is used to receive the shipment."
msgstr ""
"Med funktionen :doc:`lagerplaceringer <../../inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"inventory_management/use_locations>` aktiveret vises feltet :guilabel:`levér "
"til`, som angiver hvilken lageroperation (indstillet i **Lager**-appen), der "
"bruges til at modtage forsendelsen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:141
msgid ""
"Select the receiving warehouse address here, or select :guilabel:`Dropship` "
"to indicate that this order is to be shipped directly to the end customer. "
"When :guilabel:`Dropship` is selected, the :guilabel:`Dropship address` "
"field is enabled. Contact names auto-populate here from the **Contacts** app."
msgstr ""
"Vælg den modtagende lageradresse her, eller vælg :guilabel:`dropship` for at "
"angive, at denne ordre skal sendes direkte til slutkunden. "
"Når :guilabel:`dropship` er valgt, aktiveres feltet :guilabel:`dropship-"
"adresse`. Kontaktnavne udfyldes automatisk herfra fra **Adressebog**-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:147
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Dropship` options only appear if the :guilabel:`Dropshipping` "
"setting is enabled in the **Inventory** app. To do so, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`, then tick "
"the :guilabel:`Dropshipping` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Mulighederne for :guilabel:`dropship` vises kun, hvis "
"indstillingen :guilabel:`dropshipping` er aktiveret i **Lager**-appen. For "
"at gøre dette, naviger til :menuselection:`Lager --> Konfiguration --> "
"Indstillinger`, og sæt derefter flueben ved :guilabel:`dropshipping`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:152
msgid ""
"To create |RFQs| using different currencies, each currency needs to be "
"enabled in the **Invoicing** app settings. See :doc:`../../../sales/sales/"
"products_prices/prices/currencies` to learn more."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette |RFQs| ved hjælp af forskellige valutaer skal hver valuta "
"aktiveres i **Fakturering**-appens indstillinger. Se :doc:`../../../sales/"
"sales/products_prices/prices/currencies` for at lære mere."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:157
msgid "Products tab"
msgstr "Fanen Produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:159
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Products` tab, add the products to be ordered. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add a product`, and type in the product name, or select the "
"item from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Produkter` tilføjes de produkter, der skal bestilles. "
"Klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj et produkt`, og indtast produktnavnet, eller vælg "
"varen fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:162
msgid ""
"To create a new product and add it, type the new product name in "
"the :guilabel:`Product` column, select :guilabel:`Create [product name]` "
"from the resulting drop-down menu and manually add the unit price. "
"Alternatively, select :guilabel:`Create and edit...` to be taken to the "
"product form for that new item."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette et nyt produkt og tilføje det, indtast det nye produktnavn i "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Produkt`, vælg :guilabel:`Opret [produktnavn]` fra den "
"fremkomne rullemenu og tilføj enhedsprisen manuelt. Alternativt kan du "
"vælge :guilabel:`Opret og rediger...` for at blive ført til "
"produktformularen for den nye vare."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:167
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Catalog` can also be selected to navigate to a product menu from "
"the chosen vendor. From here, products can be added to the cart."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Katalog` kan også vælges for at navigere til en produktmenu fra "
"den valgte leverandør. Herfra kan produkter tilføjes til kurven."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:171
msgid ""
"To make adjustments to products and prices, access the product form by "
"clicking the :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(right arrow)` icon that "
"becomes available upon hovering over the :guilabel:`Product` name."
msgstr ""
"For at foretage justeringer af produkter og priser, få adgang til "
"produktformularen ved at klikke på ikonet :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`(pil til højre)`, der bliver tilgængeligt ved at holde "
"musen over :guilabel:`Produkt`-navnet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:176
msgid "Send the |RFQ|"
msgstr "Send |RFQ|"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:178
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Send by Email` reveals a :guilabel:`Compose Email` pop-"
"up window, with a :guilabel:`Purchase: Request for Quotation` template "
"loaded, ready to send to the vendor's email address (configured in the "
"**Contacts** app)."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Send via e-mail` for at få vist et pop op-vindue "
"til :guilabel:`Skriv e-mail`, med en skabelon for :guilabel:`Indkøb: "
"Anmodning om tilbud` indlæst, klar til at sende til leverandørens e-"
"mailadresse (konfigureret i **Adressebog**-appen)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:182
msgid ""
"After crafting the desired message, click :guilabel:`Send`. Once sent, the |"
"RFQ| moves to the :guilabel:`RFQ Sent` stage."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have udformet den ønskede besked, klik på :guilabel:`Send`. Når den "
"er sendt, flytter |RFQ| til :guilabel:`RFQ sendt`-fasen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:185
msgid "Clicking :guilabel:`Print RFQ` downloads a PDF of the |RFQ|."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Udskriv RFQ` for at downloade en PDF af |RFQ|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:188
msgid ":doc:`../../../essentials/contacts`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../essentials/contacts`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:193
msgid "Confirm order"
msgstr "Bekræft ordre"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:195
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Confirm Order` directly transforms the |RFQ| into an "
"active |PO|."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Bekræft ordre` for direkte at omdanne |RFQ| til en aktiv |"
"PO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:198
msgid ""
"Odoo tracks communications on each order through the chatter of the |PO| "
"form. This shows the emails sent between the user and the contact, as well "
"as any internal notes and activities. Messages, notes, and activities can "
"also be logged on the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Odoo sporer kommunikation på hver ordre gennem chatteren på |PO|-formularen. "
"Dette viser de e-mails, der er sendt mellem brugeren og kontakten, samt "
"eventuelle interne noter og aktiviteter. Beskeder, noter og aktiviteter kan "
"også logges i chatteren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:202
msgid "Once an |RFQ| is confirmed, it creates a |PO|."
msgstr "Når en |RFQ| er bekræftet, opretter den en |PO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:204
msgid ""
"On the new |PO|, the :guilabel:`Order Deadline` field changes "
"to :guilabel:`Confirmation Date`, which displays the date and time the user "
"confirmed the order."
msgstr ""
"På den nye |PO| ændres feltet :guilabel:`Ordrefrist` "
"til :guilabel:`Bekræftelsesdato`, som viser datoen og tidspunktet, hvor "
"brugeren bekræftede ordren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:207
msgid ""
"Depending on the user's chosen configuration in the **Purchase** app "
"settings, a *vendor bill* is created once products have been ordered or "
"received. For more information, refer to the documentation on :doc:`managing "
"vendor bills <manage>`."
msgstr ""
"Afhængigt af brugerens valgte konfiguration i **Indkøb**-appens "
"indstillinger, oprettes en *leverandørfaktura*, når produkter er blevet "
"bestilt eller modtaget. For mere information, se dokumentationen "
"om :doc:`håndtering af leverandørfakturaer <manage>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:212
msgid ""
"After an order is placed, clicking :guilabel:`Receive Products` records the "
"reception of new products into the database."
msgstr ""
"Efter at en ordre er afgivet, registrerer klik på :guilabel:`Modtag "
"produkter` modtagelsen af nye produkter i databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:216
msgid ""
"With the **Inventory** app installed, confirming a |PO| automatically "
"creates a receipt document, with the product information and expected "
"arrival dates automatically populated."
msgstr ""
"Med **Lager**-appen installeret, opretter bekræftelse af en |PO| automatisk "
"et modtagelsesdokument, hvor produktinformationen og forventede "
"ankomstdatoer automatisk udfyldes."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products.rst:5
msgid "Products"
msgstr "Varer"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:40
msgid "Import vendor pricelist"
msgstr "Importer leverandørprisliste"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:5
msgid ""
"Set vendor prices to auto-populate requests for quotations (RFQs) or "
"purchase orders (POs) with the unit price, once the product is added, which "
"reduces errors and saves time."
msgstr ""
"Indstil leverandørpriser til automatisk at udfylde anmodninger om tilbud "
"(RFQer) eller indkøbsordrer (POer) med enhedsprisen, når produktet tilføjes, "
"hvilket reducerer fejl og sparer tid."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:8
msgid ""
"In Odoo, vendor pricelists can be :ref:`added individually <purchase/"
"products/pricelist>` on the product form, or :ref:`imported in bulk "
"<purchase/products/import-pricelist>`, via an XLSX or CSV file."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo kan leverandørprislister :ref:`tilføjes individuelt <purchase/"
"products/pricelist>` på produktformularen, eller :ref:`importeres samlet "
"<purchase/products/import-pricelist>`, via en XLSX- eller CSV-fil."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:13
msgid ""
"Please review this :doc:`import guide <../../../essentials/"
"export_import_data>` before uploading vendor pricelists."
msgstr ""
"Gennemgå venligst denne :doc:`importguide <../../../essentials/"
"export_import_data>`, før du uploader leverandørprislister."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:19
msgid "On product form"
msgstr "På produktformular"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:21
msgid ""
"To manually add the vendor price on the product form, go to "
"the :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Products --> Products`, and click the "
"desired product."
msgstr ""
"For manuelt at tilføje leverandørprisen på produktformularen skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Indkøb-appen --> Produkter --> Produkter` og klikke på "
"det ønskede produkt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:25
msgid ""
"Product forms are accessible from multiple apps, such as **Sales**, "
"**Inventory**, and **Manufacturing**."
msgstr ""
"Produktformularer er tilgængelige fra flere apps, såsom **Salg**, **Lager** "
"og **Produktion**."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:28
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Purchase` tab of the product form, input the vendor and "
"their price, to have this information auto-populate on a request for "
"quotation each time the product is listed."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Indkøb` på produktformularen skal du indtaste "
"leverandøren og deres pris, så disse oplysninger automatisk udfyldes på en "
"tilbudsanmodning, hver gang produktet vises."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:32
msgid ""
":ref:`Vendor pricelist on product form <purchase/manage_deals/vendor-"
"pricelist>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Leverandørprisliste på produktformular <purchase/manage_deals/vendor-"
"pricelist>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:None
msgid "Vendor pricelist on product form."
msgstr "Leverandørprisliste på produktformular."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:42
msgid ""
"To import vendor pricelists, ensure the XLSX or CSV file is accurately "
"completed. The best way to obtain a correctly formatted template, including "
"product names, references, and vendor details, is to first :ref:`export a "
"pricelist <purchase/products/export-price>` from the database."
msgstr ""
"For at importere leverandørprislister skal du sikre, at XLSX- eller CSV-"
"filen er korrekt udfyldt. Den bedste måde at få en korrekt formateret "
"skabelon, inklusive produktnavne, referencer og leverandøroplysninger, er "
"først at :ref:`eksportere en prisliste <purchase/products/export-price>` fra "
"databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:46
msgid ""
"Modify the exported file, as needed, then import it back into the Odoo "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Rediger den eksporterede fil efter behov, og importer den derefter tilbage i "
"Odoo-databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:51
msgid "Export pricelist"
msgstr "Eksporter prisliste"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:53
msgid ""
"To export a pricelist, go to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Configuration "
"--> Vendor Pricelists`."
msgstr ""
"For at eksportere en prisliste skal du gå til :menuselection:`Indkøb-app --> "
"Konfiguration --> Leverandørprislister`."

