#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:3
msgid "Configure reordering rules"
msgstr "Konfigurer genbestillingsregler"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:5
msgid ""
"For certain products, it is necessary to ensure that there is always a "
"minimum amount available on hand at any given time. Maintaining a minimum "
"stock level ensures that businesses can meet customer demand without delays, "
"and keep operations running smoothly. It also helps buffer against supply "
"chain disruptions and unexpected spikes in demand. Inefficiencies may arise "
"from inaccurate demand forecasting, supply chain delays, and warehouse "
"mismanagement, all of which can lead to increased operational costs and "
"wasted resources."
msgstr ""
"For visse produkter er det nødvendigt at sikre, at der altid er en "
"minimumslagerbeholdning tilgængelig til enhver tid. At opretholde et "
"minimumslager sikrer, at virksomheder kan opfylde kundernes efterspørgsel "
"uden forsinkelser og holde driften kørende problemfrit. Det hjælper også med "
"at beskytte mod forstyrrelser i forsyningskæden og uventede stigninger i "
"efterspørgslen. Ineffektivitet kan opstå fra unøjagtig "
"efterspørgselsprognose, forsinkelser i forsyningskæden og forkert "
"lagerstyring, hvilket alt sammen kan føre til øgede driftsomkostninger og "
"spildte ressourcer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:12
msgid ""
"Keep highly demanded products in-stock at all times using reordering rules, "
"that trigger a RFQ (Request for Quotation) each time the forecasted stock "
"quantities fall below the minimum. :abbr:`RFQs (Requests for Quotation)` "
"generated from reordering rules have the vendor, price, quantity needed to "
"reorder, which makes things faster and more convenient."
msgstr ""
"Hold højt efterspurgte produkter på lager til enhver tid ved hjælp af "
"genbestillingsregler, der udløser en tilbudsanmodning hver gang de "
"forventede lagermængder falder under "
"minimumsværdien. :abbr:`Tilbudsanmodninger`, der genereres fra "
"genbestillingsregler, indeholder leverandør, pris og den mængde, der skal "
"genbestilles, hvilket gør tingene hurtigere og mere praktisk."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:18
msgid ""
"The **Inventory** app must be installed to use reordering rules, as it keeps "
"track of stock quantity."
msgstr ""
"Appen **Lager** skal være installeret for at bruge genbestillingsregler, da "
"den holder styr på lagermængden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:22
msgid "Configure products for reordering"
msgstr "Konfigurer produkter til genbestilling"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:24
msgid ""
"Products must be configured in a specific way before a reordering rule can "
"be added to them."
msgstr ""
"Produkter skal konfigureres på en bestemt måde, før der kan tilføjes en "
"genbestillingsregel til dem."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:26
msgid ""
"Starting from "
"the :menuselection:`Inventory`, :menuselection:`Manufacturing`, :menuselection:`Purchase`, "
"or :menuselection:`Sales` app, navigate to :menuselection:`Products --> "
"Products` and then click :guilabel:`New` to make a new product. "
"Alternatively, find a product that already exists in the database and click "
"into it's product form."
msgstr ""
"Start fra "
"appen :menuselection:`Lager`, :menuselection:`Produktion`, :menuselection:`Indkøb` "
"eller :menuselection:`Salg`, naviger til :menuselection:`Produkter --> "
"Produkter`, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Ny` for at oprette et nyt "
"produkt. Alternativt kan du finde et produkt, der allerede findes i "
"databasen, og klikke ind på dets produktformular."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:31
msgid ""
"Next, on the product form, enable reordering by ticking "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase` checkbox underneath the :guilabel:`Product` name "
"field. Then, under the :guilabel:`General Information` tab, set "
"the :guilabel:`Product Type` to :guilabel:`Goods`. Finally, tick the "
"checkbox labeled :guilabel:`Track Inventory`, and select an :doc:`option "
"<../../inventory/product_management/product_tracking>` from the drop-down."
msgstr ""
"Derefter skal du på produktformularen aktivere genbestilling ved at markere "
"afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Purchase` under feltet :guilabel:`Product`. "
"Under fanen :guilabel:`General Information` skal du "
"indstille :guilabel:`Product Type` til :guilabel:`Goods`. Afslut med at "
"markere afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Track Inventory` og vælge "
"en :doc:`mulighed <../../inventory/product_management/product_tracking>` fra "
"rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:None
msgid "Configure a product for reordering in Odoo."
msgstr "Konfigurer et produkt til genbestilling i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:41
msgid "Add a reordering rule to a product"
msgstr "Tilføj en genbestillingsregel til et produkt"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:43
msgid ""
"After properly configuring a product, a reordering rule can be added to it "
"by selecting the now visible :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`Reordering Rules` "
"smart button at the top of that product's form, then "
"clicking :guilabel:`Create` on the :guilabel:`Reordering Rules` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Når et produkt er konfigureret korrekt, kan der tilføjes en "
"genbestillingsregel ved at klikke på den nu synlige :icon:`fa-"
"refresh` :guilabel:`Reordering Rules` smart-knap øverst på produktets "
"formular og derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Create` på :guilabel:`Reordering "
"Rules` dashboardet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:48
msgid ""
"If the :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`Reordering Rules` smart button is not "
"visible, click :guilabel:`More`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`Reordering Rules` smart-knappen ikke er "
"synlig, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`More`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:51
msgid ""
"Once created, the reordering rule can be configured to generate purchase "
"orders automatically by defining the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Når reglen er oprettet, kan genbestillingsreglen konfigureres til automatisk "
"at generere indkøbsordrer ved at definere følgende felter:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:54
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Location` specifies where the ordered quantities should be stored "
"once they are received and entered into stock."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Location` angiver, hvor de bestilte mængder skal lagres, når de "
"er modtaget og registreret på lager."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:56
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Min Quantity` sets the lower threshold for the reordering rule "
"while :guilabel:`Max Quantity` sets the upper threshold. If the stock on "
"hand falls below the minimum quantity, a new purchase order is then created "
"to replenish it up to the maximum quantity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Min Quantity` angiver den nedre grænse for genbestillingsreglen, "
"mens :guilabel:`Max Quantity` angiver den øvre grænse. Hvis "
"lagerbeholdningen falder under minimumsmængden, oprettes der en ny "
"indkøbsordre for at genopfylde op til maksimumsmængden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:61
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Min Quantity` is set to `5` and :guilabel:`Max Quantity` is "
"set to `25` and the stock on hand falls to four, a purchase order is then "
"created for 21 units of the product."
msgstr ""
"Hvis :guilabel:`Min Quantity` er sat til `5` og :guilabel:`Max Quantity` er "
"sat til `25`, og lagerbeholdningen falder til fire, oprettes der en "
"indkøbsordre på 21 enheder af produktet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Multiple Quantity` can be configured so that products are only "
"ordered in batches of a certain quantity. Depending on the number entered, "
"this can result in the creation of a purchase order that would put the "
"resulting stock on hand above what is specified in the :guilabel:`Max "
"Quantity` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Multiple Quantity` kan konfigureres, så produkter kun bestilles i "
"partier af en bestemt mængde. Afhængigt af det indtastede tal kan dette "
"resultere i oprettelse af en indkøbsordre, der ville bringe den resulterende "
"lagerbeholdning over det, der er angivet i feltet :guilabel:`Max Quantity`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:70
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Max Quantity` is set to `100` but :guilabel:`Multiple "
"Quantity` is set to order the product in batches of `200`, a purchase order "
"is then created for 200 units of the product."
msgstr ""
"Hvis :guilabel:`Max Quantity` er sat til `100`, men :guilabel:`Multiple "
"Quantity` er sat til at bestille produktet i partier af `200`, oprettes der "
"en indkøbsordre på 200 enheder af produktet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:74
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unit` specifies the unit of measurement by which the quantity is "
"to be ordered. For discrete products, this should be set to `Units`. "
"However, it can also be set to units of measurement like `Volume` or "
"`Weight` for non-discrete products like water or bricks."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Unit` angiver den måleenhed, som mængden skal bestilles i. For "
"diskrete produkter bør dette sættes til `Units`. Det kan dog også sættes til "
"måleenheder som `Volume` eller `Weight` for ikke-diskrete produkter som vand "
"eller mursten."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:None
msgid "Configure the reordering rule in Odoo."
msgstr "Konfigurer genbestillingsreglen i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:85
msgid "Manually trigger reordering rules using the scheduler"
msgstr "Udløs genbestillingsregler manuelt ved hjælp af scheduleren"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:87
msgid ""
"Reordering rules are automatically triggered by the scheduler, which runs "
"once a day by default. To trigger reordering rules manually, turn on "
"developer mode, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations --> "
"Procurement: Run Scheduler`. On the pop-up window, confirm the manual action "
"by clicking :guilabel:`Run Scheduler`."
msgstr ""
"Genbestillingsregler udløses automatisk af scheduleren, som som standard "
"kører én gang dagligt. For at udløse genbestillingsregler manuelt skal du "
"aktivere udviklertilstand og navigere til :menuselection:`Lager app --> "
"Operationer --> Indkøb: Kør scheduler`. I pop-up-vinduet skal du bekræfte "
"den manuelle handling ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Run Scheduler`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:93
msgid ""
"Manually triggering reordering rules will also trigger any other scheduled "
"actions."
msgstr ""
"Manuel udløsning af genbestillingsregler vil også udløse andre planlagte "
"handlinger."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:96
msgid "Manage reordering rules"
msgstr "Administrer genbestillingsregler"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:98
msgid ""
"To manage the reordering rules for a single product, navigate to that "
"product page's form and select the :guilabel:`Reordering Rules` smart button "
"at the top of the form."
msgstr ""
"For at administrere genbestillingsreglerne for et enkelt produkt skal du "
"navigere til produktets formular og vælge :guilabel:`Reordering Rules` smart-"
"knappen øverst på formularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/reordering.rst:101
msgid ""
"To manage all reordering rules for every product, go "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations --> Replenishment`. From "
"this dashboard, typical bulk actions in Odoo can be performed such as "
"exporting data or archiving rules that are no longer needed. As well, "
"the :guilabel:`Filters`, :guilabel:`Group By` or triple-dotted menu on the "
"form are available to search for and/or organize the reordering rules as "
"desired."
msgstr ""
"For at administrere alle genbestillingsregler for hvert produkt skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Lager app --> Operationer --> Genopfyldning`. Fra dette "
"dashboard kan typiske massehandlinger i Odoo udføres, såsom eksport af data "
"eller arkivering af regler, der ikke længere er nødvendige. Derudover "
"er :guilabel:`Filters`, :guilabel:`Group By` eller menuen med tre prikker på "
"formularen tilgængelig til at søge efter og/eller organisere "
"genbestillingsreglerne efter behov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:3
msgid "Temporary reordering rules"
msgstr "Midlertidige genbestillingsregler"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:5
msgid ""
"Some businesses require certain products to always have a minimum quantity "
"of stock on-hand at any given time. To avoid stock falling below a certain "
"threshold, companies can create *reordering rules* in Odoo to automate "
"purchase orders for specific products."
msgstr ""
"Nogle virksomheder kræver, at visse produkter altid har en "
"minimumslagerbeholdning til rådighed på et givet tidspunkt. For at undgå, at "
"lagerbeholdningen falder under en vis tærskel, kan virksomheder oprette "
"*genbestillingsregler* i Odoo til at automatisere indkøbsordrer for "
"specifikke produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:9
msgid ""
"Reordering rules keep the forecasted stock levels above a certain threshold, "
"without exceeding a specified upper limit, or maximum amount. When a product "
"with a reordering rule falls below a specified quantity, Odoo generates an "
"order using the specified *route* (e.g. *Buy* or *Manufacture*) to replenish "
"the stock."
msgstr ""
"Genbestillingsregler holder de forventede lagerniveauer over en bestemt "
"tærskel uden at overskride en specificeret øvre grænse eller "
"maksimumsmængde. Når et produkt med en genbestillingsregel falder under en "
"specificeret mængde, genererer Odoo en ordre ved hjælp af den specificerede "
"*rute* (f.eks. *Køb* eller *Fremstil*) for at genopfylde lageret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:14
msgid ""
"In certain cases, businesses might opt for *temporary reordering rules* when "
"they do not want specific products to be replenished automatically."
msgstr ""
"I visse tilfælde kan virksomheder vælge *midlertidige genbestillingsregler*, "
"når de ikke ønsker, at specifikke produkter skal genopfyldes automatisk."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:17
msgid ""
"In Odoo, a \"temporary\" reordering rule is created in the replenishment "
"dashboard when a product:"
msgstr ""
"I Odoo oprettes en \"midlertidig\" genbestillingsregel i "
"genopfyldningsdashboardet, når et produkt:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:19
msgid "is configured with a *Buy* route"
msgstr "er konfigureret med en *Køb*-rute"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:20
msgid "has no reordering rule configured"
msgstr "ikke har nogen genbestillingsregel konfigureret"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:21
msgid "has `0` quantity in stock"
msgstr "har `0` antal på lager"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:22
msgid "is included in a sales order (SO)."
msgstr "er inkluderet i en salgsordre (SO)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:24
msgid ""
"This rule is deleted upon confirmation of the purchase order (PO) generated "
"for the product."
msgstr ""
"Denne regel slettes ved bekræftelse af den indkøbsordre (PO), der genereres "
"for produktet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:28
msgid ":doc:`../../purchase/products/reordering`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../purchase/products/reordering`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:33
msgid ""
"To configure a product that triggers temporary reordering rules when its "
"stock reaches `0`, begin by going to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Products --> Products`, and click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"For at konfigurere et produkt, der udløser midlertidige "
"genbestillingsregler, når dets lager når `0`, skal du starte med at gå "
"til :menuselection:`Lager app --> Produkter --> Produkter` og klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:37
msgid ""
"The same configurations can also be made on an existing product, by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Products --> Products`, and selecting "
"an existing product."
msgstr ""
"De samme konfigurationer kan også foretages på et eksisterende produkt ved "
"at gå til :menuselection:`Lager app --> Produkter --> Produkter` og vælge et "
"eksisterende produkt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:40
msgid ""
"On the product form, enter the product name, and ensure the :guilabel:`Can "
"be Sold` and :guilabel:`Can be Purchased` options are enabled, located "
"beneath the :guilabel:`Product Name` field."
msgstr ""
"På produktformularen skal du indtaste produktnavnet og sikre, "
"at :guilabel:`Kan sælges` og :guilabel:`Kan købes` er aktiveret, placeret "
"under :guilabel:`Produktnavn`feltet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:44
msgid ""
"Then, set the :guilabel:`Product Type` to `Storable Product`, under "
"the :guilabel:`General Information` tab."
msgstr ""
"Indstil derefter :guilabel:`Produkttype` til `Lagerprodukt` under "
"fanen :guilabel:`Generelle oplysninger`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:47
msgid ""
"Next, click the :guilabel:`Purchase` tab, and under :guilabel:`Vendor`, "
"click :guilabel:`Add a line` to select a vendor from the drop-down menu. "
"Then, set a purchase price under :guilabel:`Price`."
msgstr ""
"Klik derefter på fanen :guilabel:`Indkøb`, og under :guilabel:`Leverandør` "
"skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` for at vælge en leverandør fra "
"rullemenuen. Indstil derefter en indkøbspris under :guilabel:`Pris`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:51
msgid ""
"A vendor **must** be set for temporary reordering rules to work. While "
"a :abbr:`PO (purchase order)` can still be created automatically, attempting "
"to replenish the product from the :guilabel:`Replenishment` dashboard in the "
"*Inventory* app triggers a warning to add a vendor on the product form."
msgstr ""
"En leverandør **skal** være indstillet, for at midlertidige "
"genbestillingsregler virker. Selvom en :abbr:`PO (indkøbsordre)` stadig kan "
"oprettes automatisk, vil et forsøg på at genopfylde produktet "
"fra :guilabel:`Genopfyldning`dashboardet i *Lager*-appen udløse en advarsel "
"om at tilføje en leverandør på produktformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:0
msgid "Warning pop-up upon clicking to replenish product with no set vendor."
msgstr ""
"Advarselspopup ved klik på genopfyldning af produkt uden angivet leverandør."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:60
msgid ""
"Before creating a :abbr:`SO (sales order)` for the product, ensure "
"the :guilabel:`On Hand` smart button on the product form reads `0.00 Units`. "
"Then, ensure that the :guilabel:`Reordering Rules` smart button reads `0`, "
"indicating there are no rules applied to this product."
msgstr ""
"Før oprettelse af en :abbr:`SO (salgsordre)` for produktet skal du sikre, at "
"den smarte knap :guilabel:`På lager` på produktformularen viser `0,00 "
"enheder`. Sørg derefter for, at den smarte "
"knap :guilabel:`Genbestillingsregler` viser `0`, hvilket indikerer, at der "
"ikke er anvendt regler på dette produkt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:None
msgid ""
"Product form smart button row displaying reordering rules and on hand "
"buttons."
msgstr ""
"Produktformularens række med smarte knapper, der viser genbestillingsregler "
"og lagerbeholdningsknapper."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:69
msgid "Trigger temporary reordering rule"
msgstr "Udløs midlertidig genbestillingsregel"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:71
msgid ""
"To trigger a temporary reordering rule, create a new sales order for a "
"product by navigating to :menuselection:`Sales app --> New`."
msgstr ""
"For at udløse en midlertidig genbestillingsregel skal du oprette en ny "
"salgsordre for et produkt ved at navigere til :menuselection:`Salg app --> "
"Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:74
msgid ""
"Then, add a customer in the :guilabel:`Customer` field, and "
"click :guilabel:`Add a product` under the :guilabel:`Product` column in "
"the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab. Next, select the desired product from the "
"drop-down menu. Lastly, :guilabel:`Confirm` the :abbr:`SO (sales order)`."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj derefter en kunde i feltet :guilabel:`Kunde`, og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Tilføj et produkt` under kolonnen :guilabel:`Produkt` i "
"fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer`. Vælg herefter det ønskede produkt fra "
"rullemenuen. Til sidst skal du :guilabel:`bekræfte` :abbr:`SO (salgsordre)`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:None
msgid "Sales order for product with no set reordering rules."
msgstr "Salgsordre for produkt uden angivne genbestillingsregler."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:85
msgid "Check replenishment report"
msgstr "Tjek genbestillingsrapport"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:87
msgid ""
"To see the temporary reordering rule created for the out-of-stock product "
"included in the sales order, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Operations --> Replenishment`. Doing so opens the :guilabel:`Replenishment` "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"For at se den midlertidige genbestillingsregel, der er oprettet for det "
"udsolgte produkt, der er inkluderet i salgsordren, skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Lager app --> Operationer --> Genbestilling`. Dette "
"åbner :guilabel:`Genbestillings`-dashboardet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:91
msgid ""
"On this dashboard, locate the product for which the temporary reordering "
"rule was created. On its product line, its :guilabel:`On Hand` quantity, "
"negative :guilabel:`Forecast` quantity, *Buy* :guilabel:`Route`, "
"and :guilabel:`To Order` quantity to replenish can be seen."
msgstr ""
"På dette dashboard skal du finde det produkt, som den midlertidige "
"genbestillingsregel blev oprettet for. På dets produktlinje kan "
"dets :guilabel:`På lager`-mængde, negative :guilabel:`Prognose`-mængde, "
"*Køb* :guilabel:`Rute` og :guilabel:`At bestille`-mængde til genbestilling "
"ses."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:95
msgid ""
"Additionally, two replenishment options are located to the far-right of the "
"row: :guilabel:`Order Once` and :guilabel:`Automate`."
msgstr ""
"Derudover er der to genbestillingsmuligheder placeret helt til højre i "
"rækken: :guilabel:`Bestil én gang` og :guilabel:`Automatiser`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:None
msgid "Replenishment report displaying temporary reordering rule and options."
msgstr ""
"Genbestillingsrapport, der viser midlertidig genbestillingsregel og "
"muligheder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:102
msgid ""
"To use the one-time, temporary reordering rule, click :guilabel:`Order "
"Once`. This action triggers a confirmation pop-up window in the top-right "
"corner, reading :guilabel:`The following replenishment order has been "
"generated`, along with a new purchase order number."
msgstr ""
"For at bruge den engangsmidlertidige genbestillingsregel skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Bestil én gang`. Denne handling udløser et bekræftelsespopup-"
"vindue i øverste højre hjørne med teksten :guilabel:`Følgende "
"genbestillingsordre er blevet genereret` sammen med et nyt "
"indkøbsordrenummer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:107
msgid ""
"Once the purchase order has been generated after clicking :guilabel:`Order "
"Once`, refresh the page. The temporary reordering rule for the product no "
"longer appears in the :guilabel:`Replenishment` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Når indkøbsordren er blevet genereret efter at have klikket "
"på :guilabel:`Bestil én gang`, skal du opdatere siden. Den midlertidige "
"genbestillingsregel for produktet vises ikke længere "
"på :guilabel:`Genbestillings`-dashboardet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:112
msgid "Complete purchase order"
msgstr "Fuldfør indkøbsordre"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:114
msgid ""
"To view the purchase order created from the :guilabel:`Replenishment` "
"dashboard, navigate to the :menuselection:`Purchase app`, and select the "
"generated :abbr:`PO (purchase order)` from the :guilabel:`Requests for "
"Quotation` overview."
msgstr ""
"For at se indkøbsordren oprettet fra :guilabel:`Genbestillings`-dashboardet "
"skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Indkøb app` og vælge den "
"genererede :abbr:`PO (indkøbsordre)` fra "
"oversigten :guilabel:`Tilbudsanmodninger`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:118
msgid ""
"From here, click :guilabel:`Confirm Order`, then click :guilabel:`Receive "
"Products`. Finally, click :guilabel:`Validate` to complete the purchase "
"order."
msgstr ""
"Klik herfra på :guilabel:`Bekræft ordre`, klik derefter på :guilabel:`Modtag "
"produkter`. Klik til sidst på :guilabel:`Valider` for at fuldføre "
"indkøbsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:None
msgid "Purchase order for product ordered with temporary reordering rule."
msgstr "Indkøbsordre for produkt bestilt med midlertidig genbestillingsregel."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:125
msgid "Now, the original sales order can be delivered and invoiced."
msgstr "Nu kan den oprindelige salgsordre leveres og faktureres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:128
msgid ""
"Once the :abbr:`SO (sales order)` is delivered and invoiced, ensure there "
"are no reordering rules on the product form."
msgstr ""
"Når :abbr:`SO (salgsordre)` er leveret og faktureret, skal du sikre dig, at "
"der ikke er nogen genbestillingsregler på produktformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/temporary_reordering.rst:131
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Products --> Products`, select the "
"product, and confirm that the :guilabel:`Reordering Rules` smart button "
"displays `0`."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Lager app --> Produkter --> Produkter`, vælg "
"produktet, og bekræft, at den smarte knap :guilabel:`Genbestillingsregler` "
"viser `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality.rst:9
msgid ""
"**Odoo Quality** helps ensure product quality throughout manufacturing "
"processes and inventory movements. Conduct quality checks, automate quality "
"inspection frequency, and create quality alerts when issues arise."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Kvalitet** hjælper med at sikre produktkvalitet gennem "
"produktionsprocesser og lagerbevægelser. Udfør kvalitetskontroller, "
"automatiser kvalitetsinspektionsfrekvens og opret kvalitetsalarmer, når der "
"opstår problemer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality.rst:14
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Quality Overview <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/quality-"
"overview-5590>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo-tutorials: Kvalitetsoversigt <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"quality-overview-5590>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types.rst:5
msgid "Quality check types"
msgstr "Typer af kvalitetskontrol"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:3
msgid "Instructions quality check"
msgstr "Kvalitetskontrol af instruktioner"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:8
msgid ""
"In Odoo *Quality*, an *Instructions* check is one of the quality check types "
"that can be selected when creating a new quality check or quality control "
"point (QCP). *Instructions* checks consist of a text entry field that allows "
"the creator to provide instructions for how to complete the check."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo *Kvalitet* er en *Instruktions*-kontrol en af de "
"kvalitetskontroltyper, der kan vælges ved oprettelse af en ny "
"kvalitetskontrol eller kvalitetskontrolpunkt (QCP). *Instruktions*-"
"kontroller består af et tekstindtastningsfelt, der giver skaberen mulighed "
"for at give instruktioner om, hvordan kontrollen skal gennemføres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:12
msgid ""
"For a full overview of how to configure a quality check or a |QCP|, see the "
"documentation on :ref:`quality checks <quality/quality_management/quality-"
"checks>` and :ref:`quality control points <quality/quality_management/"
"quality-control-points>`."
msgstr ""
"For et komplet overblik over, hvordan man konfigurerer en kvalitetskontrol "
"eller et |QCP|, se dokumentationen om :ref:`kvalitetskontroller <quality/"
"quality_management/quality-checks>` og :ref:`kvalitetskontrolpunkter "
"<quality/quality_management/quality-control-points>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:17
msgid "Process an Instructions quality check"
msgstr "Behandle en instruktions kvalitetskontrol"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:19
msgid ""
"There are multiple ways that *Instructions* quality checks can be processed. "
"If a quality check is assigned to a specific manufacturing, inventory, or "
"work order, the check can be processed on the order itself. Alternatively, a "
"check can be processed from the check's page."
msgstr ""
"Der er flere måder, hvorpå *Instruktions*-kvalitetskontroller kan behandles. "
"Hvis en kvalitetskontrol er tildelt en specifik produktions-, lager- eller "
"arbejdsordre, kan kontrollen behandles på selve ordren. Alternativt kan en "
"kontrol behandles fra kontrollens side."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:24
msgid "Process from the quality check's page"
msgstr "Behandle fra kvalitetskontrollens side"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:26
msgid ""
"To process an *Instructions* quality check from the check's page, begin by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Quality --> Quality Control --> Quality "
"Checks`, and select a quality check. Follow the :guilabel:`Instructions` for "
"how to complete the check."
msgstr ""
"For at behandle en *Instruktions*-kvalitetskontrol fra kontrollens side, "
"start med at navigere til :menuselection:`Kvalitet --> Kvalitetskontrol --> "
"Kvalitetskontroller`, og vælg en kvalitetskontrol. "
"Følg :guilabel:`instruktionerne` for, hvordan kontrollen skal gennemføres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:30
msgid ""
"If the product passes the check, click the :guilabel:`Pass` button above the "
"quality check form. If the product does not pass the check, click "
"the :guilabel:`Fail` button, instead."
msgstr ""
"Hvis produktet består kontrollen, klik på knappen :guilabel:`Godkendt` over "
"kvalitetskontrolformularen. Hvis produktet ikke består kontrollen, klik i "
"stedet på knappen :guilabel:`Ikke godkendt`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:34
msgid "Process quality check on an order"
msgstr "Behandle kvalitetskontrol på en ordre"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:36
msgid ""
"To process an *Instructions* quality check on an order, select a "
"manufacturing order or inventory order (receipt, delivery, return, etc.) for "
"which a check is required. Manufacturing orders can be selected by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Manufacturing --> Operations --> Manufacturing "
"Orders`, and clicking on an order. Inventory orders can be selected by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Inventory`, clicking the :guilabel:`# To "
"Process` button on an operation card, and selecting an order."
msgstr ""
"For at behandle en *Instruktions*-kvalitetskontrol på en ordre, vælg en "
"produktionsordre eller lagerordre (modtagelse, levering, retur osv.), som "
"kræver en kontrol. Produktionsordrer kan vælges ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Produktion --> Operationer --> Produktionsordrer`, og "
"klikke på en ordre. Lagerordrer kan vælges ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Lager`, klikke på knappen :guilabel:`# Til behandling` "
"på et operationskort og vælge en ordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:43
msgid ""
"On the selected manufacturing or inventory order, a "
"purple :guilabel:`Quality Checks` button appears above the order. Click the "
"button to open the :guilabel:`Quality Check` pop-up window, from which any "
"quality checks created for the order can be processed."
msgstr ""
"På den valgte produktions- eller lagerordre vises en lilla "
"knap :guilabel:`Kvalitetskontroller` over ordren. Klik på knappen for at "
"åbne pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Kvalitetskontrol`, hvorfra eventuelle "
"kvalitetskontroller oprettet til ordren kan behandles."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:None
msgid "The Quality Check pop-up window on a manufacturing or inventory order."
msgstr "Pop op-vinduet Kvalitetskontrol på en produktions- eller lagerordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:51
msgid ""
"To complete an *Instructions* quality check, follow the instructions "
"detailed in the :guilabel:`Quality Check` pop-up window. Finally, "
"click :guilabel:`Validate` to confirm that the check has been completed."
msgstr ""
"For at gennemføre en *Instruktions*-kvalitetskontrol, følg instruktionerne "
"beskrevet i pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Kvalitetskontrol`. Klik til sidst "
"på :guilabel:`Valider` for at bekræfte, at kontrollen er gennemført."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:55
msgid ""
"If an issue or defect is found during the quality check, a quality alert may "
"need to be created to notify a quality team. To do so, click "
"the :guilabel:`Quality Alert` button that appears at the top of the "
"manufacturing or inventory order after the check is validated."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der findes et problem eller en defekt under kvalitetskontrollen, skal "
"der muligvis oprettes en kvalitetsalarm for at underrette et kvalitetsteam. "
"For at gøre dette, klik på knappen :guilabel:`Kvalitetsalarm`, der vises "
"øverst på produktions- eller lagerordren, efter at kontrollen er valideret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:59
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Quality Alert` opens a quality alert form on a new page. "
"For a complete guide on how to fill out quality alert forms, view the "
"documentation on :ref:`quality alerts <quality/quality_management/quality-"
"alerts>`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Kvalitetsalarm` åbner en kvalitetsalarmformular på en ny "
"side. For en komplet guide til, hvordan kvalitetsalarmformularer udfyldes, "
"se dokumentationen om :ref:`kvalitetsalarmer <quality/quality_management/"
"quality-alerts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:64
msgid "Process work order quality check"
msgstr "Behandle kvalitetskontrol for arbejdsordre"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:66
msgid ""
"When configuring a |QCP| that is triggered by a manufacturing order, a "
"specific work order can also be specified in the :guilabel:`Work Order "
"Operation` field on the |QCP| form. If a work order is specified, an "
"*Instructions* quality check is created for that specific work order, rather "
"than the |MO| as a whole."
msgstr ""
"Når der konfigureres et |QCP|, der udløses af en produktionsordre, kan en "
"specifik arbejdsordre også angives i feltet :guilabel:`Arbejdsordre "
"operation` på |QCP|-formularen. Hvis en arbejdsordre er angivet, oprettes en "
"*Instruktions*-kvalitetskontrol for den specifikke arbejdsordre i stedet for "
"|MO| som helhed."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:71
msgid ""
"Quality checks configured for work orders **must** be completed from the "
"*Shop Floor* module. To do so, begin by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Manufacturing --> Operations --> Manufacturing Orders`. "
"Select an |MO| that includes a work order for which an *Instructions* "
"quality check is required."
msgstr ""
"Kvalitetskontroller konfigureret til arbejdsordrer **skal** gennemføres fra "
"modulet *Værksted*. For at gøre dette, start med at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Produktion --> Operationer --> Produktionsordrer`. Vælg "
"en |MO|, der inkluderer en arbejdsordre, som kræver en *Instruktions*-"
"kvalitetskontrol."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:75
msgid ""
"On the |MO|, select the :guilabel:`Work Orders` tab, and click "
"the :guilabel:`Open Work Order (square with arrow coming out of it)` button "
"on the line of the work order to be processed. On the "
"resulting :guilabel:`Work Orders` pop-up window, click the :guilabel:`Open "
"Shop Floor` button to open the *Shop Floor* module."
msgstr ""
"På |MO| vælg fanen :guilabel:`Arbejdsordrer`, og klik på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Åbn arbejdsordre (firkant med pil ud af den)` på linjen "
"for den arbejdsordre, der skal behandles. I det resulterende pop op-"
"vindue :guilabel:`Arbejdsordrer`, klik på knappen :guilabel:`Åbn værksted` "
"for at åbne modulet *Værksted*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:84
msgid ""
"Begin processing the work order's steps until the *Instructions* quality "
"check step is reached. Click on the step to open a pop-up window that "
"details how to complete the quality check. Once completed, click "
"the :guilabel:`Next` button to complete the check, and move on to the next "
"step."
msgstr ""
"Begynd at behandle arbejdsordrens trin, indtil trinnet med *Instruktions*-"
"kvalitetskontrol nås. Klik på trinnet for at åbne et pop op-vindue, der "
"beskriver, hvordan kvalitetskontrollen skal gennemføres. Når den er "
"gennemført, klik på knappen :guilabel:`Næste` for at gennemføre kontrollen "
"og gå videre til næste trin."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:None
msgid "An Instruction check as it appears in the Shop Floor module."
msgstr "En instruktionskontrol, som den vises i modulet Værksted."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:92
msgid ""
"Alternatively, an *Instructions* quality check can be completed by clicking "
"the checkbox that appears on the right side of the step's line on the work "
"order card. When using this method, the quality check automatically passes, "
"without a pop-up window appearing."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt kan en kvalitetskontrol af typen *Instruktioner* gennemføres ved "
"at klikke på afkrydsningsfeltet, der vises på højre side af trinnets linje "
"på arbejdsordrekortet. Ved brug af denne metode består kvalitetskontrollen "
"automatisk, uden at der vises et pop op-vindue."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/instructions_check.rst:97
msgid ""
"For a full guide to the *Shop Floor* module, see the :doc:`../../"
"manufacturing/shop_floor/shop_floor_overview` documentation."
msgstr ""
"For en komplet guide til *Værksted*-modulet, se :doc:`../../manufacturing/"
"shop_floor/shop_floor_overview` dokumentationen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:3
msgid "Measure quality check"
msgstr "Kvalitetskontrol af typen måling"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:9
msgid ""
"In Odoo *Quality*, a *Measure* check is one of the quality check types that "
"can be selected when creating a new quality check or quality control point "
"(QCP). *Measure* checks prompt users to measure a certain aspect of a "
"product and record the measurement in Odoo. For the quality check to pass, "
"the recorded measurement must be within a certain *tolerance* of a *norm* "
"value."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo *Kvalitet* er en kontrol af typen *Måling* en af de "
"kvalitetskontroltyper, der kan vælges ved oprettelse af en ny "
"kvalitetskontrol eller kvalitetskontrolpunkt (QCP). Kontroller af typen "
"*Måling* beder brugere om at måle et bestemt aspekt af et produkt og "
"registrere målingen i Odoo. For at kvalitetskontrollen består, skal den "
"registrerede måling være inden for en bestemt *tolerance* af en *norm*-værdi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:15
msgid "Create a Measure quality check"
msgstr "Opret en kvalitetskontrol af typen måling"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:17
msgid ""
"There are two distinct ways that *Measure* quality checks can be created. A "
"single check can be manually created. Alternatively, a |QCP| can be "
"configured that automatically creates checks at a predetermined interval."
msgstr ""
"Der er to forskellige måder, hvorpå kvalitetskontroller af typen *Måling* "
"kan oprettes. En enkelt kontrol kan oprettes manuelt. Alternativt kan et |"
"QCP| konfigureres, der automatisk opretter kontroller med et forudbestemt "
"interval."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:21
msgid ""
"This documentation only details the configuration options that are unique to "
"*Measure* quality checks and |QCPs|. For a full overview of all the "
"configuration options available when creating a single check or a |QCP|, see "
"the documentation on :ref:`quality checks <quality/quality_management/"
"quality-checks>` and :ref:`quality control points <quality/"
"quality_management/quality-control-points>`."
msgstr ""
"Denne dokumentation beskriver kun de konfigurationsmuligheder, der er unikke "
"for kvalitetskontroller af typen *Måling* og |QCPs|. For et komplet overblik "
"over alle konfigurationsmuligheder, der er tilgængelige ved oprettelse af en "
"enkelt kontrol eller et |QCP|, se dokumentationen "
"om :ref:`kvalitetskontroller <quality/quality_management/quality-checks>` "
"og :ref:`kvalitetskontrolpunkter <quality/quality_management/quality-control-"
"points>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:28
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:28
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:27
msgid "Quality check"
msgstr "Kvalitetskontrol"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:30
msgid ""
"To create a single *Measure* quality check, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Quality --> Quality Control --> Quality Checks`, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. Fill out the new quality check form as follows:"
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en enkelt kvalitetskontrol af typen *Måling*, gå "
"til :menuselection:`Kvalitet --> Kvalitetskontrol --> Kvalitetskontroller`, "
"og klik på :guilabel:`Ny`. Udfyld den nye kvalitetskontrolformular som "
"følger:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:33
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Type` drop-down field, select the :guilabel:`Measure` "
"quality check type."
msgstr ""
"I rullemenuen :guilabel:`Type` vælges "
"kvalitetskontroltypen :guilabel:`Måling`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:34
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:35
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:34
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Team` drop-down field, select the quality team responsible "
"for managing the check."
msgstr ""
"I rullemenuen :guilabel:`Team` vælges det kvalitetsteam, der er ansvarligt "
"for at håndtere kontrollen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:36
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:36
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Instructions` text field of the :guilabel:`Notes` tab, "
"enter instructions for how the picture should be taken."
msgstr ""
"I tekstfeltet :guilabel:`Instruktioner` under fanen :guilabel:`Noter` "
"indtastes instruktioner for, hvordan billedet skal tages."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:None
msgid "A quality check form configured for a Measure quality check."
msgstr ""
"En kvalitetskontrolformular konfigureret til en kvalitetskontrol af typen "
"måling."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:44
msgid "Quality control point (QCP)"
msgstr "Kvalitetskontrolpunkt (QCP)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:46
msgid ""
"To create a |QCP| that generates *Measure* quality checks automatically, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Quality --> Quality Control --> Control Points`, "
"and click :guilabel:`New`. Fill out the new |QCP| form as follows:"
msgstr ""
"For at oprette et |QCP|, der automatisk genererer kvalitetskontroller af "
"typen *Måling*, gå til :menuselection:`Kvalitet --> Kvalitetskontrol --> "
"Kontrolpunkter`, og klik på :guilabel:`Ny`. Udfyld den nye |QCP|-formular "
"som følger:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:50
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Type` drop-down field, select the :guilabel:`Measure` "
"quality check type. Doing so causes two new fields to "
"appear: :guilabel:`Norm` and :guilabel:`Tolerance`."
msgstr ""
"I rullemenuen :guilabel:`Type` vælges "
"kvalitetskontroltypen :guilabel:`Måling`. Dette medfører, at to nye felter "
"vises: :guilabel:`Norm` og :guilabel:`Tolerance`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:53
msgid ""
"Use the first text-entry field of the :guilabel:`Norm` field to record the "
"ideal measurement that the product should conform to. Use the second text-"
"entry field to specify the unit of measurement that should be used."
msgstr ""
"Brug det første tekstfelt i feltet :guilabel:`Norm` til at registrere den "
"ideelle måling, som produktet skal overholde. Brug det andet tekstfelt til "
"at angive den måleenhed, der skal bruges."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:56
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tolerance` field features two sub-fields: :guilabel:`from` "
"and :guilabel:`to`. Use the :guilabel:`from` field to specify the minimum "
"acceptable measurement, and the :guilabel:`to` field to specify the maximum "
"acceptable measurement."
msgstr ""
"Feltet :guilabel:`Tolerance` indeholder to underfelter: :guilabel:`fra` "
"og :guilabel:`til`. Brug feltet :guilabel:`fra` til at angive den minimalt "
"acceptable måling, og feltet :guilabel:`til` til at angive den maksimalt "
"acceptable måling."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:60
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:52
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:55
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Team` drop-down field, select the quality team responsible "
"for managing the checks created by the |QCP|."
msgstr ""
"I rullemenuen :guilabel:`Team` vælges det kvalitetsteam, der er ansvarligt "
"for at håndtere de kontroller, der oprettes af |QCP|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:62
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Instructions` text field, enter instructions for how the "
"measurement should be taken."
msgstr ""
"I tekstfeltet :guilabel:`Instruktioner` indtastes instruktioner for, hvordan "
"målingen skal udføres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:None
msgid "A QCP form configured to create Measure quality checks."
msgstr ""
"Et QCP-formular konfigureret til at oprette Måling kvalitetskontroller."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:70
msgid "Process a Measure quality check"
msgstr "Behandle en Måling kvalitetskontrol"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:72
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:64
msgid ""
"Once created, there are multiple ways that *Measure* quality checks can be "
"processed. If a quality check is assigned to a specific inventory, "
"manufacturing, or work order, the check can be processed on the order "
"itself. Alternatively, a check can be processed from the check's page."
msgstr ""
"Når de er oprettet, er der flere måder, hvorpå *Måling* kvalitetskontroller "
"kan behandles. Hvis en kvalitetskontrol er tildelt en specifik lager-, "
"produktions- eller arbejdsordre, kan kontrollen behandles på selve ordren. "
"Alternativt kan en kontrol behandles fra kontrollens side."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:77
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:69
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:72
msgid "From the check's page"
msgstr "Fra kontrollens side"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:79
msgid ""
"To process a *Measure* quality check from the check's page, begin by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Quality --> Quality Control --> Quality "
"Checks`, and select a quality check. Follow the :guilabel:`Instructions` for "
"how to take the measurement."
msgstr ""
"For at behandle en *Måling* kvalitetskontrol fra kontrollens side skal du "
"starte med at navigere til :menuselection:`Kvalitet --> Kvalitetskontrol --> "
"Kvalitetskontroller` og vælge en kvalitetskontrol. "
"Følg :guilabel:`Instruktionerne` for, hvordan målingen udføres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:83
msgid ""
"After taking the measurement, record the value in the :guilabel:`Measure` "
"field on the quality check form. To manually pass or fail the check, "
"click :guilabel:`Pass` or :guilabel:`Fail` at the top-left corner of the "
"check."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have foretaget målingen skal du registrere værdien i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Måling` på kvalitetskontrolformularen. For manuelt at "
"godkende eller underkende kontrollen skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Godkend` "
"eller :guilabel:`Afvis` i øverste venstre hjørne af kontrollen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:87
msgid ""
"Alternatively, if the quality check is assigned to a |QCP| for which *norm* "
"and *tolerance* values have been specified, click :guilabel:`Measure` at the "
"top-left corner of the check instead. Doing so automatically marks the check "
"as *Passed* if the recorded value is within the specified *tolerance*, or "
"*Failed* if the value is outside of it."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt, hvis kvalitetskontrollen er tildelt et |QCP|, for hvilket "
"*norm*- og *toleranceværdier* er angivet, skal du i stedet klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Måling` i øverste venstre hjørne af kontrollen. Herved "
"markeres kontrollen automatisk som *Godkendt*, hvis den registrerede værdi "
"er inden for den angivne *tolerance*, eller *Afvist*, hvis værdien er uden "
"for den."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:93
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:79
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:88
msgid "On an order"
msgstr "På en ordre"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:95
msgid ""
"To process a *Measure* quality check on an order, select a manufacturing "
"order or inventory order (receipt, delivery, return, etc.), for which a "
"check is required. Manufacturing orders can be selected by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Manufacturing --> Operations --> Manufacturing Orders`, "
"and clicking on an order. Inventory orders can be selected by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory`, clicking the :guilabel:`# To Process` button "
"on an operation card, and selecting an order."
msgstr ""
"For at behandle en *Måling* kvalitetskontrol på en ordre skal du vælge en "
"produktionsordre eller lagerordre (modtagelse, levering, returnering osv.), "
"som der kræves en kontrol til. Produktionsordrer kan vælges ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Produktion --> Operationer --> Produktionsordrer` og "
"klikke på en ordre. Lagerordrer kan vælges ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Lager`, klikke på knappen :guilabel:`# Til behandling` "
"på et operationskort og vælge en ordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:102
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:97
msgid ""
"On the selected manufacturing or inventory order, a "
"purple :guilabel:`Quality Checks` button appears at the top of the page. "
"Click the button to open the :guilabel:`Quality Check` pop-up window, which "
"shows all of the quality checks required for that order."
msgstr ""
"På den valgte produktions- eller lagerordre vises en lilla "
"knap :guilabel:`Kvalitetskontroller` øverst på siden. Klik på knappen for at "
"åbne pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Kvalitetskontrol`, som viser alle de "
"kvalitetskontroller, der kræves til den pågældende ordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:106
msgid ""
"To process a *Measure* quality check, measure the product as instructed, "
"then enter the value in the :guilabel:`Measure` field on the pop-up window. "
"Finally, click :guilabel:`Validate` to register the recorded value."
msgstr ""
"For at behandle en *Måling* kvalitetskontrol skal du måle produktet som "
"instrueret og derefter indtaste værdien i feltet :guilabel:`Måling` i pop op-"
"vinduet. Til sidst skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Valider` for at registrere "
"den registrerede værdi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:None
msgid ""
"A Measure quality check pop-up window on a manufacturing or inventory order."
msgstr ""
"Et Måling kvalitetskontrol pop op-vindue på en produktions- eller lagerordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:114
msgid ""
"If the value entered is within the range specified in "
"the :guilabel:`Tolerance` section of the |QCP|, the quality check passes and "
"the pop-up window closes. The rest of the manufacturing or inventory order "
"can then be processed as usual."
msgstr ""
"Hvis den indtastede værdi er inden for det interval, der er angivet i "
"afsnittet :guilabel:`Tolerance` i |QCP|, godkendes kvalitetskontrollen, og "
"pop op-vinduet lukkes. Resten af produktions- eller lagerordren kan derefter "
"behandles som sædvanligt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:118
msgid ""
"However, if the value entered is outside of the specified range, a new pop-"
"up window appears, titled :guilabel:`Quality Check Failed`. The body of the "
"pop-up shows a warning message that states, :guilabel:`You measured # units "
"and it should be between # units and # units.`, as well as the instructions "
"entered in the :guilabel:`Message If Failure` tab of the |QCP|. At the "
"bottom of the pop-up, two buttons appear: :guilabel:`Correct Measure` "
"and :guilabel:`Confirm Measure`."
msgstr ""
"Men hvis den indtastede værdi ligger uden for det angivne interval, vises et "
"nyt pop op-vindue med titlen :guilabel:`Kvalitetskontrol mislykkedes`. Pop "
"op-vinduets indhold viser en advarselsmeddelelse, der angiver, :guilabel:`Du "
"målte # enheder, og det skulle være mellem # enheder og # enheder.`, samt de "
"instruktioner, der er indtastet under fanen :guilabel:`Meddelelse ved fejl` "
"i |QCP|. Nederst i pop op-vinduet vises to knapper: :guilabel:`Ret måling` "
"og :guilabel:`Bekræft måling`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:None
msgid "The \"Quality Check Failed\" pop-up window."
msgstr "Pop op-vinduet \"Kvalitetskontrol mislykkedes\"."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:128
msgid ""
"If the measurement was not entered correctly and should be changed, "
"select :guilabel:`Correct Measure`. Doing so re-opens the :guilabel:`Quality "
"Check` pop-up window. Enter the corrected measurement in "
"the :guilabel:`Measure` field, and then click :guilabel:`Validate` to "
"complete the check."
msgstr ""
"Hvis målingen ikke blev indtastet korrekt og skal ændres, skal du "
"vælge :guilabel:`Ret måling`. Herved åbnes pop op-"
"vinduet :guilabel:`Kvalitetskontrol` igen. Indtast den korrigerede måling i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Måling`, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Valider` for at "
"fuldføre kontrollen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:133
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:195
msgid ""
"If the measurement was entered correctly, click :guilabel:`Confirm Measure` "
"instead, and the quality check fails. Follow any instructions that were "
"listed on the :guilabel:`Quality Check Failed` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Hvis målingen blev indtastet korrekt, skal du i stedet klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Bekræft måling`, og kvalitetskontrollen mislykkes. Følg "
"eventuelle instruktioner, der var anført i pop op-"
"vinduet :guilabel:`Kvalitetskontrol mislykkedes`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:137
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:100
msgid ""
"If a quality alert must be created, click the :guilabel:`Quality Alert` "
"button that appears at the top of the manufacturing or inventory order after "
"the check fails. Clicking :guilabel:`Quality Alert` opens a quality alert "
"form on a new page."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der skal oprettes en kvalitetsalarm, skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Kvalitetsalarm`, der vises øverst på produktions- eller "
"lagerordren, efter at kontrollen mislykkes. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Kvalitetsalarm` åbner en kvalitetsalarmformular på en ny side."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:142
msgid ""
"For a complete guide on how to fill out the quality alert form, view the "
"documentation on :doc:`quality alerts <../quality_management/"
"quality_alerts>`."
msgstr ""
"For en komplet vejledning i, hvordan kvalitetsalarmformularen udfyldes, kan "
"du se dokumentationen om :doc:`kvalitetsalarmer <../quality_management/"
"quality_alerts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:146
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/pass_fail_check.rst:109
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:121
msgid "On a work order"
msgstr "På en arbejdsordre"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:148
msgid ""
"When configuring a |QCP| that is triggered during manufacturing, a specific "
"work order can also be specified in the :guilabel:`Work Order Operation` "
"field on the |QCP| form. If a work order is specified, a *Measure* quality "
"check is created for that specific work order, rather than the manufacturing "
"order as a whole."
msgstr ""
"Při konfiguraci |QCP|, který se spouští během výroby, lze v "
"poli :guilabel:`Operace pracovního příkazu` na formuláři |QCP| specifikovat "
"také konkrétní pracovní příkaz. Je-li pracovní příkaz specifikován, vytvoří "
"se kontrola kvality *Měření* pro tento konkrétní pracovní příkaz, nikoli pro "
"celý výrobní příkaz."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:153
msgid ""
"*Measure* quality checks configured for work orders **must** be completed "
"from the *Shop Floor* module. To do so, begin by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Manufacturing --> Operations --> Manufacturing Orders`. "
"Select an |MO| that includes a work order for which a *Measure* quality "
"check is required."
msgstr ""
"Kontroly kvality *Měření* nakonfigurované pro pracovní příkazy **musí** být "
"dokončeny z modulu *Værksted*. Začněte přechodem "
"na :menuselection:`Produktion --> Operace --> Výrobní příkazy`. Vyberte |"
"MO|, který obsahuje pracovní příkaz vyžadující kontrolu kvality *Měření*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:158
msgid ""
"On the |MO|, select the :guilabel:`Work Orders` tab, and click "
"the :guilabel:`Open Work Order (external link icon)` button on the line of "
"the work order to be processed. On the resulting :guilabel:`Work Orders` pop-"
"up window, click the :guilabel:`Open Shop Floor` button to open the *Shop "
"Floor* module."
msgstr ""
"Na |MO| vyberte kartu :guilabel:`Pracovní příkazy` a klikněte na "
"tlačítko :guilabel:`Otevřít pracovní příkaz (ikona externího odkazu)` na "
"řádku pracovního příkazu, který má být zpracován. Ve vyskakovacím "
"okně :guilabel:`Pracovní příkazy` klikněte na tlačítko :guilabel:`Otevřít "
"værksted`, čímž otevřete modul *Værksted*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:163
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:138
msgid ""
"When accessed from a specific work order, the *Shop Floor* module opens to "
"the page for the work center where the order is configured to be processed, "
"and isolates the work order's card, so no other cards are shown."
msgstr ""
"Když je k němu přistupováno z konkrétního pracovního příkazu, otevře se "
"modul *Værksted* na stránce pracovního centra, kde má být příkaz zpracován, "
"a izoluje kartu pracovního příkazu, takže se nezobrazují žádné další karty."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:167
msgid ""
"Process the work order's steps until the *Measure* quality check step is "
"reached. Click on the step to open a pop-up window that includes "
"instructions for how the measurement should be taken. After taking the "
"measurement, enter it in the :guilabel:`Measure` field of the pop-up window, "
"and then click :guilabel:`Validate`."
msgstr ""
"Zpracovávejte kroky pracovního příkazu, dokud nedosáhnete kroku kontroly "
"kvality *Měření*. Klikněte na krok, čímž se otevře vyskakovací okno s "
"pokyny, jak má být měření provedeno. Po provedení měření jej zadejte do "
"pole :guilabel:`Měření` vyskakovacího okna a poté klikněte "
"na :guilabel:`Ověřit`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:None
msgid "A Measure check in the Shop Floor module."
msgstr "Kontrola měření v modulu Værksted."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:176
msgid ""
"If the measurement entered is within the range specified in "
"the :guilabel:`Tolerance` section of the |QCP|, the quality check passes, "
"and the pop-up window moves on to the next step of the work order. However, "
"if the measurement entered is outside of the specified range, a new pop-up "
"window appears, titled :guilabel:`Quality Check Failed`."
msgstr ""
"Pokud zadané měření spadá do rozsahu specifikovaného v "
"sekci :guilabel:`Tolerance` v |QCP|, kontrola kvality projde a vyskakovací "
"okno přejde na další krok pracovního příkazu. Pokud však zadané měření spadá "
"mimo specifikovaný rozsah, objeví se nové vyskakovací okno s "
"názvem :guilabel:`Kontrola kvality selhala`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:181
msgid ""
"The body of the :guilabel:`Quality Check Failed` pop-up window shows a "
"message that states, :guilabel:`You measured # units and it should be "
"between # units and # units`, as well as the instructions entered in "
"the :guilabel:`Message If Failure` tab of the |QCP|. At the bottom of the "
"pop-up window, two buttons appear: :guilabel:`Correct Measure` "
"and :guilabel:`Confirm Measure`."
msgstr ""
"Tělo vyskakovacího okna :guilabel:`Kontrola kvality selhala` zobrazuje "
"zprávu :guilabel:`Naměřili jste # jednotek a mělo by to být mezi # "
"jednotkami a # jednotkami`, stejně jako pokyny zadané na "
"kartě :guilabel:`Zpráva při selhání` v |QCP|. V dolní části vyskakovacího "
"okna se zobrazují dvě tlačítka: :guilabel:`Opravit měření` "
"a :guilabel:`Potvrdit měření`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Quality Check Failed pop-up window for a Measure check in the Shop Floor "
"module."
msgstr ""
"Vyskakovací okno Kontrola kvality selhala pro kontrolu měření v modulu "
"Værksted."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:190
msgid ""
"If the measurement was not entered correctly, and should be changed, "
"select :guilabel:`Correct Measure`. Doing so opens a new pop-up window, "
"titled :guilabel:`Quality Check`. Enter the corrected measure in "
"the :guilabel:`Measure` field, and then click :guilabel:`Validate` to "
"complete the check and close the pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Pokud měření nebylo zadáno správně a mělo by být změněno, "
"vyberte :guilabel:`Opravit měření`. Tím se otevře nové vyskakovací okno s "
"názvem :guilabel:`Kontrola kvality`. Zadejte opravené měření do "
"pole :guilabel:`Měření` a poté klikněte na :guilabel:`Ověřit`, čímž kontrolu "
"dokončíte a zavřete vyskakovací okno."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:199
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:158
msgid ""
"If a quality alert must be created, exit the pop-up window by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`X (close)` button in the top-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Pokud je nutné vytvořit upozornění na kvalitu, zavřete vyskakovací okno "
"kliknutím na tlačítko :guilabel:`X (zavřít)` v pravém horním rohu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:202
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:161
msgid ""
"Then, click the :guilabel:`⋮ (three vertical dots)` button on the bottom-"
"right corner of the work order card to open the :guilabel:`What do you want "
"to do?` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Poté klikněte na tlačítko :guilabel:`⋮ (tři svislé tečky)` v pravém dolním "
"rohu karty pracovního příkazu, čímž otevřete vyskakovací okno :guilabel:`Co "
"chcete udělat?`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/measure_check.rst:205
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:164
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`What do you want to do?` pop-up window, select "
"the :guilabel:`Create a Quality Alert` button. Doing so opens a blank "
"quality alert form in a new :guilabel:`Quality Alerts` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Ve vyskakovacím okně :guilabel:`Co chcete udělat?` vyberte "
"tlačítko :guilabel:`Vytvořit upozornění na kvalitu`. Tím se v novém "
"vyskakovacím okně :guilabel:`Upozornění na kvalitu` otevře prázdný formulář "
"upozornění na kvalitu."

