msgstr ""
"I rullemenuen :guilabel:`Type` skal du vælge "
"kvalitetskontroltypen :guilabel:`Tag et billede`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:None
msgid "A quality check form configured for a Take a Picture quality check."
msgstr ""
"En kvalitetskontrolformular konfigureret til en Tag et billede "
"kvalitetskontrol."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:44
msgid "Quality control point"
msgstr "Kvalitetskontrolpunkt"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:46
msgid ""
"To create a |QCP| that generates *Take a Picture* quality checks "
"automatically, navigate to :menuselection:`Quality --> Quality Control --> "
"Control Points`, and click :guilabel:`New`. Fill out the new |QCP| form as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""
"For at oprette et |QCP|, der automatisk genererer *Tag et billede* "
"kvalitetskontroller, skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Kvalitet --> "
"Kvalitetskontrol --> Kontrolpunkter` og klikke på :guilabel:`Ny`. Udfyld den "
"nye |QCP|-formular som følger:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:51
msgid ""
"If the *Maintenance* app is installed, a :guilabel:`Device` field appears "
"after selecting the *Take a Picture* check type. Use this field to specify a "
"device that should be used to take quality check pictures. For information "
"about managing devices in the *Maintenance* app, see the documentation "
"on :ref:`adding new equipment <maintenance/equipment_management/"
"add_new_equipment>`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis appen *Vedligeholdelse* er installeret, vises et :guilabel:`Enhed`-"
"felt, efter kvalitetskontroltypen *Tag et billede* er valgt. Brug dette felt "
"til at angive en enhed, der skal bruges til at tage "
"kvalitetskontrolbilleder. For information om administration af enheder i "
"appen *Vedligeholdelse*, se dokumentationen om :ref:`tilføjelse af nyt "
"udstyr <maintenance/equipment_management/add_new_equipment>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:57
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Instructions` text field, enter instructions for how the "
"picture should be taken."
msgstr ""
"I tekstfeltet :guilabel:`Instruktioner` skal du indtaste instruktioner for, "
"hvordan billedet skal tages."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:None
msgid ""
"A Quality Control Point (QCP) form configured to create a Take a Picture "
"quality check."
msgstr ""
"En kvalitetskontrolpunkt (QCP)-formular konfigureret til at oprette en Tag "
"et billede kvalitetskontrol."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:65
msgid "Process a Take a Picture quality check"
msgstr "Behandl en Tag et billede kvalitetskontrol"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:67
msgid ""
"Once created, there are multiple ways that *Take a Picture* quality checks "
"can be processed. If a quality check is assigned to a specific inventory, "
"manufacturing, or work order, the check can be processed on the order "
"itself. Alternatively, a check can be processed from the check's page."
msgstr ""
"Når de er oprettet, er der flere måder, hvorpå *Tag et billede* "
"kvalitetskontroller kan behandles. Hvis en kvalitetskontrol er tildelt en "
"specifik lager-, produktions- eller arbejdsordre, kan kontrollen behandles "
"på selve ordren. Alternativt kan en kontrol behandles fra kontrollens side."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:74
msgid ""
"To process a *Take a Picture* quality check from the check's page, begin by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Quality --> Quality Control --> Quality "
"Checks`, and then select a quality check. Follow "
"the :guilabel:`Instructions` for how to take the picture."
msgstr ""
"For at behandle en *Tag et billede* kvalitetskontrol fra kontrollens side "
"skal du begynde med at navigere til :menuselection:`Kvalitet --> "
"Kvalitetskontrol --> Kvalitetskontroller` og derefter vælge en "
"kvalitetskontrol. Følg :guilabel:`Instruktionerne` for, hvordan billedet "
"skal tages."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:78
msgid ""
"After taking the picture, make sure it is stored on the device being used to "
"process the quality check (computer, tablet, etc.). Then, click "
"the :guilabel:`✏️ (pencil)` button in the :guilabel:`Picture` section to open "
"the device's file manager. In the file manager, navigate to the picture, "
"select it, and click :guilabel:`Open` to attach it."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have taget billedet skal du sørge for, at det er gemt på den enhed, "
"der bruges til at behandle kvalitetskontrollen (computer, tablet osv.). Klik "
"derefter på knappen :guilabel:`✏️ (blyant)` i afsnittet :guilabel:`Billede` "
"for at åbne enhedens filhåndtering. I filhåndteringen skal du navigere til "
"billedet, vælge det og klikke på :guilabel:`Åbn` for at vedhæfte det."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:None
msgid "The edit button (pencil) on a Take a Picture quality check."
msgstr "Redigeringsknappen (blyant) på en Tag et billede kvalitetskontrol."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:90
msgid ""
"To process a *Take a Picture* quality check on an order, select a "
"manufacturing order or inventory order (receipt, delivery, return, etc.), "
"for which a check is required. Manufacturing orders can be selected by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Manufacturing --> Operations --> Manufacturing "
"Orders`, and clicking on an order. Inventory orders can be selected by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Inventory`, clicking the :guilabel:`# To "
"Process` button on an operation card, and selecting an order."
msgstr ""
"For at behandle en *Tag et billede* kvalitetskontrol på en ordre skal du "
"vælge en produktionsordre eller lagerordre (modtagelse, levering, "
"returnering osv.), som der kræves en kontrol for. Produktionsordrer kan "
"vælges ved at navigere til :menuselection:`Produktion --> Operationer --> "
"Produktionsordrer` og klikke på en ordre. Lagerordrer kan vælges ved at "
"navigere til :menuselection:`Lager`, klikke på knappen :guilabel:`# At "
"behandle` på et operationskort og vælge en ordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:101
msgid ""
"Follow the instructions detailing how to take the picture, which are shown "
"on the :guilabel:`Quality Check` pop-up window. After taking the picture, "
"make sure it is stored on the device being used to process the quality check "
"(computer, tablet, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Følg instruktionerne om, hvordan man tager billedet, som vises i pop op-"
"vinduet :guilabel:`Kvalitetskontrol`. Efter du har taget billedet, skal du "
"sikre dig, at det er gemt på den enhed, der bruges til at behandle "
"kvalitetskontrollen (computer, tablet osv.)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:105
msgid ""
"Then, click the :guilabel:`Take a Picture` button in the :guilabel:`Picture` "
"section to open the device's file manager. In the file manager, navigate to "
"the picture, select it, and click :guilabel:`Open` to attach it. Finally, "
"click :guilabel:`Validate` on the :guilabel:`Quality Check` pop-up window to "
"complete the quality check."
msgstr ""
"Klik derefter på knappen :guilabel:`Tag et billede` i "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Billede` for at åbne enhedens filhåndtering. Naviger "
"til billedet i filhåndteringen, vælg det, og klik på :guilabel:`Åbn` for at "
"vedhæfte det. Klik til sidst på :guilabel:`Valider` i pop op-"
"vinduet :guilabel:`Kvalitetskontrol` for at fuldføre kvalitetskontrollen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:None
msgid ""
"A Take a Picture quality check pop-up window on a manufacturing or inventory "
"order."
msgstr ""
"Et pop op-vindue til Tag et billede-kvalitetskontrol på en produktions- "
"eller lagerordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:114
msgid ""
"If a quality alert must be created, click the :guilabel:`Quality Alert` "
"button that appears at the top of the manufacturing or inventory order after "
"the check is validated. Clicking :guilabel:`Quality Alert` opens a quality "
"alert form on a new page. For a complete guide on how to fill out quality "
"alert forms, view the documentation on :ref:`quality alerts <quality/"
"quality_management/quality-alerts>`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der skal oprettes en kvalitetsadvarsel, skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Kvalitetsadvarsel`, der vises øverst på produktions- "
"eller lagerordren, efter kontrollen er valideret. Når du klikker "
"på :guilabel:`Kvalitetsadvarsel`, åbnes en kvalitetsadvarselformular på en "
"ny side. For en komplet guide til, hvordan man udfylder "
"kvalitetsadvarselformularer, se dokumentationen om :ref:`kvalitetsadvarsler "
"<quality/quality_management/quality-alerts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:123
msgid ""
"When configuring a |QCP| that is triggered during manufacturing, a specific "
"work order can also be specified in the :guilabel:`Work Order Operation` "
"field on the |QCP| form. If a work order is specified, a *Take a Picture* "
"quality check is created for that specific work order, rather than the "
"manufacturing order as a whole."
msgstr ""
"Når du konfigurerer et |QCP|, der udløses under produktion, kan en specifik "
"arbejdsordre også angives i feltet :guilabel:`Arbejdsordreoperation` på |"
"QCP|-formularen. Hvis en arbejdsordre er angivet, oprettes en *Tag et "
"billede*-kvalitetskontrol for den specifikke arbejdsordre i stedet for "
"produktionsordren som helhed."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:128
msgid ""
"*Take a Picture* quality checks configured for work orders **must** be "
"completed from the *Shop Floor* module. To do so, begin by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Manufacturing --> Operations --> Manufacturing Orders`. "
"Then, select an |MO| that includes a work order for which a *Take a Picture* "
"quality check is required."
msgstr ""
"*Tag et billede*-kvalitetskontroller konfigureret til arbejdsordrer **skal** "
"udføres fra *Værksted*-modulet. For at gøre dette skal du begynde med at "
"navigere til :menuselection:`Produktion --> Operationer --> "
"Produktionsordrer`. Vælg derefter en |MO|, der inkluderer en arbejdsordre, "
"for hvilken en *Tag et billede*-kvalitetskontrol er påkrævet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:142
msgid ""
"Process the work order's steps until the *Take a Picture* quality check step "
"is reached. Click on the step to open a pop-up window that includes "
"instructions for how the picture should be taken. After taking the picture, "
"make sure it is stored on the device being used to process the quality check "
"(computer, tablet, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Udfør arbejdsordrens trin, indtil *Tag et billede*-kvalitetskontrol-trinnet "
"nås. Klik på trinnet for at åbne et pop op-vindue, der inkluderer "
"instruktioner om, hvordan billedet skal tages. Efter du har taget billedet, "
"skal du sikre dig, at det er gemt på den enhed, der bruges til at behandle "
"kvalitetskontrollen (computer, tablet osv.)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:147
msgid ""
"Then, click the :guilabel:`Take a Picture` button on the pop-up window to "
"open the device's file manager. In the file manager, navigate to the "
"picture, select it, and click :guilabel:`Open` to attach it."
msgstr ""
"Klik derefter på knappen :guilabel:`Tag et billede` i pop op-vinduet for at "
"åbne enhedens filhåndtering. Naviger til billedet i filhåndteringen, vælg "
"det, og klik på :guilabel:`Åbn` for at vedhæfte det."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:151
msgid ""
"Finally, click :guilabel:`Validate` at the bottom of the pop-up window to "
"complete the quality check. The pop-up window then moves on to the next step "
"of the work order."
msgstr ""
"Klik til sidst på :guilabel:`Valider` nederst i pop op-vinduet for at "
"fuldføre kvalitetskontrollen. Pop op-vinduet går derefter videre til næste "
"trin i arbejdsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:None
msgid "A Take a Picture check in the Shop Floor module."
msgstr "En Tag et billede-kontrol i Værksted-modulet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:173
msgid "Review picture attached to quality check"
msgstr "Gennemse billede vedhæftet kvalitetskontrol"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:175
msgid ""
"After a picture has been attached to a check, it can then be reviewed by "
"quality team members or other users. To do so, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Quality --> Quality Control --> Quality Checks`, and "
"select a quality check to review."
msgstr ""
"Efter et billede er blevet vedhæftet til en kontrol, kan det derefter "
"gennemses af kvalitetsteammedlemmer eller andre brugere. For at gøre dette "
"skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Kvalitet --> Kvalitetskontrol --> "
"Kvalitetskontroller`, og vælge en kvalitetskontrol, der skal gennemses."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:179
msgid ""
"The attached picture appears in the :guilabel:`Picture` section of the "
"quality check form. After reviewing the picture, click the :guilabel:`Pass` "
"button if the check passes, or the :guilabel:`Fail` button if the check "
"fails."
msgstr ""
"Det vedhæftede billede vises i sektionen :guilabel:`Billede` på "
"kvalitetskontrolformularen. Efter gennemgang af billedet skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Godkendt`, hvis kontrollen består, eller på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Ikke godkendt`, hvis kontrollen ikke består."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_check_types/picture_check.rst:None
msgid "A Take a Picture check with a picture attached."
msgstr "En Tag et billede-kontrol med et vedhæftet billede."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management.rst:5
msgid "Quality control basics"
msgstr "Grundlæggende kvalitetskontrol"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:3
msgid "Failure locations"
msgstr "Placering af fejl"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:8
msgid ""
"In Odoo, *quality control points* (QCPs) are used to create *quality "
"checks*, which prompt employees to confirm the quality of products, when "
"they are included in certain operations. By setting one or more *failure "
"locations* on a |QCP|, products that fail the quality checks it creates can "
"be sent to one of the specified locations."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo bruges *kvalitetskontrolpunkter* (QCP'er) til at oprette "
"*kvalitetskontroller*, som beder medarbejdere om at bekræfte kvaliteten af "
"produkter, når de indgår i bestemte operationer. Ved at angive en eller "
"flere *fejlplaceringer* på et |QCP|, kan produkter, der ikke består de "
"kvalitetskontroller, det opretter, sendes til en af de angivne placeringer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:14
msgid ""
"The *Failure Location* feature was added in version 17.0 of Odoo, and does "
"**not** appear in any previous version. To upgrade an Odoo database to a "
"more recent version, see the documentation on :doc:`database upgrades "
"<../../../../administration/upgrade>`."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen *Fejlplacering* blev tilføjet i version 17.0 af Odoo og vises "
"**ikke** i nogen tidligere version. For at opgradere en Odoo-database til en "
"nyere version, se dokumentationen om :doc:`databaseopgraderinger "
"<../../../../administration/upgrade>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:21
msgid ""
"To use failure locations, the *Storage Locations* setting **must** be "
"enabled in the settings of the *Inventory* app. This setting allows for the "
"creation of sub-locations within a warehouse, including failure locations."
msgstr ""
"For at bruge fejlplaceringer **skal** indstillingen *Lagerplaceringer* være "
"aktiveret i indstillingerne for *Lager*-appen. Denne indstilling giver "
"mulighed for at oprette underplaceringer i et lager, herunder "
"fejlplaceringer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:25
msgid ""
"To enable the *Storage Locations* setting, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`, and tick "
"the checkbox next to :guilabel:`Storage Locations`, under "
"the :guilabel:`Warehouses` heading. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"For at aktivere indstillingen *Lagerplaceringer* skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Lager-app --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, og sætte "
"flueben ud for :guilabel:`Lagerplaceringer` under "
"overskriften :guilabel:`Lagre`. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:None
msgid "The Storage Locations setting on the Inventory app settings page."
msgstr "Indstillingen Lagerplaceringer på Lager-appens indstillingsside."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:34
msgid ""
"Failure locations are most effective when used for products configured as "
"*storable products*. This is because inventory counts are only tracked for "
"storable products, versus *consumable* products, for which exact counts are "
"not tracked."
msgstr ""
"Fejlplaceringer er mest effektive, når de bruges til produkter konfigureret "
"som *lagerbare produkter*. Dette skyldes, at lagerbeholdninger kun spores "
"for lagerbare produkter, i modsætning til *forbrugsprodukter*, hvor eksakte "
"beholdninger ikke spores."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:38
msgid ""
"Quality checks can still be created for consumable products, and those "
"products can be sent to a failure location if they fail a check. However, "
"Odoo does not track the exact quantity of a consumable product stored at a "
"failure location."
msgstr ""
"Kvalitetstjek kan stadig oprettes for forbrugsprodukter, og disse produkter "
"kan sendes til en fejlplacering, hvis de ikke består et tjek. Odoo sporer "
"dog ikke den eksakte mængde af et forbrugsprodukt, der opbevares på en "
"fejlplacering."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:42
msgid ""
"To configure a product as storable, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory "
"app --> Products --> Products`, and select a product. In "
"the :guilabel:`Product Type` field on the :guilabel:`General Information` "
"tab, make sure that :guilabel:`Storable Product` is selected from the drop-"
"down menu."
msgstr ""
"For at konfigurere et produkt som lagerbart skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Lager-appen --> Produkter --> Produkter` og vælge et "
"produkt. I feltet :guilabel:`Produkttype` under fanen :guilabel:`Generelle "
"oplysninger` skal du sikre dig, at :guilabel:`Lagerbart produkt` er valgt i "
"rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:48
msgid "Add failure location to QCP"
msgstr "Tilføj fejlplacering til kvalitetskontrolpunkt"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:50
msgid ""
"To add a failure location to a |QCP|, navigate to :menuselection:`Quality "
"app --> Quality Control --> Control Points`. Select an existing |QCP| from "
"the list, or create a new one by clicking :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje en fejlplacering til et |QCP| skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Kvalitet-appen --> Kvalitetskontrol --> Kontrolpunkter`. "
"Vælg et eksisterende |QCP| fra listen, eller opret et nyt ved at klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:55
msgid ""
"The following instructions only detail the configuration settings necessary "
"for adding a failure location to a |QCP|. For a full overview of |QCPs| and "
"all of the options available when configuring them, see the documentation "
"on :doc:`quality control points <quality_control_points>`."
msgstr ""
"Følgende instruktioner beskriver kun de konfigurationsindstillinger, der er "
"nødvendige for at tilføje en fejlplacering til et |QCP|. For en komplet "
"oversigt over |QCPs| og alle tilgængelige muligheder ved konfiguration af "
"dem, se dokumentationen om :doc:`kvalitetskontrolpunkter "
"<quality_control_points>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:60
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Control Per` field on the |QCP| form, select "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` option. Doing so causes a :guilabel:`Failure "
"Locations` field to appear on the form. This field is only available when "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` option is selected."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Kontrol pr.` på |QCP|-formularen skal du vælge "
"indstillingen :guilabel:`Antal`. Dette medfører, at "
"et :guilabel:`Fejlplaceringer`-felt vises på formularen. Dette felt er kun "
"tilgængeligt, når indstillingen :guilabel:`Antal` er valgt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:64
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Failure Locations` field, select one or more locations "
"from the drop-down menu. To create a new location, type the desired location "
"name into the field, and then select :guilabel:`Create \"[name]\"` from the "
"drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Fejlplaceringer` skal du vælge en eller flere "
"placeringer fra rullemenuen. For at oprette en ny placering skal du indtaste "
"det ønskede placeringsnavn i feltet og derefter vælge :guilabel:`Opret "
"\"[navn]\"` fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:None
msgid "A QCP form in the Quality app, configured with a failure location."
msgstr ""
"En kvalitetskontrolpunktsformular i Kvalitet-appen, konfigureret med en "
"fejlplacering."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:73
msgid "Send products to failure location"
msgstr "Send produkter til fejlplacering"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:75
msgid ""
"Once a |QCP| has been configured with one or more failure locations, "
"products that fail a check created by the |QCP| can be routed to one of the "
"locations."
msgstr ""
"Når et |QCP| er blevet konfigureret med en eller flere fejlplaceringer, kan "
"produkter, der ikke består et tjek oprettet af |QCP|, dirigeres til en af "
"placeringerne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:78
msgid ""
"To do so, open an order that requires a quality check created by a |QCP| "
"configured with a failure location. For example, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations --> Receipts`, and select a "
"receipt."
msgstr ""
"For at gøre dette skal du åbne en ordre, der kræver et kvalitetstjek "
"oprettet af et |QCP| konfigureret med en fejlplacering. Naviger for eksempel "
"til :menuselection:`Lager-appen --> Operationer --> Modtagelser`, og vælg en "
"modtagelse."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:82
msgid ""
"At the top of the selected order, click the :guilabel:`Quality Checks` "
"button to open a pop-up window, from which the quality check can be "
"processed. At the bottom of the pop-up window, click the :guilabel:`Fail` "
"button to fail the quality check, which opens a second pop-up window, "
"titled :guilabel:`Quality Check Failed for [Product]`."
msgstr ""
"Øverst på den valgte ordre skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Kvalitetstjek` for at åbne et pop op-vindue, hvorfra "
"kvalitetstjekket kan behandles. Nederst i pop op-vinduet skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Ikke bestået` for at markere kvalitetstjekket som ikke "
"bestået, hvilket åbner et andet pop op-vindue med "
"titlen :guilabel:`Kvalitetstjek ikke bestået for [Produkt]`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:87
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Quantity Failed` field, enter the quantity of the product "
"that failed to pass the quality check. In the :guilabel:`Failure Location` "
"field, select a location to which the failed quantity should be sent. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm` at the bottom of the pop-up window to close it."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Ikke-bestået antal` skal du indtaste antallet af "
"produktet, der ikke bestod kvalitetstjekket. I "
"feltet :guilabel:`Fejlplacering` skal du vælge en placering, som den ikke-"
"beståede mængde skal sendes til. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Bekræft` "
"nederst i pop op-vinduet for at lukke det."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:None
msgid "The pop-up window that appears after a quality check fails."
msgstr "Pop op-vinduet, der vises, efter at et kvalitetstjek ikke er bestået."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:96
msgid ""
"Finally, on the order, click the :guilabel:`Validate` button at the top of "
"the page. Doing so confirms the products that failed the quality check were "
"sent to the failure location, while products that passed it were sent to "
"their normal storage locations."
msgstr ""
"Klik endelig på knappen :guilabel:`Valider` øverst på siden på ordren. Dette "
"bekræfter, at produkterne, der ikke bestod kvalitetstjekket, blev sendt til "
"fejlplaceringen, mens produkter, der bestod det, blev sendt til deres "
"normale lagerplaceringer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:101
msgid "View failure location inventory"
msgstr "Vis lagerbeholdning på fejlplacering"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:103
msgid ""
"To view the product quantities stored in a failure location, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Locations`. Select a "
"failure location from the list. Then, click the :guilabel:`Current Stock` "
"smart button on the location's page."
msgstr ""
"For at se produktmængderne, der er opbevaret på en fejlplacering, skal du "
"navigere til :menuselection:`Lager-appen --> Konfiguration --> Placeringer`. "
"Vælg en fejlplacering fra listen. Klik derefter på den smarte "
"knap :guilabel:`Aktuel lagerbeholdning` på placeringens side."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/failure_locations.rst:107
msgid ""
"A failure location's page lists all of the products stored within the "
"location, along with the quantity of each."
msgstr ""
"En fejlplacerings side viser alle produkterne, der er opbevaret på "
"placeringen, sammen med mængden af hvert produkt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:3
msgid "Quality alerts"
msgstr "Kvalitetsadvarsler"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:8
msgid ""
"In the Odoo *Quality* app, *quality alerts* are used to notify quality teams "
"of product defects or other issues. Quality alerts can be created from a "
"manufacturing or inventory order, from a work order in the *Shop Floor* "
"module, or directly within the *Quality* app."
msgstr ""
"I Odoos *Kvalitet*-app bruges *kvalitetsalarmer* til at underrette "
"kvalitetsteams om produktdefekter eller andre problemer. Kvalitetsalarmer "
"kan oprettes fra en produktions- eller lagerordre, fra en arbejdsordre i "
"*Værksted*-modulet eller direkte i *Kvalitet*-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:13
msgid "Create quality alerts"
msgstr "Opret kvalitetsalarmer"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:15
msgid "There are multiple ways to create a new quality alert:"
msgstr "Der er flere måder at oprette en ny kvalitetsalarm på:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:17
msgid ""
"**From the Quality app itself**, by to :menuselection:`Quality -->  Quality "
"Control --> Quality Alerts`, and then click :guilabel:`New` to open a "
"quality alert form."
msgstr ""
"**Fra selve Kvalitet-appen** ved at gå til :menuselection:`Kvalitet --> "
"Kvalitetskontrol --> Kvalitetsalarmer`, og derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Ny` "
"for at åbne en kvalitetsalarmformular."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:19
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Manufacturing --> Operations --> Manufacturing "
"Orders`, and then select an |MO|. Click the :guilabel:`Quality Alert` button "
"at the top of the |MO| to open a quality alert form in a new page."
msgstr ""
"Naviger til :menuselection:`Produktion --> Operationer --> "
"Produktionsordrer`, og vælg derefter en |MO|. Klik på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Kvalitetsalarm` øverst på |MO| for at åbne en "
"kvalitetsalarmformular på en ny side."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:24
msgid ""
"This method can only be used if a quality check has been requested for the |"
"MO|. The :guilabel:`Quality Alert` button will not appear otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Denne metode kan kun bruges, hvis der er anmodet om en kvalitetskontrol for |"
"MO|. Knappen :guilabel:`Kvalitetsalarm` vises ikke ellers."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:27
msgid ""
"Open the :menuselection:`Inventory` app, click the :guilabel:`# To Process` "
"button on an inventory order type card (Receipts, Delivery Orders, etc.), "
"and then select an order. Click the :guilabel:`Quality Alert` button at the "
"top of the order to open a quality alert form in a new page."
msgstr ""
"Åbn appen :menuselection:`Lager`, klik på knappen :guilabel:`# At behandle` "
"på et lagerodretype-kort (Modtagelser, Leveringsordrer osv.), og vælg "
"derefter en ordre. Klik på knappen :guilabel:`Kvalitetsalarm` øverst på "
"ordren for at åbne en kvalitetsalarmformular på en ny side."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:33
msgid ""
"This method can only be used if a quality check has been requested for the "
"inventory order. The :guilabel:`Quality Alert` button will not appear "
"otherwise. If the button does not appear, a quality alert can also be "
"created by clicking the :guilabel:`⚙️ (gear)` icon at the top of the page and "
"selecting the :guilabel:`Quality Alert` option from the resulting menu."
msgstr ""
"Denne metode kan kun bruges, hvis der er anmodet om en kvalitetskontrol for "
"lagerordren. Knappen :guilabel:`Kvalitetsalarm` vises ikke ellers. Hvis "
"knappen ikke vises, kan en kvalitetsalarm også oprettes ved at klikke på "
"ikonet :guilabel:`⚙️ (tandhjul)` øverst på siden og vælge "
"muligheden :guilabel:`Kvalitetsalarm` fra den resulterende menu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:38
msgid ""
"Open the :menuselection:`Shop Floor` module, and then select a work center "
"from the navigation bar at the top of the page. Then, click the :guilabel:`⋮ "
"(three vertical dots)` button at the bottom-right of a work order card to "
"open the :guilabel:`What do you want to do?` menu. Select "
"the :guilabel:`Create a Quality Alert` option from this menu to open a "
"quality alert in a pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Åbn modulet :menuselection:`Værksted`, og vælg derefter et arbejdscenter fra "
"navigationslinjen øverst på siden. Klik derefter på knappen :guilabel:`⋮ "
"(tre lodrette prikker)` nederst til højre på et arbejdsordrekort for at åbne "
"menuen :guilabel:`Hvad vil du gøre?`. Vælg muligheden :guilabel:`Opret en "
"kvalitetsalarm` fra denne menu for at åbne en kvalitetsalarm i et pop op-"
"vindue."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:45
msgid ""
"Depending on how a new quality alert form is opened, certain fields on the "
"form may already be filled in. For example, if a quality alert is created "
"from a work order card in the *Shop Floor* module, the :guilabel:`Product` "
"and :guilabel:`Work Center` are pre-filled."
msgstr ""
"Afhængigt af hvordan en ny kvalitetsalarmformular åbnes, kan visse felter på "
"formularen allerede være udfyldt. For eksempel, hvis en kvalitetsalarm "
"oprettes fra et arbejdsordrekort i *Værksted*-modulet, "
"er :guilabel:`Produkt` og :guilabel:`Arbejdscenter` udfyldt på forhånd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:50
msgid "Quality alerts form"
msgstr "Kvalitetsalarmformular"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:52
msgid ""
"After opening a new quality alert form, begin by giving it a "
"short :guilabel:`Title` that summarizes the issue with the product."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have åbnet en ny kvalitetsalarmformular, start med at give den en "
"kort :guilabel:`Titel`, der opsummerer problemet med produktet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:55
msgid "Then, if the quality alert is referencing:"
msgstr "Hvis kvalitetsalarmen derefter refererer til:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:57
msgid ""
"**A specific product or product variant**, select it from "
"the :guilabel:`Product` or :guilabel:`Product Variant` drop-down menus."
msgstr ""
"**Et specifikt produkt eller produktvariant**, vælg det fra "
"rullemenuen :guilabel:`Produkt` eller :guilabel:`Produktvariant`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:59
msgid ""
"**A specific work center**, select it from the :guilabel:`Work Center` drop-"
"down menu."
msgstr ""
"**Et specifikt arbejdscenter**, vælg det fra "
"rullemenuen :guilabel:`Arbejdscenter`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:60
msgid ""
"**A specific picking order**, select it from the :guilabel:`Picking` drop-"
"down menu."
msgstr ""
"**En specifik plukordre**, vælg den fra rullemenuen :guilabel:`Plukning`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:62
msgid ""
"Next in the :guilabel:`Team` field, select the quality team that is "
"responsible for managing the quality alert. If a specific employee should be "
"responsible for the quality alert, select them from "
"the :guilabel:`Responsible` drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Team` vælges derefter det kvalitetsteam, der er "
"ansvarligt for at håndtere kvalitetsalarmen. Hvis en bestemt medarbejder "
"skal være ansvarlig for kvalitetsalarmen, vælges vedkommende fra "
"rullemenuen :guilabel:`Ansvarlig`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:66
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Tags` field, select any tags relevant to the quality alert "
"from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Tags` vælges eventuelle tags, der er relevante for "
"kvalitetsalarmen, fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:69
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Root Cause` field to select the cause of the quality "
"issue, if known."
msgstr ""
"Brug feltet :guilabel:`Grundårsag` til at vælge årsagen til "
"kvalitetsproblemet, hvis den er kendt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:71
msgid ""
"Lastly, choose a :guilabel:`Priority` level by selecting a :guilabel:`⭐ "
"(star)` number between one and three. Quality alerts with higher priorities "
"appear at the top of the :guilabel:`Quality Alerts` Kanban board in the "
"*Quality* app."
msgstr ""
"Vælg til sidst et :guilabel:`Prioritet`sniveau ved at vælge et :guilabel:`⭐ "
"(stjerne)`-nummer mellem en og tre. Kvalitetsalarmer med højere prioriteter "
"vises øverst på :guilabel:`Kvalitetsalarmer` Kanban-tavlen i *Kvalitet*-"
"appen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:75
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the quality alert form are four tabs which aid in adding "
"supplemental information or actions to be taken for the quality alert. They "
"can be filled out as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Nederst på kvalitetsalarmformularen er der fire faner, der hjælper med at "
"tilføje supplerende information eller handlinger, der skal udføres for "
"kvalitetsalarmen. De kan udfyldes som følger:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:78
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Description` tab, enter a description of the quality issue."
msgstr ""
"På fanen :guilabel:`Beskrivelse` skal du angive en beskrivelse af "
"kvalitetsproblemet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:79
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Corrective Actions` tab to detail the steps that should "
"be taken to fix the issue."
msgstr ""
"Brug fanen :guilabel:`Korrigerende handlinger` til at detaljere de trin, der "
"skal tages for at løse problemet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:81
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Preventive Actions` tab to detail what should be done to "
"prevent the issue from occurring in the future."
msgstr ""
"Brug fanen :guilabel:`Forebyggende handlinger` til at detaljere, hvad der "
"skal gøres for at forhindre problemet i at opstå i fremtiden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:83
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Miscellaneous` tab, select the :guilabel:`Vendor` of the "
"product. If using an Odoo database which manages multiple companies, select "
"the relevant company in the :guilabel:`Company` field. Finally, specify when "
"the alert was assigned to a quality team in the :guilabel:`Date Assigned` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"På fanen :guilabel:`Diverse` skal du vælge "
"produktets :guilabel:`Leverandør`. Hvis du bruger en Odoo-database, der "
"håndterer flere virksomheder, skal du vælge den relevante virksomhed i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Virksomhed`. Angiv til sidst, hvornår advarslen blev "
"tildelt til et kvalitetsteam i feltet :guilabel:`Dato for tildeling`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:None
msgid "A quality alert form that has been filled out."
msgstr "En kvalitetsadvarselformular, der er udfyldt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:93
msgid "Manage quality alerts"
msgstr "Administrer kvalitetsadvarsler"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:95
msgid ""
"To view all existing quality alerts, navigate to :menuselection:`Quality --> "
"Quality Control --> Quality Alerts`. By default, alerts are displayed in a "
"Kanban board view, which organizes them into different stages based on where "
"they are in the review process."
msgstr ""
"For at se alle eksisterende kvalitetsadvarsler skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Kvalitet --> Kvalitetskontrol --> Kvalitetsadvarsler`. "
"Som standard vises advarsler i en Kanban-tavlevisning, der organiserer dem i "
"forskellige faser baseret på, hvor de er i gennemgangsprocessen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:99
msgid ""
"To move an alert to a different stage, simply drag and drop it on the "
"desired stage. Alternatively, select a quality alert to open it, and then "
"click the desired stage above the top-right corner of the quality alert form."
msgstr ""
"For at flytte en advarsel til en anden fase skal du blot trække og slippe "
"den på den ønskede fase. Alternativt kan du vælge en kvalitetsadvarsel for "
"at åbne den og derefter klikke på den ønskede fase over øverste højre hjørne "
"af kvalitetsadvarselformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:103
msgid ""
"To create a new alert within a specific stage, click the :guilabel:`+ "
"(plus)` button to the right of the stage name. In the new alert card that "
"appears below the stage title, enter the :guilabel:`Title` of the alert, and "
"then click :guilabel:`Add`. To configure the rest of the alert, select the "
"alert card to open its form."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en ny advarsel inden for en bestemt fase skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`+ (plus)` til højre for fasenavnet. I det nye "
"advarselskort, der vises under fasetitlen, skal du indtaste "
"advarslens :guilabel:`Titel` og derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj`. For "
"at konfigurere resten af advarslen skal du vælge advarselskortet for at åbne "
"dets formular."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_alerts.rst:None
msgid "The Quality Alerts page, displaying alerts in a Kanban view."
msgstr "Siden Kvalitetsadvarsler, der viser advarsler i en Kanban-visning."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:3
msgid "Quality checks"
msgstr "Kvalitetskontrol"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:9
msgid ""
"Quality checks are manual inspections conducted by employees, and are used "
"to ensure the quality of products. In Odoo, a quality check can be conducted "
"for a single product, or multiple products within the same inventory "
"operation or manufacturing order."
msgstr ""
"Kvalitetskontroller er manuel inspektion udført af medarbejdere og bruges "
"til at sikre kvaliteten af produkter. I Odoo kan en kvalitetskontrol udføres "
"for et enkelt produkt eller flere produkter inden for samme lageroperation "
"eller produktionsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:13
msgid ""
"Using a Quality Control Point (QCP), it is possible to create quality checks "
"automatically at regular intervals. When quality checks are created by a |"
"QCP|, they appear on a manufacturing or inventory order, where the employee "
"processing the order will be prompted to complete them. For a full "
"explanation of how to create and configure a |QCP|, see the documentation "
"on :ref:`quality control points <quality/quality_management/quality-control-"
"points>`."
msgstr ""
"Ved hjælp af et kvalitetskontrolpunkt (QCP) er det muligt at oprette "
"kvalitetskontroller automatisk med regelmæssige intervaller. Når "
"kvalitetskontroller oprettes af et |QCP|, vises de på en produktions- eller "
"lagerordre, hvor medarbejderen, der behandler ordren, vil blive bedt om at "
"fuldføre dem. For en fuld forklaring af, hvordan man opretter og "
"konfigurerer et |QCP|, se dokumentationen om :ref:`kvalitetskontrolpunkter "
"<quality/quality_management/quality-control-points>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:19
msgid ""
"While quality checks are most commonly created automatically by a |QCP|, it "
"is also possible to manually create a single quality check. Creating a check "
"manually is useful when an employee wants to schedule a quality check that "
"will only occur once, or register a quality check that they conduct "
"unprompted."
msgstr ""
"Selvom kvalitetskontroller oftest oprettes automatisk af et |QCP|, er det "
"også muligt at oprette en enkelt kvalitetskontrol manuelt. At oprette en "
"kontrol manuelt er nyttigt, når en medarbejder ønsker at planlægge en "
"kvalitetskontrol, der kun vil forekomme én gang, eller registrere en "
"kvalitetskontrol, som de udfører uden forudgående anmodning."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:27
msgid "Manual quality check"
msgstr "Manuel kvalitetskontrol"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:29
msgid ""
"To manually create a single quality check, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Quality --> Quality Control --> Quality Checks`, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"For manuelt at oprette en enkelt kvalitetskontrol skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Kvalitet --> Kvalitetskontrol --> Kvalitetskontroller` "
"og klikke på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:32
msgid ""
"On the quality check form, begin by specifying a :guilabel:`Title` for the "
"quality check. This should be a brief description of what the quality check "
"entails."
msgstr ""
"Begynd på kvalitetskontrolformularen med at angive en :guilabel:`Titel` for "
"kvalitetskontrollen. Dette skal være en kort beskrivelse af, hvad "
"kvalitetskontrollen indebærer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:35
msgid "Select an option from the :guilabel:`Control per` drop-down menu:"
msgstr "Vælg en mulighed fra rullemenuen :guilabel:`Kontrol pr.`:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:37
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Operation` requests a check for an entire operation (such as a "
"delivery order) and all products within it."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Operation` anmoder om en kontrol for en hel operation (såsom en "
"leveringsordre) og alle produkter inden for den."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product` requests a check for every unit of a product that is "
"part of an operation (e.g., every unit of a product within a delivery order)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produkt` anmoder om en kontrol for hver enhed af et produkt, der "
"er en del af en operation (f.eks. hver enhed af et produkt inden for en "
"leveringsordre)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quantity` requests a check for every quantity of a product that "
"is part of an operation (e.g., one check for five units of a product within "
"a delivery order)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Antal` anmoder om en kontrol for hvert antal af et produkt, der "
"er en del af en operation (f.eks. én kontrol for fem enheder af et produkt "
"inden for en leveringsordre)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:44
msgid ""
"When :guilabel:`Product` or :guilabel:`Quantity` are selected, it is "
"possible to select a :guilabel:`Product` in inventory. If that product is "
"tracked by lot or serial number, the :guilabel:`Lot/Serial` field appears, "
"where the lot or serial number to be quality checked must be specified."
msgstr ""
"Når :guilabel:`Produkt` eller :guilabel:`Antal` er valgt, er det muligt at "
"vælge et :guilabel:`Produkt` på lageret. Hvis produktet spores efter lot- "
"eller serienummer, vises feltet :guilabel:`Lot/serienummer`, hvor det lot- "
"eller serienummer, der skal kvalitetskontrolleres, skal angives."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:49
msgid ""
"Next, select an inventory operation from the :guilabel:`Picking` drop-down "
"menu or a manufacturing order from the :guilabel:`Production Order` drop-"
"down menu. This is necessary because Odoo needs to know for which operation "
"the quality check is being conducted."
msgstr ""
"Vælg derefter en lageroperation fra rullemenuen :guilabel:`Plukning` eller "
"en produktionsordre fra rullemenuen :guilabel:`Produktionsordre`. Dette er "
"nødvendigt, fordi Odoo skal vide, for hvilken operation kvalitetskontrollen "
"udføres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:54
msgid ""
"It is also possible to create a quality check directly from an *Inventory* "
"operation. To do so, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Operations` and select an operation type from the :guilabel:`Transfers` "
"menu. Open an operation from the list, then click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(cog)` icon and select :guilabel:`Quality Check`. "
"The :guilabel:`Control per`, :guilabel:`Product`, and :guilabel:`Picking` "
"fields are automatically filled."
msgstr ""
"Det er også muligt at oprette en kvalitetskontrol direkte fra en *Lager*-"
"operation. Gå til :menuselection:`Lager-appen --> Operationer` og vælg en "
"operationstype fra menuen :guilabel:`Overførsler`. Åbn en operation fra "
"listen, klik derefter på ikonet :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(tandhjul)` og "
"vælg :guilabel:`Kvalitetskontrol`. Felterne :guilabel:`Kontrol "
"pr.`, :guilabel:`Produkt` og :guilabel:`Plukning` udfyldes automatisk."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:60
msgid ""
"If the quality check should be assigned to a specific |QCP|, select it from "
"the :guilabel:`Control Point` drop-down menu. This is useful if the quality "
"check is being created manually, but should still be recognized as belonging "
"to a specific |QCP|."
msgstr ""
"Hvis kvalitetskontrollen skal tildeles til et bestemt |QCP|, skal du vælge "
"det fra rullemenuen :guilabel:`Kontrolpunkt`. Dette er nyttigt, hvis "
"kvalitetskontrollen oprettes manuelt, men stadig skal anerkendes som "
"tilhørende et bestemt |QCP|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:64
msgid "Select a quality check type from the :guilabel:`Type` drop-down field:"
msgstr "Vælg en kvalitetskontroltype fra feltet :guilabel:`Type`:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:66
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Instructions` provides specific instructions for how to conduct "
"the quality check."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Instruktioner` giver specifikke instruktioner for, hvordan "
"kvalitetskontrollen skal udføres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:67
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Take a Picture` requires a picture to be attached to the check "
"before the check can be completed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tag et billede` kræver, at et billede vedhæftes til kontrollen, "
"før kontrollen kan fuldføres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:69
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Print label` opens a pop-up from which labels can be printed. "
"This step can be customized to provide instructions about where to add the "
"labels on a product."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Udskriv etiket` åbner en pop-up, hvorfra etiketter kan udskrives. "
"Dette trin kan tilpasses for at give instruktioner om, hvor etiketterne skal "
"placeres på et produkt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:71
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pass - Fail` is used when the product being checked must meet a "
"certain criteria to pass the check."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bestået - Ikke bestået` bruges, når det produkt, der "
"kontrolleres, skal opfylde visse kriterier for at bestå kontrollen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:73
msgid ""
"Selecting :guilabel:`Measure` causes a :guilabel:`Measure` input field to "
"appear, in which a measurement must be entered before the check can be "
"completed."
msgstr ""
"Valg af :guilabel:`Måling` medfører, at et :guilabel:`Måling` inputfelt "
"vises, hvor en måling skal indtastes, før kontrollen kan gennemføres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:75
msgid ""
"Selecting :guilabel:`Worksheet` causes a :guilabel:`Quality Template` drop-"
"down field to appear. Use it to select a quality worksheet that must be "
"filled out to complete the check."
msgstr ""
"Valg af :guilabel:`Arbejdsark` medfører, at et :guilabel:`Kvalitetsskabelon` "
"rullemenufelt vises. Brug det til at vælge et kvalitetsarbejdsark, der skal "
"udfyldes for at gennemføre kontrollen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:78
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Team` field, select the quality team that is responsible "
"for the quality check. In the :guilabel:`Company` field, select the company "
"that owns the product being inspected."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Team` vælges det kvalitetsteam, der er ansvarligt for "
"kvalitetskontrollen. I feltet :guilabel:`Virksomhed` vælges den virksomhed, "
"der ejer det produkt, der inspiceres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:81
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Notes` tab at the bottom of the form, enter any relevant "
"instructions in the :guilabel:`Instructions` text entry box (e.g., `Attach a "
"picture of the product`). In the :guilabel:`Notes` text entry box, enter any "
"relevant information about the quality check (who created it, why it was "
"created, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"På fanen :guilabel:`Noter` nederst på formularen skal du indtaste relevante "
"instruktioner i tekstfeltet :guilabel:`Instruktioner` (f.eks. `Vedhæft et "
"billede af produktet`). I tekstfeltet :guilabel:`Noter` skal du indtaste "
"relevante oplysninger om kvalitetskontrollen (hvem oprettede den, hvorfor "
"den blev oprettet osv.)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:86
msgid ""
"Finally, if the check is being processed immediately, click "
"the :guilabel:`Pass` button at the top left of the screen if the check "
"passes, or the :guilabel:`Fail` button if the check fails."
msgstr ""
"Endelig, hvis kontrollen behandles med det samme, klikkes på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Bestået` øverst til venstre på skærmen, hvis kontrollen "
"bestås, eller på knappen :guilabel:`Ikke bestået`, hvis kontrollen ikke "
"bestås."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:None
msgid "A quality check form filled out for a Pass - Fail check."
msgstr ""
"En kvalitetskontrolformular udfyldt til en Bestået - Ikke bestået kontrol."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:93
msgid "Process quality check"
msgstr "Behandle kvalitetskontrol"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:95
msgid ""
"Quality checks can be processed directly on the quality check's page, or "
"from a manufacturing or inventory order for which a check is required. "
"Alternatively, if a quality check is created for a specific work order "
"operation, the check is processed in the *Shop Floor* module."
msgstr ""
"Kvalitetskontroller kan behandles direkte på kvalitetskontrollens side eller "
"fra en produktions- eller lagerordre, hvor en kontrol er påkrævet. "
"Alternativt, hvis en kvalitetskontrol oprettes til en specifik "
"arbejdsordrehandling, behandles kontrollen i modulet *Værksted*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:100
msgid ""
"It is not possible to manually create a single quality check that is "
"assigned to a specific work order operation. Quality checks for work order "
"operations can only be created by a |QCP|. See the documentation "
"on :ref:`Quality Control Points <quality/quality_management/quality-control-"
"points>` for information about how to configure a |QCP| that will create "
"quality checks for a specific work order operation."
msgstr ""
"Det er ikke muligt manuelt at oprette en enkelt kvalitetskontrol, der er "
"tildelt en specifik arbejdsordrehandling. Kvalitetskontroller til "
"arbejdsordrehandlinger kan kun oprettes af et |QCP|. Se dokumentationen "
"om :ref:`kvalitetskontrolpunkter <quality/quality_management/quality-control-"
"points>` for information om, hvordan man konfigurerer et |QCP|, der opretter "
"kvalitetskontroller til en specifik arbejdsordrehandling."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:107
msgid "Quality check page"
msgstr "Kvalitetskontrolside"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:109
msgid ""
"To process a quality check from the check's page, begin by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Quality --> Quality Control --> Quality Checks`, then "
"select the check to process. Follow the instructions for how to complete the "
"check, listed in the :guilabel:`Instructions` field of the :guilabel:`Notes` "
"tab at the bottom of the page."
msgstr ""
"For at behandle en kvalitetskontrol fra kontrollens side, start med at "
"navigere til :menuselection:`Kvalitet --> Kvalitetskontrol --> "
"Kvalitetskontroller`, og vælg derefter den kontrol, der skal behandles. Følg "
"instruktionerne for, hvordan kontrollen gennemføres, angivet i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Instruktioner` på fanen :guilabel:`Noter` nederst på siden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:114
msgid ""
"If the quality check passes, click the :guilabel:`Pass` button at the top of "
"the page. If the check fails, click the :guilabel:`Fail` button, instead."
msgstr ""
"Hvis kvalitetskontrollen bestås, klikkes på knappen :guilabel:`Bestået` "
"øverst på siden. Hvis kontrollen ikke bestås, klikkes i stedet på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Ikke bestået`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:118
msgid "Quality check on order"
msgstr "Kvalitetskontrol på ordre"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:120
msgid ""
"To process a quality check on an order, select a manufacturing or inventory "
"order (receipt, delivery, return, etc.), for which a check is required. "
"Manufacturing orders can be selected by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Manufacturing --> Operations --> Manufacturing Orders`, "
"and clicking on an order. Inventory orders can be selected by navigating to "
"the :menuselection:`Inventory` app, clicking the :guilabel:`# To` button on "
"an operation card (e.g., :guilabel:`5 to Deliver`), and selecting an order."
msgstr ""
"For at behandle en kvalitetskontrol på en ordre skal du vælge en "
"produktions- eller lagerordre (modtagelse, levering, retur osv.), som kræver "
"en kontrol. Produktionsordrer kan vælges ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Produktion --> Operationer --> Produktionsordrer` og "
"klikke på en ordre. Lagerordrer kan vælges ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Lager`-appen, klikke på :guilabel:`# Til`-knappen på et "
"operationskort (f.eks. :guilabel:`5 at levere`) og vælge en ordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:127
msgid ""
"On the selected inventory or manufacturing order, a "
"purple :guilabel:`Quality Checks` button appears at the top of the order. "
"Click the button to open the quality check pop-up window, which shows all of "
"the quality checks required for that order."
msgstr ""
"På den valgte lager- eller produktionsordre vises en "
"lilla :guilabel:`Kvalitetskontroller`-knap øverst på ordren. Klik på knappen "
"for at åbne pop op-vinduet til kvalitetskontrol, som viser alle de "
"kvalitetskontroller, der kræves for den pågældende ordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:131
msgid ""
"Follow the instructions that appear on the quality check pop-up window. If a "
"Pass - Fail check is being processed, complete the check by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Pass` or :guilabel:`Fail` at the bottom of the pop-up "
"window. For all other quality check types, a :guilabel:`Validate` button "
"appears instead. Click it to complete the check."
msgstr ""
"Følg instruktionerne, der vises i pop op-vinduet til kvalitetskontrol. Hvis "
"en Bestået - Ikke bestået-kontrol behandles, skal du fuldføre kontrollen ved "
"at klikke på :guilabel:`Bestået` eller :guilabel:`Ikke bestået` nederst i "
"pop op-vinduet. For alle andre kvalitetskontroltyper vises "
"en :guilabel:`Valider`-knap i stedet. Klik på den for at fuldføre kontrollen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:None
msgid "The quality check pop-up window on a manufacturing order."
msgstr "Pop op-vinduet til kvalitetskontrol på en produktionsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:140
msgid "Quality check on work order"
msgstr "Kvalitetskontrol på arbejdsordre"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:142
msgid ""
"To process a quality check for a work order, begin by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Manufacturing --> Operations --> Manufacturing Orders`. "
"Select an |MO| that includes a work order for which a quality check is "
"required."
msgstr ""
"For at behandle en kvalitetskontrol for en arbejdsordre, start med at "
"navigere til :menuselection:`Produktion --> Handlinger --> "
"Produktionsordrer`. Vælg en |MO|, der inkluderer en arbejdsordre, hvor en "
"kvalitetskontrol er påkrævet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:152
msgid ""
"For a full guide to the Shop Floor module, see the :doc:`Shop Floor overview "
"<../../manufacturing/shop_floor/shop_floor_overview>` documentation."
msgstr ""
"For en komplet guide til modulet Værksted, se "
"dokumentationen :doc:`Værktedsoversigt <../../manufacturing/shop_floor/"
"shop_floor_overview>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:159
msgid ""
"Process the work order's steps until the quality check step is reached. "
"Click on the step to open a pop-up window that details how the check should "
"be completed. After following the instructions, click :guilabel:`Validate` "
"to complete the check. Alternatively, if a *Pass - Fail* check is being "
"processed, click either the :guilabel:`Pass` or :guilabel:`Fail` button."
msgstr ""
"Behandl arbejdsordrens trin, indtil kvalitetskontrolstrinnet nås. Klik på "
"trinnet for at åbne et pop op-vindue, der beskriver, hvordan kontrollen skal "
"gennemføres. Efter at have fulgt instruktionerne, klikkes "
"på :guilabel:`Valider` for at gennemføre kontrollen. Alternativt, hvis en "
"*Bestået - Ikke bestået* kontrol behandles, klikkes enten på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Bestået` eller :guilabel:`Ikke bestået`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:164
msgid ""
"It is also possible to complete a quality check by clicking the checkbox on "
"the right side of the step. Doing so automatically marks the check as "
"*Passed*."
msgstr ""
"Det er også muligt at gennemføre en kvalitetskontrol ved at klikke på "
"afkrydsningsfeltet på højre side af trinnet. Dette markerer automatisk "
"kontrollen som *Bestået*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:168
msgid ""
"The specific steps for processing a quality check depend upon the type of "
"check being conducted. For information about processing each type of quality "
"check, see the associated documentation:"
msgstr ""
"De specifikke trin til behandling af en kvalitetskontrol afhænger af den "
"type kontrol, der udføres. For information om behandling af hver type "
"kvalitetskontrol, se den tilknyttede dokumentation:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:171
msgid ":doc:`../quality_check_types/instructions_check`"
msgstr ":doc:`../quality_check_types/instructions_check`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:172
msgid ":doc:`../quality_check_types/pass_fail_check`"
msgstr ":doc:`../quality_check_types/pass_fail_check`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:173
msgid ":doc:`../quality_check_types/measure_check`"
msgstr ":doc:`../quality_check_types/measure_check`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_checks.rst:174
msgid ":doc:`../quality_check_types/picture_check`"
msgstr ":doc:`../quality_check_types/picture_check`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:11
msgid ""
"In Odoo, *quality control points* (QCPs) create :doc:`quality checks "
"<quality_checks>` at predetermined intervals. |QCPs| can be configured to "
"create quality checks for specific operations (manufacturing, delivery, "
"etc.), as well as specific products within those operations."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo vytváří *kontrolní body kvality* (QCP) :doc:`kontroly kvality "
"<quality_checks>` v předem stanovených intervalech. |QCPs| lze "
"nakonfigurovat tak, aby vytvářely kontroly kvality pro konkrétní operace "
"(výroba, dodání atd.) i konkrétní produkty v rámci těchto operací."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:15
msgid ""
"Using |QCPs| allows quality teams to ensure products are being regularly "
"inspected for defects and other issues."
msgstr ""
"Brug af |QCPs| gør det muligt for kvalitetsteams at sikre, at produkter "
"bliver regelmæssigt inspiceret for defekter og andre problemer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:19
msgid "Configure quality control points"
msgstr "Konfigurer kvalitetskontrolpunkter"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:21
msgid ""
"To create a new |QCP|, navigate to :menuselection:`Quality --> Quality "
"Control --> Control Points`, and then click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette et nyt |QCP|, gå til :menuselection:`Kvalitet --> "
"Kvalitetskontrol --> Kontrolpunkter`, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:24
msgid ""
"Begin filling out the new |QCP| by entering a unique :guilabel:`Title` that "
"makes the |QCP| easily identifiable."
msgstr ""
"Begynd at udfylde det nye |QCP| ved at indtaste en unik :guilabel:`Titel`, "
"der gør |QCP| let identificerbar."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:27
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Products` field, select one or more products the |QCP| "
"should apply to. If the |QCP| should apply to an entire product category, "
"select it in the :guilabel:`Product Categories` field."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Produkter` vælges et eller flere produkter, som |QCP| "
"skal gælde for. Hvis |QCP| skal gælde for en hel produktkategori, vælges den "
"i feltet :guilabel:`Produktkategorier`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:31
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Operations` field, select the operations that should "
"trigger the |QCP|. For example, selecting the :guilabel:`Manufacturing` "
"option in the :guilabel:`Operations` field causes a quality check to be "
"created for new manufacturing orders (MOs)."
msgstr ""
"V poli :guilabel:`Operace` vyberte operace, které by měly spustit |QCP|. "
"Například výběr možnosti :guilabel:`Produktion` v poli :guilabel:`Operace` "
"způsobí vytvoření kontroly kvality pro nové výrobní příkazy."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:36
msgid ""
"When creating a new |QCP|, at least one operation must be listed in "
"the :guilabel:`Operations` field. However, the :guilabel:`Products` "
"and :guilabel:`Product Categories` fields can be left blank. If they are "
"left blank, the |QCP| generates quality checks for every instance of the "
"specified operations."
msgstr ""
"Při vytváření nového |QCP| musí být v poli :guilabel:`Operace` uvedena "
"alespoň jedna operace. Pole :guilabel:`Produkty` a :guilabel:`Kategorie "
"produktů` však mohou zůstat prázdná. Pokud zůstanou prázdná, |QCP| generuje "
"kontroly kvality pro každou instanci specifikovaných operací."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:41
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Manufacturing` operation is selected in "
"the :guilabel:`Operations` field, a new field appears below it, "
"titled :guilabel:`Work Order Operation`. From this field, select a specific "
"work order to generate quality checks for that operation, rather than the "
"manufacturing operation in general."
msgstr ""
"Je-li v poli :guilabel:`Operace` vybrána operace :guilabel:`Produktion`, "
"objeví se pod ní nové pole s názvem :guilabel:`Operace pracovního příkazu`. "
"Z tohoto pole vyberte konkrétní pracovní příkaz pro generování kontrol "
"kvality pro tuto operaci místo výrobní operace obecně."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:47
msgid ""
"A |QCP| could be configured to create quality checks for the `Assembly` work "
"order of the `Coffee Table` product. Then, if a new |MO| is confirmed for a "
"`Coffee Table`, the |QCP| creates a quality check specifically for the "
"`Assembly` operation."
msgstr ""
"Et |QCP| kunne konfigureres til at oprette kvalitetskontroller for "
"arbejdsordren `Assembly` for produktet `Coffee Table`. Hvis en ny |MO| "
"derefter bekræftes for et `Coffee Table`, opretter |QCP| en kvalitetskontrol "
"specifikt for handlingen `Assembly`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:51
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Company` field, select a company for which this |QCP| is "
"valid."
msgstr ""
"V poli :guilabel:`Společnost` vyberte společnost, pro kterou je tento |QCP| "
"platný."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:53
msgid ""
"If a specific quality team member is responsible for the |QCP|, select them "
"in the :guilabel:`Responsible` field."
msgstr ""
"Je-li za |QCP| odpovědný konkrétní člen týmu kvality, vyberte ho v poli "
":guilabel:`Odpovědná osoba`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:56
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Control per` field to one of three options that determine "
"*when* a new quality check is created:"
msgstr ""
"Nastavte pole :guilabel:`Kontrola na` na jednu ze tří možností, které "
"určují, *kdy* se vytvoří nová kontrola kvality:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Operation`: One check is requested for the specified operation as "
"a whole."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Operace`: Pro specifikovanou operaci jako celek je vyžádána jedna "
"kontrola."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:60
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product`: One check is requested for each *unique* product "
"included in the specified operation. For example, a delivery operation for "
"one table and four chairs would generate two checks, since two *unique* "
"products are included in the operation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produkt`: Der anmodes om én kontrol for hvert *unikt* produkt, "
"der indgår i den angivne operation. For eksempel vil en leveringsoperation "
"for ét bord og fire stole generere to kontroller, da to *unikke* produkter "
"indgår i operationen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:63
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quantity`: A check is requested for a certain percentage of items "
"within the specified operation. This percentage is set by specifying "
"a :guilabel:`Partial Test` value in the percentage field that appears below. "
"If `100` % is specified, one quality check is created for the full quantity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Množství`: Kontrola je vyžádána pro určité procento položek v "
"rámci specifikované operace. Toto procento se nastaví zadáním hodnoty "
":guilabel:`Částečný test` v procentním poli, které se zobrazí níže. Je-li "
"zadáno `100` %, vytvoří se jedna kontrola kvality pro celé množství."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:68
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Control Frequency` field to one of four options that "
"determine *how often* a new quality check is created:"
msgstr ""
"Nastavte pole :guilabel:`Frekvence kontroly` na jednu ze čtyř možností, "
"které určují, *jak často* se vytvoří nová kontrola kvality:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:71
msgid ""
":guilabel:`All`: A quality check is requested every time the conditions of "
"the |QCP| are met."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Alle`: Der anmodes om en kvalitetskontrol, hver gang "
"betingelserne for |QCP| er opfyldt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:72
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Randomly`: A quality check is randomly requested for a certain "
"percentage of operations, which can be specified in the :guilabel:`#% of the "
"time` field that appears below."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Náhodně`: Kontrola kvality je náhodně vyžádána pro určité "
"procento operací, které lze zadat v poli :guilabel:`#% času`, které se "
"zobrazí níže."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:74
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Periodically`: A quality check is requested once every set period "
"of time, which is specified by entering a numerical value in the field below "
"and choosing either :guilabel:`Days`, :guilabel:`Weeks`, "
"or :guilabel:`Months` as the desired time interval."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Periodicky`: Kontrola kvality je vyžádána jednou za nastavenou "
"dobu, která se určí zadáním číselné hodnoty do pole níže a výběrem buď "
":guilabel:`Dny`, :guilabel:`Týdny`, nebo :guilabel:`Měsíce` jako požadovaný "
"časový interval."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:77
msgid ":guilabel:`On-Demand`: A quality check must be manually requested."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Na vyžádání`: Kontrola kvality musí být vyžádána ručně."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:79
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Type` field, specify the type of quality check that should "
"be performed. The method for processing quality checks created by the |QCP| "
"depends upon the type of quality check selected:"
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Type` skal du angive typen af kvalitetskontrol, der skal "
"udføres. Metoden til behandling af kvalitetskontroller oprettet af |QCP| "
"afhænger af den valgte type kvalitetskontrol:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:83
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Instructions` checks provide specific instructions for how to "
"complete the quality check."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Instruktioner`-kontroller giver specifikke instruktioner for, "
"hvordan kvalitetskontrollen skal gennemføres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:85
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Take a Picture` checks require a picture of the product be "
"uploaded for later review by the assigned quality team. Optionally specify "
"a :guilabel:`Device` for this check."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tag et billede`-kontroller kræver, at der uploades et billede af "
"produktet til senere gennemgang af det tildelte kvalitetsteam. Angiv "
"eventuelt en :guilabel:`Enhed` til denne kontrol."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:87
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Register Consumed Materials` checks prompt employees to confirm "
"the materials consumed during the manufacturing operation. "
"A :guilabel:`Product To Register` must be specified."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Registrer forbrugte materialer`-kontroller beder medarbejdere om "
"at bekræfte de materialer, der er forbrugt under produktionsoperationen. Et "
":guilabel:`Produkt til registrering` skal angives."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Register Production` checks prompt manufacturing employees to "
"confirm the quantity of the product that was produced during the "
"manufacturing operation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Registrer produktion`-kontroller beder produktionsmedarbejdere om "
"at bekræfte mængden af produktet, der blev produceret under "
"produktionsoperationen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Print label` checks prompt operators to download and print a "
"label to attach to the product or its packaging. Specify a :guilabel:`Report "
"Type` file format to save labels to, and optionally specify "
"a :guilabel:`Device` to which the label should print."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Udskriv label`-kontroller beder operatører om at downloade og "
"udskrive en label til at sætte på produktet eller dets emballage. Angiv et "
":guilabel:`Rapporttype`-filformat til at gemme labels i, og angiv eventuelt "
"en :guilabel:`Enhed`, som labelen skal udskrives til."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pass - Fail` checks specify a criterion that products must meet "
"for the check to pass."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bestået - Ikke bestået`-kontroller angiver et kriterium, som "
"produkter skal opfylde, for at kontrollen kan bestås."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Measure` checks prompt employees to record a measurement of the "
"product that must be within a :guilabel:`Tolerance` of a :guilabel:`Norm` "
"value for the check to pass. Optionally specify a :guilabel:`Device` that "
"should conduct the measurement."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mål`-kontroller beder medarbejdere om at registrere en måling af "
"produktet, der skal være inden for en :guilabel:`Tolerance` af en "
":guilabel:`Norm`-værdi for at kontrollen kan bestås. Angiv eventuelt en "
":guilabel:`Enhed`, der skal foretage målingen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:98
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Spreadsheet` checks require the employee processing the check to "
"fill out an interactive spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Regneark`-kontroller kræver, at medarbejderen, der behandler "
"kontrollen, udfylder et interaktivt regneark."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:100
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Worksheet` checks require the employee processing the check to "
"fill out an interactive worksheet."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arbejdsark`-kontroller kræver, at medarbejderen, der behandler "
"kontrollen, udfylder et interaktivt arbejdsark."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:104
msgid ""
"An *Instructions* check is the same as a step on a work order for an |MO|."
msgstr ""
"En *Instruktioner*-kontrol er det samme som et trin på en arbejdsordre for "
"en |MO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:106
msgid ""
"When a step is added to a work order, Odoo stores it in the **Quality** app "
"as a |QCP|. It is possible to manually create a |QCP| with the "
"*Instructions* check type, and even assign it to an operation other than "
"manufacturing, like receipts."
msgstr ""
"Når et trin tilføjes til en arbejdsordre, gemmer Odoo det i appen "
"**Kvalitet** som en |QCP|. Det er muligt manuelt at oprette en |QCP| med "
"kontroltypen *Instruktioner* og endda tildele den til en anden operation end "
"produktion, f.eks. modtagelser."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:110
msgid ""
"However, when creating a control point specifically for quality control "
"purposes, using a different check type is probably more effective."
msgstr ""
"Men når der oprettes et kontrolpunkt specifikt til kvalitetskontrolformål, "
"er det formentlig mere effektivt at bruge en anden kontrol-type."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:114
msgid ""
"When a |QCP| is created with the :guilabel:`Spreadsheet` check type, specify "
"a :guilabel:`Spreadsheet Template` and a :guilabel:`Success cell`."
msgstr ""
"Når en |QCP| oprettes med kontroltypen :guilabel:`Regneark`, angiv en "
":guilabel:`Regnearksskabelon` og en :guilabel:`Succescelle`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:117
msgid ""
"When a |QCP| is created with the :guilabel:`Worksheet` check type, specify "
"a :guilabel:`Template` and :guilabel:`Success Conditions`."
msgstr ""
"Når en |QCP| oprettes med kontroltypen :guilabel:`Arbejdsark`, angiv en "
":guilabel:`Skabelon` og :guilabel:`Succesbetingelser`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:120
msgid ""
"The selected template is duplicated for each quality check created by the |"
"QCP| and **must** be filled out to complete the quality check."
msgstr ""
"Den valgte skabelon duplikeres for hver kvalitetskontrol, der oprettes af "
"|QCP|, og **skal** udfyldes for at fuldføre kvalitetskontrollen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:123
msgid ""
"To create a new template, navigate to :menuselection:`Quality app --> "
"Configuration --> Quality Worksheet/Spreadsheet Templates`, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en ny skabelon skal du gå til :menuselection:`Kvalitet-app --"
"> Konfiguration --> Kvalitetsarbejdsark/Regnearksskabeloner` og klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:126
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Team` field, specify the quality team that is responsible "
"for managing the |QCP| and the quality checks it creates."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Team` angives det kvalitetsteam, der er ansvarligt for "
"at styre |QCP| og de kvalitetskontroller, den opretter."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:129
msgid ""
"In the *Instructions* tab at the bottom of the form, enter instructions for "
"how to complete the quality checks created by the |QCP|."
msgstr ""
"I fanen *Instruktioner* nederst på formularen indtastes instruktioner for, "
"hvordan kvalitetskontrollerne, der oprettes af |QCP|, skal fuldføres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:132
msgid ""
"In the *Worksheet* tab, add a PDF worksheet to accompany the |QCP| by "
"clicking the :guilabel:`Upload your file` button and selecting a file."
msgstr ""
"I fanen *Arbejdsark* tilføjes et PDF-arbejdsark til at ledsage |QCP| ved at "
"klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Upload din fil` og vælge en fil."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:135
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Type` field is set to :guilabel:`Register "
"Production`, :guilabel:`Pass - "
"Fail`, :guilabel:`Measure`, :guilabel:`Spreadsheet`, "
"or :guilabel:`Worksheet`, the *Message If Failure* tab appears. In this tab, "
"include instructions for what to do if the quality check fails. For example, "
"instruct the employee processing the quality check to create a :doc:`quality "
"alert <quality_alerts>`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis feltet :guilabel:`Type` er sat til :guilabel:`Registrer produktion`, "
":guilabel:`Bestået - Ikke bestået`, :guilabel:`Mål`, :guilabel:`Regneark` "
"eller :guilabel:`Arbejdsark`, vises fanen *Besked ved fejl*. I denne fane "
"inkluderes instruktioner for, hvad der skal gøres, hvis kvalitetskontrollen "
"fejler. Instruer f.eks. medarbejderen, der behandler kvalitetskontrollen, i "
"at oprette en :doc:`kvalitetsalarm <quality_alerts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:141
msgid ""
"Use the *Notes* tab to provide additional information about the |QCP|, like "
"the reason it was created. The information entered in this tab is **not** "
"shown to employees processing the quality checks created by the |QCP|."
msgstr ""
"Brug fanen *Noter* til at give yderligere oplysninger om |QCP|, f.eks. "
"årsagen til, at den blev oprettet. Oplysningerne i denne fane vises **ikke** "
"til medarbejdere, der behandler de kvalitetskontroller, der oprettes af "
"|QCP|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/quality/quality_management/quality_control_points.rst:None
msgid ""
"A QCP configured to create Pass - Fail checks for a work order operation."
msgstr ""
"En QCP konfigureret til at oprette bestået/fejlet-kontroller for en "
"arbejdsordrehandling."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs.rst:8
msgid "Repairs"
msgstr "Reparationer"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs.rst:10
msgid ""
"Odoo *Repairs* assists companies in creating and processing repairs for "
"damaged products returned by customers."
msgstr ""
"Odoo *Reparationer* hjælper virksomheder med at oprette og behandle "
"reparationer af beskadigede produkter returneret af kunder."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:3
msgid "Process repair orders"
msgstr "Behandle reparationsordrer"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:10
msgid ""
"Sometimes, products delivered to customers can break or be damaged in "
"transit, and need to be returned for a refund, delivery of a replacement "
"product, or repairs."
msgstr ""
"Nogle gange kan produkter leveret til kunder gå i stykker eller blive "
"beskadiget under transport og skal returneres for at få refunderet beløbet, "
"levering af et erstatningsprodukt eller reparationer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Odoo, repairs for products returned by customers can be tracked in the "
"**Repairs** app. Once repaired, products can be redelivered to the customer."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo kan reparationer af produkter returneret af kunder spores i "
"**Reparationer**-appen. Når de er repareret, kan produkter genleveres til "
"kunden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:16
msgid ""
"The return and repair process for damaged products typically follows the "
"below steps:"
msgstr ""
"Retur- og reparationsprocessen for beskadigede produkter følger typisk "
"nedenstående trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:18
msgid ""
":ref:`Process return order for damaged product <repairs/repair_orders/return-"
"order>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Behandle returordre for beskadiget produkt <repairs/repair_orders/"
"return-order>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:19
msgid ""
":ref:`Create repair order for returned product <repairs/repair_orders/"
"repair>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Oprette reparationsordre for returneret produkt <repairs/repair_orders/"
"repair>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:20
msgid ""
":ref:`Return repaired product to customer <repairs/repair_orders/return-"
"customer>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Returnere repareret produkt til kunden <repairs/repair_orders/return-"
"customer>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:25
msgid "Return order"
msgstr "Returordre"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:27
msgid ""
"Returns can be processed in Odoo via *reverse transfers*, created directly "
"from a sales order (SO) once products have been delivered to a customer."
msgstr ""
"Returneringer kan behandles i Odoo via *omvendte overførsler*, der oprettes "
"direkte fra en salgsordre, når produkter er blevet leveret til en kunde."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:30
msgid ""
"To create a return, navigate to the :menuselection:`Sales app`, and click "
"into an |SO| from which a product should be returned. Then, from the |SO| "
"form, click the :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button. Doing so opens the "
"delivery order (DO) form."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en returordre skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Salg-"
"appen` og klikke ind i en |SO|, hvorfra et produkt skal returneres. Klik "
"derefter fra |SO|-formularen på smart-knappen :guilabel:`Levering`. Dette "
"åbner leveringsordreformularen (DO)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:34
msgid ""
"From this form, click :guilabel:`Return`. This opens a :guilabel:`Reverse "
"Transfer` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Fra denne formular skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Retur`. Dette åbner et pop "
"op-vindue :guilabel:`Omvendt overførsel`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:None
msgid "Reverse transfer pop-up window on delivery order form."
msgstr "Pop op-vindue med omvendt overførsel på leveringsordreformular."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:39
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:196
msgid ""
"This pop-up lists the :guilabel:`Product` included in the order, "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` delivered to the customer, and the :guilabel:`Unit "
"of Measure` the product was in."
msgstr ""
"Dette pop op-vindue viser :guilabel:`Produktet` inkluderet i "
"ordren, :guilabel:`Antallet` leveret til kunden og :guilabel:`Måleenheden`, "
"som produktet var i."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:42
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:199
msgid ""
"Click the value in the :guilabel:`Quantity` field to change the quantity of "
"the product to be returned, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Klik på værdien i feltet :guilabel:`Antal` for at ændre antallet af "
"produktet, der skal returneres, hvis det er nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:45
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:202
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`🗑️ (trash)` icon at the far-right of the product line to "
"remove it from the return, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Klik på ikonet :guilabel:`🗑️ (papirkurv)` yderst til højre på produktlinjen "
"for at fjerne det fra returneringen, hvis det er nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:48
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Return` to confirm the return. This creates a "
"new receipt for the returned products."
msgstr ""
"Når du er klar, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Retur` for at bekræfte "
"returneringen. Dette opretter en ny kvittering for de returnerede produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:51
msgid ""
"Once the product has been returned to the warehouse, receipt of the return "
"can be registered in the database by clicking :guilabel:`Validate` from the "
"reverse transfer form."
msgstr ""
"Når produktet er returneret til lageret, kan modtagelsen af returneringen "
"registreres i databasen ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Valider` fra den "
"omvendte overførselsformular."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:55
msgid ""
"Once a reverse transfer for a return is validated, the value in "
"the :guilabel:`Delivered` column on the original |SO| updates to reflect the "
"difference between the original :guilabel:`Quantity` ordered, and "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` returned by the customer."
msgstr ""
"Når en omvendt overførsel for en returnering er valideret, opdateres værdien "
"i kolonnen :guilabel:`Leveret` på den oprindelige |SO| for at afspejle "
"forskellen mellem det oprindelige bestilte :guilabel:`Antal` og "
"det :guilabel:`Antal`, som kunden har returneret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:0
msgid "Delivered and Quantity columns on sales order after return."
msgstr "Kolonnerne Leveret og Antal på salgsordre efter returnering."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:65
msgid "Create repair order"
msgstr "Opret reparationsordre"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:67
msgid ""
"Once products have been returned, their repairs can be tracked by creating a "
"repair order (RO)."
msgstr ""
"Når produkter er blevet returneret, kan deres reparationer spores ved at "
"oprette en reparationsordre (RO)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:70
msgid "Repair form configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguration af reparationsformular"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:72
msgid ""
"To create a new |RO|, navigate to :menuselection:`Repairs app`, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. This opens a blank |RO| form."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en ny |RO|, naviger til :menuselection:`Reparationer-appen`, "
"og klik på :guilabel:`Ny`. Dette åbner en tom |RO|-formular."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:None
msgid "Repair order form in Odoo Repairs."
msgstr "Reparationsordreformular i Odoo Reparationer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:78
msgid ""
"On this form, begin by selecting a :guilabel:`Customer` to whom the order "
"should be invoiced and delivered."
msgstr ""
"På denne formular skal du begynde med at vælge en :guilabel:`Kunde`, som "
"ordren skal faktureres og leveres til."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:81
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Product to Repair` field, click the drop-down menu to "
"select the product that needs repair. If the product chosen is tracked by "
"lot or serial number, an additional :guilabel:`Lot/Serial` field appears for "
"the user to specify the lot or serial number of the repair product."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Produkt der skal repareres` skal du klikke på "
"rullemenuen for at vælge det produkt, der skal repareres. Hvis det valgte "
"produkt spores efter lot- eller serienummer, vises et ekstra "
"felt :guilabel:`Lot/Serienummer`, hvor brugeren kan angive lot- eller "
"serienummeret på reparationsproduktet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:86
msgid ""
"Next, tick the :guilabel:`Under Warranty` checkbox, if the product being "
"repaired is covered by a warranty. If ticked, the :guilabel:`Customer` is "
"not charged for all the parts used in the repair order."
msgstr ""
"Sæt derefter flueben i afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Under garanti`, hvis "
"det produkt, der repareres, er dækket af en garanti. Hvis afkrydset, "
"opkræves :guilabel:`Kunden` ikke for alle dele, der bruges i "
"reparationsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:90
msgid ""
"After specifying details about the customer's repair, fill in the following "
"fields:"
msgstr ""
"Efter at have angivet detaljer om kundens reparation skal du udfylde "
"følgende felter:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:92
msgid ":guilabel:`Scheduled Date`: Specific date to start the repair."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Planlagt dato`: Specifik dato for at starte reparationen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Responsible`: Specific user in the database responsible for the "
"repair."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ansvarlig`: Specifik bruger i databasen, der er ansvarlig for "
"reparationen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: Specific company this |RO| belongs to, if in a multi-"
"company environment. This field is automatically populated and non-"
"modifiable."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Virksomhed`: Specifik virksomhed, som denne |RO| tilhører, hvis i "
"et flerfirma-miljø. Dette felt udfyldes automatisk og kan ikke ændres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:96
msgid ":guilabel:`Tags`: Relevant tags to apply to this |RO|."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mærkater`: Relevante mærkater, der skal anvendes på denne |RO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:99
msgid "Parts tab"
msgstr "Fanen Dele"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:101
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Parts` tab allows users to specify parts to add, remove, or "
"recycle during the repair. To specify a part, click :guilabel:`Add a line`."
msgstr ""
"Fanen :guilabel:`Dele` giver brugerne mulighed for at angive dele, der skal "
"tilføjes, fjernes eller genanvendes under reparationen. For at angive en del "
"skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:104
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Type` column, click the box to reveal three options to "
"choose from:"
msgstr ""
"I kolonnen :guilabel:`Type` skal du klikke på feltet for at afsløre tre "
"valgmuligheder at vælge imellem:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:106
msgid ":guilabel:`Add`: Add this component for use during the repair."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tilføj`: Tilføj denne komponent til brug under reparationen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:107
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Remove`: Remove this component from the product being repaired."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fjern`: Fjern denne komponent fra det produkt, der repareres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:108
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Recycle`: Recycle this component during the repair, saving it for "
"later use in the warehouse."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Genanvend`: Genanvend denne komponent under reparationen og gem "
"den til senere brug på lageret."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:111
msgid "Next, configure information about the part in the remaining columns:"
msgstr "Konfigurer derefter oplysninger om delen i de resterende kolonner:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:113
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product`: Select which part should be added, removed, or recycled."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produkt`: Vælg hvilken del der skal tilføjes, fjernes eller "
"genanvendes."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:114
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Demand`: Specify the quantity of this part to be used in the "
"repair, if necessary."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Behov`: Angiv mængden af denne del, der skal bruges i "
"reparationen, hvis nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quantity`: Automatically updated with the number of parts "
"actually used. This field can be manually changed, if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Antal`: Opdateres automatisk med antallet af dele, der faktisk "
"bruges. Dette felt kan ændres manuelt, hvis det er nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:117
msgid ":guilabel:`Unit`: Select the |UoM| for the part."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Enhed`: Vælg |UoM| for delen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:120
msgid ""
"To add additional columns to the line, click the :icon:`oi-settings-"
"adjust` :guilabel:`(optional columns drop-down)` icon in the header row. "
"Select the desired options to add to the line."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje yderligere kolonner til linjen skal du klikke på "
"ikonet :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(rullemenuen for valgfrie "
"kolonner)` i overskriftsrækken. Vælg de ønskede indstillinger, der skal "
"tilføjes til linjen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:124
msgid "Repair Notes tab"
msgstr "fanen Reparationsnoter"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:126
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Repair Notes` tab to add internal notes about this "
"specific |RO| (e.g., anything the user performing the repair might need to "
"know)."
msgstr ""
"Klik på fanen :guilabel:`Reparationsnoter` for at tilføje interne noter om "
"denne specifikke |RO| (f.eks. alt, som brugeren, der udfører reparationen, "
"måtte have brug for at vide)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:130
msgid "Initiate repair"
msgstr "Igangsæt reparation"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:132
msgid ""
"Once all desired configurations have been made on the |RO| form, "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm Repair`. This moves the |RO| to "
"the :guilabel:`Confirmed` stage and reserves the necessary components needed "
"for the repair. A :guilabel:`Component Status` also appears on the |RO| "
"form, indicating whether the repair order is *Available* or *Not Available* "
"based on the availability of the parts."
msgstr ""
"Når alle ønskede konfigurationer er foretaget på |RO|-formularen, "
"klik :guilabel:`Bekræft reparation`. Dette flytter |RO| til "
"stadiet :guilabel:`Bekræftet` og reserverer de nødvendige komponenter, der "
"er nødvendige for reparationen. En :guilabel:`Komponentstatus` vises også på "
"|RO|-formularen, som angiver, om reparationsordren er *Tilgængelig* eller "
"*Ikke tilgængelig* baseret på delenes tilgængelighed."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:137
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Start Repair`. This moves the |RO| to "
"the :guilabel:`Under Repair` stage. If the |RO| should be cancelled instead, "
"click :guilabel:`Cancel Repair`."
msgstr ""
"Når du er klar, klik :guilabel:`Start reparation`. Dette flytter |RO| til "
"stadiet :guilabel:`Under reparation`. Hvis |RO| i stedet skal annulleres, "
"klik :guilabel:`Annuller reparation`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:140
msgid ""
"Once all products have been successfully repaired, the |RO| is completed. To "
"register this in the database, click :guilabel:`End Repair`."
msgstr ""
"Når alle produkter er blevet repareret med succes, er |RO| fuldført. For at "
"registrere dette i databasen, klik på :guilabel:`Afslut reparation`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:144
msgid ""
"If all parts added to the |RO| were not used, clicking :guilabel:`End "
"Repair` causes a :guilabel:`Confirmation` pop-up window to appear. The pop-"
"up window informs the user that there is a difference between the initial "
"demand and the actual quantity used for the repair order."
msgstr ""
"Hvis alle dele tilføjet til |RO| ikke blev brugt, får klik "
"på :guilabel:`Afslut reparation` et pop op-vindue :guilabel:`Bekræftelse` "
"til at vises. Pop op-vinduet informerer brugeren om, at der er forskel "
"mellem det oprindelige behov og den faktiske mængde, der blev brugt til "
"reparationsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:148
msgid "To validate, click :guilabel:`Ok`. Otherwise, click :guilabel:`Cancel`."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Ok` for at validere. Klik ellers :guilabel:`Annuller`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:150
msgid ""
"Ending the repair moves the |RO| to the :guilabel:`Repaired` stage. "
"A :guilabel:`Product Moves` smart button also appears above the form."
msgstr ""
"Afslutning af reparationen flytter |RO| til stadiet :guilabel:`Repareret`. "
"En smart-knap :guilabel:`Produktbevægelser` vises også over formularen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:153
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Product Moves` smart button to view the product's moves "
"history during and after the repair process."
msgstr ""
"Klik på smartknappen :guilabel:`Produktbevægelser` for at se produktets "
"flyttehistorik under og efter reparationsprocessen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:None
msgid "Moves history of product included in the repair order."
msgstr "Flyttehistorik for produkt inkluderet i reparationsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:162
msgid "Return product to customer"
msgstr "Returner produkt til kunde"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:164
msgid ""
"If the product is under warranty, it can be returned to the customer after "
"the repair."
msgstr ""
"Hvis produktet er under garanti, kan det returneres til kunden efter "
"reparationen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:166
msgid ""
"However, if the product is not under warranty, click :guilabel:`Create "
"Quotation`. This opens a new |SO| form, pre-populated with the parts used in "
"the |RO|, with the total cost of the repair calculated."
msgstr ""
"Men hvis produktet ikke er under garanti, klik :guilabel:`Opret tilbud`. "
"Dette åbner en ny |SO|-formular, forhåndsudfyldt med de dele, der blev brugt "
"i |RO|, med de samlede omkostninger ved reparationen beregnet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:None
msgid "Pre-populated new quotation for parts included in repair order."
msgstr "Forududfyldt nyt tilbud for dele inkluderet i reparationsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:173
msgid ""
"If this |SO| should be sent to the customer, click :guilabel:`Confirm`, and "
"proceed to invoice the customer for the repair."
msgstr ""
"Hvis denne |SO| skal sendes til kunden, klik på :guilabel:`Bekræft`, og "
"fortsæt med at fakturere kunden for reparationen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:177
msgid ""
"If the customer should be charged for a repair service, a service type "
"product can be created and added to the |SO| for a repaired product."
msgstr ""
"Hvis kunden skal opkræves for en reparationsservice, kan et produkt af "
"servicetypen oprettes og tilføjes til |SO| for et repareret produkt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:180
msgid ""
"To return the product to the customer, navigate to the :menuselection:`Sales "
"app`, and select the original |SO| from which the initial return was "
"processed. Then, click the :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button."
msgstr ""
"For at returnere produktet til kunden, naviger til :menuselection:`Salg-"
"appen`, og vælg den oprindelige |SO|, hvorfra den første returnering blev "
"behandlet. Klik derefter på smartknappen :guilabel:`Levering`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:184
msgid ""
"From the resulting list of operations, click the reverse transfer, indicated "
"by the :guilabel:`Source Document`, which should read `Return of WH/OUT/"
"XXXXX`."
msgstr ""
"Fra den resulterende liste over operationer, klik på den omvendte "
"overførsel, angivet ved :guilabel:`Kildedokument`, som skal læse `Return af "
"WH/OUT/XXXXX`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:187
msgid ""
"This opens the return form. At the top of this form, a :guilabel:`Repair "
"Orders` smart button now appears, linking this return to the completed |RO|."
msgstr ""
"Dette åbner returformularen. Øverst på denne formular vises nu en "
"smartknap :guilabel:`Reparationsordrer`, som forbinder denne returnering med "
"den fuldførte |RO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:190
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Return` at the top of the form. This opens "
"a :guilabel:`Reverse Transfer` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Returner` øverst på formularen. Dette åbner et pop-op-"
"vindue :guilabel:`Omvendt overførsel`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:205
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Return` to confirm the return. This creates a "
"new delivery for the returned products."
msgstr ""
"Når du er klar, klik på :guilabel:`Returner` for at bekræfte returneringen. "
"Dette opretter en ny levering for de returnerede produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:208
msgid ""
"When the delivery has been processed and the product has been returned to "
"the customer, click :guilabel:`Validate` to validate the delivery."
msgstr ""
"Når leveringen er blevet behandlet, og produktet er blevet returneret til "
"kunden, klik på :guilabel:`Valider` for at validere leveringen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:212
msgid ":doc:`../../sales/sales/products_prices/returns`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../sales/sales/products_prices/returns`"

