#~ msgstr ""
#~ ":guilabel:`Generate Return Label`: Marker afkrydsningsfeltet for "
#~ "automatisk at generere en returetiket ved validering af en leveringsordre."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In Odoo, *quality control points* (QCPs), are used to automatically "
#~ "create :doc:`quality checks <quality_checks>` at predetermined intervals. "
#~ "|QCPs| can be configured to create quality checks for specific operations "
#~ "(manufacturing, delivery, etc.), as well as specific products within "
#~ "those operations."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "I Odoo bruges *kvalitetskontrolpunkter* (QCPs) til automatisk at "
#~ "oprette :doc:`kvalitetskontroller <quality_checks>` med forudbestemte "
#~ "intervaller. |QCPs| kan konfigureres til at oprette kvalitetskontroller "
#~ "for specifikke operationer (produktion, levering osv.) samt specifikke "
#~ "produkter inden for disse operationer."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In the :guilabel:`Operations` field, select the operation(s) that should "
#~ "trigger the |QCP|. For example, selecting the :guilabel:`Manufacturing` "
#~ "option in the :guilabel:`Operations` field causes a quality check to be "
#~ "created for new manufacturing orders (MOs)."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "I feltet :guilabel:`Operationer` vælges den eller de operationer, der "
#~ "skal udløse |QCP|. For eksempel medfører valg af "
#~ "indstillingen :guilabel:`Produktion` i feltet :guilabel:`Operationer`, at "
#~ "der oprettes en kvalitetskontrol for nye produktionsordrer (MOs)."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When creating a new |QCP|, at least one operation must be listed in "
#~ "the :guilabel:`Operations` field. However, the :guilabel:`Products` "
#~ "and :guilabel:`Product Categories` fields can be left blank. If they are "
#~ "left blank, the |QCP| generates quality checks for every instance of the "
#~ "specified operation(s)."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ved oprettelse af et nyt |QCP| skal mindst én operation være angivet i "
#~ "feltet :guilabel:`Operationer`. Felterne :guilabel:`Produkter` "
#~ "og :guilabel:`Produktkategorier` kan dog stå tomme. Hvis de står tomme, "
#~ "genererer |QCP| kvalitetskontroller for hver forekomst af den eller de "
#~ "angivne operationer."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If the :guilabel:`Manufacturing` operation is selected in "
#~ "the :guilabel:`Operations` field, a new field appears below it, "
#~ "titled :guilabel:`Work Order Operation`. From this field, select a "
#~ "specific work order to generate quality checks for that operation, rather "
#~ "than the manufacturing operation, in general."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Hvis operationen :guilabel:`Produktion` vælges i "
#~ "feltet :guilabel:`Operationer`, vises et nyt felt nedenfor med "
#~ "titlen :guilabel:`Arbejdsordrehandling`. Fra dette felt vælges en "
#~ "specifik arbejdsordre for at generere kvalitetskontroller for den "
#~ "pågældende handling frem for produktionsoperationen generelt."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The :guilabel:`Control Per` field is set to one of three options that "
#~ "determine *when* a new quality check is created:"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Feltet :guilabel:`Kontrol pr.` er indstillet til en af tre muligheder, "
#~ "der bestemmer *hvornår* der oprettes en ny kvalitetskontrol:"

#~ msgid ""
#~ ":guilabel:`Operation`: One check is requested for the specified "
#~ "operation, as a whole."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ ":guilabel:`Operation`: Der anmodes om én kontrol for den angivne "
#~ "operation som helhed."

#~ msgid ""
#~ ":guilabel:`Quantity`: A check is requested for a certain percentage of "
#~ "items within the specified operation. This percentage is set by enabling "
#~ "the :guilabel:`Partial Transfer Test` checkbox, and then entering a "
#~ "numerical value in the :guilabel:`Percentage` field that appears below. "
#~ "If the checkbox is not enabled, one quality check is created for the full "
#~ "quantity."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ ":guilabel:`Antal`: Der anmodes om en kontrol for en bestemt procentdel af "
#~ "varerne inden for den angivne operation. Denne procentdel angives ved at "
#~ "aktivere afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Test af delvis overførsel` og "
#~ "derefter indtaste en numerisk værdi i feltet :guilabel:`Procent`, der "
#~ "vises nedenfor. Hvis afkrydsningsfeltet ikke er aktiveret, oprettes én "
#~ "kvalitetskontrol for hele antallet."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The :guilabel:`Control Frequency` field is set to one of three options "
#~ "that determine *how often* a new quality check is created:"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Feltet :guilabel:`Kontrolfrekvens` er indstillet til en af tre "
#~ "muligheder, der bestemmer *hvor ofte* der oprettes en ny kvalitetskontrol:"

#~ msgid ""
#~ ":guilabel:`Randomly`: A quality check is randomly requested for a certain "
#~ "percentage of operations, which can be specified in the :guilabel:`Every "
#~ "#% of Operations` field that appears below."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ ":guilabel:`Tilfældigt`: Der anmodes tilfældigt om en kvalitetskontrol for "
#~ "en bestemt procentdel af operationerne, som kan angives i "
#~ "feltet :guilabel:`Hver # % af operationerne`, der vises nedenfor."

#~ msgid ""
#~ ":guilabel:`Periodically`: A quality check is requested once every set "
#~ "period of time, which is specified by entering a numerical value in the "
#~ "field below, and choosing either :guilabel:`Days`, :guilabel:`Weeks`, "
#~ "or :guilabel:`Months` as the desired time interval."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ ":guilabel:`Periodisk`: En kvalitetskontrol anmodes om én gang for hver "
#~ "fastsat tidsperiode, som specificeres ved at indtaste en numerisk værdi i "
#~ "feltet nedenfor og vælge enten :guilabel:`Dage`, :guilabel:`Uger` "
#~ "eller :guilabel:`Måneder` som det ønskede tidsinterval."

#~ msgid ""
#~ ":guilabel:`Take a Picture` checks require a picture of the product be "
#~ "uploaded for later review by the assigned quality team."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ ":guilabel:`Tag et billede`-kontroller kræver, at der uploades et billede "
#~ "af produktet til senere gennemgang af det tildelte kvalitetsteam."

#~ msgid ""
#~ ":guilabel:`Measure` checks prompt employees to record a measurement of "
#~ "the product that must be within a tolerance of a norm value for the check "
#~ "to pass."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ ":guilabel:`Mål`-kontroller beder medarbejdere om at registrere en måling "
#~ "af produktet, som skal være inden for en tolerance af en normværdi, for "
#~ "at kontrollen kan bestås."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "An *Instructions* check is the same as a step on a work order for an MO."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "En *Instruktioner*-kontrol er det samme som et trin på en arbejdsordre "
#~ "for en produktionsordre."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When a step is added to a work order, Odoo stores it in the Quality app "
#~ "as a |QCP|. It is possible to manually create a |QCP| with the "
#~ "*Instructions* check type, and even assign it to an operation other than "
#~ "manufacturing, like receipts."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Når et trin tilføjes til en arbejdsordre, gemmer Odoo det i Kvalitet-"
#~ "appen som et |QCP|. Det er muligt manuelt at oprette et |QCP| med kontrol-"
#~ "typen *Instruktioner* og endda tildele det til en anden operation end "
#~ "produktion, som f.eks. modtagelser."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When creating a |QCP| with the :guilabel:`Worksheet` "
#~ "or :guilabel:`Spreadsheet` check types, it is necessary to specify a "
#~ "*Quality Worksheet Template* or *Quality Spreadsheet Template* in "
#~ "the :guilabel:`Template` field that appears below the :guilabel:`Type` "
#~ "field."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Når der oprettes et |QCP| med kontrol-typerne :guilabel:`Arbejdsark` "
#~ "eller :guilabel:`Regneark`, er det nødvendigt at angive en "
#~ "*kvalitetsarbejdsarksskabelon* eller *kvalitetsregnearksskabelon* i "
#~ "feltet :guilabel:`Skabelon`, som vises under feltet :guilabel:`Type`."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The selected template is duplicated for each quality check created by the "
#~ "|QCP|, and **must** be filled out to complete the quality check."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Den valgte skabelon duplikeres for hver kvalitetskontrol oprettet af |"
#~ "QCP|, og **skal** udfyldes for at fuldføre kvalitetskontrollen."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In the :guilabel:`Team` field, specify the quality team that is "
#~ "responsible for managing the |QCP|, and the quality checks it creates. If "
#~ "a specific quality team member is responsible for the |QCP|, select them "
#~ "in the :guilabel:`Responsible` field."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "I feltet :guilabel:`Team` skal du angive det kvalitetsteam, der er "
#~ "ansvarligt for at styre |QCP| og de kvalitetskontroller, det opretter. "
#~ "Hvis et specifikt kvalitetsteammedlem er ansvarligt for |QCP|, skal du "
#~ "vælge vedkommende i feltet :guilabel:`Ansvarlig`."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The :guilabel:`Step Document` field has two options that specify the "
#~ "location of an instructional document detailing how to complete the "
#~ "quality checks created by the |QCP|."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Feltet :guilabel:`Trindokument` har to muligheder, der angiver "
#~ "placeringen af et instruktionsdokument, der beskriver, hvordan man "
#~ "udfører de kvalitetskontroller, der oprettes af |QCP|."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Select :guilabel:`Specific Page of Operation Worksheet` if the document "
#~ "is included with the instructional worksheet for the work order, then "
#~ "enter the page number in the :guilabel:`Worksheet Page` field that "
#~ "appears below."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Vælg :guilabel:`Specifik side af operationsarbejdsark`, hvis dokumentet "
#~ "er inkluderet i instruktionsarket for arbejdsordren, og indtast derefter "
#~ "sidenummeret i feltet :guilabel:`Arbejdsarksside`, som vises nedenfor."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Select :guilabel:`Custom` if the document should be included in "
#~ "the :guilabel:`Instructions` tab at the bottom of the |QCP|."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Vælg :guilabel:`Brugerdefineret`, hvis dokumentet skal inkluderes under "
#~ "fanen :guilabel:`Instruktioner` nederst på |QCP|."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In the :guilabel:`Instructions` tab at the bottom of the form, enter "
#~ "instructions for how to complete the quality checks created by the |QCP|."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Under fanen :guilabel:`Instruktioner` nederst på formularen skal du "
#~ "indtaste instruktioner for, hvordan man udfører de kvalitetskontroller, "
#~ "der oprettes af |QCP|."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If the :guilabel:`Custom` option was selected in the :guilabel:`Step "
#~ "Document` field above, a document can be attached in this tab. To do so, "
#~ "either select the :guilabel:`Upload your file` button to open the "
#~ "device's file manager, and then select a file, or add a link to a Google "
#~ "Slides document in the :guilabel:`Google Slide Link` field."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Hvis :guilabel:`Brugerdefineret` blev valgt i "
#~ "feltet :guilabel:`Trindokument` ovenfor, kan et dokument vedhæftes i "
#~ "denne fane. For at gøre dette skal du enten vælge "
#~ "knappen :guilabel:`Upload din fil` for at åbne enhedens filhåndtering og "
#~ "derefter vælge en fil, eller tilføje et link til et Google Slides-"
#~ "dokument i feltet :guilabel:`Google Slide-link`."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In the :guilabel:`Message If Failure` tab, include instructions for what "
#~ "to do if the quality check fails. For example, instruct the employee "
#~ "processing the quality check to create a :doc:`quality alert "
#~ "<quality_alerts>`."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "I fanen :guilabel:`Besked ved fejl` skal du inkludere instruktioner for, "
#~ "hvad der skal gøres, hvis kvalitetskontrollen fejler. For eksempel kan du "
#~ "instruere medarbejderen, der behandler kvalitetskontrollen, i at oprette "
#~ "en :doc:`kvalitetsalarm <quality_alerts>`."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The :guilabel:`Notes` tab is used to provide additional information about "
#~ "the |QCP|, like the reason it was created. The information entered in "
#~ "this tab is **not** shown to employees processing the quality checks "
#~ "created by the |QCP|."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Fanen :guilabel:`Noter` bruges til at give yderligere oplysninger om |"
#~ "QCP|, såsom årsagen til, at den blev oprettet. Oplysningerne i denne fane "
#~ "vises **ikke** til medarbejdere, der behandler kvalitetskontrollerne "
#~ "oprettet af |QCP|."

